NK020(wa)001:1: // si d+d+ha k+aa ma d+ha nu n+aa ma s+au tra
NK020(wa)001:2: s+y+aa ng+ga s+ya ma n+da l+aa n+aam s+aa d+ha na
NK020(wa)001:3: ma n+da la bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK020(wa)001:4: mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK020(wa)001:6: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:7: rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo zhes bya
NK020(wa)001:8: ba / bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:9: rang don mchog tu mi 'agyur bde chen brnyes //
NK020(wa)001:10: gzhan don thogs med 'gro sgrol phrin las can //
NK020(wa)001:11: zung 'jug dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' dang //
NK020(wa)001:12: dbyer med gter chen ja mar gus phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:13: mgon des gsung gi 'od kyis bdag blo yi //
NK020(wa)001:14: pad+ma rnam par bzhad las byung ba'i dngos //
NK020(wa)001:15: grub gnyis sbrang rtsi'i dga' ston 'dod 'jo'i skyes //
NK020(wa)001:16: ster ro skal bzang rkang drug tshogs rnams rol //
NK020(wa)001:17: 'dir mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas te //
NK020(wa)001:18: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dkyil 'khor gnyis gsungs
NK020(wa)001:19: pa'i nang nas yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams ston
NK020(wa)001:20: pa las / thog mar rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK020(wa)001:21: gi dkyil 'khor kun gyi'ang yan lag tu 'gro bas
NK020(wa)001:22: spyi la gces pa cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor ni
NK020(wa)001:23: pa las / / gang du bya ba'i gzhi der dri dang ba byung gis byugs la /
NK020(wa)001:25: stong pa'i ngang las 'bru lnga yongs su gyur pa las rigs lngar bskyed cing /
NK020(wa)001:27: de zhu ba las thig tshon du gyur par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:30: badz+ra tsi tra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:33: badz+ra sa ma ya s+au tra ma ti kra ma h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:34: zhes pas gnam sa'i thig spyi ltar btab la /
NK020(wa)001:35: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bang rim bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:36: dbus ling tshe dgu'i lte ba mthing ga /
NK020(wa)001:37: shar dkar ba sogs phyogs mdog dang /
NK020(wa)001:41: mgron dman pa'i khor yug nag po /
NK020(wa)001:43: 'od phreng ste tshon lhag ma spyi dang mthun zhing /
NK020(wa)001:44: lha gnas so sor ji ltar rigs pa'i mtshan ma 'god /
NK020(wa)001:45: de'i mdun du stegs bu gtsang ma'i steng snod dag
NK020(wa)001:46: par dkyil 'khor pa'i 'das gtor dkar zlum mtheb kyus
NK020(wa)001:47: bskor ba / cha dang po yon tan gyi mgron dang /
NK020(wa)001:48: cha gnyis pa 'byung po rnams la gtor zlum mtheb
NK020(wa)001:49: kyus bskor ba 'bru sman dri dang me tog rin
NK020(wa)001:50: chen dar sna tshogs pas brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:51: cha gnyis pa'i mdun du rigs drug dang yi dwags la bsil gtor /
NK020(wa)001:52: cha gsum pa bgegs la dmar gtor zlum po changs
NK020(wa)001:53: bu dang ting lo can sha chang la phug 'bru
NK020(wa)001:54: dang 'bras chan rnams kyis brgyan pa bsham /
NK020(wa)001:55: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor dang gtor ma'i mdun du'ang chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i nyer spyod lnga dang /
NK020(wa)001:56: rang gi mdun du dri chab 'thor yab dang bcas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:57: rdor dril sogs yo byad thams cad tshogs par bsham mo //
NK020(wa)001:59: khrus byas nas stan la 'dug ste /
NK020(wa)001:60: bla ma dang dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sangs
NK020(wa)001:61: rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba
NK020(wa)001:62: mdun gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs sad pa'i
NK020(wa)001:63: spyan sngar thal mo sbyar te /
NK020(wa)001:64: na mo gu ru bud+d+ha bo d+hi sa t+wa b+h+yah zhes pas phyag dang /
NK020(wa)001:65: badz+ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:68: bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK020(wa)001:69: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK020(wa)001:70: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:71: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK020(wa)001:72: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:73: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:74: dag pa'i mchod pa zhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:75: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK020(wa)001:76: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:77: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK020(wa)001:78: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK020(wa)001:79: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK020(wa)001:80: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK020(wa)001:81: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK020(wa)001:82: dag pa gsum gyis lus 'bul lo //
NK020(wa)001:83: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK020(wa)001:84: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK020(wa)001:85: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:86: sdug bsngal kun dang bral bar shog /
NK020(wa)001:87: bde dang rtag tu mi 'bral zhing //
NK020(wa)001:88: chos kun mnyam nyid rtogs par shog /
NK020(wa)001:89: ces lan gsum gyis rgyud dag par byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:91: tshogs zhing rnams rang gnas su gshegs par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)001:94: stong pa'i ngang las skad cig gis pad+ma dang zla
NK020(wa)001:95: ba'i gdan la h'u yig yongs su gyur pa las
NK020(wa)001:96: / rang nyid bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK020(wa)001:97: zhi zhing 'dzum la mtshan dpe'i lang tsho rab tu rgyas pa /
NK020(wa)001:98: phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar gtod de 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:99: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK020(wa)001:101: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis mdzes
NK020(wa)001:102: par brgyan cing zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis
NK020(wa)001:103: bzhugs pa / sku las dri ma med pa'i 'od zer dpag tu med par 'phro ba /
NK020(wa)001:107: h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas bsgoms pa dang 'dra
NK020(wa)001:108: ba'i ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs
NK020(wa)001:109: / badz+ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:111: dzahh+aum bam hohs rang la dgug gzhug bcing mnyes bya /
NK020(wa)001:112: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum gi 'od zer gyis dbang gi lha rigs lnga spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:113: mchod cing gsol ba btab pas /
NK020(wa)001:114: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)001:115: mi bskyod pas dbu rgyan par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:116: thugs kar zla ba la gnas pa'i h+aum yig sngags
NK020(wa)001:117: phreng gis bskor ba'i 'od kyis rang gzhan gyi sdig
NK020(wa)001:118: sgrib thams cad sbyangs par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:119: badz+ra sa t+wa +aah zhes ci nus bzla ste bdag bskyed de /
NK020(wa)001:120: 'di cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor sgos su sgrub pa'i tshe dgos kyi /
NK020(wa)001:121: 'og gi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dkyil 'khor ram /
NK020(wa)001:122: dkyil 'khor gzhan dang 'brel nas gtong kyang rung ste /
NK020(wa)001:123: de dang de'i tshe de dag gi bdag bskyed kyi go chod pas 'di zur du mi dgos so //
NK020(wa)001:124: de nas dri chab sgrub ste /
NK020(wa)001:125: rang gi thugs ka nas khro bo bgegs mthar byed
NK020(wa)001:126: ljang nag rdo rje rgya gram bsnams pa zhig phyungs
NK020(wa)001:127: te / dri chab kyi nang du pad nyi'i gdan la 'khor par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:128: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i rgyas dri chab la reg la /
NK020(wa)001:130: ces nyer gcig bzlas pas byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)001:131: bgegs mthar byed kyi rang bzhin gyi chu'i rdul phra rab tu gyur par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:132: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+he d+ha mra t+aa badz+ra sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:133: zhes gnas yo thams cad la gtor bas nyes skyon thams cad dag par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)001:137: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod du
NK020(wa)001:138: yig zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod rdzas rnams kun
NK020(wa)001:139: tu bzang mo'i mchod pa'i sprin phung ltar bzang zhing
NK020(wa)001:140: rgya che ba nam mkha'i mtha' klas par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:141: so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:152: dril bu rgyun chags su dkrol bzhin du rol mo'i sngags /
NK020(wa)001:156: sarba bud+d+ha she ta pra ts+aa li ni pra dz+ny+aa p+aa ra mi ta n+aa da sam b+ha be /
NK020(wa)001:157: sarba sa t+wa hri da ya san+to sha ni h+aum h+aum h+aum ho ho ho +aa kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:159: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:160: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra s+aa ra pra mrda ne /
NK020(wa)001:161: ta th+aa ga ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:166: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta badz+re /
NK020(wa)001:167: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+do pa sam kra ma na
NK020(wa)001:168: badz+ra sarba karma +aa wa ra na bi sho d+ha
NK020(wa)001:170: zhes pas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK020(wa)001:175: stong pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang nyi ma'i steng du
NK020(wa)001:176: h+aum las sna tshogs rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa
NK020(wa)001:178: rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla
NK020(wa)001:179: re 'bar ba me'i 'od zer kun tu 'phro bas
NK020(wa)001:180: yongs su bskor ba'i nang du 'jig rten pa'i khor
NK020(wa)001:181: yug nag po / de'i nang du sna tshogs pad+ma'i
NK020(wa)001:182: ge sar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyis khebs pa'i lte
NK020(wa)001:183: yug nag po / bar / sna tshogs rdo rje rwa bcu gnyis pa phyogs kyi mdog can /
NK020(wa)001:184: lte ba sngon po gru bzhi pa'i steng du b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:185: nang nas rim pa bzhin dkar mthing ser dmar ljang
NK020(wa)001:186: pa'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang ldan pa'i steng
NK020(wa)001:187: na rin po che'i pha gu ser po rin po
NK020(wa)001:188: che sna tshogs kyis bkra ba /
NK020(wa)001:189: de'i steng du bre phul gyi snam bu la gser
NK020(wa)001:190: gyi ska rags bzhi'i phyi ngos su ma ka ra'i
NK020(wa)001:191: kha nas rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba
NK020(wa)001:193: de'i phyi ngos su bya 'dab las dpyangs pa'i rin po che'i shar bu /
NK020(wa)001:194: steng ngos su mda' yab pad+ma 'dab ma phyed pa'i dbyibs can /
NK020(wa)001:195: rtsig pa'i 'gram nas 'dod yon gyi snam bu dmar
NK020(wa)001:196: pos bskor ba la gzungs ma rnams kyis mchod pa'i
NK020(wa)001:197: sprin spro ba / sgo logs kyi phyi zur bzhi
NK020(wa)001:198: nas bum pa la gnas pa'i ka ba bzhi bzhis
NK020(wa)001:199: btegs pa'i rta babs snam bu bzhi dang ldan pa'i
NK020(wa)001:200: rtse mor pad+ma la gnas pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK020(wa)001:201: gdugs kyis phub pa'i g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho
NK020(wa)001:203: nang ka ba brgyad kyis btegs pa'i rdo rje'i gdung zlum dang /
NK020(wa)001:204: gdung chen bzhis mdzes par phub pa'i dbus phyur bur
NK020(wa)001:205: gyur pa'i rtse mor rdo rje rin po che'i tog
NK020(wa)001:206: gis mdzes pa / gzhal yas khang gi nang lha
NK020(wa)001:207: snam ljang gu gru chad dang bcas pa'i lte ba
NK020(wa)001:213: dbus sngo ba dwangs shing sgrib pa med pa kun tu gsal ba /
NK020(wa)001:214: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan dang ba dan sogs rgyan sna
NK020(wa)001:215: tshogs kyis mdzes par brgyan pa'i dbus su rin po
NK020(wa)001:216: che'i khri pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan la h+aum yig
NK020(wa)001:217: dkar po / de las 'od zer 'phros 'phags pa mchod /
NK020(wa)001:219: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)001:220: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' sku ma dog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK020(wa)001:221: zhi zhing 'dzum la mtshan dpe'i lang tsho rab tu rgyas pa /
NK020(wa)001:222: phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar gtod de 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:223: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK020(wa)001:225: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis mdzes par brgyan cing /
NK020(wa)001:226: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:227: sku las dri ma med pa'i 'od zer dpag tu med pa 'phro ba /
NK020(wa)001:228: phyi rim ling tshe brgyad la gtso bo zhal nub
NK020(wa)001:229: tu phyogs pa'i mdun du sgeg mo dkar mo me
NK020(wa)001:230: long 'dzin pa / g.yas su phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:231: rgyab tu glu ma dmar mo pi wam 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:232: g.yon du gar ma ljang gu gar rgya mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:233: grwa bzhi'i nub byang du spos ma dkar ser spos khang 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:234: byang shar du me tog ma dmar ser me tog gi phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:235: shar lhor mar me ma dmar ljang mar me 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:236: lho nub tu dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung phor 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:237: nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:238: byang sgor dril bu ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:239: shar sgor lcags kyu ma dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:240: lho sgor zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:241: thams cad kyang zhi 'dzum sgeg pa'i nyams can /
NK020(wa)001:242: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:243: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:244: khyams kyi lha snam ljang gu la tshangs pa dang brgya byin la sogs te phyogs skyong ba bcu /
NK020(wa)001:245: yul 'khor srung la sogs te rgyal po chen po bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:246: dbang phyug dang khyab 'jug la sogs te lha chen po brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:247: nyi ma dang zla ba la sogs te gza' chen po brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:248: smin drug dang snar ma la sogs te rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:249: nor rgyas dang pad ma la sogs te klu chen po brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:250: gang ba bzang po dang nor bu bzang po la sogs pa gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon /
NK020(wa)001:251: 'jigs byed chen po dgu ste gtsang ris kyi mgon
NK020(wa)001:252: po bdun cu rtsa lnga sogs yon tan gyi mgron
NK020(wa)001:253: rnams rang rang gi rgyan dang phyag mtshan la sogs
NK020(wa)001:254: pa rnam 'phrul mtha' yas pas bcom ldan 'das la
NK020(wa)001:256: phyi'i khor yug la snying rje'i mgron du gyur pa 'gro ba rigs drug /
NK020(wa)001:258: skye gnas bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:259: khyad par lha klu gnod sbyin sogs 'byung po phal pa'i rigs su gyur pa thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:260: me'i phyi rol du bu lon lan chags kyi mgron rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:261: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:264: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas rang bzhin gyi gnas
NK020(wa)001:265: nas bsgoms pa dang 'dra ba'i ye shes kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:266: lo ma lus shing lus pa med pa thams cad
NK020(wa)001:267: mdun gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs
NK020(wa)001:268: par bsam zhing / rdor dril spos dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:270: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab //
NK020(wa)001:271: sems ni rgya chen mchog tu rab bskyed de //
NK020(wa)001:272: 'gro ba 'di dag ma lus sangs rgya rgyu //
NK020(wa)001:273: 'di na snod min sems can gang yang med //
NK020(wa)001:274: bzhengs shig bzhengs shig stobs bcu mnga' ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:275: dus la mi 'da' thugs rje'i dbang gis na //
NK020(wa)001:276: sems can don dgongs bcom ldan rdo rje sems //
NK020(wa)001:277: ma lus 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:278: de nas mchod yon sbreng bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:279: bcom ldan 'khor bcas byon pa legs //
NK020(wa)001:280: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK020(wa)001:281: bdag gi mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:282: 'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:283: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra sa t+wa sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:288: ye shes pa rnams dam tshig pa la dgug gzhug bcings pas mnyes bzhin du bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:289: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum gi 'od zer gyis dbang
NK020(wa)001:290: gi lha de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga 'khor bcas
NK020(wa)001:291: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:292: pany+tsa k+au la sa pa ri l+w+aa ra ar+g+ham sogs kyis mchod /
NK020(wa)001:293: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi shiny+tsa tu mam /
NK020(wa)001:295: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i dbang lha rnams kyis /
NK020(wa)001:296: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyi ni /
NK020(wa)001:298: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ye sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:299: zhes bum pa'i chus dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)001:301: chu'i lhag ma spyi bor 'khyil ba las mi bskyod pas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:303: dkyil 'khor pa rnams mchod pa'i sprin phung mtha' yas pas mchod par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:304: 'jig rten khams ni dpag med na //
NK020(wa)001:305: mchod yon ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:306: bdag gi gus par bshams pa 'di //
NK020(wa)001:307: sangs rgyas sras dang bcas la 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:308: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra sa t+wa sa pa
NK020(wa)001:309: ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha p+au dza me
NK020(wa)001:310: g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye
NK020(wa)001:311: h+aum / mchod yon gyi gnas su /
NK020(wa)001:325: shap+da rnams bcug nas rang rang gi phyag rgyas dbul zhing /
NK020(wa)001:326: mthar dril bu gsil ba dang bcas /
NK020(wa)001:327: badz+ra d+har+m+aa ra ni sogs rol mo'i sngags kyang sngar ltar brjod /
NK020(wa)001:331: gos zung rnams kyis kyang mchod de /
NK020(wa)001:332: khams gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:333: bu bzhin skyob pa'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK020(wa)001:334: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin sku //
NK020(wa)001:335: bla med mgon la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:336: rang bzhin chos sku dag pa'i klong //
NK020(wa)001:337: sna tshogs thabs mkhas thugs rje yis //
NK020(wa)001:338: rigs lnga ye shes lngar ston pa //
NK020(wa)001:339: rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:340: gzugs mdzes phreng ba dbyangs snyan gar //
NK020(wa)001:341: nyes spyod bzhi dang phyag rgya bzhis //
NK020(wa)001:342: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mdzad ma //
NK020(wa)001:343: lha mo bcu gnyis la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:344: 'jig rten skyong ba grags ldan pa //
NK020(wa)001:345: sde bo che la stobs po che //
NK020(wa)001:346: 'jigs byed lha klu gza' skar dang //
NK020(wa)001:347: phyogs skyong rgyal chen tshogs la bstod //
NK020(wa)001:348: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:349: zhes sogs kyis bstod par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:351: gtso bo'i thugs kar pad+ma dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:352: gyi dbus su h+aum yig dkar po dri ma med
NK020(wa)001:353: pa zla ba ltar gsal ba bzla bya'i sngags phreng
NK020(wa)001:354: gis bskor ba / de las byung ba'i 'od zer
NK020(wa)001:355: gyis bdag dang sems can thams cad la reg pas
NK020(wa)001:356: sdig sgrib dang sdug bsngal thams cad sbyangs par bsam
NK020(wa)001:357: gis bskor ba / zhing / badz+ra sa t+wa +aah
NK020(wa)001:358: zhes pa ci nus bzlas pa'i mthar thal mo sbyar
NK020(wa)001:359: gis bskor ba / zhing / te / bcom ldan
NK020(wa)001:360: 'das bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK020(wa)001:361: sems sdig sgrib nyes ltung gi 'ching ba las rnam
NK020(wa)001:362: par grol ba mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:364: de nas cha gsum gtong ba'i thog mar 'das gtor dbul bar bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:368: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las gtor gzhong rin po
NK020(wa)001:369: che'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du bcud
NK020(wa)001:370: yig zhu ba las byung ba'i gtor rdzas 'dod yon
NK020(wa)001:371: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa'i sprin phung
NK020(wa)001:372: mtha' yas pa spro bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:374: de nas gtor mgron spyan drang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:375: spos 'thul zhing mchod yon sbreng ba dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:377: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)001:378: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)001:379: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK020(wa)001:380: mchod pas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:381: ye shes phung po mkha' 'dra ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:382: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK020(wa)001:383: sprul pa kun gyi 'byung gnas gtso //
NK020(wa)001:384: rdo rje sems dpa' gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:385: dmigs pa kun las rab 'das shing //
NK020(wa)001:386: byin rlabs kun gyi gzhir gyur pa /
NK020(wa)001:387: rnal 'byor kun gyi dbang phyug che //
NK020(wa)001:388: sa gzhi lta bur gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:389: thugs rje chen po thabs mkhas pas //
NK020(wa)001:390: gdug pa 'dul phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:391: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK020(wa)001:392: sprul pa mang po'i tshogs bcas gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:393: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK020(wa)001:394: ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK020(wa)001:395: ma ya s+t+wam / zhes pas snyan gsan dbab //
NK020(wa)001:396: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK020(wa)001:397: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK020(wa)001:398: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nya gnas bskyod la //
NK020(wa)001:399: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes par bskyed //
NK020(wa)001:400: so so'i phyag rgya bca' zhing /
NK020(wa)001:401: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:403: badz+ra g+han+de hoh k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK020(wa)001:404: zhes pas dgug gzhug bcing mnyes brtan par byas la /
NK020(wa)001:405: a nut+ta ra p+au dza ut+ga te s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:406: zhes bla na med pa'i mchod pa nam mkha' 'phags
NK020(wa)001:407: shing khyab pa'i sprin spros pas dgyes par bsam zhing
NK020(wa)001:408: // rin chen 'tsher bas brgyan pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:410: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK020(wa)001:412: rim bzhin yangs par bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:413: pad+ma ka ma la ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:414: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sat+wa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:415: dzahh+aum bam hoh ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:416: zhes gdan phul ba la bzhugs su gsol te mchod yon dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:417: de nas dri la sogs pa'i mchod pa rnams so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas pas dbul te /
NK020(wa)001:418: nags tshal bcud ni yi gar 'ong //
NK020(wa)001:419: dri zhim rgyas pa lha yi rdzas //
NK020(wa)001:420: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:421: lha rdzas bzang po'i bdug spos 'di //
NK020(wa)001:422: bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK020(wa)001:423: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:424: badz+ra d+h+au pe p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:425: gtsang zhing gtsang mar skyes pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:426: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog 'di //
NK020(wa)001:429: badz+ra push+pe p+au dza me g+ha sa sdug bsngal 'joms shing bkra shis la //
NK020(wa)001:430: dge zhing mun sel mar me 'di //
NK020(wa)001:433: badz+ra +aa lo ke p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra /
NK020(wa)001:434: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:435: lha rdzas bzang po'i dri chab 'di //
NK020(wa)001:438: badz+ra gan+d+he p+au dza me g+ha sa mu sman rnams bcud dang yi gar 'ong //
NK020(wa)001:439: sngags kyi zhal zas bshos 'di dag /
NK020(wa)001:441: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:442: badz+ra nee wad+yap+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra /
NK020(wa)001:443: sgra dbyangs snyan zhing yid 'ong ldan //
NK020(wa)001:444: lha rdzas dam pa'i rol mo 'di //
NK020(wa)001:446: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:447: badz+ra shap+da p+au dza me g+ha sa dril bu rgyu chags su dkrol bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:451: sarba bud+d+ha she ta pra ts+aa li ni pra dz+ny+aa p+aa ra mi ta n+aa da sam b+ha be /
NK020(wa)001:452: sarba sa t+wa hri da ya san+to sha nih+aum h+aum h+aum ho ho ho +aa kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:455: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:456: na mo b+ha ga w+aa te badz+ra s+w+aa ra pra mrda ni /
NK020(wa)001:457: ta th+aa ga ta ya ar+ha te samya k+sam bud+d+ha ya /
NK020(wa)001:463: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta badz+re /
NK020(wa)001:464: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+do pa sam kra ma nabadz+ra
NK020(wa)001:465: sarba karma +aa wa ra na bi sho d+ha na
NK020(wa)001:466: badz+re s+w+aa h+aa / yid du 'ong ba'i mchod sprin dang /
NK020(wa)001:467: rol mo sil snyan sprin gyi tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:468: mchod 'os tshul dang mthun pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:469: nam mkha'i khams kun khyab gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:470: de nas yan lag bdun pa bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:471: ji snyed su dag phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na //
NK020(wa)001:472: dus gsum gshegs pa mi yi seng ge kun //
NK020(wa)001:473: bdag gis ma lus de dag thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:474: lus dang ngag yid dang bas phyag bagyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:475: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam stobs dag gis //
NK020(wa)001:476: rgyal ba thams cad yid kyi mngon sum du //
NK020(wa)001:477: zhing gi rdul snyed lus rab btud pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:478: rgyal ba kun la rab tu phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:479: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed sangs rgyas rnams //
NK020(wa)001:480: sangs rgyas sras kyi dbus na bzhugs pa dag /
NK020(wa)001:481: de ltar chos kyi dbyings rnams ma lus pa //
NK020(wa)001:482: thams cad rgyal ba dag gis gang bar mos //
NK020(wa)001:483: de dag basngagasa pa mi zad rgya mtsho rnams //
NK020(wa)001:484: dbyangs kyi yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgra kun gyis //
NK020(wa)001:485: rgyal ba kun gyi yon tan rab brjod cing //
NK020(wa)001:486: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad bdag gis bstod //
NK020(wa)001:487: me tog dam pa phreng ba dam pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:488: sil snyan rnams dang byug pa gdugs mchog dang //
NK020(wa)001:489: mar me mchog dang bdug spos dam pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:490: rgyal ba de dag la ni mchod par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:491: na bza' dam pa rnams dang dri mchog dang //
NK020(wa)001:492: phye ma'i phur ma ri rab mnyam pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:493: bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa'i mchog kun gyis //
NK020(wa)001:494: rgyal ba de dag la ni mchod par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:495: mchod pa gang rnams bla med rgya che ba //
NK020(wa)001:496: de dag rgyal ba thams cad la yang mos //
NK020(wa)001:497: bzang po spyod la dad pa'i stobs dag gis //
NK020(wa)001:498: rgyal ba kun la phyag 'tshal mchod par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:499: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dbang gis ni //
NK020(wa)001:500: lus dang ngag dang de bzhin yid kyis kyang //
NK020(wa)001:501: sdig pa bdag gis bgyis pa ci mchis pa //
NK020(wa)001:502: de dag thams cad bdag gis so sor bshags //
NK020(wa)001:503: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba kun dang sangs rgyas sras //
NK020(wa)001:504: rang rgyal rnams dang slob dang mi slob dang //
NK020(wa)001:505: 'gro ba kun gyi bsod nams gang la yang //
NK020(wa)001:506: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag yi rang //
NK020(wa)001:507: gang rnams phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten sgrol ma dag /
NK020(wa)001:508: byang chub rim bar sangs rgyas ma chags brnyes //
NK020(wa)001:509: mgon po de dag bdag gis thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:510: 'khor lo bla na med pa bskor bar bskul //
NK020(wa)001:511: mya ngan 'da' ston gang bzhed de dag la //
NK020(wa)001:512: 'gro ba kun la phan zhing bde ba'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:513: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed bzhugs par yang //
NK020(wa)001:514: bdag gis thal mo rab sbyar gsol bar bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:515: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod cing bshags pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:516: rjes su yi rang bskul zhing gsol ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:517: bdag gis thal mo rab sbyar gsol bar bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:518: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod cing bshags pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:519: rjes su yi rang bskul zhing gsol ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:520: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
NK020(wa)001:521: thams cad bdag gis byang chub phyir bsngo'o //
NK020(wa)001:523: dkyil 'khor pa la sogs te dkon mchog srid zhu'i
NK020(wa)001:524: mgron thams cad la gtor ma ye shes kyi bdud
NK020(wa)001:525: rtsi nam mkha' dang mnyam pa phul bas dgyes par
NK020(wa)001:526: bsam la // nam mkha' mdzod kyi rgya dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:527: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi sh+w+aa mu
NK020(wa)001:528: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK020(wa)001:529: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:530: zhes lan gsum gyis phul la /
NK020(wa)001:531: 'dod don gsol zhing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:532: lag tu spos dang me tog thogs la thal mo sbyar //
NK020(wa)001:533: mgo btud cing yid rtse gcig pas /
NK020(wa)001:534: mi mnyam mnyam pa'i lha khyod rtag tu bdag la ni //
NK020(wa)001:535: thugs rje'i spyan gyis gzigs shing rgyun du 'gro ba'i dpal //
NK020(wa)001:536: byang chub mchog gi spyod pa bsgrub par dam bcas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:537: bdag gi re ba'i 'bras bu 'di yang mchis par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:538: gti mug mun pa 'dra bas ldongs gyur na //
NK020(wa)001:539: byams mgon ci slad bdag la thugs mi brtse //
NK020(wa)001:540: khyod kyi mkhyen rab bskal pa'i me 'dra bas //
NK020(wa)001:541: sems kyi mun sel sgron me bdag la stsol //
NK020(wa)001:542: mgon po thugs rje che dang ldan gyur pas //
NK020(wa)001:543: sems can don la bskul ba mi 'tshal yang //
NK020(wa)001:544: sdug bsngal rang bzhin dbang du bdag gyur pas //
NK020(wa)001:545: skyob pa'i spyan sngar gdung bas gsol ba 'debs //
NK020(wa)001:546: gang zhig pha dang mas ni slob pa la //
NK020(wa)001:547: shin tu skyo ngal med pa de bzhin du //
NK020(wa)001:548: 'gro ba'i don brtson mdzad pa khyed lags kyis //
NK020(wa)001:549: tshe rabs kun tu bdag gi skyabs mdzod cig /
NK020(wa)001:551: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas mu med
NK020(wa)001:552: pa na dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs
NK020(wa)001:553: rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK020(wa)001:554: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod kyis mi
NK020(wa)001:555: langs pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su
NK020(wa)001:556: mchi'o // bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi zhal nas
NK020(wa)001:557: gsungs pa'i chos dkon mchog 'jig rten dang 'jig rten
NK020(wa)001:558: las 'das pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos
NK020(wa)001:559: bsam gyis mi khyab pa la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs
NK020(wa)001:560: mchi'o // su mchi'o // bde bar gshegs pa rnams
NK020(wa)001:561: kyi thugs kyi sras su gyur pa dge 'dun rnams
NK020(wa)001:562: la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK020(wa)001:563: dkon mchog rnams gdan 'dzom pa'i spyan sngar lha dang mi'i zhal zas /
NK020(wa)001:568: dngos su 'byor ba dang yid kyi sprul pa'i mchod
NK020(wa)001:569: pa'i sprin phung bsam gyis mi khyab pa phul bas
NK020(wa)001:570: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur cig
NK020(wa)001:571: / sems can 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas
NK020(wa)001:572: gzung 'dzin rang ga mar zhen pa'i dbang gis nyon
NK020(wa)001:573: mongs pa 'phel zhing rgyas pas 'khor ba dang ngan
NK020(wa)001:575: mtho ris dang thar pa'i sgrib par gyur pa ci
NK020(wa)001:576: mchis pa thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig
NK020(wa)001:577: / 'di ltar bgyis pa'i dge ba sems can thams cad dang thun mong du bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:578: de ltar bsngosa pas sems can thams cad kyis bla
NK020(wa)001:579: na med pa'i byang chub rin po che myur du
NK020(wa)001:581: gnas skabs su tshe ring ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:583: dpal dang 'byor pa rgyas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:584: dge ba sgrub pa la bar chad med pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:585: 'phrin las phun sum tshogs pa sgrub nus par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:586: sangs rgyas sku gsum brnyes pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK020(wa)001:587: chos nyid mi 'gyur bden pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK020(wa)001:588: dge 'dun mi phyed 'dun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)001:589: ji ltar bsngosa shing smon lam 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:591: de nas 'jig rten pa'i gtor ma cha gsum ni /
NK020(wa)001:593: zhes rang sngags kyis rdor sems lta bur bdag bskyed gang yin gyi lha de nyid gsal btab /
NK020(wa)001:595: h+r+aihpad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:596: a tsan+d+ra man+da la s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra ta ahzhesa brjod pas
NK020(wa)001:597: zla nyi brtsegs pa'i steng du bdag nyid rta mgrin
NK020(wa)001:599: sku mdog dmar po dkar sngo dmar ba'i zhal gsum pa /
NK020(wa)001:600: spyi bor rta mgo ljang khu rta skad 'tsher zhing rngog ma las me stag 'phro ba /
NK020(wa)001:601: phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis rdo rje dang lcags kyu /
NK020(wa)001:603: zhabs gnyis gyad chen po'i stabs kyis klu pho mo bardzisa pa /
NK020(wa)001:604: khro bo'i chas can khams gsum pa'i dbang phyug che
NK020(wa)001:605: btsan 'gran zla dang bral bar bsam la snyems pa
NK020(wa)001:606: brtan pos rang sngags cung zad bzlas rjes /
NK020(wa)001:607: lag pa thal sbyar las mdzub mo dang mathe'u chung bskum /
NK020(wa)001:608: mthe bong so sor sgreng ba'i rgya lte mgrin snying ga spyi bo bzhir bzhag pas bsrung ngo //
NK020(wa)001:609: de nas gtor ma cha gsum mchod pa dang bcas pa la dri chab 'thor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:610: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+ha d+harma t+aa badz+ra sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:612: cho ga gang dang 'brel ba de'i las bum yod na bum chu 'thor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:615: a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:618: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod du
NK020(wa)001:619: yig zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod rdzas rnams 'dod
NK020(wa)001:620: yon gyi phung po zad mi shes par bsam la
NK020(wa)001:622: gtor ma gsum po sbyang spel bsgyur thob kyi brtag pa bzhis spyir rlob ste /
NK020(wa)001:623: chos nyid rnam dag gi rgya thal mo khog stong snying gar bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:624: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+hahsarba d+ha r+m+aa swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho & ham /
NK020(wa)001:626: ma dag pa thams cad sbyangs nas stongs pa nyid du bsam /
NK020(wa)001:627: thal mo khong stong las sor rtse sprad de tshigs bcag pa nam mkha' mdzod kyi rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:628: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK020(wa)001:629: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ud+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK020(wa)001:630: mam ga ga na kh+aam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:632: mgron so so'i mos pa dang mthun pa'i yo byad zad mi shes par spel /
NK020(wa)001:633: mthe bong bsnol nas thal mo phyir 'gyed pa bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:634: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:636: thams cad kyang sdug bsngal zhi byed bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor bsgyur bar bsam /
NK020(wa)001:637: g.yas khu tshur las mdzub mo sgreng ba snying ga
NK020(wa)001:638: dang g.yon mchog sbyin brkyang ba shugs ldan 'od kyi
NK020(wa)001:639: rgya bcas la / na mah sarba ta th+aa ga
NK020(wa)001:640: ta a wa lo ki te sam+b+ha ra sam+b+ha ra
NK020(wa)001:641: rgya bcas la / h+aum / zhes pas /
NK020(wa)001:642: mgron rnams kyi spyod yul du 'dod pa'i longs spyod
NK020(wa)001:643: zad mi shes pa so sor thob par bsam ste
NK020(wa)001:644: / sngags rnams lan gsum la sogs pa brjod cing /
NK020(wa)001:645: bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs dag dang //
NK020(wa)001:646: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyin stobs dang //
NK020(wa)001:647: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)001:648: 'phags pa rnams la mchod pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:649: sems can rnams la phan gdags slad //
NK020(wa)001:650: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //
NK020(wa)001:651: de dag thams cad ci rigs par //
NK020(wa)001:652: thogs pa med par 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:654: de nas bye brag tu byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:655: lag pa g.yas rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:656: cha dang po la bstan te /
NK020(wa)001:659: gtor snod rin po che las grub pa rgya tshad med par bsam /
NK020(wa)001:662: bcud gtor rdzas thams cad ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK020(wa)001:663: rang bzhin rgya che rgyun mi chad pa nam mkha'
NK020(wa)001:665: de nas cha dang po gtsang gtor dbul ba'i phyir
NK020(wa)001:666: mgon po yon tan gyi mgron rnams la snyan gsan
NK020(wa)001:667: dbab pa ni / tshangs pa dang ni brgya byin dang //
NK020(wa)001:668: rgyal chen bzhi dang phyogs skyong bcu //
NK020(wa)001:669: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin dang //
NK020(wa)001:670: gza' dang rgyu skar la sogs pa //
NK020(wa)001:671: phyi yi mgon po thugs dam can //
NK020(wa)001:672: dam tshig dbang gis spyan 'dren na //
NK020(wa)001:673: gnas 'dir brtse bas gshegs par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:674: de nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:675: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:676: badz+ra ang+ku sha +aa kar+sha ya sarba /
NK020(wa)001:677: d+h+ri ta rash+ta ya gan+d+harba a d+hi pa ta ye
NK020(wa)001:678: h+aum dzah bi r+au d+ha k+aa ya kun+w+aan+d+he a d+hi
NK020(wa)001:679: pa ta ye h+aum dzah bi r+au p+aak+sha ya n+aa
NK020(wa)001:680: ga a d+hi pa ta ye h+aum dzah bee sh+ra
NK020(wa)001:681: wa n+aa ya yak+sha a d+hi pa ta ye h+aum
NK020(wa)001:682: dzah brah+ma ne h+aum dzah in+d+ra ya h+aum dzah ag+na
NK020(wa)001:683: ye h+aum dzah ya m+aa ya h+aum dzah nee tri
NK020(wa)001:684: t+ya ya h+aum dzah wa ru n+aa ya h+aum dzah
NK020(wa)001:685: w+aa ya we h+aum dzah ku be r+aa ya h+aum
NK020(wa)001:686: dzah +ai sha n+aa ye h+aum dzah pri thi w+ai
NK020(wa)001:687: a d+hi pa ta ye h+aum dzah ash+ta ma h+aa
NK020(wa)001:688: d+ae wa h+aum dzah an+ta ma h+aa gra ha h+aum
NK020(wa)001:689: dzah sarba nak+sha tra h+aum dzah ash+ta ma h+aa n+aa
NK020(wa)001:690: ga h+aum dzah na ba ma h+aa yak+sha se n+aa
NK020(wa)001:691: pa ti h+aum dzah zhes dang /
NK020(wa)001:693: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)001:694: tshur gshegs chos skyong mgon po rnams //
NK020(wa)001:695: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK020(wa)001:696: mchod pas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:697: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+h+aa ra
NK020(wa)001:698: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha n+aam ga ga
NK020(wa)001:699: kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:701: pad+ma ka ma la ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:702: zhes gdan phul ba la bzhugs par bsam zhing //
NK020(wa)001:703: de nas so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas te mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:704: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:705: lha rdzas bzang po'i bdug spos 'di //
NK020(wa)001:706: chos skyong mgon po rnams la 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:707: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:708: badz+ra d+h+au pe p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:709: de bzhin bdug spos kyi gnas su /
NK020(wa)001:720: shap+da rnams bcug ste dbul zhing /
NK020(wa)001:721: sngar ltar rol mo'i sngags dang /
NK020(wa)001:722: mchod sprin gyi gzungs kyang brjod //
NK020(wa)001:723: de nas bstod cing phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:724: ri rgyal lhun po'i phyogs bzhi yi //
NK020(wa)001:725: so so'i pho brang bkod legs na //
NK020(wa)001:726: zab cing rgya che gzigs pa po //
NK020(wa)001:728: spyan mi bzang dang rnam thos sras //
NK020(wa)001:729: btsun mo sras dang blon po dang //
NK020(wa)001:730: 'khor g.yog sde dpung bcas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:731: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:732: dbang po rdo rje 'chang ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:733: lha yi rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:734: shar phyogs gdon gyi tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:735: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:736: me ste bsreg bya za ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:737: drang srong rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:738: shar lho me lha'i tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:740: gshin rje be con 'chang ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:741: ma mo'i rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:742: lho phyogs gshin rje'i tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:744: bden dang bral ba legs ldan lha //
NK020(wa)001:745: srin po'i rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:746: lho nub srin po'i tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:748: zhags pa thogs pa chu yi lha //
NK020(wa)001:749: klu yi rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:750: nub phyogs chu lha'i tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:752: rlung ste srog kyang 'dzin pa'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:753: rig 'dzin rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:754: nub byang rlung lha'i tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:756: gnod sbyin lag na dbyug to thogs //
NK020(wa)001:757: nor srung rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:758: byang phyogs gnod sbyin tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:760: dbang dang ldan pa 'dren pa'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:761: 'byung po'i rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK020(wa)001:762: byang shar dbang ldan tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:764: steng gi tshangs pa chen po dang //
NK020(wa)001:765: nyi ma zla ba gza' chen po //
NK020(wa)001:766: gza' dang rgyu skar bcas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:768: 'og gi klu ste sa yi lha //
NK020(wa)001:769: sa 'dzin lag pa chen po dang //
NK020(wa)001:770: dam tshig shes pa'i tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:772: lha chen brgyad dang klu chen brgyad //
NK020(wa)001:773: gza' brgyad rgyu skar nyi shu brgyad //
NK020(wa)001:774: 'jigs byed dgu yi tshogs bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:775: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:776: mthu chen 'jig rten skyong ba'i gtso //
NK020(wa)001:777: gtsang ris dpal mgon 'khor bcas kyis //
NK020(wa)001:778: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK020(wa)001:779: bdag gi re ba sgrub par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:781: yon tan gyi mgron rnams la gtor ma ye shes
NK020(wa)001:782: kyi bdud rtsi rgya che rgyun mi chad par phul
NK020(wa)001:783: bas dgyes shing tshim par bsam ste /
NK020(wa)001:784: d+h+ri ta r+aash+t+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:785: bi r+au d+ha k+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:786: bi r+au p+aak+sha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:787: bee sh+ra wa n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:792: nee tri t+ya ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:793: wa ru n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:795: ku be r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:803: na mah sarba ta th+aa ga te sogs nam mkha'
NK020(wa)001:804: mdzod kyi sngags btags la rang rang gi phyag rgyas
NK020(wa)001:805: rgyal chen bzhi dang phyogs skyong bcu la dbul lo
NK020(wa)001:806: // de la rang rang gi phyag rgya ni /
NK020(wa)001:807: g.yas pa'i khu tshur gyi steng du g.yon pa'i khu tshur nang bstan sgreng ba ni yul 'khor srung /
NK020(wa)001:808: g.yas pa'i khu tshur las gung mdzub sgreng ba 'phags skyes po //
NK020(wa)001:809: rdo rje phyi bsdams las mdzub mo phyung ba mig mi bzang /
NK020(wa)001:810: rdo rje phyi bsdams las mathe'u chung sgreng ba rnam sras /
NK020(wa)001:811: mig steng du phyogs shing thal mo khong stong du sbyar ba ni tshangs pa /
NK020(wa)001:812: lag gnyis kyi mathe'u chung mthe bong gis mnan cing
NK020(wa)001:813: sor mo lhag ma gsum sgrengs te g.yon snying ga
NK020(wa)001:814: dang g.yas dkur bzhag pa ni dbang po //
NK020(wa)001:815: lag gnyis khu tshur las gung mo sgreng ba'i tshigs
NK020(wa)001:816: gsum par mdzub rtse sbyar ba g.yas snying ga dang
NK020(wa)001:817: g.yon dkur bzhag pa ni me lha /
NK020(wa)001:818: rdo rje nang bsdams las srin lag gnyis brkyang ba ni gshin rje /
NK020(wa)001:819: lag gnyis khu tshur las gung mdzub gnyis brkyang ba
NK020(wa)001:820: g.yas snying ga dang g.yon dkur bzhag pa ni srin
NK020(wa)001:821: po / khu tshur gnyis kyi mtheb mdzub zhags mig
NK020(wa)001:822: gi tshul du sbyar ba snying gar bzhag pa ni
NK020(wa)001:823: po / chu lha / sngar me lha'i phyag rgya
NK020(wa)001:824: ltar bcas pa las g.yon snying ga dang g.yas dkur
NK020(wa)001:826: rdo rje nang bsdams las mathe'u chung gshibs nas brkyang
NK020(wa)001:827: ba de srin lag brkyang zhing rtse sbyar ba'i nang
NK020(wa)001:828: du bcug pa ni gnod sbyin /
NK020(wa)001:829: rdo rje nang bsdams las gung mo gnyis brkyang ba'i
NK020(wa)001:830: sen mo la mdzub mo gnyis reg cing mthe bong
NK020(wa)001:831: gnyis so so'i phyogs kyi gung mo la sbyar ba
NK020(wa)001:832: ni dbang ldan / nyi ma dang zla ba gnyis ni tshangs pa dang 'dra'o //
NK020(wa)001:833: mig mthur du blta zhing lag gnyis thal mo khong
NK020(wa)001:834: stong du sbyar ba las mthe bong gnyis nang du
NK020(wa)001:835: bcug la thal mo'i rtse mo mthur du bstan pa
NK020(wa)001:838: lha min gsum gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK020(wa)001:839: lha chen brgyad la thal mo khong stong las gung mo gshibs la bsnol /
NK020(wa)001:840: mdzub mo bkug pa'i steng du mthe bong bzhag pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:841: de ba swam swam ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:843: klu chen brgyad la lag gnyis kyis thal mo phyir
NK020(wa)001:844: bstan bkan pa gdegs ka ltar bzung ba'i rgya dang
NK020(wa)001:845: / re re na ti na n+aa ga li ri
NK020(wa)001:846: phu ta ta ri tsi ye swa h+aa'i sngags dang
NK020(wa)001:847: / rgyas dbul / gza' chen brgyad la lag gnyis
NK020(wa)001:848: gcig tu sbyar zhing mthe bong gnyis gshibs te sgreng
NK020(wa)001:849: / rgyas dbul / ba'i rgya dang / gra he
NK020(wa)001:850: tsa ri ya pra ba dam dzo ti ma ra
NK020(wa)001:851: ye s+w+aa h+aa'i sngags kyis dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:852: rgyu skar nyer brgyad la gaza'i phyag rgya de nyid
NK020(wa)001:853: las gung mo dang mthe bong gnyis ldog ste sbyar
NK020(wa)001:854: ba dang / nak+sha tra da ni rat+na da ni ye s+w+aa h+aa'i sngags kyis dbul //
NK020(wa)001:855: 'jigs byed dgu la lag g.yon pa'i thal mo lte
NK020(wa)001:856: ba'i phyogs su bkan te bzhag pa'i mdzub mo bkug
NK020(wa)001:857: cing g.yas pa'i gung mo sgreng bas de la phyogs
NK020(wa)001:859: yak+she pra r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa'i sngags kyi dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:860: de ltar lha klu la sogs kyi sngags mthar yang nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags btags la /
NK020(wa)001:861: thams cad la lan gsum la sogs pas phul la /
NK020(wa)001:862: 'dod don gsol zhing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:863: tshad ma mchis pa'i mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma 'bul zhing bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:864: yon tan gyi mgron tshangs pa dang brgya byin /
NK020(wa)001:865: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:870: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:872: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon pany+tsi ka dang /
NK020(wa)001:873: btsun mo dpal ldan ha ri ka dang /
NK020(wa)001:874: sras 'phrog ma'i bu lnga brgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:875: rdo rje rigs kyi srung ma thugs dam can gtsang
NK020(wa)001:876: mar gnas pa 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi pho
NK020(wa)001:877: brang du / yid bzhin gyi nor bu /
NK020(wa)001:882: cang shes kyi rta la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon
NK020(wa)001:883: tan ma tshang ba med pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK020(wa)001:884: pa'i mchod rdzas phun sum tshogs pa 'byung bar gyur
NK020(wa)001:885: cig / de ltar byung ba thugs brtse bas dgongs te byin gyis brlabs nas bzhes su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:888: de ltar phul bas bdag cag rnams kyi mchod pa'i yo byad dman pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:889: rgyu rkyen ma tshogs pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:890: brjod pa ma dag pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:891: ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:892: spyod lam bag med pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:893: le lo dang snyoms las su gyur pa ci mchis
NK020(wa)001:894: pa thams cad srung ma dam tshig can khyed rnams
NK020(wa)001:895: kyi spyan sngar mthol zhing bshag so //
NK020(wa)001:896: de ltar mthol zhing bshags pas bdag cag dpon slob
NK020(wa)001:897: yon bdag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi sngon gyi
NK020(wa)001:899: 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur kyang rung /
NK020(wa)001:900: 'jig rten 'dir yang nad mang ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:902: sems kyi sdug bsngal thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:904: gnod pa'i bgegs la sogs pa bsam pa ngan zhing sbyor ba rtsub par byed pa thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:907: ltas ngan pa thams cad phyir bzlog cing zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:908: gzhan yang 'byung po mi dang mi ma yin pa /
NK020(wa)001:909: sdang ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:910: gdug pa'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:911: drag shul gyi sems dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:912: de dag thams cad bzlog cing gdul ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:913: zhi zhing bsgyur bar mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:914: gal te zhi bas gdul du ma 'tshal na /
NK020(wa)001:915: gang la gang 'tshams pa'i chad pas bcad pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:917: bsdigs shing spa bkong bar mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:918: srung ma dam tshig dang mthu stobs can khyed rnams kyi mnga' 'og tu ma 'dus pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:919: sde rigs su gtogs pa gang yang ma mchis pas /
NK020(wa)001:920: de dag thams cad zhi ba dang dul bar mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:921: mdor na nyes pa'i skyon thams cad byang zhing dag pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:922: legs pa'i yon tan thams cad 'phel zhing rgyas par mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:923: zhes gsol te gtsang gtor ro //
NK020(wa)001:924: de nas cha gnyis pa spyi gtor dbul ba'i phyir brtag pa bzhi'i byin rlabs sngar song nas /
NK020(wa)001:925: 'dir lag g.yas rtse gsum gyi rgya cha bar pa la gtad de /
NK020(wa)001:928: sarba sid+d+hi h+aum gis bcud sngar ltar rlob cing /
NK020(wa)001:929: h+r+aih pad+man+ta krita sogs kyis nga rgyal gsal btab la /
NK020(wa)001:930: snying rje'i mgron rnams 'gugs pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:931: lha dang lha min gnod sbyin lto 'phye grul /
NK020(wa)001:932: nam mkha' lnging dang 'dab bzang lus srul po /
NK020(wa)001:933: dri za srin po gdon gyi rigs rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:934: gang dag sa la gnas pa'i rdzu 'phrul can /
NK020(wa)001:935: bu smad bcas shing g.yog 'khor bcas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:936: bdag gi pus mo sa la btsugs nas ni //
NK020(wa)001:937: thal mo sbyar nas khyod la gsol 'debs kyis //
NK020(wa)001:938: gsan nas phan gdags slad du 'dir gshegs shig /
NK020(wa)001:939: srid rtse man chad mnar med yan chad du //
NK020(wa)001:940: skye ba rnam bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams //
NK020(wa)001:941: gtad pa med pa'i mgron du spyan 'dren gyis //
NK020(wa)001:942: dga' dang gus pa'i sems kyis 'dir gshegs shig /
NK020(wa)001:943: e h+ye hi lo ka k+aa ra ya /
NK020(wa)001:954: a ma nu sh+ya sa pa ri w+aa ra sa ma ya /
NK020(wa)001:955: a n+ri su tri pre du dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa bkug la /
NK020(wa)001:956: de ba ga ne b+h+yah n+aa ga ga ne b+h+yah
NK020(wa)001:957: yak+sha ga ne b+h+yah rak+sha sa ga ne b+h+yah gan+d+ha
NK020(wa)001:958: rba ga ne b+h+yah a su ra ga ne b+h+yah
NK020(wa)001:959: ga ru da ga ne b+h+yah kan+ni ra ga ne
NK020(wa)001:960: b+h+yah ma ho r+aa ga ga ne b+h+yah ma nu
NK020(wa)001:961: sh+ye ga ne b+h+yah a ma nu sh+ya ga ne
NK020(wa)001:967: shap+da p+au dza me g+ha sogs kyis mchod pa lnga dang /
NK020(wa)001:969: de wa ga ne b+h+yah sogs kyis mthar /
NK020(wa)001:970: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs btags pa' sngags lan gsum dang /
NK020(wa)001:971: lag g.yas mchog sbyin 'degs rgya dang g.yon khu tshur
NK020(wa)001:972: bcang pa las mdzub mo sgreng ba gtor ma'i phyogs
NK020(wa)001:973: su gtad pa'i phyag rgyas gtor ma phul bas /
NK020(wa)001:974: snying rje'i mgron rnams kyi spyod yul du rang rang
NK020(wa)001:975: gi mos pa dang mthun pa'i yo byad dpag tu
NK020(wa)001:976: med pa thob pas tshim par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:977: bsngo zhing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:979: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma bar pa 'di 'bul zhing
NK020(wa)001:980: bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni mtho srid pa'i
NK020(wa)001:982: dma' na rag dmyal khams yan chad du rgyu zhing gnas pa /
NK020(wa)001:985: skye gnas rnam pa bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can snying
NK020(wa)001:986: rje'i mgron du gyur pa thams cad la 'bul lo
NK020(wa)001:990: de ltar bsngosa pas rigs drug so so'i sdug bsngal
NK020(wa)001:991: las grol nas myur du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK020(wa)001:993: gzhan yang long ba rnams kyis gzugs mthong ba gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:994: 'on pa rnams kyi rna bas sgra thos par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:995: dig pa rnams kyis smra shes par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:996: zha bo rnams bde bar 'gro nus par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:997: gcer bu rnams kyis gos rnyed par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:998: dbul po rnams kyis nor rnyed par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:999: ltogs pa rnams kyis bza' btung rnyed par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1000: 'jigs pa rnams kyis skyabs rnyed par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1001: nad pa rnams kyi nad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1002: sbyin pa dam pa sems kyi rgyan du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1003: sems kyi yo byad du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1004: don gyi mchog tu gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1005: 'di ltar mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma 'di la brten
NK020(wa)001:1006: nas gnas skabs su'ang bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod
NK020(wa)001:1007: 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi nad dang gnod pa
NK020(wa)001:1008: zhi zhing tshe dang bsod nams 'phel ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:1009: bdag sogs sems can thams cad kyi sgrib gnyis byang /
NK020(wa)001:1010: tshogs rnam pa gnyis rdzogs nas bla na med pa'i
NK020(wa)001:1011: byang chub rin po che myur du thob par gyur
NK020(wa)001:1012: cig / 'byung po gang dag ri rab steng gnas dang //
NK020(wa)001:1013: dga' ba'i tshal dang lha yi gnas rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:1014: shar nub ri dang nyi zla'i khyim rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:1015: ri bo kun la gang dag gnas pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1016: rin chen gling na lhag par gang gnas dang //
NK020(wa)001:1017: chu bo kun dang chu yi mdo rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:1018: mtsho dang rdzing bu lteng ka chu ngogs dang //
NK020(wa)001:1019: g.ya' chu bsil ma can na gang gnas dang //
NK020(wa)001:1020: grong dang phyugs lhas grong khyer stongs pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1021: khang stong dag dang lha yi khang pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1022: gtsug lag khang dang mchod rten gnas rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:1023: dka' thub gnas dang glang chen bres rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:1024: rgyal po'i dkon khang dag na gnas pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1025: lam srang sum mdo dang ni bzhi mdo dang //
NK020(wa)001:1026: gang dag lam po che dang shing gcig drung //
NK020(wa)001:1027: dur khrod chen po nags tshal chen po dang //
NK020(wa)001:1028: seng ge dred dang gcan gzan gnas rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:1029: 'brog chen 'jigs su rung ba gang gnas dang //
NK020(wa)001:1030: gang dag gling mchod dag na gnas pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1031: lhun po dur khrod dag na gnas pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:1032: rab tu dgyes shing mgu bar gyur nas su //
NK020(wa)001:1033: phreng ba dri dang byug pa me tog dang //
NK020(wa)001:1034: bstod dang gtor ma mar me gus 'bul na //
NK020(wa)001:1035: 'di dag gsol zhing legs par bsnams nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:1036: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:1037: bdag gi bsod nams mthu yis ni //
NK020(wa)001:1038: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1039: kun kyang gnod pa rnams dang bral //
NK020(wa)001:1040: sgrib pa med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK020(wa)001:1041: ma thogs par ni 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:1042: byol song gcig la gcig za ba //
NK020(wa)001:1043: gnod pa de dag yongs mi 'byung //
NK020(wa)001:1044: yi dwags rnams la zas dang skom //
NK020(wa)001:1045: thogs pa med par 'byung bar shog /
NK020(wa)001:1046: sems can dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gang //
NK020(wa)001:1047: mi zad rnam pa sna tshogs dag /
NK020(wa)001:1048: bsod nams 'di yi byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)001:1049: de dag myur du zhi gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1051: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK020(wa)001:1053: dag pa'i bsam pa rdzogs gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1054: ces las bcol zhing bsngosa nas /
NK020(wa)001:1055: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung //
NK020(wa)001:1057: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:1058: zhes pa la sogs pas chos kyi sbyin pa'ang byin pa'i mthar /
NK020(wa)001:1059: khro bo chen po'i bka' yin ni //
NK020(wa)001:1060: rang rang gnas su bde bar dengs //
NK020(wa)001:1061: badz+ra muh ya hi gats+tshasa rang gnas su btang ngo //
NK020(wa)001:1062: de nas cha gsum pa bgegs gtor ster pa'i phyir /
NK020(wa)001:1063: brtags pa bzhis spyir rlobs pa rngar song nas /
NK020(wa)001:1064: 'dir rtse gsum gyi rgya gtor ma tha ma la gtad de /
NK020(wa)001:1067: zhes pas snod bcud lngar ltar rlob cing /
NK020(wa)001:1069: bdag nyid rta mgrin sku che la bzod par dka'
NK020(wa)001:1070: ba'i gzi byin can khro tshogs 'bar ba'i sprin spro
NK020(wa)001:1071: ba'i nga rgyal gsal btab ste bstod pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1072: h+r+aih rgyal ba kun gyi bdag po chos kyi sku //
NK020(wa)001:1073: chos rje 'od dpag med pa rdo rje chos //
NK020(wa)001:1074: spyan ras gzigs sprul h+r+aihls rngams chen sku //
NK020(wa)001:1075: rta mgrin rta skad bzhad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1076: dbang chen dbang 'dul dbang gi rgyal po ste //
NK020(wa)001:1077: dbang gi mdog dmar bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NK020(wa)001:1078: dbang chen rngams brjid nyi ma 'bul gyi gzi //
NK020(wa)001:1079: dbang mdzad dbang gi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1080: chos nyid bdud rtsi mchog gi dbang bskur zhing //
NK020(wa)001:1081: dug gsum gtan nas 'thung mdzad dpal 'bar ba //
NK020(wa)001:1082: gdug pa'i klu rnams brjid pa'i zhabs kyis gnon //
NK020(wa)001:1083: dug chen bdug rtsir bsgyur la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1084: rig pa'i rgya po khro bo kun gyi rje //
NK020(wa)001:1085: byams chen rab khros khro rgyal kun gyis bskor //
NK020(wa)001:1086: stong nyid dbyings las ma g.yos mkha' dkyil nas //
NK020(wa)001:1087: 'jigs gzugs nyi zla 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:1088: rang nyid rta'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas /
NK020(wa)001:1089: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing
NK020(wa)001:1090: ci yang ma yin pa la ji ltar bsam pa
NK020(wa)001:1092: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyis ye shes
NK020(wa)001:1093: thugs su chud cing sems can gyi don la dgongs
NK020(wa)001:1094: pa skad cig kyang mi g.yel ba'i bden pa dang
NK020(wa)001:1095: / dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa
NK020(wa)001:1096: bskang zhing sems can gyi mgon skyabs mdzad par zhal
NK020(wa)001:1097: gyi bzhes pa'i bden pa'i byin rlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:1098: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:1099: dkon mchog gsum dag bla ma dam pa'i bka' bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)001:1100: gdug cing sdang ba'i sems dang ldan pa'i bgegs kyi rigs thams cad skad cig la 'dir 'dus shig /
NK020(wa)001:1102: phata phata badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala ha la ha la /
NK020(wa)001:1104: sprul pa'i pho nya mkha' khyab tu spros pa rnams
NK020(wa)001:1105: kyis bgegs rnams rang dbang med par bkug par bsam
NK020(wa)001:1106: zhing / lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:1107: trang ka ri trang ka ri /
NK020(wa)001:1109: ra ra sra sra tri tri /
NK020(wa)001:1111: tri yam dzah badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:1113: badz+ra g+han+de hoh zhes pas bkug la /
NK020(wa)001:1114: trang ka ri trang ka ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1115: mi tsi mi tsi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1116: gum hing gum hing s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1117: a narta ri k+sha ra tsa nam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1118: bo pu ta ma nam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1119: ba ta la ba sa nam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1122: sarba big+h+n+aana grih+ne dam ar+g+ham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1126: sarba big+h+n+aam gyi bar sngar ltar gyis mthar /
NK020(wa)001:1127: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK020(wa)001:1128: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra ne i
NK020(wa)001:1129: mam ga ga na kham gri h+ne dam ba lim
NK020(wa)001:1130: ta s+w+aa h+aa / zhes pa'i sngags btags pa lan gsum dang /
NK020(wa)001:1131: lag g.yon khu tshur gyen bstan gyi mdzub mo sgreng ba gtor mar gtad //
NK020(wa)001:1132: g.yas pa sngags tshan so so'i mthar se gol gtogs pa'i rgyas gtor ma phul bas /
NK020(wa)001:1133: gnod cing 'tshe ba'i bgegs rnams kyi spyod yul du
NK020(wa)001:1134: rang rang gi mos pa dang mthun pa'i yo byad
NK020(wa)001:1135: zad mi shes pa thob pas so so'i rgyud tshim
NK020(wa)001:1136: nas bu lon dang lan chags sha 'khon thams cad
NK020(wa)001:1137: byang ste phan tshun byams pa la gnas par bsam
NK020(wa)001:1138: la / bsngo zhing smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1140: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma tha ma 'di sbyin zhing
NK020(wa)001:1141: bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni bdag cag dpon
NK020(wa)001:1142: slob yon mchod 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi tshe
NK020(wa)001:1143: rabs thog ma med pa nas da lta yan chad
NK020(wa)001:1144: kyi lan chags dang bu lon gyi mgron du gyur
NK020(wa)001:1145: pa bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu sogs gdon bgegs
NK020(wa)001:1146: kyi rigs thams cad la lus dang srog gi glud
NK020(wa)001:1147: dang longs spyod kyi skyin du 'bul lo //
NK020(wa)001:1150: de ltar phul bas bsad pas tshe thung ba /
NK020(wa)001:1152: 'phrog pas nor dbul ba'i lan chags thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1153: bu lon thams cad khyer bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1154: 'khon rtsod thams cad byang bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1155: bgegs kyi bar chad thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1156: sngar gyi gnod pa 'phro bsdus la /
NK020(wa)001:1157: phyin chad mi byed pa'i dam bca' brtan po khas longs shig /
NK020(wa)001:1159: dri chab 'thor bzhin du dam bsgrag ste /
NK020(wa)001:1160: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK020(wa)001:1161: dam tshig nyams na bsreg par byed //
NK020(wa)001:1162: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub mchog /
NK020(wa)001:1164: ci ste dam tshig las 'das na //
NK020(wa)001:1165: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:1166: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK020(wa)001:1167: bdun rgyud rigs kyang brlag par byed //
NK020(wa)001:1168: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:1169: rdo rje chen po mchog 'dzin pa //
NK020(wa)001:1170: mgon po chen pos byin rlabs pas //
NK020(wa)001:1171: blo ldan gang zhig 'da' ba ni //
NK020(wa)001:1172: rdo rje 'dzin pas mod la spong //
NK020(wa)001:1173: spangs pa'i sems can chen po ste //
NK020(wa)001:1174: ji snyed 'khor ba'i spyod rgyud du //
NK020(wa)001:1175: ngan song gsum du yang nas yang //
NK020(wa)001:1176: shin tu mi bzad cho nges 'debs //
NK020(wa)001:1177: bdag nyid chen po sangs rgyas bka'i //
NK020(wa)001:1178: tshig las 'das na rdul phran bzhin //
NK020(wa)001:1179: nga ni dbang phyug chen po ste //
NK020(wa)001:1180: rgyal chen rigs bzhi nga yi g.yog /
NK020(wa)001:1181: lha srin sde brgyad nga yi bran //
NK020(wa)001:1182: dam tshig dag las 'da' ma byed //
NK020(wa)001:1183: de ltar khyod kyis shes gyis la //
NK020(wa)001:1184: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' ma bcag /
NK020(wa)001:1185: dam pa chos kyi gzhung ma dbral //
NK020(wa)001:1186: sems can dmyal ba'i rgyu ma gsog /
NK020(wa)001:1188: sngags kyi dam tshig tshul ma bshig /
NK020(wa)001:1190: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK020(wa)001:1191: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK020(wa)001:1192: rang gi sems ni yongs su dul //
NK020(wa)001:1193: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK020(wa)001:1194: lus kyi sdom pa legs pa ste //
NK020(wa)001:1195: ngag gi sdom pa legs pa yin //
NK020(wa)001:1196: yid kyi sdom pa legs pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:1197: thams cad du ni sdom pa legs //
NK020(wa)001:1198: thams cad bsrung ba'i dge slong dag /
NK020(wa)001:1199: sdug bsngal kun las nges par grol //
NK020(wa)001:1200: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK020(wa)001:1201: gsal zhing dag la rnyog pa med //
NK020(wa)001:1202: gzung du med cing brjod du med //
NK020(wa)001:1203: rgyu dang las las kun tu 'byung //
NK020(wa)001:1204: de ltar chos rnams shes gyis la //
NK020(wa)001:1205: sems can don ni mnyam med byos //
NK020(wa)001:1206: 'on kyang skyob pa'i sras su skye //
NK020(wa)001:1207: zhes pas chos sbyin byin la /
NK020(wa)001:1208: gnod pa'i las spang bar gdams pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1209: rgyan gyis brgyan par byas kyang chos spyod cing //
NK020(wa)001:1210: dul zhing yang dag sdom la tshangs par spyod //
NK020(wa)001:1211: 'byung po kun la chad pa spangs pa ni //
NK020(wa)001:1212: dge slong dge sbyong de yin bram ze'ang de //
NK020(wa)001:1213: mtshon chas mi 'jigs gang yang med //
NK020(wa)001:1215: rang gi lus la dpe long la //
NK020(wa)001:1216: gzhan la gnod pa ma byed cig //
NK020(wa)001:1217: chen po'am chung ngu gang dag gi /
NK020(wa)001:1218: lus la mngon par gnod gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:1219: nad de nye bar phyungs nas su //
NK020(wa)001:1220: gdon de rang gi gnas su dengs //
NK020(wa)001:1223: su m+b+ha zhes sogs kyi rang rang gi gnas su bskrad cing /
NK020(wa)001:1224: gtor ma 'phral du gshegs na bgegs gtor de nyid du btang //
NK020(wa)001:1226: 'jig rten skyong ba grags ldan pa //
NK020(wa)001:1227: gtsang rigs dpal mgon bdun cu lnga //
NK020(wa)001:1228: 'khor du gtogs pa'i sde brgyad sogs //
NK020(wa)001:1229: mi dang mi min 'byung po'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:1230: bdag gi rnam lnga'i mchod pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1231: mchod sbyin gtor ma blang bar mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:1232: de dag rnams kyi brtson 'grus dang //
NK020(wa)001:1233: gzi brjid dbang phyug stobs kyis kyang //
NK020(wa)001:1234: mi shis pa kun 'joms gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1235: 'jig rten bde zhing lo legs dang //
NK020(wa)001:1236: zhes sogs kyis gtsang sar dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:1240: bdag nyid rdor sems su nga rgyal 'phos te /
NK020(wa)001:1241: mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor gsal btab nas /
NK020(wa)001:1242: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra sa t+wa sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham la sogs pas mchod /
NK020(wa)001:1243: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:1245: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:1246: dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs thams cad bdag cag
NK020(wa)001:1248: khyed rnams la mkhyen pa'i ye shes /
NK020(wa)001:1250: mdzad pa'i phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba lags pas /
NK020(wa)001:1251: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:1252: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu rnams sku tshe brtan zhing
NK020(wa)001:1253: thugs kyi bzhed pa'i don lhun gyis grub pa dang
NK020(wa)001:1254: / bdag dang sems can thams cad bde zhing skyid par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK020(wa)001:1255: khyad par du'ang bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod 'khor
NK020(wa)001:1256: dang bcas pas thog drangs sems can thams cad kyi
NK020(wa)001:1257: gnas skabs su mthar thug gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK020(wa)001:1258: thams cad zhi nas 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las
NK020(wa)001:1259: 'das pa'i dngos grub tshe 'di nyid la thob par
NK020(wa)001:1261: zhes 'dod don la gsol ba btab /
NK020(wa)001:1263: ma rnyed yongs su ma tshang dang /
NK020(wa)001:1264: zhes sogs kyis bzod par gsol /
NK020(wa)001:1266: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyi brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:1268: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK020(wa)001:1269: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK020(wa)001:1271: a ham yu ti dzah badz+ra muh zhes pas ye shes kyi 'khor lo dang gtor mgron rnams gshegs /
NK020(wa)001:1272: dam tshig pa rang la bsdu /
NK020(wa)001:1273: rang nyid lhar gsal ba'i spyi bo nas h+aum yig
NK020(wa)001:1274: zhu ba thim pas lus thams cad rdo rje'i go
NK020(wa)001:1276: dge ba bsngo zhing shis pa brjod pas bde legs su bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:1277: de yang phyag bzhes su phyi'i thugs dam skong ba'i
NK020(wa)001:1278: tshe 'di nyid sngar dkyus su bkod pa ltar rgyas
NK020(wa)001:1279: par btang rjes brtan bzhugs byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:1280: mdo dbang ma grol bar mi bsdu bar /
NK020(wa)001:1281: nyin re zhing bdag bskyed dkyil 'khor gang dang 'brel
NK020(wa)001:1282: ba des mdzad cing mdun bskyed kyang sgo 'byed kyi
NK020(wa)001:1283: dus phyag rdor / lha mi la rnam snang /
NK020(wa)001:1284: nyan rang la sh+aaka thub sogs gtso bo skabs thob kyis bsgyur bar mdzad mod /
NK020(wa)001:1286: bdag bskyed so sos byas phyir mdun skyed ma bsgyur
NK020(wa)001:1287: bar thams cad kyi gtso bo rdor sems rang bsgoms
NK020(wa)001:1289: rdo rje sems dpa' ni rigs dang dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi khyab byed du 'gro ba'i phyir dang /
NK020(wa)001:1290: da lta yongs grags kyi yig cha zur ham lugs las kyang /
NK020(wa)001:1291: sgo 'byed kyi dkyil 'khor dang sbrel nas gtso bo ma barjesa par ma zad /
NK020(wa)001:1292: phyag rdor dkyil 'khor gyi lha yang rdor sems kyi
NK020(wa)001:1293: thugs ka nas spros te sgom pa sogs mdzad pa'i
NK020(wa)001:1294: phyir ro // gal te go yul gyis ma shod na /
NK020(wa)001:1295: sngon 'bro phyi'i thugs dam skong ba'i skabs su cha
NK020(wa)001:1296: gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs shing cho ga zin ma
NK020(wa)001:1297: thag bsdus la / de phyin dkyil 'khor so so'i
NK020(wa)001:1298: sgrub mchod kyi tshe rang rang gi skabs babs kyi
NK020(wa)001:1300: 'das gtor dang bcas te cha bzhi pa'i gtor chog rkyang pa btang bas chig cing /
NK020(wa)001:1301: phyag len du'ang 'di ltar mdzad pa shas che'o //
NK020(wa)001:1302: tshul 'di kun la grags na yang //
NK020(wa)001:1303: lhag chad nor bas gtsang dag dkon //
NK020(wa)001:1304: ngag la dbang thob legs bshad 'di /
NK020(wa)001:1305: chos mig can gyi dpal du 'gyur //
NK020(wa)001:1306: cha gsum dkyil 'khor gyi sgrub thabs gtor chog dang bcas pa'i kha tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:1309: 'jigs rung ngan song gnas zab las //
NK020(wa)001:1311: dbyer med phyag na rdo rje la //
NK020(wa)001:1312: btud nas de yi sgrub thabs bshad //
NK020(wa)001:1313: 'dir phyag na rdo rje ngan song gnas 'dren zhes
NK020(wa)001:1314: bya ba gab pa'i dbang le dang po la brten
NK020(wa)001:1316: gang du bya ba'i gzhir chag chag gdab pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:1317: thig tshon byin rlabs sngar ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)001:1318: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs snam bu bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:1319: dbus 'khor lo'i lte ba mthing ga /
NK020(wa)001:1324: 'od phreng ste tshon lhag ma spyi dang 'dra zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1325: lha mtshan ji ltar rigs pa dgod /
NK020(wa)001:1326: bum pa gnyis gu gul gyis bdug cing drag sngags bzlas pa'i thun gyis brab /
NK020(wa)001:1327: dri'i chus sum gnyis bkang zhing rdzas nyer lnga blug /
NK020(wa)001:1328: mgul chings sogs chas su bcug pa kha rgyun dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:1329: rnam bum dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi la 'god /
NK020(wa)001:1330: tsakli rnams kyang ji ltar rigs pa'i gnas su bsham /
NK020(wa)001:1331: dkyil 'khor gyi mdun du 'das gtor dang /
NK020(wa)001:1332: mtha' chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i nyer spyod kyis bskor /
NK020(wa)001:1333: cha gsum gtor ma'ang ci bder bsham /
NK020(wa)001:1334: rang gi mdun du las bum /
NK020(wa)001:1335: dri chab 'thor g.yab dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:1337: 'thor nas sogs nyer mkho thams cad tshogs par bya /
NK020(wa)001:1338: de nas stan bde ba la 'dug ste rgyud sbyang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:1339: bla ma dang dpal phyag na rdo rje la sangs
NK020(wa)001:1340: rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba
NK020(wa)001:1341: mdun gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs sad pa'i
NK020(wa)001:1342: spyan sngar / bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK020(wa)001:1343: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK020(wa)001:1344: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1345: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK020(wa)001:1346: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:1347: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:1348: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:1349: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK020(wa)001:1350: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:1351: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK020(wa)001:1352: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK020(wa)001:1353: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK020(wa)001:1354: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK020(wa)001:1355: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK020(wa)001:1356: dag pa gsum gyis lus dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:1357: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK020(wa)001:1358: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK020(wa)001:1359: zhes lan gsum gyis rgyud dag par byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:1361: tshogs zhing rnams rang la bsdus /
NK020(wa)001:1362: chos thams cad rang sems kyi snang ba tsam ste /
NK020(wa)001:1363: de yang sgyu ma lta bu'o zhes de'i ngang la dar gcig bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:1364: de nas bad ga skyed bni /
NK020(wa)001:1365: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+h+aahsarba d+har+m+aahs+w+aa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&aham /
NK020(wa)001:1366: zhes brjod pas sgyu mar snang ba de yang mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK020(wa)001:1367: stong pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:1368: gyi steng du h+aum las gser gyi rdo rje rtse
NK020(wa)001:1369: lnga pa h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK020(wa)001:1372: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)001:1373: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag po phyag
NK020(wa)001:1374: na rdo rje sku mdog sngon po 'bar ba chen
NK020(wa)001:1377: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1378: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum pa /
NK020(wa)001:1379: sma ra dang smin ma dmar ser 'bar zhing dbu
NK020(wa)001:1380: skra gyen du 'khyil ba rdo rje'i ba spu can
NK020(wa)001:1381: / phyag g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:1383: ba ti khra bo dang dar sngon pos stod g.yogs shing /
NK020(wa)001:1384: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs dkris pa /
NK020(wa)001:1385: sbrul gyi rgyan dang rin po che'i cod pan can /
NK020(wa)001:1386: zhabs gnyis g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1390: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:1391: lo mdun gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan
NK020(wa)001:1394: tish+tha badz+re s+w+aa h+aas brtan par byas /
NK020(wa)001:1395: spyi bo'i gnas lngar h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aa gnas pa zhu
NK020(wa)001:1396: ba las byung ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun gyis
NK020(wa)001:1397: dbang bskur bas mi bskyod pa bdag por gyur pa'i
NK020(wa)001:1398: rigs lngas dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:1399: slar yang gnas gsum gyi yi ge las 'od zer
NK020(wa)001:1400: 'phros rdo rje gsum gyi lha tshogs spyan drangs pa
NK020(wa)001:1401: thim pas byin gyis brlabs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:1402: rang gi srog gi gor rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' /
NK020(wa)001:1403: de'i thugs kar rdo rje'i lte bar h+aum yig bzla
NK020(wa)001:1404: bya'i sngags phreng gis bskor ba las 'od zer 'phros
NK020(wa)001:1405: / khams gsum thams cad snang bar byas //
NK020(wa)001:1407: sems can thams cad sems nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba
NK020(wa)001:1408: las rnam par grol te sangs rgyas kyi zhing du
NK020(wa)001:1410: n+ai lam wa ra ng+ha ra badz+ra p+aa ni r+aa dz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1412: las bum dang dri chab bsgrub ste /
NK020(wa)001:1413: rang gi thugs ka nas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang
NK020(wa)001:1414: mdog rgya gram dang dril bu bsnams pa dar dang
NK020(wa)001:1415: rin po ches brgyan pa phyungs nas bum nang pad
NK020(wa)001:1416: nyi'i gdan la sems skyil gyis gnas pa /
NK020(wa)001:1417: de'i thugs ka nas bgegs mthar byed ljang nag rgya
NK020(wa)001:1418: gram bsnams pa zhig phyungs te dri chab kyi nang
NK020(wa)001:1419: du pad nyi'i gdan la 'khod pa ra bsam zhing
NK020(wa)001:1421: badz+ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa nas /
NK020(wa)001:1423: 'jigs pa'i h+aum sgra nges sgrog cing //
NK020(wa)001:1424: bgegs rnams ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:1425: dngos grub ma lus stsol ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:1426: bgegs kyi dgra la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:1428: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgyas so sor reg la /
NK020(wa)001:1430: +aah badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:1434: ces bzlas pas byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)001:1435: 'khyil ba dang bgegs mthar byed kyi rang bzhin gyi chu'i rdul phra rab tu gyur par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1436: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+he d+harma t+aa badz+ra sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:1438: a mri ta'i sngags kyis bum chu ste /
NK020(wa)001:1439: gnas yo thams cad la bsangs gtor bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:1443: ram yam kham gis nyes skyon rnams sbyangs /
NK020(wa)001:1444: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i snod
NK020(wa)001:1445: du yig zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod rdzas rnams
NK020(wa)001:1446: 'dod pa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sprin
NK020(wa)001:1449: shap+da'i bar brjod pas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK020(wa)001:1450: de nas mdun bskyed sgrub pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1452: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK020(wa)001:1453: stong pa'i ngang las mdun gyi nam mkhar bcom ldan
NK020(wa)001:1454: 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad rgyal ba'i sprin phung
NK020(wa)001:1455: mtha' yas par 'phro ba sad de /
NK020(wa)001:1456: sku'i 'od kyis 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kun tu snang bar byas shing sbyangs /
NK020(wa)001:1457: ngan song gi rgyud thams cad la kun tu gzigs
NK020(wa)001:1458: te thugs ka nas gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga
NK020(wa)001:1459: pa h+aum yig gis mtshan pa 'od 'phro ba zhig
NK020(wa)001:1462: ma dag pa'i snod thams cad sbyangs nas rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:1463: srung ba'i gur khang ye shes kyi me 'bar bas
NK020(wa)001:1464: yongs su bskor ba'i nang pad nyi'i steng du sna
NK020(wa)001:1465: tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba la rdzogs pa'i gzhal yas
NK020(wa)001:1466: khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa nang nas rim pa
NK020(wa)001:1467: bzhin mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba'i rtsig pa rim
NK020(wa)001:1468: pa lngas bskor ba'i steng du pha gu dang d+r+wa
NK020(wa)001:1469: ba d+r+wa phyed shar bu mda' yab dang bcas pa
NK020(wa)001:1470: / rtsig pa'i rtsa bar 'dod snam dmar po la gzungs ma rnams 'khod pa /
NK020(wa)001:1471: nang ka ba brgyad kyi btegs shing rdo rje'i gdung
NK020(wa)001:1472: gis phub pa'i ya phub phyur bu'i rtser rdo rje'i
NK020(wa)001:1474: sgo bzhir ka ba bzhi bzhis btegs pa'i rta babs
NK020(wa)001:1475: snam bu bzhi pa chos 'khor ri dwags gdugs dang
NK020(wa)001:1476: bcas pa / steng 'og thams cad shar dkar /
NK020(wa)001:1480: dbus sngo ba dwangs shing sgrib pa med pa kun tu gsal ba /
NK020(wa)001:1481: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan la sogs rgyan thams
NK020(wa)001:1482: cad kyis mdzes par brgyan pa'i dbus su 'khor lo
NK020(wa)001:1483: rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs
NK020(wa)001:1484: pa'i gdan gyi steng du nam mkhar gnas pa'i rdo
NK020(wa)001:1486: de las 'od zer 'phros bcom ldan 'das rnam par
NK020(wa)001:1487: snang mdzad la sogs te mkha' khyab tu bzhugs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:1488: rgyal ba thams cad spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:1489: rdo rje'i lte ba'i h+aum la thim /
NK020(wa)001:1490: de yongs su gyur pa las gsang ba'i bdag po
NK020(wa)001:1491: phyag na rdo rje sku mdog sngon po 'bar ba
NK020(wa)001:1494: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1495: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum pa /
NK020(wa)001:1496: sma ra dang smin ma dmar ser 'bar zhing dbu
NK020(wa)001:1497: skra gyen du 'khyil ba rdo rje'i ba spu can
NK020(wa)001:1498: / phyag g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:1500: ba ti khra bo dang dar sngon pos stod g.yogs shing /
NK020(wa)001:1501: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs dkris pa /
NK020(wa)001:1502: sprul gyi rgyan dang rin po che'i cod pan can /
NK020(wa)001:1503: zhabs gnyis g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1504: shar gyi rtsibs la sgeg mo dkar mo me long /
NK020(wa)001:1505: lhor m+aa le ma ser mo phreng ba /
NK020(wa)001:1506: nub tu glu ma dmar mo pi wam /
NK020(wa)001:1507: byang du gar ma ljang gu gar rgya /
NK020(wa)001:1508: grwa bzhi'i shar lhor spos ma dkar ser /
NK020(wa)001:1509: lho nub tu me tog ma dmar ser /
NK020(wa)001:1510: nub byang du mar me ma dmar ljang /
NK020(wa)001:1511: byang shar du dri chab ma dkar ljang /
NK020(wa)001:1512: shar sgor lcags kyu ma dkar mo /
NK020(wa)001:1513: lho sgor zhags pa ma ser mo /
NK020(wa)001:1514: nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo /
NK020(wa)001:1515: byang sgor dril bu ma ljang gu /
NK020(wa)001:1516: thams cad kyang khro 'dzum chags pa'i nyams can /
NK020(wa)001:1517: rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan 'dzin zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1518: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:1519: g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis pad zla'i gdan la rol ba /
NK020(wa)001:1520: khyams la gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po lag
NK020(wa)001:1521: na rdo rje la sogs pa srung ma thugs dam
NK020(wa)001:1523: de thams cad kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:1526: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:1527: lo mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs par bsam la
NK020(wa)001:1529: dmigs med mkha' ltar khyab cing dag pa'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:1530: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK020(wa)001:1531: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK020(wa)001:1532: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:1533: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:1534: dzah h+aum bam hoh tish+tha badz+re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1535: zhes pas gnyis su med par bstim zhing brtan par byas /
NK020(wa)001:1536: lha thams cad kyi spyi bor h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:1539: ltag par h+r+ai rna ltag g.yon par +ai gnas par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:1540: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah zhes brjod pas yi ge lnga zhu
NK020(wa)001:1541: ba las byung ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun gyis
NK020(wa)001:1544: lhag ma dbang gnas su 'khyil ba las mi bskyod
NK020(wa)001:1545: pa bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan par
NK020(wa)001:1546: bsam / slar yang gnas gsum gyi yi ge las 'od zer 'phros /
NK020(wa)001:1547: rdo rje gsum gyi lha tshogs spyan drangs te thim pas /
NK020(wa)001:1548: dpral ba'i yig sku rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:1550: snying ga'i h+aum yig thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid du byin gyis brlabs /
NK020(wa)001:1552: rang gi thugs ka nas spros pa'i mchod sprin mtha' yas pas mchod par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1553: 'jig rten khams ni dpag med na /
NK020(wa)001:1554: mchod yon ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1555: bdag gis gus par bshams pa 'di //
NK020(wa)001:1557: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra p+aa ni sa pa
NK020(wa)001:1558: ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham p+au dza me g+ha sa mu
NK020(wa)001:1559: dra spa ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:1564: shap+da'i bar rang rang gi phyag rgyas dbul /
NK020(wa)001:1566: khams gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:1567: bu gzhin skyong ba'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK020(wa)001:1568: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin sku //
NK020(wa)001:1569: bla med mgon la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:1570: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
NK020(wa)001:1572: thugs rje'i stobs kyis gdug pa 'dul //
NK020(wa)001:1573: rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:1574: gzugs mdzes phreng ba dbyangs snyan gar //
NK020(wa)001:1575: nyer spyod bzhi dang phyag rgya bzhis //
NK020(wa)001:1576: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mdzad ma //
