NK020(wa)001:1577: lha mo bcu gnyis la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:1578: las kyi gnod sbyin chen po ni //
NK020(wa)001:1579: 'jigs su rung ba'i cha byad can //
NK020(wa)001:1580: thams cad ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:1582: bstod par 'os pa sogs kyis kyang bstod do //
NK020(wa)001:1584: gtso bo'i srog gi gor rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' //
NK020(wa)001:1585: de'i thugs kar rdo rje'i lte bar h+aum yig bzla
NK020(wa)001:1586: bya'i sngags phreng gis bskor ba las 'od zer 'phros
NK020(wa)001:1587: / khams gsum thams cad snang bar byas /
NK020(wa)001:1589: sems can thams cad kyi sems nyon mongs pa'i 'ching
NK020(wa)001:1590: ba las rnam par grol te sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK020(wa)001:1592: n+ai li w+aa ra d+ha ra badz+ra p+aa ni ra dz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:1593: zhes pa ci nus bzla zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1594: mjug tu rtsa sngags kyi sham bur /
NK020(wa)001:1595: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka ga ti he tum h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:1596: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ka ga ti he tum h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:1597: ma tha ma tha sarba ti r+yaka ga ti he tum h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:1598: ces btags pa'ang cung zad bzlas pa'i nus pa bye ma'am yungs kar la bstim mo //
NK020(wa)001:1599: mjug tu thal mo sbyar te /
NK020(wa)001:1600: bcom ldan 'das bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can
NK020(wa)001:1601: thams cad sems sdig sgrib nyes ltung gi 'ching ba
NK020(wa)001:1602: las rnam par grol ba mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:1604: de nas rnam bum bskyed chog ni /
NK020(wa)001:1605: dri chab dang las bum gyi chu 'thor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1609: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las ye shes rin po
NK020(wa)001:1610: che'i rang bzhin can gyi bum pa mtshan nyid thams
NK020(wa)001:1611: cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbus su pad nyi zla
NK020(wa)001:1612: ba'i steng du h+aum las rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan
NK020(wa)001:1613: pa yongs su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das gsang
NK020(wa)001:1614: ba'i bdag po sku mdog sngon po rdo rje dang
NK020(wa)001:1615: sdigs mdzub mdzad pa'i skur gyur /
NK020(wa)001:1618: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:1620: tish+tha badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa sa brtan /
NK020(wa)001:1623: badz+ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa nas /
NK020(wa)001:1625: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
NK020(wa)001:1627: thugs rje'i stobs kyis gdug pa 'dul //
NK020(wa)001:1628: rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:1631: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags phreng gzungs thag la 'khril te song bas thugs rgyud bskul /
NK020(wa)001:1632: sku'i cha thams cad nas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas bum pa gang bar bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1633: n+ai lam w+aar d+ha ra ci nus bzlas mthar sngags de nyid kyis mchod yon phul bas /
NK020(wa)001:1634: bum nang gi lha sngar bas gsal zhing bum chu'i
NK020(wa)001:1635: rdul phra rab re re bzhin yang 'dod pa ma
NK020(wa)001:1636: lus pa yongs su skong ba'i nus pa can du
NK020(wa)001:1638: bum chu rang gi spyi bor gtigs shing khar btung /
NK020(wa)001:1639: h+aum lan bzhi brjod cing spyi mgrin snying ga lte ba bzhir thig le byas pas /
NK020(wa)001:1640: bdag dang lha'i sku gsung thugs ye shes rdo rje gnyis med du rig par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:1641: de nas gtor ma btang zhing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:1642: 'das gtor dang cha gsum gtor ma sngar bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK020(wa)001:1643: dbang chog ltar mchog dbang bcu drug bskur bar bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:1646: badz+ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa sogs kyis mchod /
NK020(wa)001:1647: bstod par 'os pa sogs kyi bstod /
NK020(wa)001:1649: ma rnyed yongs su sogs kyis nongs pa bshags /
NK020(wa)001:1651: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyis brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:1653: khyed kyi sems can don kun mdzad /
NK020(wa)001:1657: dam tshig gi 'khor lo rnams rang la thim /
NK020(wa)001:1658: bdag nyid thugs srog h+aum gi n+aa da'i bar bsdu /
NK020(wa)001:1659: de yang mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su thim pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:1660: de las skad cig gis lhar langs pa'i spyi bo
NK020(wa)001:1661: nas h+aum yig zhu ba thims pas lus thams cad
NK020(wa)001:1662: rdo rje'i go chas gtams par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:1663: dge ba bsngo zhing shis pa brjod pas mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:1664: gsang bdag sgrub thabs ngag 'don khrigs /
NK020(wa)001:1665: gab pa'i dbang le'i dgongs pa ste /
NK020(wa)001:1666: 'dus pa mdo yi chos kyis sgo /
NK020(wa)001:1667: thog mar 'byed byed ngo mtshar dpal /
NK020(wa)001:1668: sgo 'byed phyag rdor ngan song gnas 'dren gyi sgrub thabs le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:1669: 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo las /
NK020(wa)001:1670: sngon 'gro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis bshad pa'i skabs te dang po'o //
NK020(wa)001:1673: mngon mtho'i them skas la brten nas /
NK020(wa)001:1674: thar pa'i grong du 'khrid mkhas pa //
NK020(wa)001:1675: gter chen bla ma la btud de //
NK020(wa)001:1676: lha mi'i theg pa'i sgrub thabs bshad //
NK020(wa)001:1677: dngos gzhi chu bo bzhi'i dang po rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor la drug las /
NK020(wa)001:1678: 'dir dang po lha mi'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:1679: gang du bya ba'i gzhir dri bzang pos chag chag btab la /
NK020(wa)001:1681: ri bdun dang mtsho bdun spel mas bskor ba'i phyogs bzhin gling bcu gnyis te /
NK020(wa)001:1682: shar gling gsum dbyibs zla gam /
NK020(wa)001:1687: ri rab kyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:1688: lcags ri'i phyi rol tu khyams zlum po la gtod pa'i sgo bzhi rtsig pa ljang gus bskor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1690: rtsig pa'i phya nas 'dod snam phan chad spyi dang 'dra ba /
NK020(wa)001:1691: mda' yab kyi phyi rol rin po che'i sa gzhi'
NK020(wa)001:1692: khor yug la ljon shing dang khrus rdzing la sogs
NK020(wa)001:1693: pas brgyan pa'i mthar rdo ra dang 'od phreng tshon
NK020(wa)001:1698: gling bcu gnyis rnams shar dkar /
NK020(wa)001:1705: sgo'i nang khyams sngon po mig mngas ris dang /
NK020(wa)001:1707: sgo phan chad gzhan thams cad spyi dang 'dra'o //
NK020(wa)001:1708: dkyil 'khor gyi lha gnas rnams su sku rten lha tsaka /
NK020(wa)001:1709: gsung rten rgya bod kyi yi ge /
NK020(wa)001:1710: thugs rten s+aats+tsha dkar po mi grangs sam so so'i lo grangs kyis dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor /
NK020(wa)001:1711: rin chen 'bru sman gyi rdzas dang dri'i chu rten
NK020(wa)001:1712: ring bsrel can la khrus byas pa'i khrus chu rnams
NK020(wa)001:1713: kyis bkang ba'i bum pa mgul chings kha rgyan dang
NK020(wa)001:1714: bcas pas brgyan pa dkyil 'khor gyi mdun dang /
NK020(wa)001:1715: rdzas dbang gi tsakli rnams kyang ci bder bsham /
NK020(wa)001:1716: mtha' ar+g+ham la sogs pa'i mchod pas bskor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1717: mdun du gtsang zhing bsod pa'i bza' bcas brgyan pa'i 'das gtor dang cha gsum kyang bsham /
NK020(wa)001:1718: rang gi mdun du rdor dril spos snod 'thor nas sogs yo byad thams cad tshogs par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:1721: de nas phyogs bcu'i 'phags pa thams cad mngon sum
NK020(wa)001:1722: pa lta bur dmigs te phyag byas nas stan la
NK020(wa)001:1724: sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs kyi mchog rnams la //
NK020(wa)001:1725: byang chub par du bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:1726: bdag gis sbyin sogs bgyis pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK020(wa)001:1727: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:1729: tshad med bzhi bsgom pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1730: sems can thams cad bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1731: sdug bsngal dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1732: sdug bsngal med pa'i bde ba dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1733: nye ring chags sdang dang bral ba'i btang snyoms tshad med pa la gnas par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1735: de nas dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1736: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:1737: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa nyan
NK020(wa)001:1738: thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi byin gyis
NK020(wa)001:1739: brlabs dang / lha dang mi bden tshig grub pa thams cad kyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:1740: bdag cag la sogs pa mi dang lha rnams kyi smon lam dang /
NK020(wa)001:1743: deng 'dir de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:1745: rgyal po chen po bzhi la sogs te gtsang ris
NK020(wa)001:1746: kyi mgon po thugs dam can thams cad la mchod
NK020(wa)001:1747: pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang bkod pa mtha' yas
NK020(wa)001:1748: pa'i yon tan da nga ldan par gyur te /
NK020(wa)001:1749: sa gzhi rin po che sna tshogs kyi rang bzhin lag mthil ltar mnyam pa /
NK020(wa)001:1750: reg na 'jam zhing yangs la mtha' gru che ba'i gzhi la /
NK020(wa)001:1751: rin po che sna tshogs kyi pha gus zlum por brtsigs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1752: phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi dod pa /
NK020(wa)001:1753: rtsig pa'i steng du pha gu d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed shar bu mda' yab dang /
NK020(wa)001:1754: rtsa bar 'dod pa'i snam bu dmar pos bskor ba /
NK020(wa)001:1755: de'i nang du beed+aur+ya'i rang bzhin gyi khyams kyis yongs su bskor ba'i dbus su /
NK020(wa)001:1756: rin po che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin las grub pa'i lhun po /
NK020(wa)001:1757: rtsa bar gser gyi ri bdun /
NK020(wa)001:1759: phyogs bzhi na rgya mtsho chen po bzhi dang /
NK020(wa)001:1761: 'khor yug dang bcas pas yongs su bskor ba'i dbus na /
NK020(wa)001:1762: rin po che pad+ma'i rgyal po 'dab ma bzhi pa
NK020(wa)001:1763: yangs shing rgya che ba shin tu mdzes par gyur
NK020(wa)001:1764: pa la / 'phags pa'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK020(wa)001:1765: rnams gdan 'dzom pa chen po mdzad pa'i stan so
NK020(wa)001:1766: so'i smon lam dang bsod nams khyad par can gyi
NK020(wa)001:1767: mnga' thang dang 'tshams par grub pa mdzes pa sha
NK020(wa)001:1770: mchod pa byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1771: phyi nang kun tu yang cha rigs dang 'tshams par lha dang mi'i yo byad dam pa /
NK020(wa)001:1775: reg pa dang ldan pa yid du 'ong ba /
NK020(wa)001:1776: gya nom pa'i zhal zas dang /
NK020(wa)001:1778: rgyan dang rol mo la sogs pa phul du phyin
NK020(wa)001:1779: pa sna tshogs pa mchod pa'i sprin rgya mtsho thams
NK020(wa)001:1780: cad kyis rgyas par bkang zhing rgyan klubs pa dang
NK020(wa)001:1782: 'phags pa'i tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad gdan 'dzom nas /
NK020(wa)001:1783: de bzhin du byin gyis brlabs shing bzhes te longs spyod par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:1786: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:1787: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra s+w+aa ra pra mrda ne /
NK020(wa)001:1788: ta th+aa ga t+aa ya +aar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:1794: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta badz+re /
NK020(wa)001:1795: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+do pa sam kra ma na
NK020(wa)001:1796: badz+ra sarba karma +aa wa ra na bi shod+ha na
NK020(wa)001:1797: badz+re s+w+aa h+aa / zhes pa'ang brjod /
NK020(wa)001:1798: de nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:1800: lag g.yas spos snod thogs shing g.yon dril bu gsil ba dang bcas te 'dun pa rtse gcig pas /
NK020(wa)001:1801: bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad la sogs
NK020(wa)001:1802: pa phyogs bcu na dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i de
NK020(wa)001:1803: bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs
NK020(wa)001:1805: de dag gis legs par gsungs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1807: legs par thugs su chud pa dam pa'i chos thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:1808: thugs kyi sras su gyur pa byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:1809: gsung gi sras nyan rang 'phags pa'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:1811: byin gyis rlabs pa bsam gyi mi khyab pa mnga' zhing /
NK020(wa)001:1812: 'gro ba'i don du smon lam khyad par can mdzad pa las glengs te /
NK020(wa)001:1813: bdag sogs sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams spel ba'i slad du /
NK020(wa)001:1815: mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:1816: 'dir gshegs shing gdan 'dzom pa chen po mdzad de
NK020(wa)001:1817: / byin gyis rlob par ci gnang /
NK020(wa)001:1820: rgyal ba ji snyed bzhugs pa kun //
NK020(wa)001:1821: sku gsum mchog la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK020(wa)001:1822: gsung mchog chos kyis nyon mongs skyob //
NK020(wa)001:1823: nyan thos rang rgyal byang sems te //
NK020(wa)001:1824: 'das dang ma byon da ltar bzhugs //
NK020(wa)001:1825: ngag rnams kun las bcu gnyis 'phags //
NK020(wa)001:1826: gzhan gyi don phyir lam la zhugs //
NK020(wa)001:1827: nyon mongs skyob pa'i tshogs rnams kun //
NK020(wa)001:1828: bdag sogs sems can mos phyir dang //
NK020(wa)001:1829: yon mchod kun la brtse ba'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:1830: dad pa'i shugs kyis spyan 'dren na //
NK020(wa)001:1831: thugs rje'i stobs kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:1832: sarba ta th+aa ga ta e h+ye hi b+ha ga
NK020(wa)001:1833: w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka badz+ra d+h+aa tu
NK020(wa)001:1834: sa ri dzahdzah dza h+aum bam hoh sa ma ya
NK020(wa)001:1835: s+t+wam / zhes pas rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:1836: de nas lha chen po 'khor bcas spyan drang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:1837: lha'i 'jig rten mtho ris na 'phags pa gang yang
NK020(wa)001:1838: dag pa'i shes rab kyis chos thams cad kyi de
NK020(wa)001:1839: kho na nyid rtogs shing gzigs pa dang ldan pas
NK020(wa)001:1840: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa bsal ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:1845: ting nge 'dzin la dbang du gyur pa /
NK020(wa)001:1846: thabs mkhas pa'i spyod pa dang ldan pas lha'i rgyal
NK020(wa)001:1847: po'i cha lugs kyis lha mang po dag la dge
NK020(wa)001:1848: ba'i bshes gnyen mdzad cing bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1849: lha mang bo gzhan dag kyang de bzhin du bden pa rtogs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1850: thams cad kyang sngon ston pa bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK020(wa)001:1851: spyan sngar so so nas lha'i ngag brtags pas zhal
NK020(wa)001:1852: gyis bzhes pa'i thugs dam las ma g.yel bar /
NK020(wa)001:1853: deng rgyal ba sras bcas spyan drang ba'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:1855: tshangs dang lha dbang sred med bu //
NK020(wa)001:1856: dbang phyug rgyal chen sde bzhi po //
NK020(wa)001:1857: lha dang klu dang lha ma yin //
NK020(wa)001:1858: mi'am ci yi dbang po dang //
NK020(wa)001:1859: phyogs skyong bcu sogs 'khor dang bcas //
NK020(wa)001:1860: mi phyed rab dang ldan pa kun //
NK020(wa)001:1861: de ring snyan gsan dus kyi phyir //
NK020(wa)001:1862: mchod gtor bzang po bzhis pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:1863: bstan pa rgyas slad gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:1871: bee sh+ra ba na sa pa ri w+aa ra dzah
NK020(wa)001:1872: dzahh+aum bam hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya
NK020(wa)001:1875: lha'i rgyal po rnams so so'i zhing khams nas /
NK020(wa)001:1876: rang rang gi 'khor dang bcas pa rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK020(wa)001:1877: mthus byon nas rang rang gi gnas su bzhugs pa
NK020(wa)001:1878: ni / dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi gdan gyi steng
NK020(wa)001:1879: du bcom ldan 'das kun rig rnam par snang mdzad
NK020(wa)001:1882: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:1883: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:1884: rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1885: 'dab ma bzhi'i shar du zhing sbyong ba'i lha rdo
NK020(wa)001:1886: rje mi 'khrug pa sngon po g.yas sa gnon dang
NK020(wa)001:1887: g.yon mnyam bzhag gi steng na rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:1888: lhor stong gi lha ston pa sh+aakya thub pa ser
NK020(wa)001:1889: po g.yas sa gnon dang g.yon mnyam bzhag gi steng
NK020(wa)001:1890: na lhung bzed / nub tu nya'i lha 'od dpag med dmar po /
NK020(wa)001:1891: phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag gi steng na tshe bum /
NK020(wa)001:1892: byang du tshes brgyad kyi lha sman gyi bla beed+aur+ya
NK020(wa)001:1893: 'od kyi rgyal po mthing ga g.yas mchog sbyin a
NK020(wa)001:1894: ru ra dang g.yon mnyam bzhag bdud rtsi'i lhung bzed
NK020(wa)001:1895: kyis mtshan pa / de bzhi ka mchog gi sprul
NK020(wa)001:1896: sku tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can rdo rje'i
NK020(wa)001:1898: de rnams kyi mtha' bskor du phyogs bcu dang dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dkon mchog thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:1899: chos dkon mchog gi ngo bo yum chen mo /
NK020(wa)001:1900: dge 'dun dkon mchog sa chen po la bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK020(wa)001:1901: 'phags pa nyan rang gi tshogs ma lus pa thams cad sprin gtibs pa ltar bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1902: shar gling dbus mar brgya byin dkar po g.yas rdo
NK020(wa)001:1903: rje gdengs shing g.yon nor bu las mchog sbyin ster
NK020(wa)001:1904: ba'i glo g.yon na dbang mo dkar mo rgyud mang
NK020(wa)001:1906: de'i g.yas kyi gling du mngags gzhug 'gro ba yid 'ong ma ljang gu ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:1907: g.yon gyi gling du pho nya myur ba'i shugs can sngon po rtse gsum /
NK020(wa)001:1908: lho gling dbus mar tshangs pa ser po gdong bzhi
NK020(wa)001:1909: spyi blugs 'dzin pa'i glo g.yon na tshangs ma ser
NK020(wa)001:1910: mo gun+d+he bsnams pas 'dud pa'i tshul can /
NK020(wa)001:1911: de'i g.yas kyi gling du mngags gzhug lta na sdug ljang gu ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:1912: g.yon gyi gling du pho nya mgyogs byed dmar po pad dkar /
NK020(wa)001:1913: nub gling dbus mar khyab 'jug sngo nag 'khor lo
NK020(wa)001:1914: 'dzin pa'i gloo g.yon na dpal mo gsal shing bsnams
NK020(wa)001:1916: de'i g.yas kyi gling du mngags gzhug rdo rje bde ba dkar po mche ba /
NK020(wa)001:1917: g.yon gyi gling du pho na rdo rje sde dpon ljang ser 'khor lo /
NK020(wa)001:1918: byang gling dbus mar dbang phyug dmar po rtse gsum
NK020(wa)001:1919: 'dzin pa'i glo g.yon na u ma pad+ma bsnams pas
NK020(wa)001:1921: de'i g.yas kyi gling du mngags gzhug ded dpon nag po mdung thung /
NK020(wa)001:1922: g.yon gyi gling du pho nya drang srong khros pa dmar po mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1923: de thams cad kyang lha'i cha byad can dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:1924: sgo bzhi'i shar du yul 'khor srung dkar po pi wam /
NK020(wa)001:1925: lhor 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:1926: nub tu mig mi bzang dmar po sbrul zhags dang mchod rten /
NK020(wa)001:1927: byang du rnam thos sras ser po rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:1928: sgo'i nang gi khyams dang phyi'i khor yug la 'khor
NK020(wa)001:1929: du gtogs pa'i khams gsum gyi lha dang mi mtha'
NK020(wa)001:1930: yas pa / thams cad kyang rang rang gi rgyan
NK020(wa)001:1931: dang cha lugs rnam 'phrul sna tshogs pa'i rol pas
NK020(wa)001:1934: mya ngan mi 'da' thugs rje'i dang //
NK020(wa)001:1935: nyon mongs mi spong gos pa med //
NK020(wa)001:1936: ma chags rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK020(wa)001:1937: pad+ma'a stan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:1938: pad+ma ka ma la ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:1939: de nas tshogs bsags pa'i rim pa la 'jug ste /
NK020(wa)001:1940: dang po dkon mchog gsum 'khor dang bcas pa la phyag 'tshal ba'i rim pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:1941: spro na thar pa chen po phyogs bcu rgyas pa'i
NK020(wa)001:1942: mado'am rtogs pa chen po yongs su rgyas pa'i mdo
NK020(wa)001:1943: gang rung ngam / bsdu na dpang skong phyag brgya
NK020(wa)001:1944: pa las gsungs pa lta bu gang rigs bya zhing
NK020(wa)001:1945: gang rung ngam / / 'dir shin tu bsdus pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK020(wa)001:1946: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK020(wa)001:1947: ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la sogs
NK020(wa)001:1948: pa phyogs bcu dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:1949: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK020(wa)001:1951: rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:1954: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo bsgyur ba /
NK020(wa)001:1956: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das /
NK020(wa)001:1957: dkon mchog bla na med pa thams cad la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1958: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gis legs par gsungs pa /
NK020(wa)001:1960: legs par thugs su chud pa /
NK020(wa)001:1961: dam pa'i chos dkon mchog bla na med pa thams cad la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1962: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag gi thugs kyi
NK020(wa)001:1963: sras sa chen po la rab tu bzhugs pa'i byang
NK020(wa)001:1964: chub sems dpa' chen po thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:1965: ston pa bde bar gshegs pa de dag gi gsung gi sras 'phags pa rang rgyal dang /
NK020(wa)001:1966: 'phags pa nyan thos kyi dge 'dun te /
NK020(wa)001:1967: tshogs kyi mchog bla na med pa thams cad la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1968: tshangs pa dang brgya byin la sogs te 'phags pa
NK020(wa)001:1969: dam pa'i chos skyong ba 'jig rten dang 'jig rten
NK020(wa)001:1970: las 'das pa'i tshul du bzhugs pa thams cad la
NK020(wa)001:1973: ston pa bla med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK020(wa)001:1974: skyob pa bla med dam chos rin po che //
NK020(wa)001:1975: 'dren pa bla med dge 'dun rin po che //
NK020(wa)001:1976: mchod gnas dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1977: pad+ma kha 'bul kha phye 'dra ba yis //
NK020(wa)001:1978: lag gnyis spyi bor bkod nas thal sbyar te //
NK020(wa)001:1979: lus dpag med par sprul pa'i sprin tshogs kyis //
NK020(wa)001:1980: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1981: srid gsum las kyi gling nas 'khor ba'i ru bzlog cing //
NK020(wa)001:1982: nyon mongs tha ba'i gnas nas byang chub myu gu skyes //
NK020(wa)001:1983: srid dang lta phyir 'brangs pa'i bdud rigs stongs mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:1984: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1985: bde gshegs rnam par gzigs dang gtsug tor can //
NK020(wa)001:1986: thams cad skyob dang log par dad sel dang //
NK020(wa)001:1987: gser thub 'od srungs rgyal ba sh+aakya thub //
NK020(wa)001:1988: da lta'i sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1989: sa bcu mchog brnyes sangs rgyas nyid mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:1990: zhi dul dbang gis mkhyen rab 'gro ba'i ched //
NK020(wa)001:1991: rab dga' yon tan pad+mo kha 'bus pa //
NK020(wa)001:1992: ma byon sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1993: 'gro kun 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren pa'i thabs //
NK020(wa)001:1994: sgron ma lam dang 'bras bu bshad pa'i chos //
NK020(wa)001:1995: nyes spong mtho ris thar par bgrod pa'i lam //
NK020(wa)001:1996: dam chos mdo sde rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:1997: byams dang snying rje'i bdag nyid sa gzhi la //
NK020(wa)001:1998: thabs dang shes rab bloo yi lo tog brnyes //
NK020(wa)001:1999: ma lus sems can nye bar 'tsho mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:2000: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:2001: tshangs dang dbang phyug khyab 'jug ma h+aa de wa //
NK020(wa)001:2002: rgyal chen bzhi sogs gtsang ris mgon po ste //
NK020(wa)001:2003: bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes 'phags pa'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:2004: dkar phyogs skyong ba rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:2005: dkon mchog bla med yon tan rin po che //
NK020(wa)001:2006: dad mos rnams kyi yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK020(wa)001:2007: mtho dman yongs kyi skyabs mdzad 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK020(wa)001:2008: dkon mchog 'khor dang bcas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:2009: dkon mchog gsum la dad pas phyag btsal bas //
NK020(wa)001:2010: sdig pa kun byang dge tshogs rnam par 'phel //
NK020(wa)001:2011: bcom ldan so so'i bka' las ci 'byung ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:2012: yon tan khyad par can de 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:2013: de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK020(wa)001:2014: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mthu dang byang chub sems dpa'i bsod nams rab 'byams las byung ba /
NK020(wa)001:2015: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa'i mchod pa sna tshogs pa'i mchog /
NK020(wa)001:2016: gtso bo dam pa khyad par can /
NK020(wa)001:2020: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pas phyogs bcu'i snod kyi 'jig rten thams cad phyur bur bkang ste /
NK020(wa)001:2021: chos kyi mchod pa dang bcas pas /
NK020(wa)001:2022: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa'i dkon mchog
NK020(wa)001:2023: gsum la phyi ma'i mu'i mthar rtag tu rgyun mi
NK020(wa)001:2030: rgyal ba'i sku la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)001:2031: sems can nyon mongs bag chags sbyangs slad du //
NK020(wa)001:2032: sku gsung thugs la khrus chab 'di gsol bas //
NK020(wa)001:2033: khams gsum gnas pa'i bag chags dag gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2034: sarba de ba ta artsi ta a mri ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2035: zhes dkyil 'khor la me long bstan te bum chus
NK020(wa)001:2036: bkrus pa'i khrus chu slar bum par blug la bzhag
NK020(wa)001:2037: / ras kha tshar ma nyams pas 'phyi bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:2038: de dag sku la mtshungs pa med pa'i gos //
NK020(wa)001:2039: gtsang la dri rab bgos pas sku 'aphyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:2040: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2042: tshul khrims dri ldan spos mchog dam pa 'di //
NK020(wa)001:2043: ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgya byin brlabs te //
NK020(wa)001:2044: sangs rgyas zhing du spos dri ngad lngang pas //
NK020(wa)001:2045: rgyal ba sras dang bcas rnams tshim gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2046: dkyil 'khor kun tu rgyal ba mnyes byed pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2047: rin chen dbyibs legs lha rdzas me tog 'di //
NK020(wa)001:2048: nam mkha' gang bar sems kyis mngon sprul te //
NK020(wa)001:2049: gzhal yas khang du sprin bzhin gtibs gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2050: nyon mongs dug sreg ma rig mun sel ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:2051: shes rab gzi ldan dpal gyi sgron me 'di //
NK020(wa)001:2052: sprin med mkha' la nyi shar ji bzhin du //
NK020(wa)001:2053: 'od gsal snang bas phyogs bcur gsal gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2054: stong gsum kun tu dri mchog khyab gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2055: spos dang sman sbyar gtsang chab rgyas pa'i khrus //
NK020(wa)001:2056: sprin med mkha' la bdud rtsi'i char babs pas //
NK020(wa)001:2057: mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2058: rgyal ba'i sku la bkres pa mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)001:2059: 'gro ba'i don du lha rdzas bdud rtsi'i bshos //
NK020(wa)001:2060: dag cing gtsang mar sbyar te 'bul lags na //
NK020(wa)001:2061: thugs rje chen pos dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2062: dril chen sil snyan rnam grol tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK020(wa)001:2063: bsam dag gang gis bstod de gus mchod pas //
NK020(wa)001:2064: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod nas sangs rgyas sar //
NK020(wa)001:2065: tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas chos kyi rgyal por smon //
NK020(wa)001:2067: bdag gzhan don phyir sku gsum brnyes //
NK020(wa)001:2068: sems can skyob phyir chos kyi mchog /
NK020(wa)001:2069: lam la zhugs pa'i dge 'dun te //
NK020(wa)001:2070: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:2071: bstod par 'os pa sogs kyang bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:2072: rgyas par mchod pa dang bstod pa'ang phyag 'tshal ltar so sor 'byung ste /
NK020(wa)001:2074: de nas rtog chen gyi gzungs 'di brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas bzhin du bskor ba lan bdun bdun bya'o /
NK020(wa)001:2082: +aa ka sha ni s+sam b+h+aa wa /
NK020(wa)001:2087: a ti ka na p+aa la ni sh+tsa ya /
NK020(wa)001:2091: bi shad de bi shad de /
NK020(wa)001:2092: man+d+ra man+d+ra man+d+ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2094: 'dir mdo chog yig rnying du phyogs bcu dang dus
NK020(wa)001:2095: gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams sde tshan du phye nas
NK020(wa)001:2096: bskor ba bdun tshan brgyad bshad na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:2097: 'dir dkon mchog gsum po la bskor ba bdun re
NK020(wa)001:2098: ste nyer gcig tsam byas na 'tshams par 'gyur ro
NK020(wa)001:2099: // de nas sdig pa bshags pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2100: rgyas par thar pa chen po'am rtogs chen ltar bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2102: dpang skong las 'byung ba ltar 'di skad ces /
NK020(wa)001:2103: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can thams cad kyi skye ba 'di dang /
NK020(wa)001:2105: tha ma ma mchis pa nas /
NK020(wa)001:2106: srid pa gsum gyi 'khor ba na 'khor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2109: gti mug gsum gyi dbang gis lus dang ngag dang yid kyi sgo nas mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK020(wa)001:2110: mtshams med pa lnga la sogs te gsung rab kun
NK020(wa)001:2111: las 'gal ba'i sdig pa mi dge ba'i las bdag
NK020(wa)001:2114: gzhan bgyid pa la rjes su yi rang ba de
NK020(wa)001:2115: dag rdul tsam bag tsam yang ma lus par mthol
NK020(wa)001:2116: zhing bshags so // sbyangs shing bsal to //
NK020(wa)001:2121: de nas rjes su yi rang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2122: ji ltar dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas de dag bla
NK020(wa)001:2123: na med pa'i bsod nams kyi rjes su yi rang
NK020(wa)001:2124: ba ltar / bdag cag la sogs pa sems can
NK020(wa)001:2125: thams cad kyis kyang 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las
NK020(wa)001:2126: 'das pa'i bsod nams thams cad la rjes su yi
NK020(wa)001:2127: ba ltar / rang ngo // de nas chos 'khor bskor bar bskul ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2128: phyogs bcu na de bzhin gshegs pa gang dag sems
NK020(wa)001:2129: can gyi don du mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:2130: kyang dam pa'i chos btsun par mdzad pa'i slad du
NK020(wa)001:2131: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba'i sa la
NK020(wa)001:2132: bzhes pa de dag thams cad la chos kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:2133: lo bla na med par bskor bar bskul ma 'tshal
NK020(wa)001:2134: lo // de nas mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2135: 'jig rten gyi khams rab 'byams chos kyi dbying kyis khyab pa thams cad na /
NK020(wa)001:2136: de bzhin gshegs pa gang dag 'du byed thams cad mi rtag pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2137: 'byor pa thams cad mthar rgud par 'gyur pa'i tshul bstan cing /
NK020(wa)001:2138: thabs kyis mya ngan las 'da' bar bzhed pa de dag la /
NK020(wa)001:2139: sems can thams cad la phan pa dang bde ba'i
NK020(wa)001:2140: don du thugs rje chen po'i gzugs kyis phyi ma'i
NK020(wa)001:2141: mtha'i mur thug gi bar du mya ngan las mi
NK020(wa)001:2142: 'da' zhing bzhugs par gsol ba 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:2143: de nas dge ba sngo ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2144: bdag cag rnams kyi dus gsum gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad gcig tu bsdus pa'i mthus /
NK020(wa)001:2145: bdag cag la sogs pa'i sems can ma lus pa'i sdig pa thams cad ni byang /
NK020(wa)001:2146: bsod nams thams cad ni rdzogs te /
NK020(wa)001:2147: dus 'di nas nam byang chub snying po la mchis
NK020(wa)001:2148: kyi bar du dgongs pa'i dbang gis ched du sprul
NK020(wa)001:2149: pa ma gtogs par nam yang tshe rabs thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2150: du ngan song la sogs pa gnas ngan par mi
NK020(wa)001:2151: skye zhing mi ltung bar shog cig /
NK020(wa)001:2152: log pa mi dge ba'i las la mi phyogs mi bgyid par shog cig /
NK020(wa)001:2153: las dang nyon mongs pa'i rgyu la mi phyogs mi bsog par shog cig /
NK020(wa)001:2154: smad pa'i lus dang sdug bsngal gyi 'bras bu kun
NK020(wa)001:2155: las thar nas phyin chad mi myong bar shog cig
NK020(wa)001:2156: / dus 'di nas nam byang chub snying po la
NK020(wa)001:2157: mchis kyi bar du sgo gsum nas dge ba chu
NK020(wa)001:2158: bo'i rgyun bzhi du rgyun mi chad par shog cig
NK020(wa)001:2159: / / tshe rabs ga skyes kyang bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan te /
NK020(wa)001:2160: sems can thams cad kyi don bya ba la mthu dang dbang yod par shog cig /
NK020(wa)001:2161: gang de bzhin gshegs pa 'ba' zhig gis thugs su
NK020(wa)001:2162: chud pa'i chos bla na med pa'i byang chub tu
NK020(wa)001:2163: gdon mi za bar 'tshang rgya ba'i don de kho
NK020(wa)001:2164: na nyid gang yin pa de bdag sogs sems can
NK020(wa)001:2165: thams cad kyis ma nor bar khong du chud cing
NK020(wa)001:2166: bsgoms la / gzhan dag la'ang ma nor bar ston cing 'dren par shog cig /
NK020(wa)001:2167: mdor na bag chags ma lus kun byang nas //
NK020(wa)001:2168: bsod nams ye shes tshogs chen yongs rdzogs te //
NK020(wa)001:2169: 'gro ba ma lus byin gyis bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:2170: bdag nyid myur du mngon par 'tshang rgya shog /
NK020(wa)001:2171: de nas thugs dam bskul pa'i phyir gzungs bzla zhing mdo sde bklag pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2172: dkyil 'khor la bkod cing spyan drangs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:2173: sras dang bcas pa thams cad mngon sum pa lta
NK020(wa)001:2174: bur dmigs nas / dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan gyi mthu'i khyad par dang /
NK020(wa)001:2175: gzungs sngags kyi phan yon ji skad bshad pa la yid ches dang dad gus cher bskyed de /
NK020(wa)001:2176: 'dod pa'i don zhu ba'i 'dun pa rtse gcig pas /
NK020(wa)001:2177: ngan song thams cad rnam par sbyong ba'i rtsa rig /
NK020(wa)001:2178: na mo b+ha ga wa te sarba durga te pa
NK020(wa)001:2179: ri shod+ha na r+aa dza ya ta th+aa ga ta
NK020(wa)001:2180: ya ar+ha te samya k+sam bud+d+ha ya /
NK020(wa)001:2182: sho d+ha ne sho d+ha ne sarba p+aa pam bi
NK020(wa)001:2183: sho d+ha ne shud+d+he bishu d+d+he sarba karma a wa
NK020(wa)001:2184: ra na bi shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2185: las sgrib rnam par sbyong ba mi 'khrug pa'i gzungs /
NK020(wa)001:2186: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:2187: kam ka ni kam ka ni /
NK020(wa)001:2188: ro tsa ni ro tsa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2189: tro ta ni tro ta ni /
NK020(wa)001:2190: t+r+aa sa ni t+r+aa sa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2191: pra ti ha na pra ti ha na /
NK020(wa)001:2192: sarba karma pa ram pa r+aa ni me sarba sa t+wa nany+tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2193: dus bzang las stong gi gzungs /
NK020(wa)001:2194: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aa kya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2199: b+hee sha dz+ye ma h+aa b+hee sha dz+ye r+aa dza sa mung+ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2200: zhes pa rnams ci nus bzla zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2201: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi sku las 'od zer
NK020(wa)001:2202: 'phros bdag sogs sems can thams cad la khyab pas
NK020(wa)001:2203: sdig sgrib sbyangs / 'od zer des bum chu la'ang
NK020(wa)001:2204: khyab pas nus pa can du gyur par bsam mo
NK020(wa)001:2205: sdig sgrib sbyangs / // de nas 'phags pa rtogs
NK020(wa)001:2206: pa chen po yongs su rgyas pa'i mdo'i glegs bam
NK020(wa)001:2208: grogs gzhan la 'don du bcug kyang rung zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2209: spro zhing nus na thar pa chen po'i mdo dang /
NK020(wa)001:2210: dpang skongs phyag brgya pa sogs kyang bklag go /
NK020(wa)001:2211: de nas gtor ma btang zhing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2212: 'das gtor dang cha gsum gyi gtor ma sngar bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK020(wa)001:2213: dbang chog ltar lha mi'i theg pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK020(wa)001:2215: mchod pa drir med yongs dag pa //
NK020(wa)001:2216: rnam mang rgya che thams cad dang //
NK020(wa)001:2217: so so'i mnga' thang rgya chen du //
NK020(wa)001:2220: ma rnyed yongs su sogasasa kyi nongs pa bshags /
NK020(wa)001:2222: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyis brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:2224: khyed kyi sems can sogs kyi gshegs /
NK020(wa)001:2225: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas sras dang bcas pa bdag gis mchod pas /
NK020(wa)001:2226: sems can ma lus pa thams cad sa bcu la gnas par bgyis te /
NK020(wa)001:2227: kun gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i yang dag pa nyid
NK020(wa)001:2228: du thugs su chud pa dang ldan pa bgyid par
NK020(wa)001:2229: gyur cig / ces dge ba bsngo /
NK020(wa)001:2231: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba //
NK020(wa)001:2232: de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2233: ston mchog dam pa lha mis mchod 'os pa //
NK020(wa)001:2234: sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:2235: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba //
NK020(wa)001:2236: de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2237: zhi ba chags bral lha mis /
NK020(wa)001:2242: dge 'dun phyag 'tshal deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:2243: ces brjod pas phyogs dus thams cad du bde legs dang ldan par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:2244: brgyud pa'i man ngag dang bral kyang //
NK020(wa)001:2245: dbang ches rang bzor sbyar ba'i mun //
NK020(wa)001:2246: mthar byed chos kyi nyin mor byed //
NK020(wa)001:2247: skal ldan kun dag'i dpal du shar /
NK020(wa)001:2248: lha mi'i theg pa'i sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:2252: gang zag bdag med rtogs byed grub //
NK020(wa)001:2253: zhi ba'i gling du sgrol mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:2254: der btud nyan thos sgrub thabs bshad //
NK020(wa)001:2255: gnyis pa nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:2256: gang du bya ba'i gzhir byi dor byas shing dri bzang po'i chus chag chag btab pa la /
NK020(wa)001:2257: dkyil 'khor khyams dang rta babs spangs pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:2258: phyi rol tu rin po che'i bye ma brdal ba'i
NK020(wa)001:2259: sa gzhi la dpag bsam gyi shing dang khrus kyi
NK020(wa)001:2260: rdzing bu la sogs pas brgyan pa'i mthar rdo ra
NK020(wa)001:2262: dbus kyi lte ba ser po /
NK020(wa)001:2263: de'i phyi nas rim par 'dab bzhi phyogs tshon /
NK020(wa)001:2265: 'dab ma bcu drug pa rnams mdzes tshon du bya zhig /
NK020(wa)001:2267: lha gnas rnams su sku rten lha so so'i tsakli bkod /
NK020(wa)001:2268: dbus kyi ston pa'i sku dang go sa gcig par
NK020(wa)001:2269: gsung rten so thar gyi mdo lta bu'i glegs bam
NK020(wa)001:2270: dang / thugs rten ring bsrel can gyi mchod rten rnams kyang dgod /
NK020(wa)001:2271: dri'i chus rten byin can la khrus byas pa'i chu
NK020(wa)001:2272: slar yang bum pa chas su bcug pa'i nang du
NK020(wa)001:2273: blugs pa dkyil 'khor gyi mdun dang /
NK020(wa)001:2275: chos gos gsum gding lhung chu tshags sogs kyang ci bder bsham /
NK020(wa)001:2276: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor du chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i
NK020(wa)001:2277: nyer spyod mdun lta bur gtsang zhing bsod pa'i bza'
NK020(wa)001:2279: cha gsum gtor ma'ang ci bder bsham /
NK020(wa)001:2280: rang gi mdun du spos snod mthor nas rol mo'i yo byad sogs 'du bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:2282: khrus dang rgyal ba sras bcas la phyag 'tshal ba sngon du 'gro bas stan la 'dug ste /
NK020(wa)001:2283: skyabs sems tshad med bzhi bsgom pa'i rim pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2284: thub pa mchog dang dam pa'i chos //
NK020(wa)001:2285: 'gro ba'i mun sel dgra bcom gyi //
NK020(wa)001:2286: tshogs la bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:2287: rang gzhan don gnyis rab bsgrub phyir //
NK020(wa)001:2288: byang chub mchog sems bskyed par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:2290: sems can thams cad bde ba dang zhes sogs lan gsum /
NK020(wa)001:2292: bum pa'i steng du a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:2293: la gnas pa'i rten 'brel snying po'i sngags phreng 'od
NK020(wa)001:2294: zer dkar po 'phro bas 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi
NK020(wa)001:2295: thams cad bsdus nas 'od du zhu ba bum pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2296: chu dang ro gcig tu gyur par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:2297: rten 'brel snying po lan bdun bzla /
NK020(wa)001:2299: zla dkyil sngags phreng dang bcas pa'ang bum chu la thim par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2300: 'thor yab kyis blangs te gnas yo thams cad la
NK020(wa)001:2301: gtor bas rten dang mchod pa'i ma dag pa thams
NK020(wa)001:2302: cad sbyangs nas / dag cig bzang ba phun sum tshogs par byin gyis rlob par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)001:2303: 'di ni bum bskyed de rab gnas kyang yin no //
NK020(wa)001:2304: de nas dkyil 'khor bskyed cing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2305: mdun bskyed kyi gzhi gzung 'dzin rags pas bsdus pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2306: chos thams cad mi dmigs pa stong pa'i ngang la
NK020(wa)001:2308: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2309: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:2310: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' thang chen po dang /
NK020(wa)001:2311: ston pa bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
NK020(wa)001:2312: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya
NK020(wa)001:2313: thub pa sngon byang chub kyi spyad pa spyod pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2314: tshe sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su sbyangs pa'i bden
NK020(wa)001:2315: pa dang / chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing
NK020(wa)001:2316: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs kyis deng 'dir de
NK020(wa)001:2317: bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2318: 'phags pa chos skyong ba thams cad la mchod pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2319: tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor 'di dag
NK020(wa)001:2320: bcom ldan 'das 'od dpag tu med pa'i zhing gi
NK020(wa)001:2321: bkod pa'i yon tan lta bu dang ldan par gyur
NK020(wa)001:2322: te / sa gzhi rin po che sna tshogs kyi rang bzhin lag mthil ltar mnyam pa /
NK020(wa)001:2323: ljon shing chu mtsho la sogs pa rgyan thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2324: kyis rnam par brgyan pa'i zhing khams yongs su dag
NK020(wa)001:2325: pa'i dbus su / bkod pa thams cad las 'phags
NK020(wa)001:2326: pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i bkod pa la brten pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2327: pho brang rin chen sna bdun las grub pa'i khang
NK020(wa)001:2328: pa'i dbus su / pa brtsegs pa / gru bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:2333: shin tu rnam par phye bas mdzes par byas pa /
NK020(wa)001:2337: them skas bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:2338: dkyil 'khor gyi nang gi dbus su rin po che'i khri pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan /
NK020(wa)001:2339: mtha' bskor du gdan gyi ri ma pa nang nas /
NK020(wa)001:2344: shar lho'i grwa rnams su pad+ma'i gdan /
NK020(wa)001:2345: byang shar gyi grwa dang sgo bzhir rin po che'i gdan te /
NK020(wa)001:2346: ston pa bcom ldan 'das la sogs pa 'phags pa
NK020(wa)001:2347: rnams gdan 'dzom pa'i bzhugs gnas so so'i smon lam
NK020(wa)001:2348: khyad par can dang mnga' thang dang 'tshams par grub
NK020(wa)001:2349: pa mdzes pa sha stag 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2351: de nas mchod pa byin rlabs ni /
NK020(wa)001:2352: phyi nang kun tu yang cha ris dang 'tshams par lha dang mi'i yo byad dam pa /
NK020(wa)001:2356: reg pa dang ldan pa yid du 'ong ba /
NK020(wa)001:2357: gya nom pa'i zhal zas dang /
NK020(wa)001:2360: rol mo la sogs pa phul du phyin pa sna tshogs pa /
NK020(wa)001:2361: phung po gsum pa'i mdo dang /
NK020(wa)001:2362: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam las byung ba'i mchod
NK020(wa)001:2363: pa'i sprin rgya mtsho thams cad kyis rgyas par gang
NK020(wa)001:2364: zhing rgyan klubs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2366: de bzhin du byin gyis brlabs shing bzhes te longs spyod par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2369: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:2370: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra s+aa ra pra mrda ne /
NK020(wa)001:2371: ta th+aa ga ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+ha ya tad+ya th+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2377: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+do pa sam kra ma na
NK020(wa)001:2378: badz+ra sarba karma +aa wa ra na bi sho d+ha
NK020(wa)001:2380: zhes brjod pas kyang byin gyis brlab bo //
NK020(wa)001:2382: spos btul zhing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas te 'dun pa rtse gcig pas /
NK020(wa)001:2383: bdag cag gis ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub
NK020(wa)001:2384: pa la sogs pa phyogs bcu dang dus gsum du
NK020(wa)001:2385: bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang
NK020(wa)001:2386: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:2387: de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi rgyal po'i sras dgra bcom pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2390: rgyun du zhugs pa la sogs pa 'phags pa nyan
NK020(wa)001:2391: thos kyi tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad dgongs
NK020(wa)001:2392: su gsol / thugs rje chen po dang /
NK020(wa)001:2393: byin gyis brlabs bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2394: sngon gyi smon lam khyad par can las glengs te /
NK020(wa)001:2395: bdag cag la sogs pa 'gro ba mang po skyob
NK020(wa)001:2396: pa'i slad du mgon skyabs dang dpung gnyen du spyan
NK020(wa)001:2398: mchod pa'i tshogs sbyang ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:2399: 'dir gshegs shing gdan 'dzom pa chen po mdzad de
NK020(wa)001:2400: / byin gyis brlab par ci gnang /
NK020(wa)001:2402: phyogs dus kun nas skyabs gsum bka' sdod bcas //
NK020(wa)001:2403: nyon mongs 'gro la mkhyen brtses rab dgongs te //
NK020(wa)001:2404: dpag med zhing nas thogs med rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK020(wa)001:2405: 'dir gshegs mchod sprin rgya mtsho'i dbus bzhugs gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2406: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad dang //
NK020(wa)001:2407: shes rab me 'bar nyon mongs mtsho skems shing //
NK020(wa)001:2408: rnam grol bsod nams zhing du bka' sdod pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2409: phyogs bcu'i nyan thos dge 'dun bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:2410: yon sbyor mchod pa'i gnas su spyan 'dren na //
NK020(wa)001:2411: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2412: 'gro ba'i mgon po sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK020(wa)001:2413: sangs rgyas bstan pa gang gis phyag tu bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:2414: gsung rab rin chen sgrom gyi kha 'byed pa //
NK020(wa)001:2415: chos skyong dgra bcom chen po bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:2416: dam chos spel ba'i slad du spyan 'dren gyis //
NK020(wa)001:2417: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2418: spangs dang ye shes phun tshogs sangs rgyas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:2419: gdul bya'i dbang gis nyan thos tshul 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)001:2420: khyad par can gyi phrin las chos skyong ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:2421: gnas brtan bcu drug 'dir spyon gdan la bzhugs //
NK020(wa)001:2422: dge bsnyen skyabs gsol bden pa'i tshigs nyan pa //
NK020(wa)001:2423: dkon mchog gsum gyi zhabs 'bring mchis so 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:2424: bsod nams rin chen gling du spyan 'dren gyis //
NK020(wa)001:2425: 'gro ba'i don phyir mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2426: zhes brjod pas rang bzhin gyi gnas nas bcom ldan
NK020(wa)001:2427: 'das thub pa'i dbang po 'phags pa nyan thos chen
NK020(wa)001:2428: po'i dge 'dun gyi 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:2429: phyi bzhin 'brang ba tsun+da la sogs pa dge tshul dang /
NK020(wa)001:2430: d+harma t+aa la sogs pa dge bsnyen /
NK020(wa)001:2431: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi'i tshogs dang bcas pa
NK020(wa)001:2432: so so'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mthus byon nas rang rang
NK020(wa)001:2433: gi gdan la bzhugs par gyur pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2434: dbus su bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dpal
NK020(wa)001:2435: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog gser btso ma
NK020(wa)001:2436: lta bu / mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK020(wa)001:2437: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:2439: g.yon mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:2440: zhabs gnyis rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:2441: 'dab ma bzhi'i g.yas su dgra bcom pa /
NK020(wa)001:2444: rgyab tu rgyun zhugs rnams 'khar bsil dang lhung bzed bsnams pa /
NK020(wa)001:2445: 'dab brgyad nang mar mdun nas g.yas bskor du mchog brgya de /
NK020(wa)001:2447: sh+aa ri'i bun ri po che /
NK020(wa)001:2452: koo din+ya rin po che'i sgrom bu /
NK020(wa)001:2454: 'dab brgyad phyi mar mdun nas g.yas bskor du rang rgyud pa brgyad de /
NK020(wa)001:2463: phyi bskor gyi pad+ma bcu drug la mdun nas g.yas bskor du /
NK020(wa)001:2464: yan lag 'byung spos phor dang rnga yab /
NK020(wa)001:2466: nags na gnas sdigs mdzub dang rnga yab /
NK020(wa)001:2467: dus ldan gser gyi rna bsgor /
NK020(wa)001:2468: rdo rje mo'i bu sdig mdzub dang rnga yab /
NK020(wa)001:2469: bzang po chos 'chad dang mnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:2470: gser be'u rin po che'i zhags pa //
NK020(wa)001:2471: b+ha ra d+h+wa dza gser can mnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:2473: sgrag can zin rin po che'i prog zhu /
NK020(wa)001:2475: b+h+ya ra d+h+wa dza bsod snyoms len glegs bam dang lhung bzed /
NK020(wa)001:2476: lam brtan chos 'chad dang glegs bam /
NK020(wa)001:2477: klu'i sdo bum pa dang 'khar bsil /
NK020(wa)001:2479: mi phyed pa byang chub mchod rten 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:2480: de thams cad kyang gnas brtan dbang po dul ba'i cha lugs can /
NK020(wa)001:2481: shar lho'i grwar tsun+da dge tshul 'khar bsil dang lhung bzed /
NK020(wa)001:2482: byang shar gyi grwar dge bsnyen d+harma t+aa thor cog
NK020(wa)001:2483: can glegs bam khur zhing rnga yab dang bum pa
NK020(wa)001:2484: 'dzin pa / sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas la
NK020(wa)001:2485: gzigs shing pus mo g.yas pa las stag sprul pa
NK020(wa)001:2486: 'dzin pa / / shar sgor yul 'khor srung dkar po pi wam /
NK020(wa)001:2487: lhor 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:2488: nub sgor mig mi bzang dmar po sbrul zhags dang mchod rten /
NK020(wa)001:2489: byang sgor rnam thos sras ser po yid bzhin gyi rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:2490: thams cad kyang rang rang gi 'khor bsam gyi mi khyab pa dang bcas te bzhugs par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:2491: rin chen du ma las grub seng ge'i khri /
NK020(wa)001:2492: yid 'phrog sna tshogs gos kyis bkab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2493: sangs rgyas sras dang bcas la phul ba yis /
NK020(wa)001:2494: 'gro kun rdo rje'i gdan la 'khod gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2496: de nas mchod yon sbreng bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:2497: chu bo gad+g+aa'i rgyun bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:2498: ar+g+ham rgyun yang mi chad de /
NK020(wa)001:2500: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2502: chu bo gang+g+aa'i rgyun bzhin du //
NK020(wa)001:2503: zhabs bsil rgyun yang mi chad de //
NK020(wa)001:2505: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2506: de nas khrus gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2507: khrus kyi khang pa shin tu dri zhim pa //
NK020(wa)001:2508: shel gyi sa bzhi gsal zhing 'tsher ba bstar //
NK020(wa)001:2509: rin chen 'bar ba'i ka ba yid 'od ldan //
NK020(wa)001:2510: mu tig 'od chags bla re bres pa der //
NK020(wa)001:2511: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang de sras la //
NK020(wa)001:2512: rin chen bum pa mang po spos kyi chus //
NK020(wa)001:2513: yid 'ong legs par gang ba glu dang ni //
NK020(wa)001:2514: rol mor bcas pa du mas sku khrus gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2516: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK020(wa)001:2517: lha rnams kun gyis khrus gsol ltar //
NK020(wa)001:2518: lha yi chu ni dag pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:2519: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2520: sarba de ba ta artsi ta a mri ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2521: 'di ni khrus mchog dpal dang ldan //
NK020(wa)001:2522: thugs rje'i chu ni bla na med //
NK020(wa)001:2523: byin rlabs ye shes chu yis ni //
NK020(wa)001:2524: ci 'dod dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2525: sarba de ba ta artsi ta a mri ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2527: khrus khu slar yang bum par blug go /
NK020(wa)001:2528: de dag sku la mtshungs pa med pa'i gos //
NK020(wa)001:2529: gtsang la dri rab bgos pas sku phyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:2530: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2532: dri med mtshan la sgrib bsal mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)001:2533: dad pas ngur smrig rgyal mtshan phul ba yis //
NK020(wa)001:2534: nam mkha'i mtha' klas gyur pa'i sems can rnams //
NK020(wa)001:2535: sangs rgyas brtul zhugs mchog la spyod par shog /
NK020(wa)001:2536: badz+ra w+aa sa se s+w+aa h+aas na bza' dbul /
NK020(wa)001:2537: de nas tshogs bsags pa'i dang po phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2538: rgyas par dpang skong ltar bya bar gsungs pas ci 'grub dang /
NK020(wa)001:2539: 'dir mdor bsdus pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK020(wa)001:2540: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK020(wa)001:2541: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang
NK020(wa)001:2545: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo bsgyur ba /
NK020(wa)001:2547: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa mnyam med sh+aakya
NK020(wa)001:2548: thub pa 'khor 'phags pa nyan thos kyi dge 'dun
NK020(wa)001:2549: gyi tshogs dang bcas pa'i zhabs la dus thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2553: yon tan rin chen mang po'i tshogs mnga' zhing //
NK020(wa)001:2554: mtshan rab ye shes yongs su dag pa'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:2555: gser gyi mdog can lha dang mis mchod pa //
NK020(wa)001:2556: bcom ldan lha yi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:2557: sh+aa ra'i bu dang mood+gala gyi bu //
NK020(wa)001:2558: kun dga' bo dang rab 'byor ma 'gags pa //
NK020(wa)001:2559: 'char ka koo di n+ya rta thul te /
NK020(wa)001:2560: sprul pa'i nyan thos mchog brgyad la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:2561: 'od srungs nye ba 'khor dang ba lang bdag /
NK020(wa)001:2562: sgra gcan zin dang dga' bo ming can dang //
NK020(wa)001:2563: nor sbyin 'phags pa gang po rang rgyud kyi //
NK020(wa)001:2564: nyan thos mchog chen brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:2565: 'gro ba'i mgon po sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK020(wa)001:2566: sangs rgyas bstan pa gang gi phyag tu bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:2567: gsung rab rin chen sgrol gyi kha 'byed pa //
NK020(wa)001:2568: dgra bcom gnas brtan bcu drug la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:2569: de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyi rgyal po'i sras //
NK020(wa)001:2570: rgyun zhugs phyir 'ong phyir mi 'ong dgra bcom //
NK020(wa)001:2571: zhugs gnas skyes bu zung bzhi ya brgyad kyi //
NK020(wa)001:2572: nyan thos grangs las 'das la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:2573: dge bsnyen skyabs gsol bden pa'i tshig nyan pa //
NK020(wa)001:2574: dkon mchog gsum gyi zhabs 'bring d+harma t+aa //
NK020(wa)001:2575: rgyal ba'i bstan dang rnam bzhi'i 'khor skyong ba //
NK020(wa)001:2576: mthu chen rgyal chen sde bzhi la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:2577: de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2578: 'phags pa'i tshogs de dag thams cad la mchod yon dang byug pa /
NK020(wa)001:2582: gdugs dang ba dan la sogs pa dngos su ci
NK020(wa)001:2583: 'byor ba 'di dag dang phyogs bcu na bdag pos
NK020(wa)001:2584: yongs su ma bzung ba lha dang mi'i rdzas dam
NK020(wa)001:2585: pa bde ba'i yo byad phun sum tshogs pa thams
NK020(wa)001:2586: cad dang / gzungs dang rig pa'i mthu dang mos
NK020(wa)001:2587: pa'i stobs kyis bskyed pa'i mchod pa'i sprin phung po
NK020(wa)001:2588: gsum pa'i mdo dang bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam
NK020(wa)001:2589: las byung ba rgya mtsho thams cad kyis nam mkha'i
NK020(wa)001:2590: khams kyi mtha' klas pa thams cad rgyas par bkang
NK020(wa)001:2591: cad dang / ste 'bul lo // mchod do //
NK020(wa)001:2592: bdag gi bar bzhes par mdzad du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:2593: 'jig rten khams ni dpag med na /
NK020(wa)001:2594: mchod yon ji snyed yod pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2595: bdag gis gus par bshams pa 'di /
NK020(wa)001:2596: rgyal ba sras dang bcas la 'bul /
NK020(wa)001:2597: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2613: zhes pa rnams kyis barjesa nas dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:2614: de nas bshags pa la sogs pa'i yan lag phyi ma lnga ni /
NK020(wa)001:2615: bdag cag rnams kyis thog ma ma mchis pa nas
NK020(wa)001:2616: 'khor ba na 'khor ba'i tshe rabs thams cad du
NK020(wa)001:2617: sdig pa mi dge ba'i las mdor na mi bgyi
NK020(wa)001:2618: bar rigs pa'i las ni bgyis /
NK020(wa)001:2619: bgyi bar 'os pa'i las ma bgyis pa la sogs
NK020(wa)001:2620: pa mtho ris dang thar pa'i gegs su gyur cing
NK020(wa)001:2621: / 'khor ba dang ngan song gi rgyur gyur pa
NK020(wa)001:2622: ci mchis pa thams cad shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod
NK020(wa)001:2623: pa'i sems kyis mi 'chab par mthol zhing bshags so
NK020(wa)001:2624: / // dus gsum gyi 'phags pa dang so so
NK020(wa)001:2625: skye bo'i dge ba'i rtsa ba mtha' dag gi bsod
NK020(wa)001:2626: nams thams cad la rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK020(wa)001:2627: phyos bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2628: la chos kyi 'khor lo bla na med pa bskor
NK020(wa)001:2629: bar bskul lo // 'jig rten gyi sgron me gang
NK020(wa)001:2630: dag mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul ston par bzhed
NK020(wa)001:2631: pa de dag thams cad mya ngan las mi 'da'
NK020(wa)001:2632: bar 'jig rten gyi don mdzad cing yun ring du
NK020(wa)001:2634: mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:2635: 'dir ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:2636: la sogs pa 'phags pa'i tshogs de dag thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2637: la phyag 'tshal zhing mchod pa la sogs pa dge
NK020(wa)001:2638: ba'i rtsa ba rlabs po che 'di dag thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2639: la ma lus par 'phags pa'i tshogs rnams la dbul
NK020(wa)001:2640: zhing 'gro ba thams cad la bstabs shing bsngo bar
NK020(wa)001:2641: bagyi'o // de ltar phul zhing bsngosa pas bdag cag
NK020(wa)001:2642: la sogs pa sems can thams cad kyis thog ma
NK020(wa)001:2643: ma mchis pa'i 'khor ba nas bsags pa'i dge ba'i
NK020(wa)001:2644: rtsa ba ci mchis pa'i stobs dang /
NK020(wa)001:2645: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2646: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:2647: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs kyis /
NK020(wa)001:2648: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'phags
NK020(wa)001:2649: pa'i nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa la
NK020(wa)001:2650: sngon gyi thugs dam bzang po las glengs te mchod
NK020(wa)001:2651: cing gsol ba gdab pa'i cho ga bgyis pa las
NK020(wa)001:2652: phan yon ji skad bka' stsal pa thams cad bdag
NK020(wa)001:2653: cag la sogs pa'i sems can thams cad kyis 'phral
NK020(wa)001:2654: du thob cing yongs su rdzogs nas mngon du gyur
NK020(wa)001:2655: cig / bdag cag la sogs pas thog ma ma
NK020(wa)001:2656: mchis pa'i 'khor ba nas 'khor bar brgyud pa rnams
NK020(wa)001:2657: su sdig pa mi dge ba'i las kyi sgrib par
NK020(wa)001:2658: gyur pa ci mchis pa thams cad ma lus pa
NK020(wa)001:2659: cig / bsal te / gtan zhi zhing byang bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2660: sngon gyi las de lta bu'i rnam par smin pa yang rung /
NK020(wa)001:2661: 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur kyang rung ste /
NK020(wa)001:2663: mi dang mi ma yin gyi gnod pas gtses pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2665: 'khor dang longs spyod mi mthun pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2666: bsam pa mi 'grub cing bar du gcod pa mang ba sogs mi dge ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:2667: bkra mi shis pa dang ngan pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2668: sdig tor bgrang ba thams cad zhi zhing gtan mi 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2669: 'phral du yang tshe ring zhing nad ma mchis pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2670: 'khor dang yo byad thams cad mthun zhing 'byor pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2671: bsam pa thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub pa sogs
NK020(wa)001:2672: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dpal dang
NK020(wa)001:2674: tshe rabs thams cad du yang byang chub kyi tshogs
NK020(wa)001:2675: yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i lus dang longs spyod
NK020(wa)001:2676: dang 'khor dang grogs dang dge ba'i bshes gnyen phun
NK020(wa)001:2677: sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2678: dam pa'i chos dang rtag tu 'phrad cing thos pa
NK020(wa)001:2679: dang bsam pa dang sgom pa'i sgo nas don mngon
NK020(wa)001:2681: mdor na sems can thams cad kyi don bgyi zhing
NK020(wa)001:2682: 'phags pa'i lam sgyub pa la thabs mkhas pa dang
NK020(wa)001:2683: shes rab kyi mthu thogs pa med pa dang ldan
NK020(wa)001:2684: te byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rlabs po che
NK020(wa)001:2685: thams cad bde blag tu nyams 'og tu chud par
NK020(wa)001:2686: gyur cig / bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs
NK020(wa)001:2687: yongs su rdzogs pa g.yung drung gi sku sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:2688: bcom ldan 'das kyi go 'phang chen po myur du
NK020(wa)001:2689: thob nas sems can thams cad srid pa'i mtsho las
NK020(wa)001:2690: sgrol zhing mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2692: de nas gzungs bzla ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2693: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2694: de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad kyi mthu dang byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:2695: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs dang /
NK020(wa)001:2696: 'phags pa sku gsung thugs kyi spyod pa ma dag
NK020(wa)001:2697: pa mi mnga' ba rnams kyi thugs nges pa'i bden
NK020(wa)001:2698: pas / mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi
NK020(wa)001:2699: dkyil 'khor 'dir ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2700: sangs rgyas 'khor 'phags pa nyan thos kyi dge 'dun
NK020(wa)001:2701: gyi tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad gdan 'dzom pa
NK020(wa)001:2704: gzungs sngags bzlas pa tshul bzhin du 'grub par byin gyis rlob par mdzad de /
NK020(wa)001:2705: bdag sogs 'gro ba mang po'i don dpag tu med pa mdzad par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2706: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad kyi sku las
NK020(wa)001:2707: 'od zer 'phros pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2708: khyab / des 'phags pa thams cad sems can gyi don la bskul zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2709: ngan song gi gnas thams cad sbyangs te /
NK020(wa)001:2710: sems can thams cad mtho ris dang thar pa'i go 'phang la 'jug par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2711: 'od zer des bdag cag rnams la khyab pas 'gro don dpag med sgrub nus pa'i mthu thob ste /
NK020(wa)001:2712: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang sku gsung thugs mtshungs par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2713: yang 'od zer de dag gcig tu 'dus pa bum
NK020(wa)001:2714: pa'i gzungs chab la khyab ste reg pa tsam gyis
NK020(wa)001:2715: mi mthun pa'i phyogs zhi bar byed pa /
NK020(wa)001:2716: dpal dang bde legs bskyed par byed pa'i bdud rtsi'i dag byed du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2717: bdag cag la sogs pa bsgrub bya'i lus dang 'khor dang yo byad thams cad la khyab ste /
NK020(wa)001:2718: nad dang gnod pa thams cad ni bsal /
NK020(wa)001:2719: lus sems kyi skyon thams cad dang ni bral te /
NK020(wa)001:2720: chos kyi snod rung du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2721: bdag cag rnams kyis 'phags pa rnams mngon sum pa
NK020(wa)001:2722: lta bur dmigs nas gzungs bzlas pas de bzhin gshegs
NK020(wa)001:2723: pa sras dang bcas pa rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK020(wa)001:2724: gyi sgo sna tshogs dang tshig 'bru mtha' yas pa
NK020(wa)001:2725: rtogs shing rnam par dag par byin gyis rlob par
NK020(wa)001:2726: gyur cig / ces bden tshig gis bsngosa nas /
NK020(wa)001:2727: 'phags pa rnams kyis gnang zhing phrin las mdzad par nges shes bskyed de /
NK020(wa)001:2728: ji ltar bsngosa pa bzhin mngon du gyur par dmigs nas /
NK020(wa)001:2729: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2731: de nas gtor ma btang zhing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:2732: 'das gtor dang cha gsum gyi gtor ma sngar bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK020(wa)001:2733: dbang chog ltar nyan thos kyi theg pa'i dbang rnams bskur ro //
NK020(wa)001:2735: mchod pa dri med yongs dag pa //
NK020(wa)001:2736: rnam mang rgya che thams cad dang //
NK020(wa)001:2737: so so'i mnga' thang rgya chen du //
NK020(wa)001:2740: ma rnyed yongs su sogs kyis nongs pa bshags /
NK020(wa)001:2742: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyis brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:2744: khyed kyi sogs kyis gshegs nas /
NK020(wa)001:2747: bsod nams grub pa gang yod pa //
NK020(wa)001:2748: des ni 'jig rten ma lus pas //
NK020(wa)001:2749: thub dbang go 'phang thob par shog /
NK020(wa)001:2750: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sman gcig pu //
NK020(wa)001:2751: bde ba thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK020(wa)001:2752: bstan pa rnyed dang bkur sti dang //
NK020(wa)001:2753: bcas te yun ring gnas gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2754: 'jig rten bde zhing lo legs dang //
NK020(wa)001:2756: dge legs thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK020(wa)001:2758: bla med bla ma'i thugs rje dang //
NK020(wa)001:2759: rgyal dang rgyal sras rang rgyal dang //
NK020(wa)001:2760: dgra bcom bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)001:2761: bsngo ba smon lam 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:2763: bcom ldan rnam par gzigs ni rgyal rigs gzi brjid can //
NK020(wa)001:2764: tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus na grong khyer gnyen drung du //
NK020(wa)001:2765: po ta la yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2766: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:2767: bde gshegs gtsug tor can ni rgyal rigs rdzu 'phrul can //
NK020(wa)001:2768: tshe lo bdun khri'i dus na ka ni'i grong khyer du //
NK020(wa)001:2769: pun+da ri ka'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2770: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:2771: rgyal ba thams cad skyob ni rgyal rigs blo gros can //
NK020(wa)001:2772: tshe lo drug khri'i dus na grong khyer mnyam yod du //
NK020(wa)001:2773: shing drung s+aa la'i drung du mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2774: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:2775: thub pa 'khor ba 'jig ni stobs ldan bram ze'i rigs //
NK020(wa)001:2776: tshe lo bzhi khri'i dus na grong khyer bde ldan du //
NK020(wa)001:2777: shi ri sha yi drung du mngon par sangs rgya pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2778: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir /
NK020(wa)001:2779: 'dren pa gser thub bslab pa mchog ldan bram ze'i rigs //
NK020(wa)001:2780: tshe lo sum khri'i dus na grong khyer mdzes ldan du //
NK020(wa)001:2781: u duma wa ra'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2782: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir /
NK020(wa)001:2783: skyob pa 'od srungs bram ze bla med yon tan can //
NK020(wa)001:2784: tshe lo nyi khri'i dus na w+aa r+aa na s+ai ru //
NK020(wa)001:2785: ny+aa gro ta'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2786: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir /
NK020(wa)001:2787: 'gro mgon sh+aakya thub pa rgyal rigs brtson 'grus can //
NK020(wa)001:2788: tshe lo brgya pa'i dus na ser skya'i grong khyer du //
NK020(wa)001:2789: a shwat+tha yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2790: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:2791: ces brjod cing me tog 'thor bas mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:2792: ngag tshig bden pas rtse gcig tu //
NK020(wa)001:2793: dbang bcu mnga' ba'i 'phags tshogs la //
NK020(wa)001:2794: mchod cing gsol na dam pa'i chos //
NK020(wa)001:2796: nyan thos theg pa'i sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:2800: bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:2801: shes rab rdo rjesa gzhig mdzad der //
NK020(wa)001:2802: phyag byas rang rgyal sgrub thabs bshad //
NK020(wa)001:2803: gsum pa rang rgyal gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:2804: gang du bya ba'i gzhi byi dor gyis dag par bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2805: tsan+dana la sogs pa dri'i chus chag chag btab pa la /
NK020(wa)001:2806: dkyil 'khor khyams dang rta babs spangs pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:2807: phyi rol du rin po che'i bye ma brdal ba'i
NK020(wa)001:2808: sa gzhi la phyi'i rten 'brel rgyu dang 'grel ba
NK020(wa)001:2809: mtshon byed / shing gi rtsa ba /
NK020(wa)001:2820: dpyid sogs dus bzhi'i kha dog gam ming ste drug /
NK020(wa)001:2821: nang gi rten 'brel ma rig pa rgan mo long
NK020(wa)001:2822: ba lta bu sogs rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi gzugs
NK020(wa)001:2823: bri / de'i mthar khams gsum mtshon byed pad rdor 'od phreng gsum gyis bskor ba /
NK020(wa)001:2824: dbus kyi lte ba ser po /
NK020(wa)001:2825: de'i phyir 'dab ma bcu gnyis mdzes tshon du bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2826: tshon lhag ma spyi ltar dang /
NK020(wa)001:2827: lha gnas rnams su sku rten /
NK020(wa)001:2829: de'i gtso bo dang go sa gcig par gsung rten
NK020(wa)001:2830: 'phags pa rten 'brel gyi mdo lta bu mdo'i glegs
NK020(wa)001:2831: bam dang / thugs rten du rten 'brel snying po
NK020(wa)001:2832: nang gzungs su bcug pa'i mchod rten rnams kyang dgod
NK020(wa)001:2833: bam dang / / dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor du mchod pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2834: mdun du bum pa chas zhugs spyi ltar las khyad
NK020(wa)001:2835: par keng rus kyi mtshan ma btags pa'i nang du
NK020(wa)001:2836: rin chen 'bru sman dri dang bcas pa'i chu klung
NK020(wa)001:2838: me long gi ngos la tsan+dana dkar po'i brdar phye
NK020(wa)001:2839: bsres pa'i khu bas rten 'brel snying po tshar bdun
NK020(wa)001:2840: bris te tshar re re la lan bdun bdun bzlas
NK020(wa)001:2842: gzhan yang rdzas dbang gi tsakli /
NK020(wa)001:2843: gtsang zhing bsod pa'i bza' baca'i 'das gtor dang /
NK020(wa)001:2844: cha gsum gtor ma rnams ci bder bsham /
NK020(wa)001:2845: rang gi mdun du spos snod /
NK020(wa)001:2847: rol mo sogs nyer mkho'i yo byad thams cad tshogs par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:2849: khrus dang dkon mchog gsum la phyag byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:2851: skyabs sems tshad med bzhi sgom pa'i rim pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2854: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK020(wa)001:2855: bla med dkon mchog rnam gsum la //
NK020(wa)001:2856: rtag tu bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:2859: 'gro ba sems can bsgral slad du //
NK020(wa)001:2860: bla na med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK020(wa)001:2861: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:2863: sems can thams cad bde ba dang zhes sogs kyang lan gsum /
NK020(wa)001:2864: de nas gang zag gi bdag dang chos bdag bzung
NK020(wa)001:2865: ba rang bzhin ma grub pa'i ngang la dar cig
NK020(wa)001:2866: bzhag / de'i ngang las chos thams cad rten 'brel sgyu ma lta bur bltas la /
NK020(wa)001:2867: skad cig gis bum pa'i steng du zla ba'i dkyil
NK020(wa)001:2868: 'khor nya yongs su gang ba la gnas pa'i rten
NK020(wa)001:2869: 'brel snying po'i sngags phreng kha dog dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:2870: de las 'od zer dkar po 'phros pas 'jig rten
NK020(wa)001:2871: gyi khams thams cad nas lha'i bdud rtsi'i rgyun rnams
NK020(wa)001:2872: bsdus te zhu ba'i chus bum pa gang bar dmigs
NK020(wa)001:2873: nas / lag g.yas bum pa la bkab pa'i rgya bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:2874: ye d+har+m+aa he tu pra b+ha w+aa he tun+te sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya ba data /
NK020(wa)001:2875: te shany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra ma n+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:2876: zhes pa brgya rtsa brgyad bzla /
NK020(wa)001:2877: yang sngags kyi 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba
NK020(wa)001:2878: sras bcas spyan drangs nas rten rnams la thim par
NK020(wa)001:2879: bsam / mthar zla dkyil sngags phreng dang bcas pa'ang bum chu la thim par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2880: des rten dang dkyil 'khor la khrus byas pa'i chu slar yang bum par blugs so //
NK020(wa)001:2881: de nas rten 'brel snying po dang /
NK020(wa)001:2882: swa b+h+aa wa'i sngags brjod cing bum chu gtor bas /
NK020(wa)001:2883: gnas dang mchod rdzas la sogs pa'i nyes skyon thams
NK020(wa)001:2884: cad sbyangs nas dag cing bzang ba phun sum tshogs
NK020(wa)001:2887: de nas dkyil 'khor bskyed cing byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2888: mdun bskyed kyi gzhis mtshon pa'i gzung ba phra rags
NK020(wa)001:2889: dang 'dzin pa rags pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK020(wa)001:2890: rang bzhin ma grub pa'i ngang la dar cig bzhag
NK020(wa)001:2892: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2893: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:2894: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' thang chen po dang /
NK020(wa)001:2895: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK020(wa)001:2896: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa sngon byang chub
NK020(wa)001:2897: kyi spyad pa spyod pa'i tshe sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK020(wa)001:2898: yongs su sbyangs pa'i bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2899: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs kyis /
NK020(wa)001:2900: deng 'dir de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:2901: 'phags pa chos skyong ba thams cad mchod pa'i tshogs
NK020(wa)001:2902: sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor 'di dag bcom
NK020(wa)001:2903: ldan 'das 'od dpag tu med pa'i zhing gi bkod
NK020(wa)001:2904: pa'i yon tan lta bu dang ldan par gyur te
NK020(wa)001:2905: / phyi nang gi rten 'brel 'byung ldog gi 'gros
NK020(wa)001:2906: kyis 'khor zhing 'gag pa'i rgyu 'bras kyi mtshan mas
NK020(wa)001:2907: yongs su bskor ba'i sa gzhi rin po che sna
NK020(wa)001:2908: tshogs kyi rang bzhin lag mthil ltar mnyam pa'i gzhi
NK020(wa)001:2909: / la / bkod pa thams cad las 'phags pa
NK020(wa)001:2910: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bkod pa la brten pa'i pho
NK020(wa)001:2911: brang rin po che sna bdun las grub pa'i khang
NK020(wa)001:2912: / la / ba brtsegs pa / gru bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:2917: shin tu rnam par phye bas mdzes par byas pa /
NK020(wa)001:2921: them skas bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:2922: dkyil 'khor gyi nang gi dbus su rin po che'i khri pad+ma zla ba dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:2924: phyi bskor gyi pad 'dab bcu gnyis yongs su rgyas
NK020(wa)001:2925: pa'i steng so sor yang zla ba'i gdan re re
NK020(wa)001:2926: dang / sgo bzhir rin po che'i gdan rnams te /
NK020(wa)001:2927: 'phags pa rnams gdan 'dzom pa'i bzhugs gnas so so'i
NK020(wa)001:2928: smon lam khyad par can dang mnga' thang dang 'tshams
NK020(wa)001:2929: par grub pa mdzes pa sha stag 'byung bar gyur
NK020(wa)001:2932: de nas mchod pa byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:2933: phyi nang kun tu cha ris dang 'tshams par lha dang mi'i yo byad dam pa kha dog dang /
NK020(wa)001:2936: reg pa dang ldan pa yid du 'ong pa /
NK020(wa)001:2937: gya nom pa'i zhal zas dang /
NK020(wa)001:2940: rol mo la sogs pa phul du phyin pa sna tshogs pa /
NK020(wa)001:2941: phung po gsum pa'i mdo dang /
NK020(wa)001:2942: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam las byung ba'i mchod
NK020(wa)001:2943: pa'i sprin rgya mtsho thams cad kyis rgyas par gang
NK020(wa)001:2944: zhing rgyan klubs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2946: de bzhin du byin gyis brlabs shing bzhes te longs spyod par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:2950: spos btul zhing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:2953: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK020(wa)001:2954: dkon mchog bla med rin chen gsum //
NK020(wa)001:2956: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK020(wa)001:2957: thugs rjes dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2960: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i
NK020(wa)001:2961: dbang po 'khor 'phags pa rang sangs rgyas kyi tshogs
NK020(wa)001:2962: / phyi bzhin 'brang ba rgyal po chen po sde
NK020(wa)001:2963: bzhi dang bcas pa so so'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mthus
NK020(wa)001:2964: byon nas rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs par gyur
NK020(wa)001:2965: / pa ni / dbus su bcom ldan 'das de
NK020(wa)001:2966: bzhin gshegs pa dpal rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa sku
NK020(wa)001:2967: mdog gser btso ma lta bu /
NK020(wa)001:2968: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK020(wa)001:2969: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:2971: g.yon mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:2972: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:2973: de'i g.yas su rang rgyal bse ru lta bu dang /
NK020(wa)001:2974: g.yon na tshogs spyod gnyis thal mo sbyar ba /
NK020(wa)001:2975: mtha' bskor yi 'dab ma bcu gnyis la mdun nas g.yas bskor du rang rgyal bcu gnyis te /
NK020(wa)001:2977: snang ba brtsegs pa rin po che /
NK020(wa)001:2978: dpa' bo 'dul pa rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK020(wa)001:2979: nyon mongs gdung sel bsil yab /
NK020(wa)001:2980: shes rab mgyogs chen zla tshes /
NK020(wa)001:2984: bse ru lta bu mnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:2985: ri rgyal rin po che'i snye ma /
NK020(wa)001:2986: seng ge lta bu rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:2987: yid myur rnga yab bsnams pa /
NK020(wa)001:2988: thams cad kyang dge slong dgra bcom pa dbang po
NK020(wa)001:2989: dul ba'i cha lugs can gtsug tor cung zad dang
NK020(wa)001:2990: bcas pa / shar sgor yul 'khor srung dkar po pi wam /
NK020(wa)001:2991: lho sgor 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:2992: nub sgor mig mi bzang dmar po sbrul zhags dang mchod rten /
NK020(wa)001:2993: byang sgor rnam thos sras ser po yid bzhin gyi rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:2994: thams cad kyang rang rang gi 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas te bzhugs par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:2996: gnas mchog gzhal yas pho brang 'dir //
NK020(wa)001:2997: rin chen pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK020(wa)001:2998: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:2999: ye d+har+m+aa zhes pas gdan la bzhugs su gsol lo //
NK020(wa)001:3000: de nas me long gi nang du dkyil 'khor gyi
NK020(wa)001:3001: gzugs brnyan 'char du bcug la bum pa'i chus khrus
NK020(wa)001:3004: lha rdzas dam pa'i khrus chab 'di //
NK020(wa)001:3005: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:3007: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK020(wa)001:3008: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3009: ye d+har+m+aa zhes khrus gsol ba'i chu slar yang bum par blugs /
NK020(wa)001:3010: de nas ras mchog gis sku 'phyi bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:3012: lha rdzas dam pa'i sku phyis 'di //
NK020(wa)001:3019: rten cing lha rdzas dam pa'i na bza' 'di //
NK020(wa)001:3026: rgyas par dpang skong ltar bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3027: 'dir zor yang ba'i dbang du byas nas 'di skad ces /
NK020(wa)001:3028: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK020(wa)001:3029: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang
NK020(wa)001:3033: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo bsgyur ba /
NK020(wa)001:3035: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa mnyam med sh+aakya thub pa /
NK020(wa)001:3036: 'khor 'phags pa rang sangs rgyas kyi dge 'dun gyi
NK020(wa)001:3037: tshogs dang bcas pa'i zhabs la dus thams cad du
NK020(wa)001:3040: dkon mchog bla med rin chen gsum //
NK020(wa)001:3041: sku ni rten cing 'brel ba'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:3043: thugs ni rten 'brel thams cad mkhyen //
NK020(wa)001:3044: sku gsung thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3045: khams gsum pa yi 'gro kun gyi //
NK020(wa)001:3046: ngan song thams cad sbyong mdzad cing //
NK020(wa)001:3047: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:3049: rten 'brel don la brten gnas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3050: 'phags pa rang rgyal bcu gnyis ni //
NK020(wa)001:3051: 'byung dang ldog la rab bzhugs pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3052: rang rgyal gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3053: zab mo rten 'brel legs goms pas //
NK020(wa)001:3054: rang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni //
NK020(wa)001:3055: brten med tshul gyis thugs chud pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3057: zab cing rgya che gzigs pa po //
NK020(wa)001:3059: mig mi bzang dang rnam thos sras //
NK020(wa)001:3060: rgyal chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3061: phyag byar 'os pa thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:3065: lha rdzas dam pa'i yon chab 'di //
NK020(wa)001:3066: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:3068: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK020(wa)001:3069: thugs rje dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3071: ma h+aa sh+ra ma nah ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:3072: de bzhin du yon chab kyi gnas su //
NK020(wa)001:3078: rol mo rnams dang ar+g+ham gyi gnas su /
NK020(wa)001:3084: shap+da zhes pa rnams bcug nas dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:3085: de nas bshags pa la sogs pa yan lag phyi ma lnga ni /
NK020(wa)001:3087: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3088: bdag ni mi shes gti mug pas //
NK020(wa)001:3089: rang bzhin kha na ma tho'am //
NK020(wa)001:3090: bcas pa'i sdig pa gang bgyis pa //
NK020(wa)001:3091: de dag thams cad bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:3092: 'phags dang so so skye bo yi //
NK020(wa)001:3093: dge tshogs kun la rjes yi rang //
NK020(wa)001:3094: 'gro ba'i bsam pa ji bzhin du //
NK020(wa)001:3095: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK020(wa)001:3096: 'khor ba ji srid gnas kyi bar //
NK020(wa)001:3098: bdag gis dge ba gang bsags pa //
NK020(wa)001:3099: de kun byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK020(wa)001:3100: de nas gzungs bzla ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:3101: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:3102: de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad kyi mthu dang byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:3103: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs dang /
NK020(wa)001:3104: 'phags pa sku gsung thugs kyi spyod pa ma dag
NK020(wa)001:3105: pa mi mnga' ba rnams kyi thugs nges pa'i bden
NK020(wa)001:3106: pas mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil
NK020(wa)001:3107: 'dir ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:3108: 'khor 'phags pa rang sangs rgyas kyi dge 'dun gyi
NK020(wa)001:3109: tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad gdan 'dzom pa chen
NK020(wa)001:3110: po mdzad de / mchod pa bzhes shing /
NK020(wa)001:3111: gzungs sngags bzlas pa tshul bzhin du 'grub par byin gyis rlob par mdzad de /
NK020(wa)001:3112: bdag sogs 'gro ba mang po'i don dpag tu med pa mdzad par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3113: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyis thugs kar zla
NK020(wa)001:3114: ba'i dkyil 'khor nya gang ba la gnas pa'i rten
NK020(wa)001:3115: 'brel snying po'i sngags phreng kha dog dkar po las
NK020(wa)001:3116: 'od zer 'phros pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK020(wa)001:3117: khyab / des 'phags pa thams cad sems can gyi don mdzad par bskul zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3118: ngan song gi gnas thams cad kyang sbyangs te /
NK020(wa)001:3119: sems can thams cad mtho ris kyi rten phun sum
NK020(wa)001:3120: tshogs pa thob nas ma rig pa sogs rten cing
NK020(wa)001:3121: 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis lugs ldog tu 'gags
NK020(wa)001:3122: pa'i rnam grol gyi go 'phang la myur du 'jug
NK020(wa)001:3123: par gyur cig / 'od zer des bdag cag rnams
NK020(wa)001:3124: la khyab pas 'gro don dpag med sgrub nus pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3125: mthu thob ste 'phags pa'i tshogs rnams dang sku gsung
NK020(wa)001:3127: yang 'od zer de dag gcig tu 'dus pa bum
NK020(wa)001:3128: pa'i gzungs chab la khyab ste reg pa tsam gyis
NK020(wa)001:3129: mi mthun pa'i phyogs zhi bar byed pa /
NK020(wa)001:3130: dpal dang bde legs bskyed par byed pa'i bdud rtsi'i dag byed du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3131: bdag cag la sogs pa bsgrub bya'i lus dang 'khor dang longs spyod thams cad la khyab ste /
NK020(wa)001:3132: nad dang gnod pa thams cad ni bsal /
NK020(wa)001:3133: lus sems kyi skyon thams cad ni bral ste /
NK020(wa)001:3134: chos kyi snod rung du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3135: bdag cag rnams kyis 'phags pa rnams mngon sum pa
NK020(wa)001:3136: lta bur dmigs nas gzungs bzlas pas de bzhin gshegs
NK020(wa)001:3137: pa sras dang bcas pa rnams kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK020(wa)001:3138: gyi sgo sna tshogs dang tshig 'bru mtha' yas pa
NK020(wa)001:3139: rtogs shing rnam par dag par byin gyis rlob par
NK020(wa)001:3140: gyur cig / ces bden pa'i tshig gis bsngosa nas /
NK020(wa)001:3141: 'phags pa rnams kyis gnang zhing phrin las mdzad par nges shes bskyed de /
NK020(wa)001:3142: ji ltar bsngosa pa bzhin mngon du gyur par dmigs nas /
NK020(wa)001:3143: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
