NK020(wa)001:3145: ye d+har+m+aa sogs rten 'brel snying po'ang ci rigs pa bazla'o //
NK020(wa)001:3146: de nas dkyil 'khor la brtan bzhugs bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:3148: rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:3149: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK020(wa)001:3150: ji srid cho ga ma grub bar //
NK020(wa)001:3151: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3152: ye d+har+m+aa me tog 'thor bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:3153: rgyal ba dgra rgyal bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)001:3154: bden pa gsungs pa de la sdig med cing //
NK020(wa)001:3155: lhar bcas lha min gyis rtag mchod pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:3156: bden pa de yis deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:3157: ye d+har+m+aa dam chos bdud rtsi thams cad mkhyen pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:3158: zhal nas gsungs pa bsil ba'i ro 'di yis //
NK020(wa)001:3159: nyon mongs 'bar ba'i me yis gdungs gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3160: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal rtag tu zhi byed shog /
NK020(wa)001:3161: ye d+har+m+aa 'byung po gang dag 'dir ni lhags gyur tam //
NK020(wa)001:3162: sa'am 'on te bar snang 'khod kyang rung //
NK020(wa)001:3163: skye dgu rnams la rtag tu byams byed cing //
NK020(wa)001:3164: nyin dang mtshan du chos la spyod par shog /
NK020(wa)001:3165: ye d+har+m+aa de nas gtor ma btang zhing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:3166: 'das gtor dang cha gsum gtor ma sngar bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK020(wa)001:3167: dbang chog ltar rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK020(wa)001:3170: lha rdzas dam pa'i mchod tshogs kun //
NK020(wa)001:3171: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:3172: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3174: ma rnyed yongs su sogs kyis nongs pa bshags /
NK020(wa)001:3175: rten yod na sngar gyi brtan bzhugs kyi rkang pa bzhi pa nyid /
NK020(wa)001:3176: ji srid gzugs brnyan gnas kyi bar //
NK020(wa)001:3177: zhes barjesa pas brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:3179: khyed kyi sems can sogs kyis gshegs nas /
NK020(wa)001:3182: bsod nams grub pa gang yod pa //
NK020(wa)001:3183: des ni 'jig rten ma lus pas //
NK020(wa)001:3184: thub dbang go 'phang thob par shog /
NK020(wa)001:3185: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sman gcig pu //
NK020(wa)001:3188: bla med bla ma'i thugs rje dang //
NK020(wa)001:3189: rgyal dang rgyal sras rang rgyal dang //
NK020(wa)001:3190: dgra bcom bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)001:3191: bsngo ba smon lam 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:3193: shin tu brgal dka' 'khor ba'i mtsho las brgal //
NK020(wa)001:3194: bsod nams ye shes dpag yas tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK020(wa)001:3195: 'gro ba kun gyi gnyen gcig de bzhin gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:3196: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:3197: skye rga na 'chi mtha' dag rtag tu spangs //
NK020(wa)001:3198: ma rig mun pa drung 'joms sgron me'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:3199: dmigs pa'i mtha' spangs lam gyi bde 'gror zhugs /
NK020(wa)001:3201: rang don spangs shing gzhan don lhur len pa //
NK020(wa)001:3202: 'dod pa'i yon tan lta ba rgyang bsrings te /
NK020(wa)001:3203: dad dang brtson 'grus grogs mchog byang chub sems //
NK020(wa)001:3205: snyigs dus smon lam dbang gis sku sprul nas //
NK020(wa)001:3206: shin tu nyon mongs gdul dka' 'dul mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:3207: thabs mkhas thugs rje che mnga' rkang gnyis gtso //
NK020(wa)001:3209: ces me tog 'thor zhing rol mo'i sgra bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:3210: man ngag bral bas chog gzhung dang //
NK020(wa)001:3211: rab gnas ma phyed de lta na'ang //
NK020(wa)001:3212: dbang shed chos la btsongs pa'i mun //
NK020(wa)001:3214: rang rgyal theg pa'i sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:3217: rnam 'gyur sgrib gnyis bag chags dpung //
NK020(wa)001:3218: thogs med ye shes rdo rje yis //
NK020(wa)001:3219: mthar mdzad mgon po der btud nas //
NK020(wa)001:3220: byang sems theg pa'i sgrub thabs bshad //
NK020(wa)001:3221: bzhi pa byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:3222: gang du bya ba'i gzhir dri bzang po dang ba byung gi chus chag chag btab la /
NK020(wa)001:3223: dkyil 'khor khyams dang rta babs spangs pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:3224: mda' yab kyi phyi rol tu rin po che'i bye
NK020(wa)001:3225: ma brdal ba'i sa gzhi la dpag bsam gyi shing
NK020(wa)001:3226: dang khrus rdzing sogs bde ba can gyi zhing bkod
NK020(wa)001:3227: lta bus brgyan pa'i mthar rdo ra dang 'od phreng
NK020(wa)001:3228: gis bskor ba / dbus kyi lte ba ser po /
NK020(wa)001:3229: de'i mthar nang du pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi dang /
NK020(wa)001:3230: phyir 'dab ma bcu pa rnams mdzes tshon dang /
NK020(wa)001:3231: tshon lhag ma spyi ltar bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3232: lha gnas rnams su sku rten lha so so'i 'bur sku'am tsakli dang /
NK020(wa)001:3233: gtso bo'i sku dang mnyam du gsung rten sher snying gi glegs bam dang /
NK020(wa)001:3234: thugs rten de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten /
NK020(wa)001:3235: rin chen 'bru sman dri bzang po dang bcas pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3236: chus rten byin can la khrus byas pas bkang ba'i
NK020(wa)001:3237: bum pa chas su bcug pas dkyil 'khor gyi mdun
NK020(wa)001:3239: rdzas dbang gi tsakli rnams kyang ci bder bsham /
NK020(wa)001:3240: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' ar+g+ham la sogs pa'i mchod pa ci 'byor pas bskor /
NK020(wa)001:3242: cha gsum gtor ma'ang ci bder bsgrig /
NK020(wa)001:3243: rang gi mdun du rdor dril spos snod 'thor nas sogs yo byad thams cad tshang bar 'du bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:3246: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i bdag nyid phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba
NK020(wa)001:3247: sras dang bcas pa mkha' khyab tu bzhugs par mos
NK020(wa)001:3248: la phyag byas nas stan la 'dug ste /
NK020(wa)001:3249: skyabs sems tshad med bzhi sgom pa'i rim pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3251: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK020(wa)001:3252: byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK020(wa)001:3253: rtag par bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:3255: shes rab snying rje dang bcas pas //
NK020(wa)001:3256: brtson pas sems can don du bdag /
NK020(wa)001:3257: sangs rgyas mdun du gnas bgyis nas //
NK020(wa)001:3258: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:3260: sems can thams cad bde ba dang zhes sogs kyang lan gsum mo //
NK020(wa)001:3261: de nas byang chub kyi sems khyad par can sgom pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3262: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs pa
NK020(wa)001:3263: stong nyid spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'o
NK020(wa)001:3264: // zhes de'i ngang la dar cig mnyam par bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:3266: chos thams cad don dam par spros pa dang bral ba yin pa la /
NK020(wa)001:3267: 'phags pa rnams kyis de nyid thugs su chud pas
NK020(wa)001:3268: sku gsung thugs nam mkha' dang 'dra bar gyur te
NK020(wa)001:3270: mthu dang byin rlabs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i go 'phang brnyes par gyur na /
NK020(wa)001:3271: kye ma sems can 'di dag ni chos kyi de
NK020(wa)001:3272: kho na nyid ma rtogs te rmongs pas nyon mongs
NK020(wa)001:3273: pa dang sdug bsngal mang pos gzir zhing nyam thag
NK020(wa)001:3274: pa'i gnas su lhung bar gyur la /
NK020(wa)001:3275: sems can thams cad kyang bdag gi tshe rabs kyi
NK020(wa)001:3276: gnyen bshes drin can gyi 'khor lo sha stag yin
NK020(wa)001:3277: na / 'di dag ji ltar sdug bsngal las ni gdon /
NK020(wa)001:3278: bde ba la ni 'god par bya /
NK020(wa)001:3279: de'i ched du phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK020(wa)001:3280: sems dpa' chen po'i tshogs thams cad gdan 'dzom par
NK020(wa)001:3281: spyan drangs la / mthu dang dpung gnyen du gsol te /
NK020(wa)001:3282: deng ni 'phags pa'i mthu dang byin rlabs kyis 'gro
NK020(wa)001:3283: ba thams cad la phan pa bsgrub par bya la
NK020(wa)001:3284: / phyis ni bdag nyid gcig pus gzhan la ltos
NK020(wa)001:3285: pa med par thabs la mkhas pa'i sgo sna tshogs
NK020(wa)001:3286: nas sems can thams cad la phan pa dang bde
NK020(wa)001:3287: ba bla na med pa yang dag par bsgrub par
NK020(wa)001:3288: / bya'o // snyam du byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems bskyed do //
NK020(wa)001:3289: de nas dkyil 'khor bskyed cing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3290: mdun bskyed kyi gzhi mi dmigs pa stong nyid spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang las /
NK020(wa)001:3291: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:3292: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi
NK020(wa)001:3293: byin gyis brlabs dang tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3295: ston pa bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
NK020(wa)001:3296: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya
NK020(wa)001:3297: thub pa la sogs te phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs
NK020(wa)001:3298: pa thams cad kyis sngon byang chub sems dpa'i spyad
NK020(wa)001:3299: pa spyod pa'i tshe sems can thams cad kyi don
NK020(wa)001:3300: du sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su sbyangs pa'i bden
NK020(wa)001:3301: pa dang / chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing
NK020(wa)001:3302: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs kyis deng 'dir de
NK020(wa)001:3303: bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:3304: 'phags pa chos skyong ba thams cad gdan 'dzom pa'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK020(wa)001:3305: mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba 'di rnams ji ltar sangs
NK020(wa)001:3306: rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' de dag gi sngon
NK020(wa)001:3307: gyi smon lam khyad par can gyis bsgrubs pa'i sangs
NK020(wa)001:3308: rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:3309: bcom ldan 'das 'od dpag tu med pa'i zhing gi
NK020(wa)001:3310: bkod pa'i yon tan lta bu dang ldan par gyur
NK020(wa)001:3311: te / sa gzhi rin po che sna tshogs kyi rang bzhin lag mthil ltar mnyam pa la /
NK020(wa)001:3312: rin po che'i dpag bsam gyi ljon shing tshar du
NK020(wa)001:3313: dngar ba la bkra shis pa'i bya snyan par sgrog
NK020(wa)001:3315: de dag kyang gser gyi tha gus bres pa las
NK020(wa)001:3316: rin po che sna tshogs pa dpyangs shing dril bu
NK020(wa)001:3317: dang g.yer kha chos kyi sgra snyan par 'khrol bas
NK020(wa)001:3318: mdzes pa / yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i mtsho
NK020(wa)001:3319: dang rdzing bu la chu bya dang lha mo sna
NK020(wa)001:3321: lha'i me tog sna tshogs dang rin po che'i phye
NK020(wa)001:3322: ma gcal du bkram pa la sogs pa phun sum
NK020(wa)001:3323: tshogs pa'i rgyan thams cad kyis rnam par brgyan pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3324: zhing khams yongs su dag pa'i dbus su //
NK020(wa)001:3325: bkod pa thams cad las 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs
NK020(wa)001:3326: pa'i bkod pa la brten pa'i pho brang rin po
NK020(wa)001:3327: che sna bdun las grub pa'i khang pa brtsegs pa
NK020(wa)001:3333: shin tu rnam par phye bas mdzes par byas pa /
NK020(wa)001:3337: them skas bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:3339: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun dang ldan pa'i gzhal med khang chen po /
NK020(wa)001:3340: yon tan mtha' yas pa'i rgyan gyis yongs su spras
NK020(wa)001:3341: pa'i dbus su seng ges btegs pa'i rin po che'i
NK020(wa)001:3342: khri pad zla brtsegs pa'i gdan dang /
NK020(wa)001:3343: mtha' bskor gyi pad 'dab bzhi dang bcu rnams kyi
NK020(wa)001:3344: steng du'ang pad+ma dang zla ba rgyas pa'i gdan re
NK020(wa)001:3345: re / sgo bzhir rin po che'i gdan la sogs
NK020(wa)001:3346: pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa sogs phyogs bcu'i
NK020(wa)001:3349: 'phags pa dam pa'i chos skyong ba thams cad gdan 'dzom pa'i bzhugs gnas /
NK020(wa)001:3350: 'phags pa so so'i smon lam khyad par can dang /
NK020(wa)001:3351: mnga' thang dang 'tshams par grub pa mdzes pa sha stag 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3353: de nas mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3354: phyi nang kun tu yang cha rigs dang 'tshams par lha dang mi'i yo byad dam pa /
NK020(wa)001:3358: reg pa dang ldan pa yid du 'ong ba /
NK020(wa)001:3359: gya nom pa'i zhal zas dang /
NK020(wa)001:3362: rol mo la sogs pa phul du phyin pa sna tshogs pa phung po gsum pa'i mdo dang /
NK020(wa)001:3363: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam las byung ba'i mchod
NK020(wa)001:3364: pa'i sprin rgya mtsho thams cad kyis rgyas par gang
NK020(wa)001:3365: zhing rgyan klubs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3366: 'phags pa thams cad kyang gdan 'dzom nas /
NK020(wa)001:3367: de bzhin du byin gyis brlabs shing bzhes te longs spyod par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3370: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:3371: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra s+aa ra pra mrda ne /
NK020(wa)001:3372: ta th+aa ga ta ya ar+ha te sa myak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:3378: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta badz+re /
NK020(wa)001:3379: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+do pa sam kra ma na
NK020(wa)001:3380: badz+ra sarba karma +aa wa ra na bi sho d+ha
NK020(wa)001:3384: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:3385: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:3386: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' thang chen po dang /
NK020(wa)001:3387: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs kyis de bzhin du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3389: de nas snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3390: spos btul zhing me tog blangs la thal mo sbyar te /
NK020(wa)001:3391: ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la sogs
NK020(wa)001:3392: pa phyogs bcu na dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i de
NK020(wa)001:3393: bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs
NK020(wa)001:3395: de dag gis legs par gsungs pa /
NK020(wa)001:3397: legs par thugs su chud pa'i dam pa'i chos dkon
NK020(wa)001:3398: mchog gi ngo bo yum chen mo shes rab kyi
NK020(wa)001:3399: pha rol tu phyin ma dang /
NK020(wa)001:3400: byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK020(wa)001:3402: sh+aa ri'i bu la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa'i
NK020(wa)001:3403: dge 'dun dang bcas pa thams cad dgongs su gsol
NK020(wa)001:3404: / thabs mkhas shing thugs rje chen po dang /
NK020(wa)001:3405: mthu dang byin gyis brlabs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3406: 'gro ba'i don du smon lam khyad par can mdzad pa las glengs te /
NK020(wa)001:3407: bdag sogs 'gro ba mang po bskyab pa'i slad du /
NK020(wa)001:3408: deng mgon skyabs dang dpung gnyen du spyan 'dren zhing mchi na /
NK020(wa)001:3409: mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:3410: 'dir gshegs shing gdan 'dzom pa chen po mdzad de
NK020(wa)001:3411: / byin gyis brlab par ci gnang zhes dang /
NK020(wa)001:3413: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te /
NK020(wa)001:3414: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum /
NK020(wa)001:3415: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po nas /
NK020(wa)001:3417: thugs rje'i dbang gis dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:3420: spos thogs shing rol mo 'khrol ba dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:3421: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' 'khor dang bcas pa ji snyed bzhugs pa thams cad /
NK020(wa)001:3422: chos kyi dbyings dang rigs thams cad na bzhugs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3423: de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad
NK020(wa)001:3425: bdag sogs sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams spel ba'i slad du /
NK020(wa)001:3426: deng rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa spyan drangs pa'i gnas 'dir /
NK020(wa)001:3427: mchod par 'os pa'i bde bar sbyar ba thams cad kyis bstabs shing spyan 'dren gyis /
NK020(wa)001:3428: mthu bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pas rnam par 'phrul pa mdzad de /
NK020(wa)001:3429: chos kyi dbyings kun tu 'gro ba'i tshul gyis gshegs par gsol lo //
NK020(wa)001:3430: phyogs dus kun nas skyabs gsum bka' sdod bcas //
NK020(wa)001:3431: nyon mongs 'gro la mkhyen brtses rab dgongs te //
NK020(wa)001:3432: dpag med zhing nas thogs med rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK020(wa)001:3433: 'dir gshegs mchod sprin rgya mtsho'i dbus bzhugs gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3434: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK020(wa)001:3435: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha //
NK020(wa)001:3436: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3437: bcom ldan 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3438: chos nyid dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyang //
NK020(wa)001:3439: gzhi dang lam dang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen //
NK020(wa)001:3440: bdag med stong pa don dam yang dag mtha' //
NK020(wa)001:3441: yum chen pha rol phyin ma gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3442: shar phyogs rin chen bkod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK020(wa)001:3443: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3444: lho phyogs mya ngan med pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK020(wa)001:3445: bde gshegs mya ngan med pa gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3446: nub phyogs bde dang ldan pa'i bde gshegs rin chen
NK020(wa)001:3447: 'od 'phro byang phyogs rgyal ba can gyi bde gshegs
NK020(wa)001:3448: rgyal ba'i dbang po shar lho snying po byang chub
NK020(wa)001:3449: pad+mo dam pa'i dpal mnga' lho nub rdul tshogs bral
NK020(wa)001:3450: ba'i bde gshegs nyi ma snang ba nub byang dbang
NK020(wa)001:3451: du gyur pa'i bde gshegs gdugs mchog dam pa byang
NK020(wa)001:3452: shar ting 'dzin brgyan pa'i ting 'dzin glang po dpal
NK020(wa)001:3453: mnga' 'og phyogs pad+ma can gyi zhing bde gshegs pad+mo'i
NK020(wa)001:3454: dpal nyid steng phyogs 'jig rten mdangs dag'i zhing khams
NK020(wa)001:3455: nas // bde gshegs dga' ba'i dpal can gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3456: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:3458: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams rnams par dag pa nas sangs
NK020(wa)001:3459: rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs thams cad rang
NK020(wa)001:3460: rang gi 'khor dpag tu med pa dang bcas te
NK020(wa)001:3461: so so'i 'phrul gyi mthus byon nas rang rang gi
NK020(wa)001:3463: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du bcom
NK020(wa)001:3464: ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dpal rgyal ba sh+aakya
NK020(wa)001:3465: thub pa sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu /
NK020(wa)001:3466: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK020(wa)001:3467: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:3469: g.yon mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:3470: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:3471: 'dab ma bzhi'i shar du yum chen mo gser mdog phyag dang po gnyis mnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:3472: 'og ma gnyis chos 'chad dang glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:3473: lhor phyag na rdo rje sngon po rdo rje dang pad+ma /
NK020(wa)001:3474: nub tu sh+aa ri'i bu ser skya 'khar bsil dang lhung bzed /
NK020(wa)001:3475: byang du spyan ras gzigs dkar po pad+ma dang pusti /
NK020(wa)001:3476: sh+aa ri'i bu dge slong pus btsugs dang /
NK020(wa)001:3477: gzhan gsum dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad
NK020(wa)001:3478: kyis brgyan cing yum rdor skyil dang gzhan gnyis sems
NK020(wa)001:3480: 'dab ma bcu'i shar stod du sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal sngo skya bum pa dang g.yon dkur brten /
NK020(wa)001:3481: shar du dkon mchog 'byung gnas dkar po mchog sbyin gyis rin po che /
NK020(wa)001:3482: lhor mya ngan med pa'i dpal sngon po 'khor lo /
NK020(wa)001:3483: nub tu rin chen 'od 'phro dkar po mche ba /
NK020(wa)001:3484: byang du rgyal ba'i dbang po ljang gu pad+ma /
NK020(wa)001:3485: shar lhor pad+mo dam pa'i dpal dkar po pad+ma /
NK020(wa)001:3486: lho nub tu nyi ma snang ba'i dpal dam pa dmar smug nyi ma /
NK020(wa)001:3487: nub byang du gdugs chen dam pa'i dpal ljang gu sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:3488: byang shar du ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal ser po chos 'chad dang g.yon gos 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:3489: nub smad du pad+mo'i dpal ser po pad+ma dang g.yon lte bar thal mo phyir ston pa /
NK020(wa)001:3490: phyag g.yon dmigs bsal med pa rnams mnyam bzhag mdzad
NK020(wa)001:3491: cing thams cad kyang mchog gi sprul sku tshangs par
NK020(wa)001:3492: spyod pa'i cha byad can rdo rje'i skyil krung gis
NK020(wa)001:3493: bzhugs pa ste rtsa ba'i lha'o //
NK020(wa)001:3494: gzhan yang mgron thabs kyi lha gtso bo dang phyogs
NK020(wa)001:3495: bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi mtha' bskor du pad 'dab
NK020(wa)001:3496: brgyad pa re re'i gdan la /
NK020(wa)001:3497: gtso ba'i phyogs bzhir de bzhin gshegs pa bzhi dang mtshams bzhir yum bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:3498: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa bcu'i phyogs bzhir byang sems bzhi bzhi dang /
NK020(wa)001:3499: mtshams bzhir yum bzhi bzhi la sogs te sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:3500: dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs mtha' yas pa'i 'khor
NK020(wa)001:3502: de dag gi phyi rol tu mchod pa'i lha mo
NK020(wa)001:3503: brgyad gzhan yang phyogs skyong ba bcu la sogs te
NK020(wa)001:3504: dkar po la dga' ba'i lha rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:3505: sgo bzhir rgyal po chen po bzhi rnams rang rang gi 'khor dang bcas te bzhugs par mos la /
NK020(wa)001:3506: bcom ldan 'khor bcas byon pa legs //
NK020(wa)001:3507: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK020(wa)001:3508: bdag gi mchod yon 'di bzhes la //
NK020(wa)001:3509: mchod pas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:3510: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ga ga na sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:3512: mya ngan mi 'da' thugs rje'i dang //
NK020(wa)001:3513: nyon mongs mi spong gos pa med //
NK020(wa)001:3514: ma chags rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK020(wa)001:3515: mnyam nyid ngang du bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3516: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK020(wa)001:3517: thugs rjes dgongs pa'i phrin las rnams //
NK020(wa)001:3518: 'gro don rdzogs mdzad de bzhin du //
NK020(wa)001:3519: yun ring brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3520: pad+ma +aa sa na tish+tha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:3523: khyed kyi rang bzhin yongs dag pas //
NK020(wa)001:3524: sred sogs 'ching ba mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)001:3525: bdag cag sgrib pa sbyang slad du //
NK020(wa)001:3526: gtsang ma chab kyis sku khrus gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3527: sarba de wa ta artsi ta a mri ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:3528: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang de sras la //
NK020(wa)001:3529: rin chen bum pa mang po spos kyi chus //
NK020(wa)001:3530: yid 'ong legs par bkang ba glu dang ni //
NK020(wa)001:3531: rol mor bcas pa du mas sku khrus gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3533: zhes khrus gsol ba'i chu slar yang bum par blug go //
NK020(wa)001:3534: de dag sku la mtshungs pa med pa'i gos //
NK020(wa)001:3535: gtsang la dri rab bgos pas sku phyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:3536: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aas sku phyis la /
NK020(wa)001:3537: de nas de la kha dog legs bsgyur ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:3538: na bza' shin tu dri zhim dam pa 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:3539: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra w+aa sa se pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aas gos zung dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:3540: de nas phyag bya ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:3541: lus zhing gi rdul snyed du sprul nas gus pas phyag byas par mos te /
NK020(wa)001:3542: rgyas par na thar pa chen po dang rtogs pa chen po'i mdo las 'byung ba gang rung ngam /
NK020(wa)001:3543: bsdu na dpang skong ltar bya bar gsungs pa'ang 'grub dka' bas /
NK020(wa)001:3544: 'dir shin tu bsdus pa'i dbang du byas te 'di skad ces /
NK020(wa)001:3545: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK020(wa)001:3546: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rig pa dang
NK020(wa)001:3550: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo bsgyur ba /
NK020(wa)001:3552: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa mnyam med sh+aakya
NK020(wa)001:3553: thub pa la sogs pa phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi
NK020(wa)001:3554: khams mtha' yas mu med pa dag na /
NK020(wa)001:3555: dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang
NK020(wa)001:3556: byang chub sems dpa' 'khor dang bcas pa rab 'byams
NK020(wa)001:3557: ma lus pa'i dkon mchog thams cad la gus pas
NK020(wa)001:3558: phyag 'tshal lo // rnam dag sku mnga' mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK020(wa)001:3559: ye shes rgya mtsho gser gyi lhun po 'dra //
NK020(wa)001:3560: grags pa 'jig rten gsum na lhang nge ba //
NK020(wa)001:3561: mgon po mchog brnyes khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3562: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK020(wa)001:3563: ma skyes mi 'gag nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK020(wa)001:3564: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba //
NK020(wa)001:3565: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3566: zhing bcur skus khyab zab yangs gsung sgra can //
NK020(wa)001:3567: ji lta ji snyed thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs //
NK020(wa)001:3568: dus kun rnam bzhi phrin las lhun grub pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3569: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnam la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3570: gdul bya'i zhing du 'gro don rdzogs mdzad phyir //
NK020(wa)001:3571: mi bsnyel thugs rjes 'khor ba'i mtha' la gzigs //
NK020(wa)001:3572: thabs mkhas thugs rjes 'gro don lhur mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:3573: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3574: chos dbyings ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK020(wa)001:3575: bde gshegs sras bcas mchod pa'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:3576: sgyu ma'i tshul du sku sprul pa //
NK020(wa)001:3577: lha mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3578: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung mdzad cing //
NK020(wa)001:3580: phyogs skyong bcu dang rgyal chen bzhi //
NK020(wa)001:3582: mkha' ltar khyab pa'i rgyal ba sras bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:3583: bdag dang mkha' mnyam 'gro ba ma lus pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3584: lus 'di zhing rdul mnyam par rab sprul nas //
NK020(wa)001:3585: rtag tu gus pa'i yid kyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3586: de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:3587: 'phags pa'i tshogs de dag thams cad la mchod yon dang byug pa /
NK020(wa)001:3591: gdugs dang ba dan la sogs pa dngos su ci 'byor ba 'di dag dang /
NK020(wa)001:3592: phyogs bcu na bdag pos yongs su ma bzung ba
NK020(wa)001:3593: lha dang mi'i rdzas dam pa bde ba'i yo byad
NK020(wa)001:3594: phun sum tshogs pa thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:3595: gzungs dang rig pa'i mthu dang /
NK020(wa)001:3596: mos pa'i stobs kyis bskyed pa'i mchod pa'i sprin phung
NK020(wa)001:3597: po gsum pa'i mdo dang bzang po spyod pa'i smon
NK020(wa)001:3598: lam las byung ba rgya mtsho thams cad kyis nam
NK020(wa)001:3599: mkha'i khams kyi mtha' klas pa thams cad rgyas par
NK020(wa)001:3602: bdag gi bar bzhes par mdzad do gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3603: mchod yon phal chen mchod yon bla re dang //
NK020(wa)001:3604: mchod yon bkod pa'i 'od zer rab bkye zhing //
NK020(wa)001:3605: mchod yon sna tshogs kun tu bkram byas nas //
NK020(wa)001:3606: bdag nyid chen po de dag rgyal ba mchod //
NK020(wa)001:3607: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra
NK020(wa)001:3608: ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sa mu
NK020(wa)001:3609: dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:3610: de bzhin du mchod yon gyi gnas su /
NK020(wa)001:3616: bla med dkon mchog gsum po dang //
NK020(wa)001:3617: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:3618: yid 'ong mchod sprin thams cad dang //
NK020(wa)001:3619: rol mo sil snyan 'phan gdugs dang //
NK020(wa)001:3620: bla re rgyal mtshan lhab lhub dang //
NK020(wa)001:3621: me tog phreng ba bdug pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:3622: mar me dri chab zhal zas sogs //
NK020(wa)001:3623: mchod sprin sna tshogs phyogs bcur 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:3624: sna tshogs rig pa'i bden pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:3625: dngos 'byor yid kyis sprul pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:3626: sangs rgyas zhing khams rab 'byams su //
NK020(wa)001:3627: bla med mchod pa'i sprin 'byung zhing //
NK020(wa)001:3628: yon tan dpag med thams cad kyis //
NK020(wa)001:3629: zhabs la spyi bos gtugs gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3631: mchod pa'i sprin gyi gzungs kyang brjod do //
NK020(wa)001:3632: de nas yan lag phyi ma lnga ni /
NK020(wa)001:3633: bdag cag rnams kyis thog ma ma mchis pa nas
NK020(wa)001:3634: 'khor ba nas 'khor ba'i tshe rabs thams cad du
NK020(wa)001:3635: sdig pa mi dge ba'i las mdor na mi bgyi
NK020(wa)001:3636: bar rigs pa'i las ni bgyis /
NK020(wa)001:3637: bgyi bar 'os pa'i las ma bgyis pa la sogs
NK020(wa)001:3638: pa dngos sdig ci mchis pa thams cad yang dag
NK020(wa)001:3639: par 'chags so // dus gsum gyi 'phags pa dang
NK020(wa)001:3640: so so skye bo'i dge ba'i rtsa ba mtha' dag
NK020(wa)001:3641: gi bsod nams thams cad la rjes su yi rang
NK020(wa)001:3642: par 'chags so // ngo // phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba
NK020(wa)001:3643: sras dang bcas pa thams cad la chos kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:3644: lo bla na med pa bskor bar bskul lo //
NK020(wa)001:3645: 'jig rten gyi sgron ma gang dag mya ngan las
NK020(wa)001:3646: 'da' ba'i tshul ston par bzhed pa de dag thams
NK020(wa)001:3647: cad la mya ngan las mi 'da' bar 'jig rte
NK020(wa)001:3648: gyi don mdzad cing yun ring du bzhugs par gsol
NK020(wa)001:3649: bar 'tshal lo // de ltar bgyis pa'i bsod nams
NK020(wa)001:3650: kyi phung po ci mchis pa thams cad bdag gzhan
NK020(wa)001:3651: ma lus pa bla na med pa'i byang chub mngon
NK020(wa)001:3653: phyogs bcu dus gsum bzhugs pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:3654: rgyal ba sras dang bcas rnams la //
NK020(wa)001:3655: phyag 'tshal mchod cing bshags pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:3656: yi rang bskul zhing gsol ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:3657: gzhan yang dge ba ci bsags pa //
NK020(wa)001:3658: des ni sems can thams cad dang //
NK020(wa)001:3659: 'phags pa skye bo'i tshogs kun gyis //
NK020(wa)001:3660: ye shes sa yi lam gyi mchog /
NK020(wa)001:3662: spyod pa nyid kyi yul rnams ni //
NK020(wa)001:3663: go rim bzhin du rab rtogs te //
NK020(wa)001:3664: sku gsum mkhyen bzhi'i tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK020(wa)001:3665: bla med sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:3666: de nas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3667: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:3668: khyed rnams la thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes /
NK020(wa)001:3671: skyob pa'i nus mthu bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba lags pas /
NK020(wa)001:3672: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:3673: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu rnams sku tshe brtan zhing
NK020(wa)001:3674: thugs kyi bzhed pa'i don lhun gyis grub pa dang
NK020(wa)001:3675: / dge 'dun rnams kyi chos spyod bcu'i sgrub pa
NK020(wa)001:3676: thams cad gong nas gong du 'phel zhing rgyas pa
NK020(wa)001:3677: / dang / de dag gi mthu dang nus pa la brten nas /
NK020(wa)001:3678: sems can la bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa 'byung zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3679: khyad par bdag dang bdag gi slob pa 'di dag
NK020(wa)001:3680: gis gtso byas sems can thams cad sgrib gnyis byang
NK020(wa)001:3682: myur du mngon par rdzogs pa 'tshang rgya bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK020(wa)001:3683: de nas thugs dam bskul ba'i ched du gzungs bzla zhing mdo bklag pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3684: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:3685: de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad kyis mthu dang byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:3686: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs dang /
NK020(wa)001:3687: 'phags pa sku gsung thugs kyi spyod pa ma dag
NK020(wa)001:3688: pa mi mnga' ba rnams kyi thugs nges pa'i bden
NK020(wa)001:3689: pas / mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi
NK020(wa)001:3690: dkyil 'khor 'dir ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3691: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa la sogs pa phyogs bcu
NK020(wa)001:3692: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas
NK020(wa)001:3693: pa thams cad gdan 'dzom pa chen po mdzad de
NK020(wa)001:3695: gzungs sngags bzlas pa tshul bzhin du 'grub par byin gyis rlob par mdzad de /
NK020(wa)001:3696: bdag sogs 'gro ba mang po'i don dpag tu med pa mdzad par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3697: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad kyi sku las
NK020(wa)001:3698: 'od zer 'phros pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK020(wa)001:3699: khyab / des 'phags pa thams cad sems can gyi don la bskul zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3700: ngan song gi gnas thams cad sbyangs te /
NK020(wa)001:3701: sems can thams cad mtho ris dang thar pa'i go 'phang la 'jug par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3702: 'od zer des bdag cag rnams la khyab pas 'gro don dpag med sgrub nus pa'i mthu thob ste /
NK020(wa)001:3703: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang sku gsung thugs mtshungs par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3704: yang 'od zer de dag gcig tu 'dus pa bum
NK020(wa)001:3705: pa'i gzungs chab la khyab ste reg pa tsam gyis
NK020(wa)001:3706: mi mthun pa'i phyogs zhi bar byed pa /
NK020(wa)001:3707: dpal dang bde legs bskyed par byed pa'i bdun rtsi'i dag byed du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3708: bdag cag la sogs pa bsgrub bya'i lus dang 'khod dang yo byad thams cad la khyab ste /
NK020(wa)001:3709: nad dang gnod pa thams cad ni bsal /
NK020(wa)001:3710: lus sems kyi skyon thams cad dang ni bral te /
NK020(wa)001:3711: chos kyi snod rung du gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:3712: bdag cag rnams kyis 'phags pa rnams mngon sum pa lta bur dmigs nas gzungs bzlas pas /
NK020(wa)001:3713: de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa rnams kyi
NK020(wa)001:3714: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo sna tshogs dang tshig 'bru
NK020(wa)001:3715: mtha' yas pa rtogs shing rnam par dag par byin
NK020(wa)001:3717: ces bden tshig gis bsngosa nas /
NK020(wa)001:3718: 'phags pa rnams kyis gnang zhing phrin las mdzad par nges shes bskyed de /
NK020(wa)001:3719: ji ltar bsngosa pa bzhin mngon du gyur par dmigs nas /
NK020(wa)001:3721: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:3724: ga te ga te p+aa ra ga te p+aa ra sam ga te bo d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:3725: zhes pa gnyis ci nus bzla zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3726: bye brag tu so so'i snying po bzla na /
NK020(wa)001:3727: gtso bo dang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la mu ne /
NK020(wa)001:3729: d+hi pra dz+ny+aa ma h+aa pra dz+ny+aa d+harma d+h+aa tu s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:3731: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:3733: na mah sa man+ta bud+d+h+aa nam b+ha ga w+aan pra
NK020(wa)001:3734: b+ha ta th+aa ga ta ya a ba lo ki
NK020(wa)001:3735: te k+aa ru na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:3737: ar+ya a wa lo ki te shwa ra ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka na ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:3738: zhes pa rnams kyang cung zad re bzla /
NK020(wa)001:3739: khyad par gzungs bum la dmigs te mu ne dang ga te bzlas pas /
NK020(wa)001:3740: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs dam bskul
NK020(wa)001:3741: te sku'i cha thams cad nas byung ba'i 'od zer
NK020(wa)001:3742: bum chu la khyab pas byin gyis brlab par bsam
NK020(wa)001:3743: mo // de nas shes rab snying po lta bu mdo zab mo'i glegs bam bklag cing /
NK020(wa)001:3744: spro zhing nus na thar pa chen po dang rtogs
NK020(wa)001:3745: chen dang dpang skong rnams kyang thams cad dam ci
NK020(wa)001:3746: rigs pa rang ngam gzhan gyis kyang rung ste ci
NK020(wa)001:3747: 'grub bklag go // de nas gtor ma btang zhing dbang bskur pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3748: 'das gtor dang cha gsum gtor ma sngar bzhin dang /
NK020(wa)001:3749: dbang chog ltar byang sems kyi theg pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK020(wa)001:3751: ji ltar 'jam dbyangs la sogs pas /
NK020(wa)001:3752: rgyal ba rnams la mchod mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:3753: de bzhin bdag gis de bzhin gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:3754: mgon po sras dang bcas rnams mchod //
NK020(wa)001:3755: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK020(wa)001:3756: shap+da pra t+ai ts+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sogs kyis mchod /
NK020(wa)001:3757: dus gsum gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas kun //
NK020(wa)001:3758: chos dang tshogs kyi mchog bcas la //
NK020(wa)001:3759: zhing rdul kun gyi grang snyed kyi //
NK020(wa)001:3760: lus btud pa yis bdag phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:3762: ma rnyed yongs su sogs kyis nongs pa bshags /
NK020(wa)001:3764: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyis brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:3766: khyed kyis sems can sogs kyis gshegs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:3768: 'jam dpal dpa' bos sogs sh+lo ka gnyis dang /
NK020(wa)001:3769: dge ba 'di yis skye bo kun //
NK020(wa)001:3771: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sman gcig pu //
NK020(wa)001:3774: sangs rgyas sku gsum brnyes pa'i sogs brjod do //
NK020(wa)001:3776: dam pa tog dkar dga' ldan pho brang dam pa ru //
NK020(wa)001:3777: mi pham mgon la rgyal tshab dam par dbang bskur zhing //
NK020(wa)001:3778: 'dzam gling nyid du glang chen thal ka ltar gshegs pa //
NK020(wa)001:3779: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:3780: rgyal po'i khab kyi grong khyer dam par zas gtsang sras //
NK020(wa)001:3781: bud med mchog gyur g.yo sgyu spangs pa lha mdzes yum //
NK020(wa)001:3782: lhums su zla bcur bzhugs nas 'byor ldan sh+aakya'i rigs //
NK020(wa)001:3783: bkra shis dam pa des kyang lum+bi'i tshal rab nyams dgar blak+sha'i ljon pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:3784: yal ga nas bzung bltams tshe tshangs dang dbang pos btud //
NK020(wa)001:3785: mkha' la gshegs te phyur por pad+ma byung gyur gang //
NK020(wa)001:3786: bkra shis dam pa des kyang pho brang gzhal yas khang mdzes drang srong mdun bzhag nas //
NK020(wa)001:3787: mtshan bltas shis pa brjod de ston pa 'byung 'gyur zhes //
NK020(wa)001:3788: sh+aaka rigs bud med 'khor gyis bskor zhing rab tu brgyan //
NK020(wa)001:3789: bkra shis dam pa des kyang gzhon nu stobs ldan rgyu rtsal yig 'phongs phul du phyin //
NK020(wa)001:3790: kun las mchog gyur lha mi'i 'gran zla rnams las rgyal //
NK020(wa)001:3791: sh+aaka rigs 'jig rten gsal phyir btsun mo'i 'khor la rol //
NK020(wa)001:3792: bkra shis dam pa des pho brang nas byung phyogs bzhir skye rga na 'chi gzigs //
NK020(wa)001:3793: mi rnams rmongs mdzad lha yis bteg ste mkha' la gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:3794: srid gsum dag las rgyal phyir mthon mthing dbu skra bregs //
NK020(wa)001:3795: bkra shis dam pa des kyang lha yi rdzu 'phrul gyis blangs na bza' ngur smrig phul //
NK020(wa)001:3796: nee rany+dza nar thub pa'i dka' thub lo drug rdzogs //
NK020(wa)001:3797: bsam gtan las bzhengs legs skyes mas phul 'o thug bzhes //
NK020(wa)001:3798: bkra shis dam pa pad+ma la sogs khyu mchog byang chub shing drung du //
NK020(wa)001:3799: skyil mo krung bcas mi g.yo mchog gis bdud btul nas //
NK020(wa)001:3800: tho rengs bdud rtsi 'chi med phun sum tshogs pa brnyes //
NK020(wa)001:3801: bkra shis dam pa w+aa r+aa na s+air thog mar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK020(wa)001:3802: kun shes la sogs lnga sde bzang la bden bzhi bstan //
NK020(wa)001:3803: lha dang mi dang lha min rnams kyang 'dus gyur pa //
NK020(wa)001:3804: bkra shis dam pa nga rgyal dregs pa'i mu stegs ston pa drug btul nas //
NK020(wa)001:3805: glang chen rab myos rbad pa'i ma rungs lha byin btul //
NK020(wa)001:3806: drang srong mchog dang sprel rgyal cang shes sbrang rtsis mchod //
NK020(wa)001:3807: bkra shis dam pa des pad+ma lta bur skyon gyis ma gos sh+aakya'i rigs //
NK020(wa)001:3808: zas gtsang sras po rgyal rigs mchog gyur 'khor los sgyur //
NK020(wa)001:3809: bltams pa nas bzung de yis mdzad pa ma lus rdzogs //
NK020(wa)001:3810: bkra shis dam pa byams pa'i stobs kyis 'gro ba ma lus rab tu bsgral //
NK020(wa)001:3811: sems can thams cad smin grol zhi ba'i lam la bkod //
NK020(wa)001:3812: r+ts+wa mchog grong du mdzad pa mthar phyin dgongs pa rdzogs //
NK020(wa)001:3813: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:3814: ces brjod cing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas me
NK020(wa)001:3815: tog gi sil ma phyogs kun tu 'thor bar bya'o
NK020(wa)001:3816: // 'dir lha mi nas byang sems kyi bar gyis dkyil 'khor bzhi'i chog gzhung la'ang /
NK020(wa)001:3817: kha cig bdag bskyed dang mdun bskyed la sogs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3818: rnam bzhag sbyor bar mdzad na'ang rigs par ma mthong
NK020(wa)001:3819: ste / lha rje 'gar gyi las thor /
NK020(wa)001:3820: nub gnyis pa la mdo mchod dang brgyad mchod bya /
NK020(wa)001:3821: man+dala zlum po ru lha mi nas nyan rang byang sems kyi bar gyi dbang rdzogs par bskur /
NK020(wa)001:3823: glan gyi yig rnying tho yig rnams su'ang /
NK020(wa)001:3824: rtogs pa chen po'i cho ga dpang skong gi mdo mchod dang /
NK020(wa)001:3826: yi ge kha cig las nyan thos kyi skabs gnas brtan gyi cho ga ste /
NK020(wa)001:3827: cho ga gzhung gi khog de dag gis dbub par bshad pa ltar /
NK020(wa)001:3828: de rnams su bdag mdun gyi bskyed chog sogs kyi
NK020(wa)001:3829: tha snyad yi ge khungs ma gang nas kyang mi
NK020(wa)001:3830: 'byung bas / des na 'dir bkod pa nyid gnad dang 'byor bar mthong nas bros so //
NK020(wa)001:3832: sgrol ma ba yab sras yan chad glan lugs kyi bla ma rnams /
NK020(wa)001:3836: byang sems rnams kyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK020(wa)001:3837: gtso bo'i khyad par thams cad thub dbang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:3838: lha mi la rnam snang dang byang sems la yum
NK020(wa)001:3839: chen mos barje ba 'dam khar mdzad pa'ang snang ba
NK020(wa)001:3840: las gzhan du dkyil 'khor gyi grangs re re las
NK020(wa)001:3841: mi mdzad par / glan chen po rdo rje 'od kyi chos sras 'gos kyi las tho dang /
NK020(wa)001:3842: glan bsod mgon gyi las khrigs //
NK020(wa)001:3843: gzhan yang 'dzam gling pan+di ta'i sgrub thabs sna bdun
NK020(wa)001:3844: rin po che'i mtshan can rnams kyis shes nus shing
NK020(wa)001:3845: / de bas na zur ham phyin chad nas dar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbye ba /
NK020(wa)001:3846: lha mi la bcu gcig gam lnga /
NK020(wa)001:3849: byang sems la bcu'am lngar phye ba sogs ni spros 'dod tsam du zad mod /
NK020(wa)001:3852: ces pa tsam las kri yog yan chad lta bu'i
NK020(wa)001:3853: dkyil 'khor gyi lha grangs sogs ma gsungs par ma
NK020(wa)001:3854: zad / byang sems man gyi dkyil 'khor 'di dag
NK020(wa)001:3855: tshogs gsog gi rten du bshams pa tsam yin pas
NK020(wa)001:3856: zad / na / ches che ba'i 'gal ba ni ma mthong ngo //
NK020(wa)001:3857: yang byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor la glan bsod mgon gyis dbus su thub dbang /
NK020(wa)001:3858: 'dab bzhir yum chen mo sogs bzhi bkod nas /
NK020(wa)001:3859: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas lha snam la 'god par mdzad na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:3860: 'dir ni glan rdor 'od kyi lugs 'gos kyi las
NK020(wa)001:3861: tho ltar pad 'dab bcu la bkod pa yin no
NK020(wa)001:3862: // ngag brjod las 'das dbyings zab mor //
NK020(wa)001:3863: dbang bsgyur ye shes rtogs pa'i thabs //
NK020(wa)001:3864: byang sems theg pa'i chos kyi dpal //
NK020(wa)001:3865: mi nus yi ge'i snang ba shar //
NK020(wa)001:3866: byang sems theg pa'i sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:3869: mi 'gyur thugs rje'i dpal mnga' zhing //
NK020(wa)001:3870: thogs med mkhyen pas 'gro sgrol gyi //
NK020(wa)001:3871: nus gzugs rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:3872: der btud kri ya'i sgrub thabs bshad //
NK020(wa)001:3873: de ltar 'jig rten lha mi dang 'das pa las
NK020(wa)001:3874: kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum ste bzhi song
NK020(wa)001:3876: dka' thub rig byed theg pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3877: 'di yang yul gyi gsum nyid de /
NK020(wa)001:3878: zhes pas 'dir dka' thub rig byed la /
NK020(wa)001:3879: kri ya dang u pa ya gnyis tha dad du
NK020(wa)001:3880: phye ste dkyil 'khor gsum dgos zhes 'ga' zhig gsungs
NK020(wa)001:3881: na'ang / slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las thor kri yog gnyis su bsdus shing /
NK020(wa)001:3882: mkhas pa glan sogs bla ma gong ma rnams kyang
NK020(wa)001:3883: de ltar bzhed pa nyid lugs 'di la tshad ma
NK020(wa)001:3884: yin no // des na kri yog gnyis las /
NK020(wa)001:3885: dang po yan lag gi dkyil 'khor lnga pa kri ya la /
NK020(wa)001:3886: thog mar sta go na ni /
NK020(wa)001:3887: slob dpon bdag nyid gtsang sbra dang ldan pas bdag
NK020(wa)001:3888: bskyed kyi cho ga bzlas pa'i bar 'og nas 'byung
NK020(wa)001:3890: mdun du spyan drangs pa'i lha la gtang rag dang bzod bsol byas nas gshegs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:3891: de nas rang lha'i nga rgyal la gnas pas dkyil
NK020(wa)001:3892: 'khor gyi gzhi byi dor bya zhing ba byur gis
NK020(wa)001:3893: byugs te / skya thig btab nas lha gnas rnams
NK020(wa)001:3894: su dri'i thig le gtso bo rigs gsum la gru
NK020(wa)001:3895: bzhi dang 'khor rnams la zlum po re byas pa'i
NK020(wa)001:3896: steng du me tog gi tshom bu bkod de /
NK020(wa)001:3900: swa b+h+aa wa sogs sngags rnams lan bdun re bzlas la /
NK020(wa)001:3901: lha rnams gsal gdab pa nas bstod pa'i bar spro na 'og gi mdun bskyed sor bzhag bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3902: de tsam long skabs kyis ma khom na /
NK020(wa)001:3903: dbus kyi stan la 'jam dpal dbyangs /
NK020(wa)001:3904: de'i g.yas logs su spyan ras gzigs /
NK020(wa)001:3905: g.yon du phyag na rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:3906: mtha' bskor du sbyang spel bsgyur thob tshim pa dbang du byed pa'i lha drug dang /
NK020(wa)001:3907: sgeg sogs lha mo bcu gnyis rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:3909: 'og nas 'byung ba ltar ye shes pa dgug cing bstim nas /
NK020(wa)001:3910: dri sogs mchod pa lnga sngags rgya tsam gyis mchod cing bstod pa bya /
NK020(wa)001:3911: gang ltar yang de rjes dkyil 'khor pa dang sangs
NK020(wa)001:3912: rgyas kun la dmigs nas gsol ba gdab pa ni
NK020(wa)001:3914: rigs gsum mgon po bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)001:3915: rig sngags rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:3916: slob ma rnams la brtse ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:3917: khyed rnams la yang mchod pa'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:3918: mgon po thugs rje'i bdag nyid can //
NK020(wa)001:3919: sar ni dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
NK020(wa)001:3920: de phyir bcom ldan bdag gus la //
NK020(wa)001:3921: bka' drin gnang bar mdzad par rigs //
NK020(wa)001:3922: sangs rgyas 'jig rten mgon brtse dang //
NK020(wa)001:3923: byang chub sems dpa' 'bras gnas dang /
NK020(wa)001:3924: gzhan yang gang dag gsang sngags lha //
NK020(wa)001:3925: 'jig rten skyong ba'i lha rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:3926: gang yang 'byung po mthu chen dang /
NK020(wa)001:3927: sems can bstan la mngon dga' ba //
NK020(wa)001:3928: gang su lha yi spyan mnga' rnams //
NK020(wa)001:3929: bdag la dgongs par mdzad du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3930: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yis //
NK020(wa)001:3931: rigs gsum zhes bya'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK020(wa)001:3932: ji ltar nus par nyer sbyor bas //
NK020(wa)001:3933: 'gro ba sbyar phyir bri bar bya //
NK020(wa)001:3934: de phyir bdag dang slob ma la /
NK020(wa)001:3935: rjes su brtse bas nyer dgongs te //
NK020(wa)001:3936: dkyil 'khor dang bcas thams cad ni //
NK020(wa)001:3937: nye bar gnas par mdzad pa'i rigs //
NK020(wa)001:3938: zhes lan gsum brjod cing slar yang bstod nas /
NK020(wa)001:3939: ma rnyed yongs su sogs kyi mthar yig brgya brjod la /
NK020(wa)001:3940: muhzhesa spyan drangs pa'i lha gshegs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:3941: sngags kyi sprul pa'i lha dam tshig pa rnams bdag la thim par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)001:3946: rigs gsum gtso bo khyod la 'dud //
NK020(wa)001:3947: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK020(wa)001:3948: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK020(wa)001:3949: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song zhing //
NK020(wa)001:3950: theg chen khang par gzhugs pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:3951: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK020(wa)001:3953: de nas skyabs sems kyi sdom pa 'bogs te /
NK020(wa)001:3954: slob dpon gyi rjes su zlos pas /
NK020(wa)001:3955: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:3956: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:3957: srog chags sdug bsngal zhi bya'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:3958: bdag ni ji srid 'tsho'i bar du //
NK020(wa)001:3959: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK020(wa)001:3960: gus pas yang dag skabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:3961: sems can thams cad ni mtha' yas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:3962: sdug bsngal nye bar zhi ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:3963: ngan 'gro rnams las bsgral ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:3964: nyon mongs rnams las dgrol ba'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:3965: srid pa'i mi dge dog pa na //
NK020(wa)001:3966: sdug bsngal sna tshogs ci mchis pa //
NK020(wa)001:3967: de ltar yongs su skyob pa'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:3968: bdag gis byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK020(wa)001:3969: tshe yi mtha' klas gang byed dang //
NK020(wa)001:3970: gang yang cung zad byed 'gyur pa //
NK020(wa)001:3971: mdor na sems can thams cad kyi //
NK020(wa)001:3972: nyon mongs thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:3973: grol bar bya ba'i phyir 'bad cing //
NK020(wa)001:3974: byang chub rab tu dga' brtson no //
NK020(wa)001:3975: zhes pas rgyud sbyangs nas myang 'das kyi bsam pa brtan po bskyed du gzhug /
NK020(wa)001:3976: de nas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:3977: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:3978: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK020(wa)001:3979: na mo badz+ra kro d+h+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:3986: ces pa bzla bzhin du dri'i chus slob ma'i mgo la bsang gtor bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:3989: ces pa lan bdun bzla bzhin du lag pa spyi bor bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:3992: lan gsum bzlas pas kyang byin gyis brlab cing /
NK020(wa)001:3994: so shing dzi ni dzika zhes gtad la /
NK020(wa)001:3996: h+r+aihbi shud+d+ha d+harma sarba p+aa pam nish+tsa a s+ya sho
NK020(wa)001:3997: d+ha ya sarba bi ka la pan a pa na
NK020(wa)001:3998: ya h+aum gis dri'i khyor chu lan gsum blud /
NK020(wa)001:3999: amri te h+aum phata bzlas pa'i srung skud mdud pa gsum ldan gdags shing /
NK020(wa)001:4000: de bzlas pa'i ku sha che chung stan dang sngas kyi don du sbyin la /
NK020(wa)001:4001: chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung /
NK020(wa)001:4003: skar ma rab rib sogs dang /
NK020(wa)001:4004: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:4006: 'on kyang skyob pa'i sras su skye /
NK020(wa)001:4007: zhes pa'i bar gyis chos bshad nas /
NK020(wa)001:4008: bu kye sang ni dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK020(wa)001:4009: mthong bar 'gyur ro nyol zhig dang //
NK020(wa)001:4010: rmi lam mthong ba gang yin pa //
NK020(wa)001:4011: de kun nga la legs par smros //
NK020(wa)001:4013: phyag 'tshal du bcug ste rang gnas su btang ngo //
NK020(wa)001:4015: bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa gnyis legs par bkrus shing gu gul gyis bdug /
NK020(wa)001:4016: mgul chings kha rgyan sogs chas su bcug /
NK020(wa)001:4017: 'bru lnga dang rin chen lnga'i thum bu dang sman
NK020(wa)001:4018: lnga btags pa'i phye ma rnams nang rdzas su blug
NK020(wa)001:4019: cing chu gtsang gis sum gnyis tsam bkang /
NK020(wa)001:4021: stong pa'i ngang las rin po che'i bum pa yangs
NK020(wa)001:4022: shig rgya che ba mtshan nyid thams cad tshang ba
NK020(wa)001:4023: nang lha'i chu bo dang nang rdzas kyis gang ba'i
NK020(wa)001:4024: mgrin par zla dkyil la bzla bya'i rig sngags kyi
NK020(wa)001:4025: phreng ba gnas pa las 'od zer 'phros /
NK020(wa)001:4026: sangs rgyas dang byang sems sngags kyi lha rnams bdud
NK020(wa)001:4027: rtsi'i rnam par spyan drangs pas bum pa gang bar
NK020(wa)001:4028: bsam zhing / rnam bum la rigs gsum gyi sngags dang /
NK020(wa)001:4030: tree lokya bi dza ya h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:4031: ces khams gsum rnam rgyal dang /
NK020(wa)001:4032: las kun byed pa thabs sbyor gyi sngags /
NK020(wa)001:4033: a mri te h+aum phata ces pa bzla /
NK020(wa)001:4035: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:4037: dzi na dzika gis me tog dkar po dang /
NK020(wa)001:4039: a mri te bzla zhing gu gul gyis bdug go /
NK020(wa)001:4040: de nas cha gsum gtor ma btang zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4041: bdag gi lha'i sku gzugs zla ba'i steng gi yi ge la thim /
NK020(wa)001:4043: de rnam smin gyi lus la thim par bsam la bkra shis brjod do //
NK020(wa)001:4044: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi dngos gzhi'i nyin par kha dog lnga'i srad bu la bsang gtor byas /
NK020(wa)001:4045: las sngags bzla bzhin du bsgril /
NK020(wa)001:4046: mdun gyi nam mkhar rgyal ba sras bcas bzhugs par mos la mchod de /
NK020(wa)001:4047: shar dang lhor gnas tshangs thig gnyis /
NK020(wa)001:4048: mer gnas shar lho'i rtsa thig gnyis /
NK020(wa)001:4049: rlung gnas nub byang rtsa thig gnyis /
NK020(wa)001:4050: me dang bden bral gnas zur thig /
NK020(wa)001:4051: gnyis gdab slob dpon 'dug phyogs te /
NK020(wa)001:4052: slob ma de ldog g.yas bskor 'gro /
NK020(wa)001:4053: zhes pa ltar dang po mkha' dang /
NK020(wa)001:4054: de nas sa la gdab cing /
NK020(wa)001:4055: thig thebs nas tshon rtsi la bsang gtor byas la /
NK020(wa)001:4056: las sngags bzla bzhin du thog mar slob dpon gyis dbang ldan gyi rtsig pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4057: de nas lte ba ser po /
NK020(wa)001:4059: rtsig pa nang nas ser sngo dmar nag dkar ba /
NK020(wa)001:4061: lho sngo ba sogs phyogs tshon /
NK020(wa)001:4062: rta babs mas rim bzhin ser ljang sngo dmar /
NK020(wa)001:4063: khor yug pad rdor 'od phreng sogs tshon thob lhag ma spyi dang 'dra zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4064: lha gnas rnams su so so'i sku rten lha tsaka dang /
NK020(wa)001:4065: rnam bum rig gsum gyi sngags bzla bzhin du dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi la dgod /
NK020(wa)001:4066: las bum a mri ta bzla bas dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgo'am slob dpon gyi mdun du bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:4067: dkyil 'khor gyi mthar mda' dar me long can dang /
NK020(wa)001:4069: phur bu brgyad dam bzhis bskor ba tshon skud kyis bres /
NK020(wa)001:4073: cha gsum gtor ma rnams ci bder sgrig /
NK020(wa)001:4074: rang gi mdun du mchod yon bzed zhal dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:4077: rdor dril sogs yo byad thams cad tshogs par bsham mo //
NK020(wa)001:4079: dang po kho nar gtsang sbra dang bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:4080: sangs rgyas chos tshogs ma dang /
NK020(wa)001:4081: sems can thams cad bde ba dang zhes sogs kyis
NK020(wa)001:4082: skyabs sems tshad med bzhi bsgom pa sngon du 'gro
NK020(wa)001:4083: bas / slob dpon rang nyid khyim pa yin na smos ma dgos /
NK020(wa)001:4084: rab tu byung ba yin na'ang theg pa chen po'i
NK020(wa)001:4085: gso sbyong legs pa mi 'gal zhing legs pa yin
NK020(wa)001:4086: pas dkon mchog gi rten gyi drung du pus btsugs
NK020(wa)001:4088: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4089: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK020(wa)001:4090: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rta cang
NK020(wa)001:4091: shes lta bu / glang po chen po /
NK020(wa)001:4092: bya ba byas shing byed pa byas pa /
NK020(wa)001:4094: rang gi don rjes su thob pa /
NK020(wa)001:4095: srid pa kun tu sbyor ba yongs su zad pa /
NK020(wa)001:4097: legs par rnam par grol ba'i thugs /
NK020(wa)001:4098: legs par rnam par grol ba'i shes rab can de dag gis /
NK020(wa)001:4099: sems can thams cad la phan par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK020(wa)001:4100: grol bar bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK020(wa)001:4101: nad med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK020(wa)001:4102: mu ge med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK020(wa)001:4103: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos
NK020(wa)001:4104: rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir du gso
NK020(wa)001:4105: sbyong nges par mdzad pa de bzhin du bdag ming
NK020(wa)001:4107: dus 'di nas bzung nas sang nyi ma ma shar bar du gso sbyong nges par blang bar bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:4108: deng nas srog gcod mi bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4109: gzhan gyi nor yang blang mi bya //
NK020(wa)001:4110: 'khrig pa'i chos kyang mi bya ste //
NK020(wa)001:4111: rdzun gyi tshig kyang mi smra'o //
NK020(wa)001:4112: skyon ni mang po nyer brten pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:4113: chang ni yongs su spang bar bya //
NK020(wa)001:4114: khri stan mthon po mi bya zhing //
NK020(wa)001:4115: de bzhin dus ma yin pa'i zas //
NK020(wa)001:4116: dri dang phreng ba dang ni rgyan //
NK020(wa)001:4117: gar dang glu sogs spang bar bya //
NK020(wa)001:4118: ji ltar dgra bcom rtag tu ni //
NK020(wa)001:4119: srog gcod la sogs mi byed ltar //
NK020(wa)001:4120: de bzhin srog gcod la sogs spang //
NK020(wa)001:4121: bla med byang chub myur thob shog /
NK020(wa)001:4123: a mo g+ha sh+ai la sam+b+ha ra sam+b+ha ra /
NK020(wa)001:4125: ma h+aa shud+da sa t+wa pad+ma bi b+h+au shi ti b+h+au dza d+ha ra d+ha ra /
NK020(wa)001:4126: sa man+ta a ba lo ki te h+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4128: de nas sgrub khang gi phyi rol tu dngos su 'gro ba'am song bar mos te /
NK020(wa)001:4130: ces bzlas pas ci dgar khrus bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4131: chu snyim pa gsum mgo bor blugs la dbang bskur te dril phyis byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:4132: su sid+d+hi k+aa ri h+aum zhes lan bdun bzla bzhin gtsug phud bcing /
NK020(wa)001:4133: tshog pur sdad la pus mo'i bar du lag g.yon
NK020(wa)001:4134: par chu gtsang bzhag pa las g.yas pa'i sor mos
NK020(wa)001:4135: blangs te / kha rna mig sna kha lag mgo //
NK020(wa)001:4136: lte ba rnams su gnyis gsum reg /
NK020(wa)001:4137: ces pa ltar nye reg byas te nang du 'jug pa'am zhugs par mos la /
NK020(wa)001:4138: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:4140: las bum gyi chu lag g.yon par bzhag pa las g.yas pas 'thor bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:4141: stong gsum kun tu dri mchog 'byung gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:4142: spos dang sman sbyar chu gtsang rgyal ba'i khrus //
NK020(wa)001:4143: ye shes sprin phung mkha' la char 'bebs pas //
NK020(wa)001:4144: mi gtsang dri ma'i phyogs rnams dag gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:4145: shud+d+he shud+d+he sho d+ha ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4147: tree lo kya bi dza ya h+aum phata dang /
NK020(wa)001:4149: ces bzla bas bdag gnas yo byad thams cad la bsang gtor byas pas bgegs bsal /
NK020(wa)001:4150: swa b+h+aa wa'i sngags kyis chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK020(wa)001:4151: gyis rnam par dag pa'i ngang la dar cig bzhag
NK020(wa)001:4152: / de nas dkon mchog gsum dang rigs gsum 'khor bcas mkha' khyab tu bzhugs par dmigs la /
NK020(wa)001:4155: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis
NK020(wa)001:4156: dus 'di nas bzung ste nam byang chub snying po
NK020(wa)001:4157: la mchis kyi bar du bdag la dgongs su gsol
NK020(wa)001:4158: / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas skye ba thog
NK020(wa)001:4159: ma med pa nas 'khor ba na 'khor ba'i tshe
NK020(wa)001:4160: / / bdag gis sdig pa mi dge ba'i las ci bgyis pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4162: bgyid pa la rjes su yi rang ba de dag
NK020(wa)001:4163: thams cad sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK020(wa)001:4164: cad kyi spyan sngar so sor bshags so //
NK020(wa)001:4167: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4168: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK020(wa)001:4169: nam byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du
NK020(wa)001:4170: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la skyabs su mchi'o
NK020(wa)001:4171: // de bzhin gshegs pa'i chos kyi sku zhi ba
NK020(wa)001:4172: bla na med pa so so ra nga gis rig
NK020(wa)001:4174: phyogs bzhi'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa
NK020(wa)001:4175: phyir mi ldog pa'i dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o
NK020(wa)001:4177: de nas lus dbul ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:4179: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4180: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung
NK020(wa)001:4181: ste nam byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar
NK020(wa)001:4182: du sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad
NK020(wa)001:4183: la / bdag nyid dus thams cad du yong ye 'bul gyi /
NK020(wa)001:4184: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis
NK020(wa)001:4185: bdag la thugs brtse ba'i slad du bdag bzhes su
NK020(wa)001:4187: de nas thal mo khong stong du sbyar te mdzub
NK020(wa)001:4188: mo cung zad bkug cing mthe bong gnyis sgreng ba
NK020(wa)001:4189: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bcing la /
NK020(wa)001:4190: phyag rgya 'di ni rgya che ste //
NK020(wa)001:4191: sangs rgyas skyob pa rnams kyi yin //
NK020(wa)001:4192: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dam tshig ni //
NK020(wa)001:4193: phyag rgya 'di la rab tu gnas //
NK020(wa)001:4194: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam a sa me tri sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4195: zhes pas dam tshig par byin gyis brlab /
NK020(wa)001:4196: de nas lag gnyis khu tshur bcang nas mthe bong
NK020(wa)001:4197: nang du bcug pa sbyar la mdzub mo gnyis sgreng
NK020(wa)001:4198: ba chos kyi dbyings kyi phyag rgya bcings la /
NK020(wa)001:4199: rgya 'di phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK020(wa)001:4200: chos dbyings rnams la sbyang ba'o //
NK020(wa)001:4201: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam d+harma d+h+aa tu swa b+h+au wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)001:4202: zhes pas chos kyi dbyings su brlab /
NK020(wa)001:4203: de nas sor mo rgyab sbyar ba bsnol te mthe
NK020(wa)001:4204: bong gnyis rgyab sprad pa 'khor lo'i phyag rgya bcas
NK020(wa)001:4205: la / rgyal mchog dpal dang ldan pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:4206: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba yin //
NK020(wa)001:4207: 'jig rten mgon po skyob pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:4209: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam badz+ra +aat+ma ko&aham /
NK020(wa)001:4210: zhes pas rdo rje sems dpar brlab bo /
NK020(wa)001:4212: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da l+ai h+aum ram /
NK020(wa)001:4213: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum dzah zhes pas /
NK020(wa)001:4214: bdud rtsi thabs sbyor ljang nag rgya gram dang dril bu 'dzin pa'i nga rgyal bzung la /
NK020(wa)001:4215: thal mo khong stong las mdzub mo gnyis nang du bcug /
NK020(wa)001:4216: mthe bong dang srin lag sgreng /
NK020(wa)001:4217: gung mo dang mathe'u chung cung zad bkug pa'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:4218: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yahsarba b+h+ya bi ga
NK020(wa)001:4219: te b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe b+h+yah sarba th+aa h+ai
NK020(wa)001:4220: ka rak+sha ma h+aa ba le sarba ta th+aa ga
NK020(wa)001:4221: te pun+ya ni ra dza t+ae h+aum h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:4223: a pra ti ha ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4225: bgegs rnams 'jigs par byed pa'i khro tshogs kyis bdag
NK020(wa)001:4226: gnas yo byad thams cad bsrungs te rdo rje phreng
NK020(wa)001:4227: ba'i ra bas khyab par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4228: yang thal sbyar las mdzub mo gnyis gung mo'i rgyab tu sbyar ba gnas lngar gtug cing /
NK020(wa)001:4229: na mahs man+ta badz+ra n+aam badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:4231: de nas bden stobs kyis bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:4235: bsod nams dam pa'i dpal gyi zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4236: yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung gnas thugs rje'i mnga' bdag /
NK020(wa)001:4238: mchod gnas bla na med pa dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK020(wa)001:4239: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4240: bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4241: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK020(wa)001:4242: gsang sngags dang rig sngags dang gzungs sngags dang snying po dang phyag rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:4243: lha dang drang srong rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4244: yum chen mo dang sras phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4245: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK020(wa)001:4250: phyag na rdo rje la sogs pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4251: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)001:4252: mchod pa dang cho ga la bar du gcod pa'i
NK020(wa)001:4253: bgegs dang log 'dren glog ltar g.yo zhing rlung ltar
NK020(wa)001:4254: 'tshub pa / sbal pa rma can dang /
NK020(wa)001:4259: log 'dren sna yon la sogs pa thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs shig /
NK020(wa)001:4261: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK020(wa)001:4262: mngags gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:4263: khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:4264: bgegs kyi sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK020(wa)001:4266: de nas mathe'u chung bsnol ba'i steng du srin lag gis mnan /
NK020(wa)001:4267: de'i steng du mthe bong gis mnan te /
NK020(wa)001:4268: gung mo gnyis rtse sprad pa'i rgyab nas mdzub mo rdo rje'i rwa ltar byas pa bstan la /
NK020(wa)001:4269: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:4270: na mash+tsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye /
NK020(wa)001:4271: ma h+aa yak+sha se n+aa pa ta ye /
NK020(wa)001:4272: na mo badz+ra kro d+h+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:4273: ma h+aa damsh+tod+ha ta b+hee ra b+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:4274: a si mu sa la d+h+aa r+aa ya pa ra shu p+aa sha has+t+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:4286: bis+pho ta ya bi s+pho ta ya /
NK020(wa)001:4287: sarba big+h+n+aana bi n+aa ya kam ma h+aa ga na
NK020(wa)001:4288: pa ti dzi wi ta an+ta ka r+aa ya s+w+aa
NK020(wa)001:4289: h+aa / zhes bdun bzlas pas bgegs gzhom par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:4295: thal mo sbyar ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK020(wa)001:4296: ta th+aa ga tod+b+ha ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4297: rdo rje rtse lnga'i rgya snying gar bzhag la /
NK020(wa)001:4299: zhes pas rigs gsum 'khor bcas mngon sum du bzhugs par mos te /
NK020(wa)001:4300: 'jig rten dag gi phyogs kun nas //
NK020(wa)001:4301: de bzhin gshegs pa gang bzhugs dang /
NK020(wa)001:4302: dgra bcom byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK020(wa)001:4303: bdag gis ma 'tshal sdig bgyis dang //
NK020(wa)001:4304: gang yang bgyid du stsal ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:4305: rjes su yi rang bgyis la sogs //
NK020(wa)001:4306: bag med pa ni phra mo yang //
NK020(wa)001:4307: lus ngag yid kyis bgyis pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:4308: yang dang yang du mthol zhing bshags //
NK020(wa)001:4309: slan chad de ltar yongs mi bgyid //
NK020(wa)001:4310: bdag gis mi dge bgyis pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:4311: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis mkhyen pa ltar //
NK020(wa)001:4313: srog chags sdug bsngal zhi bya'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:4314: ji srid byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK020(wa)001:4315: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK020(wa)001:4316: gus pas yang dag skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:4317: deng nas mchog gi sa bon gang //
NK020(wa)001:4318: thar pa bdud rtsi'i 'bras bu smin //
NK020(wa)001:4319: shin tu sgoms pas mchog gyur te //
NK020(wa)001:4320: dngos grub phyir ni de bskyed do //
NK020(wa)001:4321: dge ba'i las rnams gang dag kun //
NK020(wa)001:4322: 'di dang gzhan du bsags pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:4323: chos kyi longs spyod sna tshogs la //
NK020(wa)001:4324: mnyam par bzhag pas yi rang ngo //
NK020(wa)001:4325: sngon gyi rgyal ba sras bcas kyis //
NK020(wa)001:4326: smin lam ji ltar mdzad pa ltar //
NK020(wa)001:4327: bdag kyang dge ba kun rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)001:4328: de bzhin du ni smon lam 'debs //
NK020(wa)001:4329: 'phags pa rnams kyis rjes dgongs te //
NK020(wa)001:4330: mgon ma mchis pa bdag myur du //
NK020(wa)001:4331: sangs rgyas 'grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:4332: de dag ni rnal 'byor la 'jug pa'i bya ba'o //
NK020(wa)001:4333: de nas rnal 'byor dngos gzhi ni /
NK020(wa)001:4334: bya rgyud tsam po rnams su bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa mi 'byung yang /
NK020(wa)001:4335: 'dir bya rgyud khyad par can spyod rgyud dang thun
NK020(wa)001:4336: mong pa'i sgrub tshul la bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa
NK020(wa)001:4337: yod pas / de'i dbang du byas te bdag bskyed ni /
NK020(wa)001:4338: thog mar bdag gi de kho na nyid bsgom ste /
NK020(wa)001:4339: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK020(wa)001:4340: sdug bsngal rgyu dang bcas pa las bdag gis bsgral
NK020(wa)001:4341: te chos kyi dbyings byang chub mchog la 'god par
NK020(wa)001:4342: bya / de'i ched du 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad sems tsam ste /
NK020(wa)001:4343: de yang mi dmigs pa nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK020(wa)001:4345: de nas lha'i de kho na nyid ni lha drug bsgom pa ste /
NK020(wa)001:4346: bdag gi de kho na nyid don dam byang chub
NK020(wa)001:4347: sems kyi ngo bo stong pa nyid du gyur pa
NK020(wa)001:4349: de'i ngang las rang sems zla ba'i dkyil 'khor nya gang bsgom pa ni yi ge'i lha /
NK020(wa)001:4350: zla dkyil gyi steng du w+aa g+ai shwa ri mum
NK020(wa)001:4351: zhes pa'i sngags kyi yi ge'i gzugs rang sgra sgrog
NK020(wa)001:4353: sngags de nyid zla dkyil 'dren nas slar yang sngags
NK020(wa)001:4354: phreng bkod pa'i 'od zer spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi
NK020(wa)001:4355: mdzad pa bsgrubs / zla ba sngags phreng dang bcas
NK020(wa)001:4356: pa yongs su gyur pa las rang nyid 'jam dpal
NK020(wa)001:4357: gzhon nur gyur pa gser gyi mdog can zhal gcig
NK020(wa)001:4358: mdzad pa bsgrubs / phyag gnyis pa / g.yas ral
NK020(wa)001:4359: gri dang g.yon ut+pa la'i steng na glegs bam 'dzin
NK020(wa)001:4360: mdzad pa bsgrubs / phyag gnyis pa / pa /
NK020(wa)001:4361: zur phud lnga pa dar dang rin po che'i rgyan
NK020(wa)001:4363: pad zla'i gdan la rdo rje skyil krung gis bzhugs par sgom pa ni gzugs kyi lha'o //
NK020(wa)001:4365: sarba ta th+aa ga tod+b+ha ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4366: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi sngags dang thal
NK020(wa)001:4367: mo bkan pa las mdzub rtse gnyis cung zad bkug
NK020(wa)001:4368: pa'i rgyas snying mgrin smin mtshams dpung mgo gnyis te
NK020(wa)001:4369: lngar gtugs la byin gyis rlob /
NK020(wa)001:4370: de nas thal mo bkan pa las mathe'u chung gnyis
NK020(wa)001:4371: bsnol ba'i bar du srin lag gnyis bkug ste gung
NK020(wa)001:4372: mo gnyis gshibs la sgreng ba'i tshigs gsum par mdzub
NK020(wa)001:4373: mo gnyis bkug la mthe bong gnyis sbyar ba'i rgya
NK020(wa)001:4374: bcas la / badz+ra ag+ni pra d+ai p+t+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4375: zhes bardzoda pas rdo rje'i go char byas la /
NK020(wa)001:4376: de nyid las mdzub rtse gnyis bkyed de rdo rje'i
NK020(wa)001:4377: tshul du byas pa'i rgya bcas pas mgo dang dpung
NK020(wa)001:4378: ba gnyis snying mgrin lngar reg cing /
NK020(wa)001:4379: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:4380: h+aum kha gi li h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:4381: ces pas go gyon par bsam ste phyag rgya'i lha'o //
NK020(wa)001:4383: 'di ltar gnas skabs thams cad du //
NK020(wa)001:4384: yengs pa med pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK020(wa)001:4386: 'di ni mtshan ma'i lha ru grags //
NK020(wa)001:4387: de dag ni rang gi lha sgom pa'i rnal 'byor drug go //
NK020(wa)001:4388: de nas mdun gyi lha spyan drang ba'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK020(wa)001:4389: yang dag pa'i smon lam gyi stobs kyis phyogs 'dir
NK020(wa)001:4390: rin po che du ma las grub pa'i zhing khams
NK020(wa)001:4391: sa gzhi gser gyi bye ma brdal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4392: ts+aa la b+ai ra h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4393: de'i steng du 'o ma'i rgya mtsho skyon dang bral
NK020(wa)001:4394: ba pad+ma dang ut+pala la sogs pas brgyan cing 'dab
NK020(wa)001:4395: chags sna tshogs pas gang bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4396: bi ma la d+ha h+aa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:4397: de'i dbus su rin po che'i ri rab kyi steng
NK020(wa)001:4398: du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis byin gyis
NK020(wa)001:4399: brlabs pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang mtshan nyid
NK020(wa)001:4400: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbus su pad+ma'i rgyal
NK020(wa)001:4401: po yid las byung ba 'dab ma brgyad pa sngong
NK020(wa)001:4402: bu dang bcas pa ze ba rgyas shing mdzes pa'i
NK020(wa)001:4403: lte bar pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan /
NK020(wa)001:4404: steng du rin po che'i bla re dang bcas par gyur //
NK020(wa)001:4405: rdor thal gyi sor mo g.yas pa steng du yod pa byas la /
NK020(wa)001:4406: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta n+aam sarba th+aa kham
NK020(wa)001:4407: ut+ga te s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na
NK020(wa)001:4408: kham s+w+aa h+aa / zhes brjod pas rten bskyed /
NK020(wa)001:4409: de nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:4410: snod gtsang mar spos chu gtsang ma me tog dkar po dang bcas pa'i mchod yon spos kyis bdug /
NK020(wa)001:4413: sh+tmo ban+d+ha s+w+aah+aa'ang ci rigs bzlas pas byin gyis brlab la /
NK020(wa)001:4414: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:4415: zhes lan gsum gyis phyag byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:4416: rdo rje thal mo kha phye la mdzub mo gnyis
NK020(wa)001:4417: rtse sbyar te sgreng zhing mthe bong g.yas pa spyan
NK020(wa)001:4418: 'dren pa'i rgyas mchod yon btegs la /
NK020(wa)001:4419: w+aa g+ai shwa ra e h+ye hi ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4420: zhes spyi bo'i thad nas bzed zhal du phul bas /
NK020(wa)001:4421: 'jam dbyangs bsgoms pa dang 'dra ba'i ye shes pa mdun du byon par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4422: de nas thal sbyar las gung mdzub srin gsum rdo rje lnga pa ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)001:4425: mdun du gdan la bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4426: de nas g.yas pa'i mthe bos mthe chung mnan pa rdo rje rtse gsum pa ltar byas la /
NK020(wa)001:4427: sham ka re sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4429: de nas tshogs bsag pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:4430: mchod pa rnams la bsang chu 'thor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4433: dzi na dzika zhes pas bsang /
NK020(wa)001:4435: stong pa'i ngang las mchod rdzas thams cad 'phags pa
NK020(wa)001:4436: kun tu bzang po'i rnam par thar pa las byung
NK020(wa)001:4437: ba'i mchod sprin lta bu bzang zhing rgya che la
NK020(wa)001:4439: thal mo khong stong snying ga nas rim bskor gyis
NK020(wa)001:4440: btegs ste dpral bar se gol gyis dgrol bzhin du
NK020(wa)001:4443: +aa warta ya +aa wa rta ya hoh badz+ra s+pha ra na kham /
NK020(wa)001:4444: g.yon gung srin mthe bos mnan /
NK020(wa)001:4445: de'i rgyab kyi tshigs gsum par mdzub mo dang mathe'u chung gnyis gdub bu'i tshul du sbyar /
NK020(wa)001:4446: lag g.yas rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i rgya gyen bstan
NK020(wa)001:4447: g.yon gyi mtheb mdzub 'og nas bton te gung mo
NK020(wa)001:4448: bzung ba ltar byas pa'i phyag rgya bcas pas mchod
NK020(wa)001:4449: pa'i steng nas cab pe reg bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:4450: te dza te dza sam sid+hi s+aa d+h+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4451: zhes bzlas pas gzi byin bskyed /
NK020(wa)001:4453: dzi na dzika gis brtan par byas la /
NK020(wa)001:4454: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra p+au dzi te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4455: zhes sngags de kho na dang so so'i rgyas /
NK020(wa)001:4461: lag g.yas skyabs spyin gyi 'khrig ma g.yon pas bzung ba dri mchog /
NK020(wa)001:4462: thal sbyar las mdzub rtse gnyis sprad pa mthe bos mnan pa me tog /
NK020(wa)001:4463: gung srin mathe'u chung gsum gcig la gcig brten cing
NK020(wa)001:4464: mdzub rtse gnyis sprad pa mthe bos mnan pa bdug
NK020(wa)001:4465: spos / thal mo kha phye la mdzub mo gnyis
NK020(wa)001:4466: dang mthe bong gnyis cung zad bkug pa lha bshos
NK020(wa)001:4468: +aa lo k+aa ya +aa lo k+aa ya sarba bid+y+aa d+h+aa ra p+au dzi te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4469: zhes pa'i sngags dang g.yon pa'i khu tshur gyi steng
NK020(wa)001:4470: du g.yas pa'i gung mo dang mthe bong rtse sprad
NK020(wa)001:4471: pa sgreng ba'i rgyas dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:4472: gzhon nu'i sku lus 'chang ba po //
NK020(wa)001:4473: ye shes sgron ma rab rgyas shing //
NK020(wa)001:4474: 'jig rten gsum gyi mun sel ba //
NK020(wa)001:4476: zhes pas bstod pa byas te /
NK020(wa)001:4477: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK020(wa)001:4478: sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags //
NK020(wa)001:4479: dge ba kun la rjes yi rang //
NK020(wa)001:4480: chos 'khor ma lus bskor du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:4482: dge kun byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK020(wa)001:4483: de nas bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK020(wa)001:4484: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang rdo rje 'dzin pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:4485: sems can thams cad la phan pa mdzad pas bzhugs nas byin gyis rlob tu gsol s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4488: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:4489: ad+d+h+au te bi dza ya sid+d+hi sid+d+hi r+the s+w+aa h+aa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4490: ru tsi ra ma ni pra wa rta na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4491: zhes bzlas pas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK020(wa)001:4492: bdag dang mdun gyi lha gnyis ka'i thugs kar zla
NK020(wa)001:4493: dkyil la bzla bya'i sngags phreng bkod pa la dmigs
NK020(wa)001:4494: te / phreng ba bgrang bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:4496: zhes pa ci nus bzlas la /
NK020(wa)001:4497: mjug tu lha la dang bas mig blta bzhin /
NK020(wa)001:4498: na mo bud+d+ha bo d+hi sa t+wa b+h+yah zhes phyag byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:4499: srin lag gnyis kyi rgyab tu gung mo bzhag ste sbyar /
NK020(wa)001:4500: mdzub mo gnyis kyis g.yas g.yon ldog pa'i gung srin dkri /
NK020(wa)001:4501: mathe'u chung gnyis gshibs te sgreng /
NK020(wa)001:4502: mthe bong gnyis mdzub mo'i tshigs dbus mar bzhag pa bum pa'i rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:4503: bdag gi ba zlas brjod kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK020(wa)001:4504: 'di dngos grub kyi don du bcom ldan 'das la
NK020(wa)001:4505: dbul lo // mgon po khyod kyis mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4507: de nas slar btang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:4508: mdun gyi lha la mchod bstod byas nas bzod par gsol te mchod yon phul la /
NK020(wa)001:4511: spyan 'dren pa'i phyag rgya gyen du dkrol bas /
NK020(wa)001:4512: spyan drangs pa'i lha gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa gshegs par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4513: bdag lhar gsal ba ma bsdus par 'jam dpal gyi nga rgyal la gnas pas /
NK020(wa)001:4514: mdun gyi dkyil 'khor la dmigs nas tree lo kya dang /
NK020(wa)001:4516: s+w+aa b+h+aa was mdun rten gyis mtshon pa'i ma dag
NK020(wa)001:4517: pa'i snang ba sbyangs te stong pa nyid du gyur
NK020(wa)001:4518: / stong ba'i ngang las yang dag pa'i smon lam
NK020(wa)001:4519: gyi stobs kyis sa phyogs 'dir rin po che du
NK020(wa)001:4520: ma las grub pa'i zhing khams sa gzhi gser gyi
NK020(wa)001:4522: ts+aa la b+ai ra h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4523: de'i steng du 'o ma'i rgya mtsho skyon dang bral
NK020(wa)001:4524: ba pad+ma dang ut+pala la sogs pas brgyan cing 'dab
NK020(wa)001:4525: chags sna tshogs pas gang bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4526: bi ma la d+ha h+aa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:4527: de'i dbus su rin po che'i ri rab kyi steng
NK020(wa)001:4528: du de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis byin gyis
NK020(wa)001:4529: brlabs pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang rin po
NK020(wa)001:4530: che sna bdun las grub pa'i khang pa brtsegs pa
NK020(wa)001:4537: shin tu rnam par phye bas mdzes par byas pa /
NK020(wa)001:4541: them skas bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:4542: rdo rje 'dzin pa thams cad nye bar 'du ba'i gnas /
NK020(wa)001:4543: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad lhag par dgyes pas rnam par rol ba'i gzhal med khang chen po /
NK020(wa)001:4544: yon tan mtha' yas pa'i rgyan gyis yongs su spras
NK020(wa)001:4545: pa'i dbus su pad+ma 'dab ma drug pa rnam par
NK020(wa)001:4546: rgyas pas bskor ba'i lte bar pad+ma'i gdan sum sgrigs
NK020(wa)001:4547: kyi dbus dang g.yas kyi steng du zla ba'i dkyil
NK020(wa)001:4549: g.yon gyi steng du nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'bar bas mdzes pa /
NK020(wa)001:4550: 'dab ma drug sogs lha gnas gzhan rnams su'ang so so'i gdan gyi rim pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4551: steng du rin po che'i bla bre dang bcas par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4552: phyag rgya sngar ltar bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:4553: na mahsarba ta tha ga ta n+aam sarba th+aa kham
NK020(wa)001:4554: ud+ga te s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na
NK020(wa)001:4556: de nas so so'i sngags lan re brjod pas lha bsgom ste /
NK020(wa)001:4563: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+h+aa sarba d+ha r+m+aahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+hi & ham /
NK020(wa)001:4565: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK020(wa)001:4566: shi b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ud+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK020(wa)001:4567: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4569: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:4571: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta a ba lo ki te sam b+ha ra sam b+ha ra h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:4573: dz+ny+aa na a ba lo ki te na mahs man+ta
NK020(wa)001:4574: s+pha ra na rasmi sam b+ha ba sa ma ya
NK020(wa)001:4575: ma h+aa ma ni du ru du ru h+r+ai da
NK020(wa)001:4576: ya dz+wa la ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4578: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam gra he shwa ri pra
NK020(wa)001:4579: b+hany+tsa dza ti ma h+aa sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa
NK020(wa)001:4585: badz+ra ang ku sha dzah sogs bzhis sgeg sogs lha mo bcu gnyis te /
NK020(wa)001:4586: rang rang gi sngags brjod pa'i mod la lha so so yid kyis bsgom nas gsal gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:4587: dbus kyi gdan la 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa
NK020(wa)001:4588: sku mdog gser btso ma'i mdangs can 'od kyi d+r+wa
NK020(wa)001:4589: ba 'gyed pa / zhi 'dzum sgeg pa'i nyams dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:4591: g.yas shes rab kyi ral gri sngo sangs dpung pa'i thad kar 'phyar zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4592: g.yon ut+pala sngon po'i rtsa ba thugs kar 'dzin pa
NK020(wa)001:4593: snyan gyi thad kar kha byed pa'i steng na glegs
NK020(wa)001:4594: bam 'dzin pa / dbu skra ral pa'i zur phud lnga dang ldan pa /
NK020(wa)001:4595: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:4596: pad zla'i gdan la zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:4597: de'i g.yas logs kyi gdan pad zla la 'phags pa
NK020(wa)001:4598: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug sku mdog dkar po zhal
NK020(wa)001:4600: phyag dang po gnyis thugs kar thal mo sbyar zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4601: 'og ma gnyis shel phreng dang pad dkar sdong bu 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:4603: dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:4604: g.yon logs kyi gdan pad nyi la gsang ba'i bdag
NK020(wa)001:4605: po sku mdog sngon po khros pa'i nyams can zhal
NK020(wa)001:4607: g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon sdig mdzub mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:4608: zhabs g.yon brkyang ba'i dor stabs /
NK020(wa)001:4610: dar dang rin po che dang sbrul gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:4611: phyi rol pad+ma 'dab ma drug la gtso bo gsum
NK020(wa)001:4612: po zhal nub tu phyogs pa'i mdun nas brtsams te
NK020(wa)001:4613: g.yas bskor du / sbyong ba'i lha sh+aakya thub pa
NK020(wa)001:4614: dkar po thugs kar thal mo khong stong du sbyar
NK020(wa)001:4615: ba'i nang du a yig dkar pos mtshan pa /
NK020(wa)001:4616: spel ba'i lha rnam par snang mdzad ser po mdzod
NK020(wa)001:4617: spur rin po che sgrom bu'i phyag rgya kham sngon
NK020(wa)001:4618: pos mtshan pa / bsgyur ba'i lha khro bo bdud
NK020(wa)001:4619: rtsi 'khyil ba ljang sngon phyag gnyis mthe bong bsnol
NK020(wa)001:4620: nas sor mo lhag ma kha 'gram du phyir 'gyed
NK020(wa)001:4622: thob pa'i lha rin 'byung ser po g.yas mdzub mo
NK020(wa)001:4623: thugs kar sgreng zhing g.yon mchog sbyin la tram ser
NK020(wa)001:4624: pos mtshan pa / tshim pa'i lha don yod grub
NK020(wa)001:4625: pa ljang gu g.yas khur tshur thugs kar bkan zhing
NK020(wa)001:4626: g.yon mchog sbyin 'degs pa h+aa ljang gis mtshan pa
NK020(wa)001:4627: pos mtshan pa / / dbang du byed pa 'i
NK020(wa)001:4628: lha phyag rdor sngon po phyag gnyis sor mo nang
