NK020(wa)001:4629: du bsnol ba'i rgya spyi bor bcings pa la dzahdamara
NK020(wa)001:4630: pos mtshan pa / / pos mtshan pa / thub
NK020(wa)001:4631: pa tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs dang gzhan rnams
NK020(wa)001:4632: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:4633: lha snam la nub nas brtsams te phyogs bzhir /
NK020(wa)001:4634: sgeg mo dkar mo me long /
NK020(wa)001:4635: phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK020(wa)001:4636: glu ma dmar mo pi wam /
NK020(wa)001:4637: gar ma ljang khu gar rgya //
NK020(wa)001:4638: nub byang nas brtsams te mtshams bzhir spos ma dkar ser spos khang /
NK020(wa)001:4639: me tog ma dmar ser me tog /
NK020(wa)001:4640: mar me ma dmar ljang mar me /
NK020(wa)001:4641: dri chab ma dkar ljang dur phor /
NK020(wa)001:4642: shar nas brtsams te sgo bzhir lcags kyu ma dkar po lcags kyu /
NK020(wa)001:4643: zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa /
NK020(wa)001:4644: lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags sgrog /
NK020(wa)001:4645: dril bu ma ljang gu dril bu bsnams pa /
NK020(wa)001:4646: thams cad kyang zhi zhing 'dzum pa dang rin po
NK020(wa)001:4647: ches brgyan pa ste rtsa ba'i lha nyi shu rtsa
NK020(wa)001:4648: gcig go / gzhan yang mgron thabs kyi lha gtso bo rigs gsum gyi 'khor du /
NK020(wa)001:4649: rigs kyi gtso bo de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4652: rigs kyi pho nya phyag brnyan la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:4653: lha snam dang phyi'i khor yug la dpa' bar 'gro ba sogs skal bzang gi sems dpa' bcu drug /
NK020(wa)001:4654: dus ldan ma la sogs pa bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:4657: khyab 'jug sogs dkyil 'khor du 'du bar 'os pa'i
NK020(wa)001:4658: lha thams cad kyang bzhugs shing phyogs thams cad du
NK020(wa)001:4660: de nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:4661: rang gi mdun du byin gyis brlabs pa'i mchod yon dang /
NK020(wa)001:4663: lag gnyis spyan 'dren pa'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:4665: 'phags pa'i tshogs thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4666: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gzigs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4667: deng dus drug lha'i nyi ma thams cad dge /
NK020(wa)001:4668: bza' skar thams cad bkra shis /
NK020(wa)001:4669: dgra bcom pa thams cad zag pa zad /
NK020(wa)001:4670: sangs rgyas thams cad rdzu 'phrul che ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK020(wa)001:4671: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas
NK020(wa)001:4672: pa spyan 'dren zhing mchi na gshegs par mdzad du
NK020(wa)001:4673: gsol lo // stobs bcu'i rtsal mnga' mi yi seng ge gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:4674: gti mug mun sel 'jig rten sgron me gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:4675: nyon mongs nad sel sman pa'i rgyal po gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:4676: bdun bzhi pham mdzad thar pa'i lam ston gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:4677: dbang mchog rgyal po 'dir byon phrin las mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:4679: bud+h+aa d+harma sam g+ha a sa mee t+r+ai sa me ma h+aa sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4681: spyan drang ba'i phyag rgya des mchod yon btegs spyi bo'i thad nas bzed zhal du sbreng bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:4682: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK020(wa)001:4683: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)001:4684: rigs gsum rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas //
NK020(wa)001:4685: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po nas //
NK020(wa)001:4688: byin gyis rlob phyir gshegs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:4689: bdag gi mchod yon 'di bzhes la //
NK020(wa)001:4690: mchod pas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:4691: dzi na dzika w+aa g+ai shwa ra /
NK020(wa)001:4692: a ro lika lo ke shwa ra /
NK020(wa)001:4693: badz+ra d+h+r+ai ka badz+ra p+aa ni sa pa ri w+aa
NK020(wa)001:4694: ra e h+ye hi ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa
NK020(wa)001:4695: / zhes pas mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs te /
NK020(wa)001:4696: gzhal yas khang gi sgo dbye ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:4697: phyogs bcur rgya yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:4698: rin chen lhun grub gzhal yas khang //
NK020(wa)001:4699: dbye sdom rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK020(wa)001:4700: sri zhu'i tshul du sgo dabye'o //
NK020(wa)001:4701: badz+ra s+pho ta ga ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4702: zhes rdo rje nang bsdam dbye ba'i rgyas sgo phye /
NK020(wa)001:4703: de nas nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i lha la bsu ba'i mchod yon sbreng bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:4704: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)001:4705: tshur gshegs 'dir ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:4706: bdag gi mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:4707: thugs la dgongs shing gnang bar mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:4708: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra
NK020(wa)001:4709: p+au dza ga ga na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK020(wa)001:4710: / de nas lha rnams gzhal yas khang gi sgo nas byon pa la /
NK020(wa)001:4711: ye shes rin chen gzhal yas su //
NK020(wa)001:4713: bde gshegs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:4714: 'gro ba'i don du bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:4716: ces rdo rje'i 'dug stangs kyi sngags rgya sngar ltar dang /
NK020(wa)001:4717: thal mo sbyar ba kha phye la /
NK020(wa)001:4718: ka ma la ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4719: zhes pad+ma'i 'dug stangs kyi sngags rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:4720: phyag rgya de nyid las sor mo dbus ma gnyis gcig tu sbyar la /
NK020(wa)001:4721: badz+ra ka ma la h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:4722: ces dpa' bo'i 'dug stangs kyi sngags rgyas gdan phul ba la /
NK020(wa)001:4723: dam tshig pa dang gnyis med du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)001:4724: de nas mchod pa gsar ba rnams sngar ltar byin
NK020(wa)001:4725: gyis brlab cing rnying pa rnams kyang kha gsos la
NK020(wa)001:4726: / ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni /
NK020(wa)001:4727: de bzhin gshegs kun bkrus gyur pa //
NK020(wa)001:4728: de bzhin bdag gis lha rnams la //
NK020(wa)001:4729: gtsang ma'i chab kyis khrus gsol lo //
NK020(wa)001:4730: sarba de ba ta artsi ta a mri ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4732: dngos su khrus chas med na /
NK020(wa)001:4733: mnyam pa'i thal mo kha phye la mtheb mdzub sprad pa'i phyag rgyas so //
NK020(wa)001:4734: de nas de la kha dog sogs kyi rkang pa lnga pa /
NK020(wa)001:4735: 'phags pa rdo rje 'dzin dang 'jam dpal dbyangs //
NK020(wa)001:4736: zhes barjesa pas gos rgyan dbul /
NK020(wa)001:4737: gtsang zhing gtsang ma las byung ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:4738: lha rdzas bzang po'i dri 'di dag /
NK020(wa)001:4739: bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyi /
NK020(wa)001:4740: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:4741: +aa ha ra a ha ra sarba bid+h+ya d+ha ra p+au dzi te s+w+aa h+aa'i sngags rgyas dri chab /
NK020(wa)001:4742: gtsang zhing gtsang ma las skyes pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:4743: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog 'di //
NK020(wa)001:4744: bdag gis dad pas bzhes nas bdag +aa ha ra'i sngags rgyas me tog /
NK020(wa)001:4745: dri zhim rgyas pa lha yi rdzas //
NK020(wa)001:4747: bdag gis bzhes nas +aa ha ra'i sngags rgyas bdug spos //
NK020(wa)001:4748: sman rnams bcud ni yi gar 'ong //
NK020(wa)001:4749: sngags kyi zhal zas bshos 'di dag /
NK020(wa)001:4750: bdag gis bzhes nas +aa ha ra'i sngags rgyas zhal zas /
NK020(wa)001:4751: gnod rnams 'joms shing bkra shis la //
NK020(wa)001:4752: dge zhing mun pa rnam sel 'di //
NK020(wa)001:4753: bdag gis bzhes nas +aa lo k+aa ya +aa lo
NK020(wa)001:4754: k+aa ya sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra p+au dzi te s+w+aa
NK020(wa)001:4755: h+aa'i sngags rgyas mar me dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:4757: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK020(wa)001:4758: thams cad mkhyen pa ston pa po //
NK020(wa)001:4759: bsod nams yon tan rgya mtsho zhing //
NK020(wa)001:4760: de bzhin gshegs pa phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:4761: dag pa 'dod chags bral ba'i rgyu //
NK020(wa)001:4762: dge bas ngan song las grol ba //
NK020(wa)001:4763: gcig tu don dam mchog gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:4764: zhi gyur chos la grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK020(wa)001:4765: bslab pa dag la rab tu gus //
NK020(wa)001:4766: zhing gi dam pa yon tan zhing //
NK020(wa)001:4767: dge 'dun la yang gzhon nu'i sku lus 'chang ba po //
NK020(wa)001:4768: ye shes sgron me rab brgyas shing //
NK020(wa)001:4769: 'jig rten gsum gyi mun sel ba //
NK020(wa)001:4770: 'jam dpal dbyangs la sangs rgyas kun gyis rab tu basngagasa //
NK020(wa)001:4771: yon tan dam pa kun bsags pa //
NK020(wa)001:4772: spyan ras gzigs zhes mtshan gsol ba'i /
NK020(wa)001:4773: rtag par brtse la stobs po che la drag shul ldan //
NK020(wa)001:4774: rig sngags rgyal po dge ba can //
NK020(wa)001:4775: gdul dka' mtha' dag 'dul ba po //
NK020(wa)001:4776: rdo rje 'dzin la sbyangs spel bsgyur bas mchod sbyin gnas //
NK020(wa)001:4777: thob tshim dbang byed sngags kyi lha //
NK020(wa)001:4778: snang mdzad bdud rtsi rin 'byung thub //
NK020(wa)001:4779: don grub phyag rdor la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:4780: gzugs mdzes phreng ba dbyangs snyan gar //
NK020(wa)001:4781: nyer mchod bzhi dang phyag rgya bzhis //
NK020(wa)001:4782: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:4783: lha mo bcu gnyis la bde gshegs pad+ma rdo rje yi //
NK020(wa)001:4784: rigs gyur de bzhin gshegs dang yum //
NK020(wa)001:4785: rigs kyi sems dpa' pho nya dang //
NK020(wa)001:4786: phyag brnyan bcas pa la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:4787: nor bu'i rigs dang glang po'i rigs //
NK020(wa)001:4788: lnga rtsen rigs dang ba glang gi /
NK020(wa)001:4789: rigs su gtogs pa'i dkar phyogs kyi //
NK020(wa)001:4792: na mahsarba bud+d+ha bo d+hi sa t+wa n+aam sarba tra
NK020(wa)001:4793: sam ku ru mi ta a b+hi dz+ny+aa r+aa shi
NK020(wa)001:4794: ni na mo stu te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4796: 'dir glan gyi yig rnying du lha so so'i bstod pa rgyas par 'byung zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4797: rin chen phreng ba de las cung zad bsdus te bkod mod //
NK020(wa)001:4798: 'dir bris pa ni shin tu bsdus pa ste /
NK020(wa)001:4799: spro zhing nus na de gnyis gang rigs las blangs na legs par 'gyur ro //
NK020(wa)001:4803: badz+ra p+aa ni gsum po stong phrag sogs ji tsam nus dang /
NK020(wa)001:4805: many+dzu sh+r+ai ku m+aa ra m+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4807: a ba lo ki te k+aa ru na ma ram h+aum dzah s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4809: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4811: sbyang bsgyur sogs drug dang lha mo bcu gnyis kyi sngags rnams nyer gcig tsam re dang //
NK020(wa)001:4815: gsum yang brgya rtsa re bzla ste /
NK020(wa)001:4816: bsdu na de tsam gyis chog /
NK020(wa)001:4817: yang spro zhing nus na mgron thabs kyi lha rnams kyi sngags kyang bdun tsam re bzla ste /
NK020(wa)001:4818: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam bee ro tsa na s+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4820: a mi d+he ba h+r+aihs+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4822: badz+ra ak+sho b+h+yah h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4824: ru ru spu ru dz+wa la ti sh+tha sid+d+hi lo tsan na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4826: pan+da li ki ta ram pa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4828: sug sme dz+ny+aa na dzahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4830: ma h+aa sh+r+ai ye tsi ri mi ri ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4832: trag sa ri te te shan te shen s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4834: na mahs man+ta badz+ra n+aam sarba d+har+m+aa ni se ta ni badz+ra si pa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4836: badz+ra ta badz+ra pra b+ha te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4838: ban+d+ha ban+d+ha mo ha ya mo ha ya badz+ro d+d+h+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4840: dz+wa la dz+wa la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4842: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:4844: khad+ga ban+d+ha s+pho ta ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4846: a mri te ha na ha na bi du na
NK020(wa)001:4847: bi du na go sa kha a mri te ma
NK020(wa)001:4848: kha s+w+aa h+aa / bdud rtsi thab sbyor /
NK020(wa)001:4851: mo ga na pa ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4855: de nas bum pa la gzungs thag gtad de rnams bum du rigs gsum dang /
NK020(wa)001:4860: a b+hi she ka sta gon gyi skabs ltar bzla
NK020(wa)001:4861: zhing bum chu nus ldan du gyur par bsam mo
NK020(wa)001:4862: // de nas thal mo bkan pa las mdzub rtse bkug ste /
NK020(wa)001:4864: thal sbyar pad+ma kha phye ba ltar bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:4866: thal mo ldog ste sbyar la mthe bong dang mathe'u chung gnyis sbyar la /
NK020(wa)001:4868: ces snga rgya rnams lan gsum gsum gyis rgyas btab cing /
NK020(wa)001:4869: sher snying lta bu'i mdo cung zad klag go //
NK020(wa)001:4870: de nas gtor ma btang zhing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:4871: 'das gtor dang cha gsum gtor ma sngar bzhin dang /
NK020(wa)001:4872: dbang chog ltar slob dpon 'jug cing slob ma la dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:4874: mchod pa kha gsos te byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)001:4875: dri sogs mchod pa lnga sngags rgya tsam gyis phul nas /
NK020(wa)001:4876: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4877: khyed rnam la mkhyen pa'i ye shes /
NK020(wa)001:4879: mdzad pa'i phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba lags pas /
NK020(wa)001:4880: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:4881: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu thams cad sku tshe brtan
NK020(wa)001:4882: zhing thugs kyi bzhed pa'i don lhun gyis grub pa
NK020(wa)001:4883: dang / bdag dang sems can thams cad bde zhing skyid par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4884: khyad par du'ang bdag dang mkha' mnyam gyi sems can
NK020(wa)001:4885: thams cad la rang rang gi skal ba dang 'tshams
NK020(wa)001:4886: pa'i phrin las rnam pa gsum dang /
NK020(wa)001:4887: dngos grub rnam pa gsum dang /
NK020(wa)001:4888: byang chub rnam pa gsum gyi bka' drin stsal nas /
NK020(wa)001:4889: mthar thug thams cad kyang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen
NK020(wa)001:4890: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'jog par mdzad du
NK020(wa)001:4893: ma rnyed yogs su sogs kyis bzod par gsol /
NK020(wa)001:4895: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyis brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:4896: gshegs na mchod yon phul la //
NK020(wa)001:4897: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad /
NK020(wa)001:4898: sogs kyi mthar gshegs su gsol ba'i rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:4899: w+aa g+ai shwa ra lo ke shwa ra badz+ra p+aa ni gats+tsha /
NK020(wa)001:4900: zhes se gol dang bcas te phyag rgya gyen du bkrol bas /
NK020(wa)001:4901: spyan drangs pa'i lha gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa gshegs /
NK020(wa)001:4902: sngags kyi sprul pa'i lha dam tshig pa rnams rim gyis bdag la thim /
NK020(wa)001:4903: bdag gi lha'i sku gzugs zla ba'i steng gi sngags phreng la thim /
NK020(wa)001:4905: de rnam smin gyi lus la thim par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:4906: g.yon pa'i thal mo gan rgyal gyi steng du g.yas
NK020(wa)001:4907: pa'i rgyab sbyar sor mo rnams bsnol ba'i rtse mo
NK020(wa)001:4908: bkug ste rtsa ba'i phyogs su bstan pa g.yon du
NK020(wa)001:4909: bskor bzhin du / hu lu hu lu tsan+da li ma tam gi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:4910: zhes pa'i sngags rgyas mtshams bcings pa rnams dgrol bar bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:4912: bdag gi dge ba'i las rnams 'di dag gis /
NK020(wa)001:4913: 'jig rten du ni myur du 'tshang rgya shog /
NK020(wa)001:4914: 'gro la phan phyir chos rnams ston bgyid cing /
NK020(wa)001:4915: sdug bsngal gyis gzir sems can sgrol bar shog /
NK020(wa)001:4916: ces sogs rgya cher gdab bo //
NK020(wa)001:4918: bcom ldan gser mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
NK020(wa)001:4919: 'jig rten gsum mgon 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi sku //
NK020(wa)001:4920: bde gshegs sku yi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK020(wa)001:4921: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:4922: bcom ldan dngul mdog ri yi 'jig rten gsum mgon spyan ras gzigs kyi gsung //
NK020(wa)001:4923: bde gshegs gsung gi bkra shis bkra shis des kyang
NK020(wa)001:4924: bcom ldan mthing mdog 'jig rten gsum mgon phyag na
NK020(wa)001:4925: rdo rje'i thugs // bde gshegs thugs kyi bkra shis
NK020(wa)001:4926: des kyang shar lho nub byang dpal be 'khor lo
NK020(wa)001:4927: rdo rje'i thugs // dang // pad+ma rgyal mtshan gdugs bum dung dang nya //
NK020(wa)001:4928: lha mo brgyad kyi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK020(wa)001:4929: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:4930: ces brjod cing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas me tog 'thor /
NK020(wa)001:4931: de rjes sher snying gi mdo tshar gcig klog go //
NK020(wa)001:4933: rigs gsum so so la sbyar ba 'i lha sogs
NK020(wa)001:4934: drug gis bskor ba lha bdun ma'i dkyil 'khor gsum
NK020(wa)001:4938: g.yas su so so'i rigs bdag /
NK020(wa)001:4941: rgyab tu pho nya ste lha lnga ma gsum gyi
NK020(wa)001:4942: lha snam la khro bcu bkod pa lha bco lnga
NK020(wa)001:4944: de'i steng du sgeg sogs bcu gnyis bsnan pas nyer bdun ma gsum /
NK020(wa)001:4945: yang na sems dpa' bcu drug bsnan pa sogs dang /
NK020(wa)001:4946: 'ga' zhig gtso bo rnam 'joms kyis byas pa sogs bzhed srol mang na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:4947: lha'i grangs de dag ni bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las thor /
NK020(wa)001:4948: rigs gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
NK020(wa)001:4950: yang rnam snang sogs kyi gtso byas pa'i lha lnga
NK020(wa)001:4951: ma gsum dkyil 'khor gcig tu bsdus pa'i bco lnga'i
NK020(wa)001:4952: steng du sbyang ba'i lha sogs drug bsnan na gnad
NK020(wa)001:4954: sngon gyi mkhas pa lugs 'di la tshad mar gyur pa /
NK020(wa)001:4956: gtso bo'i rigs gsum rnam snang sogs rigs kyi gtso bo la ma mdzad par /
NK020(wa)001:4957: 'jam dbyangs sogs rigs kyi bdag po la ngos bzung zhing /
NK020(wa)001:4958: lam khyer gyi dus su sngags kyang w+aa g+ai shwa
NK020(wa)001:4959: ri sogs 'byung bas na 'dir bkod pa nyid man
NK020(wa)001:4960: ngag gi gnad dang 'byor ba yin no //
NK020(wa)001:4961: bla ma'i gsum ngag bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK020(wa)001:4962: shes rab dbang pos myangs pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)001:4963: rang gzhung rnam dag ston pa'i chos //
NK020(wa)001:4964: skal bzang re ba'i dpal du sbyin //
NK020(wa)001:4965: bya spyod thun mong gi theg pa'i sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:4968: gdod nas mi 'gyur chos dbyings klong //
NK020(wa)001:4969: thogs med ye shes rdo rje'i rtsal //
NK020(wa)001:4970: rigs lngar ston mdzad bla ma la //
NK020(wa)001:4971: phyag byas yo ga'i sgrub thabs bshad //
NK020(wa)001:4972: yan lag gi dkyil 'khor drug pa yo ga la /
NK020(wa)001:4973: thog mar lha sta gon ni /
NK020(wa)001:4974: lha gnas nges pa'i phyir skya thig btab cing /
NK020(wa)001:4975: mchod gtor rgyas par bshams la /
NK020(wa)001:4976: sngon gtor yak+sha dang me'i sngags rgyas bsang /
NK020(wa)001:4978: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod du
NK020(wa)001:4979: yig zhu ba las byung ba'i gtor rdzas rnams 'dod
NK020(wa)001:4980: yon bdud rtsi'i phung po zad mi shes par bsam
NK020(wa)001:4981: la / a k+aa ro brjod pas brlab /
NK020(wa)001:4982: b+h+au mi pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ra na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo nas /
NK020(wa)001:4983: ga na kham ba ling+ta s+w+aa h+aas phul /
NK020(wa)001:4984: gang dag 'dir gnas lha dang klu /
NK020(wa)001:4988: badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum gis rang rdor sems su bskyed nas mchod pa sngar ltar bsang sbyangs /
NK020(wa)001:4989: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal
NK020(wa)001:4990: yas khang mtshan nyid rdzogs pa'i phyi nang kun tu
NK020(wa)001:4991: las rin po che'i snod du yig zhu ba las
NK020(wa)001:4992: byung ba'i mchod rdzas rnams kun tu bzang po'i mchod
NK020(wa)001:4993: pa'i sprin phung ltar bzang zhing rgya che ba nam
NK020(wa)001:4996: tsan+dana chu la bden pa brdar ba yis //
NK020(wa)001:4997: phyogs bcur gtor bas yongs su dag gyur te /
NK020(wa)001:4998: mi btsang dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag gyur nas //
NK020(wa)001:4999: dri med yon tan dag dang ldan gyu cig /
NK020(wa)001:5000: sarba bi shod+ha ni h+aum h+r+aih th+aa /
NK020(wa)001:5008: de nas skyabs 'gro nas bzung bdag gi rnal 'byor rdzogs par byas la /
NK020(wa)001:5011: stong pa'i ngang las srung ba'i 'khor lo yangs shing
NK020(wa)001:5012: rgya che ba'i nang 'byung bzhi ri rab dang bcas
NK020(wa)001:5013: pa'i steng du gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi
NK020(wa)001:5014: pa nyis rim mtshan nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i lte
NK020(wa)001:5015: ba ling tshe dgu'i dbus dang phyogs bzhir 'khor lo
NK020(wa)001:5017: lha gnas kun tu so so'i gdan rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5018: de nas so so'i gnas su rang sngags bdun re
NK020(wa)001:5019: brjod cing dri'i thig le me tog gi tshom bu
NK020(wa)001:5021: dbus kyi gdan la las bcom ldan 'das rnam par
NK020(wa)001:5022: snang mdzad ser po kun tu zhal byang chub mchog
NK020(wa)001:5023: gi phyag rgya can rtsibs bzhir sbas yum bzhi phyogs
NK020(wa)001:5024: kyi ling tshe bzhi'i lte ba'i gdan la shar du
NK020(wa)001:5029: so so'i rtsibs la rang rigs kyi sems dpa' bzhi bzhis bskor ba /
NK020(wa)001:5031: grwa bzhi dang sgo rnams su sgeg sogs bcu gnyis
NK020(wa)001:5032: gzhal yas khang phyi ma'i snam bu'i phyogs rer byang
NK020(wa)001:5033: chub sems dpa' bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug rnams gsal
NK020(wa)001:5035: ma lus sems can gyis spyan drangs //
NK020(wa)001:5036: dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis med du byas pa la /
NK020(wa)001:5037: sarba ta t+aa ga ta push+pe p+au dza me g+ha sogs nas /
NK020(wa)001:5039: de nas bum pa sta gon ni /
NK020(wa)001:5040: spyir dkyil 'khor gyi sgo drug du khrus byed pa 'jug sgo'i bum pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:5044: mchod pa'i gar bum ste lnga'am /
NK020(wa)001:5045: lha bum rnam rgyal la bsdus te bzhi bshad na'ang 'grub dka' bas /
NK020(wa)001:5046: 'dir rnam rgyal dang las bum gnyis su bsdus te /
NK020(wa)001:5047: bum pa gnyis ka lha'i mtshan ma can mgul chings
NK020(wa)001:5048: kha rgyan sogs chas su bcug pa'i nang du sman
NK020(wa)001:5051: dri lnga rnams spos chu dang sbyar bas bkang ba'i steng du gzungs rdor bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:5053: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla'i steng du b+h+r+aum las
NK020(wa)001:5054: bum pa mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5055: rnam rgyal bum pa'i nang du dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK020(wa)001:5057: las bum du rdo rje gnod sbyin rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5059: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:5061: me tog la sogs pas mchod nas /
NK020(wa)001:5064: bud+d+h+aa bee ro tsa na sogs dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i sngags rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:5068: a b+hi she ka'ang ci rigs bzlas mthar me tog sogs kyis mchod de /
NK020(wa)001:5070: mchod yon phul bas dam tshig pa bum chur gyur par mos la /
NK020(wa)001:5071: yig brgyas brtan par bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:5072: bdug spos gyis kyang bdug go /
NK020(wa)001:5073: de nas cha gsum gtor ma btang la /
NK020(wa)001:5079: rdo rje dbyings gtso khyod la 'dud //
NK020(wa)001:5080: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK020(wa)001:5081: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK020(wa)001:5082: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song zhing //
NK020(wa)001:5083: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:5084: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK020(wa)001:5086: de nas rgyun bshags sngon du 'gro ba can gyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:5087: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:5088: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK020(wa)001:5089: sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags //
NK020(wa)001:5090: 'gro ba'i dge la rjes yi rang //
NK020(wa)001:5091: sangs rgyas byang chub yid kyis bzung //
NK020(wa)001:5092: sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs mchog la //
NK020(wa)001:5093: byang chub bar du bdag skyabs mchis //
NK020(wa)001:5094: rang gzhan don gnyis rab bsgrub phyir //
NK020(wa)001:5095: byang chub sems ni bskyed par bgyis //
NK020(wa)001:5096: byang chub mchog gi sesama ni bskyed bgyis nas //
NK020(wa)001:5097: sems can thams cad bdag gi mgron du gnyer //
NK020(wa)001:5098: byang chub spyod mchog yid 'ong spyad par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:5099: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:5103: slob ma'i snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor nya gang ba /
NK020(wa)001:5104: de'i ster du h+aum las rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa gsal bar mos la /
NK020(wa)001:5105: sarba yo ga tsit+ta ut+pa da y+aa mi /
NK020(wa)001:5107: rdo rje rtse lnga pas dngos su reg cing /
NK020(wa)001:5108: su ra te sa ma ya s+t+wam ho sid+d+hi badz+ra ya th+aa su kham /
NK020(wa)001:5110: de nas las bum gyi chus bsang gtor byas la /
NK020(wa)001:5113: slob ma rdo rje sems dpar gsal ba'i snying gar h+aum las rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:5114: dpral bar t+r+aam las rin po che /
NK020(wa)001:5116: spyi bor kam las sna tshogs de rdo rje rnams bsgoms pas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK020(wa)001:5121: badz+ra gan+d+he sogs kyis sbyin par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:5122: de nas so shing tshad ldan /
NK020(wa)001:5123: badz+ra sa t+wa bdun bzlas pas byin gyis brlabs nas
NK020(wa)001:5124: thal mo'i bar du sbyin pa rtsa ba 'og tu
NK020(wa)001:5125: bstan la dri'i man+dala gyi dbus su /
NK020(wa)001:5126: badz+ra ha sa has dor du bcug la dngos grub kyi ltas brtag /
NK020(wa)001:5127: rmi lam gsal ba'i phyir khyor chu /
NK020(wa)001:5128: h+r+aihbi shud+d+ha s+w+aa h+aas lan gsum blud /
NK020(wa)001:5129: bar chad bsrung phyir skud pa sum sgril mdud pa
NK020(wa)001:5130: gsum pa nyis bskor gyis dpung pa g.yon par bcings
NK020(wa)001:5131: te / bsang chu dang bcas pa'i rdo rje rgya gram du reg cing /
NK020(wa)001:5134: d+h+r+ai bzlas pa'i ku sha che chung stan dang sngas kyi don du sbyin nas /
NK020(wa)001:5136: 'jig rten du ni kun mkhyen dag /
NK020(wa)001:5137: u du m+wa ra'i me tog bzhin //
NK020(wa)001:5138: brgya lam na ni res 'ga' zhig /
NK020(wa)001:5140: gsang sngags spyod pa'i tshul 'byung ba //
NK020(wa)001:5141: de bas kyang ni dkon pa ste //
NK020(wa)001:5142: gang gis sems can mnyam med don //
NK020(wa)001:5143: bla med byed par nus pa yin //
NK020(wa)001:5144: bskal pa bye ba du ma ru //
NK020(wa)001:5145: sngon du sdig pa byas pa gang //
NK020(wa)001:5147: de dag zad par 'gyur yin na //
NK020(wa)001:5148: grags pa mtha' yas sngags spyod pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:5149: tshul la gnas na smos ci dgos //
NK020(wa)001:5150: skyob pa'i gsang sngags bzlas na ni //
NK020(wa)001:5152: gang gis spyod pa'i mchog 'di la //
NK020(wa)001:5153: blo gros shin tu mi g.yo na //
NK020(wa)001:5154: sdug bsngal thams cad 'byung ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:5156: bdag nyid chen po khyed rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)001:5157: rnyed pa mnyam med de ring rnyed //
NK020(wa)001:5158: gang phyir rgyal ba sras bcas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:5159: bdag nyid chen po kun gyi ni //
NK020(wa)001:5160: bstan pa 'di la khyed rnams kun //
NK020(wa)001:5161: yongs su bzung ste skye bzhin pa //
NK020(wa)001:5162: de phyir khyed rnams theg chen du //
NK020(wa)001:5163: sang ni rab tu skye bar 'gyur //
NK020(wa)001:5164: theg pa chen po cher 'byung ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:5165: lam mchog 'di ni dpal dang ldan //
NK020(wa)001:5166: khyed rnams 'dir ni dong bas na //
NK020(wa)001:5167: rang byung skal pa chen po pa //
NK020(wa)001:5168: 'jig rten thams cad mkhyen pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:5169: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK020(wa)001:5170: zhes brjod cing don bshad nas /
NK020(wa)001:5171: bu kye sang ni dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK020(wa)001:5172: mthong bar 'gyur ro nyol zhig dang //
NK020(wa)001:5173: rmi lam mthong ba gang yin pa //
NK020(wa)001:5174: de kun nga la legs par smros //
NK020(wa)001:5175: zhes gdams la rang gnas su btang ngo //
NK020(wa)001:5176: de nas lha sta gon gyi 'phros snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:5177: pus btsugs kyis 'dug la spos 'thul zhing dril bu 'khrol bas /
NK020(wa)001:5178: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)001:5179: rig sngags rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:5180: bdag ni brtse bar gyur nas su //
NK020(wa)001:5181: slob ma rnams la brtse ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:5182: khyed rnams la yang mchod pa'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:5184: bcom ldan bdag ni gus pa la //
NK020(wa)001:5185: de bas snang ba mdzad pa'i rigs //
NK020(wa)001:5186: sangs rgyas 'jig rten mgon brtse dang //
NK020(wa)001:5187: byang chub sems dpa' dgra bcom dang //
NK020(wa)001:5188: gsang sngags lha gzhan gang lags dang //
NK020(wa)001:5189: 'jig rten skyong ba'i lha rnams dang //
NK020(wa)001:5190: gang yang 'byung po mthu chen dang //
NK020(wa)001:5191: gang du lha yi spyan mnga' ba //
NK020(wa)001:5192: sems can don la dga' ba rnams //
NK020(wa)001:5193: bdag la dgongs par mdzad du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:5194: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yis //
NK020(wa)001:5195: sang ni dkyil 'khor bzang po'i ming //
NK020(wa)001:5196: rdo rje dbyings ni ci nus kyis //
NK020(wa)001:5197: cho ga bzhin du bri lags na //
NK020(wa)001:5198: bdag dang slob mar bcas pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:5199: tshogs pa thams cad dkyil 'khor du //
NK020(wa)001:5200: byin gyis rlob par mdzad du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:5203: zhes dkyil 'khor nam mkhar bteg pa la mchod bstod byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:5204: tshon rtsi kha dog lnga la h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih +aah bris la /
NK020(wa)001:5205: rang gi mdun du dbus su ser po dang shar
NK020(wa)001:5206: du dkar po sogs rigs lnga'i bzhugs tshul ltar bzhag
NK020(wa)001:5207: cing / thig skud kha dog lnga yang rigs 'gre'i tshon gyi steng du bkod nas /
NK020(wa)001:5208: thig tshon rnams gnyug ma'i yi ge h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah'i rnam pa lha so so'i bdag nyid du gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5209: rang gi mig gnyis dzah las nyi zla lag gnyis
NK020(wa)001:5210: khu tshur las mdzub mo sbrel ba lcags kyu'i rgya
NK020(wa)001:5211: dang / d+aip+ta dri sh+ta am ku sha dzah zhes mig gi rdzi ma bskyod pas /
NK020(wa)001:5212: rigs lnga ye shes pa'i thugs ka nas ye shes
NK020(wa)001:5213: kyi thig tshon spyan drangs te so so la thim
NK020(wa)001:5214: pa zhu ba las byung ba'i thig tshon du gyur
NK020(wa)001:5215: par mos la / badz+ra yak+sha bzlas pa'i dri'i chus dkyil 'khor gyi gzhir byugs la /
NK020(wa)001:5216: de nas thig skud slob dpon gyis bzung ba'i sne slob bur gtad la /
NK020(wa)001:5217: a nyo nya nu ga t+aa sarba d+har+m+aahspa ra spa
NK020(wa)001:5218: ra nu pra bish+tahsarba d+har+m+aaha d+ya n+t+aa nu pra tish+tahsarba
NK020(wa)001:5219: d+har+m+aah +aahh+aum / zhes sgril ba rdo rje la dkris te rin po che'i snod du bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:5220: yang 'bar ba'i blta bas nam mkha'i lha rnams bskul ba la mchod de /
NK020(wa)001:5221: rang rdor sems dang thig g.yog las kyi rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:5222: snying ga nas sprul pa la dzahzhesa thig sna gtad
NK020(wa)001:5223: cing / des kyang dzahdzahdzahzhesa blangs nas /
NK020(wa)001:5224: badz+ra sa ma ya s+au tra ma ti kra ma h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5225: zhes gnam sa'i thig bskor phyogs ma 'khrul bar gdab ste /
NK020(wa)001:5226: nub dang lhor gnas tshangs thig gnyis //
NK020(wa)001:5227: me rlung de nyid mer gnas pas //
NK020(wa)001:5228: shar nub byang lho'i log thig gdab //
NK020(wa)001:5229: me dang srid gnas zur thig gnyis //
NK020(wa)001:5230: gdab bo slob dpon 'dug phyogs te //
NK020(wa)001:5231: slob ma de ldog g.yas bskor 'gro //
NK020(wa)001:5233: las thig gi cha ji ltar dbye ba ni //
NK020(wa)001:5234: logs rer cha chen brgyad brgyad de //
NK020(wa)001:5235: bcu drug btab pa'i nang ma gsum //
NK020(wa)001:5236: phyed du bgos te drug tu bya //
NK020(wa)001:5237: dang drug phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK020(wa)001:5238: gnyis pa bzhi bgo lnga dbus dor //
NK020(wa)001:5239: de ni nang gi sgo yin no //
NK020(wa)001:5240: cha chen bzhi pa phyi yi khyams //
NK020(wa)001:5241: lnga brgyad dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK020(wa)001:5242: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK020(wa)001:5243: bdun pa bzhir bgo lnga phan gyis //
NK020(wa)001:5244: tshangs thig g.yas g.yon cha chen gnyis //
NK020(wa)001:5245: bsnan la dang po phyed phyi gdab //
NK020(wa)001:5246: phyi ma bzhir bcad phyi ma'i bsgo //
NK020(wa)001:5247: nang du rtsa thig la reg pa'i gdung zlum cha bran gcig dang /
NK020(wa)001:5248: de la rten pa'i gdung bzhi bsnol mar btab pas dbus ling tshe dgu pa /
NK020(wa)001:5249: phyi'i 'khor yug pad rdor 'od phreng spyi ltar bskor ro //
NK020(wa)001:5251: badz+ra be g+aa kra ma h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5252: zhes pas thig 'og nas 'dzul te nang du zhugs la /
NK020(wa)001:5253: hi zhes phyogs kun tu khro bo'i blta bas blta zhing /
NK020(wa)001:5254: thar pa'i sgo phye bar bsam la sgo thig dabyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:5256: badz+ra tsi tra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5257: zhes bzlas la rdul tshon bkye ste /
NK020(wa)001:5258: thog mar slob dpon gyis dbang ldan nas re kh+aa
NK020(wa)001:5259: lnga phyi nas rim par dkar sngo dmar ljang ser
NK020(wa)001:5261: de nas ci bde bar ling tshe dbus ma ser po //
NK020(wa)001:5262: shar sogs kyi ling tshe dang khyams phyi nang rnams shar dkar /
NK020(wa)001:5266: gdung rnams sngon po la rdo rje dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:5267: rta babs mas rim nas ser ljang sngo dmar /
NK020(wa)001:5268: tshon gzhan rnams spyi dang 'dra zhing /
NK020(wa)001:5269: lha gnas so sor sku rten tsakli'am /
NK020(wa)001:5270: 'god mi bde na rdul tshon gyis mtshan ma ji
NK020(wa)001:5271: ltar rigs pa lha rang rang gi snying po brjod
NK020(wa)001:5273: nam mkhar btegs pa'i lha de dang de mtshan ma
NK020(wa)001:5274: de nyid dang dbyer med par gnas der bzhugs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5275: mos pa bya / de nas lhag chad sogs kyi
NK020(wa)001:5276: nges pa sbyang ba'i phyir rdo rje sems ma'i ting
NK020(wa)001:5277: nge 'dzin gyis me tog gi phreng ba bzung /
NK020(wa)001:5278: badz+ra be g+aa kra ma h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5281: zhes dngos su dkyil 'khor gyi phyi dang /
NK020(wa)001:5282: yid kyis 'dod snam nas bskor la lhar bltas te me tog phul ba /
NK020(wa)001:5283: rkang pa bzhi bca' dang lag pad bskor gyis blangs nas mgo la bcing /
NK020(wa)001:5284: de nas dngos su dkyil 'khor gyi nub dang yid
NK020(wa)001:5285: kyis nang du 'dug nas rang h+aum mdzad kyi nga
NK020(wa)001:5286: rgyal gyis / rdo rje mdzub mo yang dag sbyar //
NK020(wa)001:5287: sbyar la bkan te bsdams nas su //
NK020(wa)001:5288: khros nas rab tu dbye ba ni //
NK020(wa)001:5289: sgo dbye ba yi mchog yin no //
NK020(wa)001:5290: badz+rod+b+ha ta sa ma ya pra be sha ya h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5291: zhes pa'i sngags rgyas sgo dbye /
NK020(wa)001:5292: de nas rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK020(wa)001:5293: rdo rje me'i sngags rgyas bsangs gtor byas la /
NK020(wa)001:5294: mchod pa rnams so so'i sngags rgyas brlabs te /
NK020(wa)001:5295: mgon po bdag gi bsod nams dang //
NK020(wa)001:5296: sangs rgyas byin rlabs gzi chen dang //
NK020(wa)001:5297: de bzhin chos dbyings stobs kyis su //
NK020(wa)001:5298: mchod pa'i tshogs rnams gnas gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:5300: bum pa gnyis lta gon ltar bzlas pa cung zad byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:5301: rnam rgyal dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi la bkod /
NK020(wa)001:5302: las bum shar sgo'i g.yon nam der lhang ka tsam byas la slob dpon gyi mdun du bsham /
NK020(wa)001:5303: dkyil 'khor gyi mthar mda' dang me long can dang /
NK020(wa)001:5304: ral gri phur bu rnams brgyad dam bzhis bskor ba tshon skud kyis bres /
NK020(wa)001:5307: rdzas dbang gi tsakli rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:5308: cha gsum gtor ma'ang ci bder bsgrig /
NK020(wa)001:5309: rang gi mdun du'ang mchod yon bzed zhal dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:5312: 'thor nas sogs yo byad thams cad tshogs par bsham mo //
NK020(wa)001:5314: badz+ra yak+sha h+aum gis kha lag bkru /
NK020(wa)001:5315: sa ma ya s+t+wam gis stan la 'dug ste /
NK020(wa)001:5316: bdag dang 'gro ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems
NK020(wa)001:5317: can thams cad dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams
NK020(wa)001:5318: dang yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la
NK020(wa)001:5319: skyabs su mchi'o // rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK020(wa)001:5320: 'das rnams la skyabs su dam pa'i chos rnams la
NK020(wa)001:5321: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun rnams la 'gro rnams bsgral 'dod
NK020(wa)001:5322: skyabs su mchi'o // bsam pa yis // sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK020(wa)001:5323: byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK020(wa)001:5324: rtag par bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK020(wa)001:5325: sher rab snying rje dang bcas pas //
NK020(wa)001:5326: brtson pas sems can don du bdag /
NK020(wa)001:5327: sangs rgyas mdun du gnas byas nas //
NK020(wa)001:5328: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:5330: swa b+h+aa wa shud+hahsarba d+har+m+aahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK020(wa)001:5331: zhes pas chos thams cad gdod ma nas rnam par
NK020(wa)001:5332: dag pa'i rang bzhin stong pa nyid du mos pas
NK020(wa)001:5334: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid skad cig gis rdo
NK020(wa)001:5335: rje sems dpar gsal ba'i lkog mar h+r+aihls pad+ma dmar
NK020(wa)001:5336: po 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lce'i thad ka'i 'dab ma
NK020(wa)001:5337: gcig lcer gyur pa'i steng du h+aum las rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:5338: dkar po rtse lnga pa nyal stabs su gnas par
NK020(wa)001:5340: lag pa gnyis su a a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK020(wa)001:5341: de'i steng du h+aum h+aum las rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa re re /
NK020(wa)001:5342: de zhu ba las rdo rje'i lag pa sor mo rnams kyang rdo rje rtse gcig par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5343: de nas rang rdor sems su gnas pa'i byang chub kyi sems mi shigs pa'i h+aum du gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5344: h+aum gi sgras gdug pa can thams cad tshar bcad /
NK020(wa)001:5345: e ma sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK020(wa)001:5346: thugs rje can gyi thabs chen gyis //
NK020(wa)001:5347: zhi yang sems can 'dul don du //
NK020(wa)001:5348: dri ma med pa'i khro bor gyur //
NK020(wa)001:5349: zhes brjod pa'i rkyen gyis rang nyid khro bo me
NK020(wa)001:5350: ltar 'bar ba sku mdog sngon po zhal khro gnyer
NK020(wa)001:5351: dang bcas pa bzhad cing mche ba cung zad gtsigs
NK020(wa)001:5352: pa / g.yas rdo rje gsor zhing g.yon dril bu snyems pa'i tshul gyis 'chang ba /
NK020(wa)001:5353: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:5356: ye shes bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba'i 'od //
NK020(wa)001:5357: ma rig 'dod pa'i mun khams thams cad bsreg /
NK020(wa)001:5358: zhe sdang gshin rje'i 'jigs pa thams cad 'joms //
NK020(wa)001:5359: dpa' bo chen po dpa' mtshan stag lpags can //
NK020(wa)001:5360: log 'dren srin po'i mtha' gnon dgra 'dul ba //
NK020(wa)001:5361: rig pa'i rgyal po khro bo bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:5362: log 'dren 'dul ba'i slad du spyan 'dren na //
NK020(wa)001:5363: 'gro ba'i don du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:5365: khro bo'i sprin dpag tu med pa spyan drangs la /
NK020(wa)001:5366: gtso bo rang la bstim zhing 'khor rnams bka' sdod du gnas par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:5367: me tog sogs sngags rgya tsam gyis mchod nas /
NK020(wa)001:5369: rang bzhin rnam dag dbyings las khro bor sprul //
NK020(wa)001:5370: skye ba med las 'jigs byed skur ston pa //
NK020(wa)001:5371: gdug pa 'dul phyir mi 'gyur thugs dam can //
NK020(wa)001:5372: khro rgyal khams gsum rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:5373: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK020(wa)001:5374: dpa' bo'i stangs stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK020(wa)001:5375: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyi sdang mig gis //
NK020(wa)001:5376: bgegs dpung sreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:5377: dkyil 'khor chen po'i sa gzhi la gnas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:5378: lha la sogs pa'i bgegs tshogs kun nyon cig /
NK020(wa)001:5379: nga ni gnas 'dir dkyil 'khor chen po sgrub //
NK020(wa)001:5380: bgegs kyi rigs tshogs gang yin byer bar gyis //
NK020(wa)001:5381: nga ni sangs rgyas kun dngos rdo rje can //
NK020(wa)001:5382: bcom ldan bka' yis dkyil 'khor rab sbyor bas //
NK020(wa)001:5383: dpal ldan sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje can //
NK020(wa)001:5384: sangs rgyas rnam 'phrul byin rlabs sgrub byed yin //
NK020(wa)001:5385: gal te nga yis bka' las 'da' byed na //
NK020(wa)001:5386: ye shes can gyi rdo rje rab 'bar bas //
NK020(wa)001:5387: mgo bo tshal pa brgyar ni 'gas byed de //
NK020(wa)001:5388: rnam par 'jig par 'gyur ba gdon mi za //
NK020(wa)001:5389: bdag rdo rje slob dpon ming 'di zhes bgyi bas
NK020(wa)001:5390: slob ma 'di dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob pa
NK020(wa)001:5392: sems can thams cad kyis bla na med pa'i ye shes kyi 'bras bu thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK020(wa)001:5393: sa phyogs bzang po 'dir nam mkha' dri ma med
NK020(wa)001:5394: pa rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po bsgrub
NK020(wa)001:5408: rigs sngags 'chang grub pa rgan po dang rgan mo
NK020(wa)001:5409: g.yog dang bcas pa gang dag 'khod pa de dag
NK020(wa)001:5410: thams cad 'di ltar rdo rje 'chang gi bka' thos
NK020(wa)001:5411: nas myur ba nyid du dengs shig /
NK020(wa)001:5412: gang dag mi 'gro ba de dag /
NK020(wa)001:5413: nga'i ye shes kyi rdo rje 'bar ba /
NK020(wa)001:5415: kun tu 'bar bas mgo bo tshal pa brgyar 'gas par byed do //
NK020(wa)001:5417: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:5418: na mash+tsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye /
NK020(wa)001:5419: ma h+aa yak+sha se n+aa pa ta ye /
NK020(wa)001:5420: na mo badz+ra kro d+h+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:5421: ma h+aa damsh+tong+ka ta b+hee ra b+aa ya /
NK020(wa)001:5422: a si mu sa la d+h+aa r+aa ya pa ra shu p+aa sha hasta ya /
NK020(wa)001:5432: bis+pho ta ya bi s+pho ta ya /
NK020(wa)001:5433: sarba big+h+n+aana bi na ya kam ma h+aa ga na
NK020(wa)001:5434: pa ti dzi bi ta an+ta ka r+aa ya s+w+aa
NK020(wa)001:5435: h+aa / zhes rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas tsham rngams kyis bskrad /
NK020(wa)001:5436: gal te mi 'gro ba rnams la /
NK020(wa)001:5437: badz+ra dz+wa l+aa na l+aarka h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5438: zhes g.yon khu tshur snying ga dang g.yas rdo rje gsor bas bgegs la bsnun /
NK020(wa)001:5440: h+aum badz+ra dz+wa la a na la ha na da
NK020(wa)001:5441: ha pa tsa ma tha b+hany+dza ra na h+aum phata
NK020(wa)001:5442: / ces rdo rje nang bsdam kyi sor mo rnams
NK020(wa)001:5443: nang du 'bar ba ltar byas la mthe bong sbyar
NK020(wa)001:5444: te sgreng ba rdo rje me'i rgyas sregs /
NK020(wa)001:5445: 'tshig dka' ba rnams rdo bsdams bcings la mthe bong
NK020(wa)001:5446: gnyis brkyang ste mnyam pa rdo rje spyan gyi rgya
NK020(wa)001:5447: bcas la / badz+ra nee tri ban+d+ha sarba big+h+n+aana /
NK020(wa)001:5448: zhes pas bcing bar bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:5449: de rnams kyis bgegs sngar yod tshar bcad pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:5450: de nas phyis mi 'jug pa'i phyir gnas bcing ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:5451: rdo rje bsdams pas la brkyang ste /
NK020(wa)001:5452: badz+ra do d+ho me b+ha ba rak+sha sarbam s+w+aa h+aa sa 'og bcing /
NK020(wa)001:5453: rdo rje khu tshur bcang la mgal me bzhin bskor
NK020(wa)001:5454: te mgo bo'i steng du mdzub mo lcags kyu'i tshul
NK020(wa)001:5455: du bzhag pa rdo rje 'jigs byed can gyi rgya
NK020(wa)001:5456: dang / hu lu hu lu h+aum phata kyis steng bcing /
NK020(wa)001:5457: rdo rje thal mo'i mthe bong gnyis brkyang la mdzub
NK020(wa)001:5458: mo gnyis mche ba ltar byas pa rdo rje gnod
NK020(wa)001:5459: sbyin gyi rgya dang badz+ra yak+sha h+aum gis de'i 'og
NK020(wa)001:5461: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis kyi mthe chung sbrel mdzub
NK020(wa)001:5462: rtse gnyis sbyar te bzlog nas spyi bor bzhag pa
NK020(wa)001:5463: rdo rje gtsug tor gyi rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:5464: drum b+han+d+ha ham gis shar phyogs bcing /
NK020(wa)001:5465: khu tshur gnyis kyi mkhrig ma mdud pa rdo rje zhags pa'i rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:5466: h+aum badz+ra p+aa sha h+r+aih zhes pas byang shar bcing /
NK020(wa)001:5467: rdo bsdams las mthe bong gnyis bsnol mdzub gnyis gshibs
NK020(wa)001:5468: te phye la mthe chung brtan par byas pa'i rgya
NK020(wa)001:5469: dang / badz+ra p+aa tam ke p+aa tam ke ni rat+ta /
NK020(wa)001:5471: rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi rgya de nyid khar bzhag pa rdo rje nag mo'i rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:5472: h+r+aihbadz+ra k+aa li ru ta ma ta /
NK020(wa)001:5474: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis kyis ri bo 'degs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5475: tshul du byas pa rdo rje rtse mo'i rgya dang
NK020(wa)001:5476: / badz+ra shi kha re ru ta ma ta /
NK020(wa)001:5478: rdo rje h+aum mdzad kyi rgya las mdzub gung gnyis
NK020(wa)001:5479: rdo rje ra byas pa rdo rje las kyi rgya
NK020(wa)001:5480: dang / h+aum badz+ra karmasa dkyil 'khor bcing /
NK020(wa)001:5481: khu tshur gnyis bcings la mkhrig ma bsnol te mathe'u
NK020(wa)001:5482: chung sbrel zhing mdzub gnyis sgreng pa h+aum mdzad kyi
NK020(wa)001:5483: rgya dang / h+aum zhes brjod pas nang du rdo rje'i ra ba bcing /
NK020(wa)001:5484: rdo rje bsdams pa'i rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:5485: badz+ra ban+d+ha bam zhes pas rdo rje'i d+r+wa ba bya /
NK020(wa)001:5486: de ltar 'og thams cad rdo rje'i sa gzhi /
NK020(wa)001:5487: steng thams cad rdo rje'i gur dang bla re /
NK020(wa)001:5488: khor yug thams cad rdo rje'i ra ba dang d+r+wa ba /
NK020(wa)001:5489: me rab tu 'bar ba'i srung 'khor gyis khyab pas cis kyang mi shigs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5490: de nas tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:5491: badz+ra he ru bam rang nyid rdo rje rgyur gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5492: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis bcings nas mdzub mo dag
NK020(wa)001:5493: dang mathe'u chung dag mdud pa g.yas su bskor ba
NK020(wa)001:5494: kha'i phyog su bzhag pa la lta bzhin pas /
NK020(wa)001:5497: srung 'khor gyi nang mdun gyi nam mkha'i phyogs su
NK020(wa)001:5498: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po sad nas
NK020(wa)001:5500: push+pe la sogs pa rnam lngas mchod //
NK020(wa)001:5501: de nas phyogs thams cad nas //
NK020(wa)001:5502: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK020(wa)001:5503: pra na me na badz+ra ban+d+ha n+aam ka ro mi
NK020(wa)001:5504: / zhes yan lag lnga gtugs pa'i phyag bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:5505: spro na 'dir sems dpa' bzhi'i lus kyi gnas sa la bab pa'i phyogs bzhi'i phyag kyang bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:5506: de nas thal mo sbyar te /
NK020(wa)001:5507: na mo phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK020(wa)001:5512: las kyi rigs su bzhugs pa thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:5516: rig sngags kyi lha'i khyad par thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:5517: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK020(wa)001:5518: nas rig sngags kyi bar gyi lha thams cad kyi
NK020(wa)001:5519: spyan sngar sdig pa thams cad so sor bla na
NK020(wa)001:5520: med pa'i so sor bshags pas so sor bshags par
NK020(wa)001:5521: bagyi'o // phyogs bcu na 'das pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:5523: da ltar byung ba'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK020(wa)001:5524: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang rang sangs rgyas dang /
NK020(wa)001:5525: 'phags pa nyan thos yang dag par song ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:5526: yang dag par zhugs pa rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:5527: sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams thams cad la rgya cher rjes su yi rang bar bagyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:5528: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das chos kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:5529: lo bskor bar mi mdzad pa thams cad la chos
NK020(wa)001:5530: kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bya ba'i phyir bskul bar
NK020(wa)001:5531: bagyi'o // phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das yongs
NK020(wa)001:5532: su mya ngan las 'das bar bzhed pa gang yin
NK020(wa)001:5533: pa de dag thams cad la mya ngan las mi
NK020(wa)001:5536: gang yang phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK020(wa)001:5537: na lha dang mi rnams kyi mchod pa'i bye brag
NK020(wa)001:5538: me tog dang / bdug spos dang /
NK020(wa)001:5542: rgod pa sogs rtsed 'jo'i bde ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:5543: dpag bsam gyi shing bzang po dang /
NK020(wa)001:5544: sems can kun gyi don du byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:5545: pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang /
NK020(wa)001:5546: lus ngag sems las byung ba'i mchod pa thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:5547: rnam par thar pa sgo gsum gyi ting nge 'dzin gsang ba'i mchod pa mchog rnams te /
NK020(wa)001:5548: mdor na 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5549: mchod pa gang dag yod do 'tshal de rnams 'di
NK020(wa)001:5550: lta ste / ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5551: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la mchod pa'i las
NK020(wa)001:5553: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rigs lnga dang bcas par bzhugs pa thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:5557: rigs sngags kyi lha'i khyad par thams cad la dbul bar bagyi'o //
NK020(wa)001:5558: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la bdag nyid 'bul gyis /
NK020(wa)001:5559: bdag dus thams cad dang rnam pa thams cad du so sor bzhes su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:5560: thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa'i mgon po khyed
NK020(wa)001:5561: rnams kyis dam tshig chen po'i dngos grub dam pa
NK020(wa)001:5563: dge ba'i rtsa ba de yang sems can thams cad dang thun mong du byas te /
NK020(wa)001:5564: dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di dag gis /
NK020(wa)001:5565: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad 'jig
NK020(wa)001:5566: rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rgud pa thams
NK020(wa)001:5567: cad dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:5568: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i phun sum
NK020(wa)001:5569: tshogs pa thams cad dang yang dag par ldan pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5570: bde ba dang yid bde ba nyid kyis mi'i mchog
NK020(wa)001:5571: sangs rgyas su tshe 'di nyid la gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:5572: bdag gi dge ba'i las rnams 'di dag gis /
NK020(wa)001:5573: 'jig rten du ni myur du 'tshang rgya shog /
NK020(wa)001:5574: 'gro la phan phyir chos kyang ston bgyid cing /
NK020(wa)001:5575: sems can duhkhasa gzir las sgrol bar shog /
NK020(wa)001:5577: de nas lag gnyis mdun du bzhag la /
NK020(wa)001:5578: lag mthil gnyis su a a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h+aum a /
NK020(wa)001:5579: thal mo gnyis la +aa li bcu drug /
NK020(wa)001:5580: mthe bong nas brtsams te sor mo rnams la h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aahlasa rigs lnga yab yum bcur gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5581: a nyo nya a nu ga ta sarba d+har+m+aah zhes
NK020(wa)001:5582: pas yab yum phan tshun reg par bsam la mnyam
NK020(wa)001:5584: s+pha ra s+pha ra a nu pra bish+ta sarba d+har+m+aah
NK020(wa)001:5585: zhes pas rjes su zhugs par bsam la rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:5586: thal mo bya / a t+yan+ta a nu bish+t+aahsarba d+ha r+m+aahbadz+ra any+dza li /
NK020(wa)001:5587: zhes pas gnyis med du 'dres par bsam la rdo rje bsdams pa'i rgya bya /
NK020(wa)001:5589: ces rdo rje bsdams pa snying gar dral bas ye
NK020(wa)001:5590: shes rdo rjes 'khor ba'i 'ching ba dral bar mos
NK020(wa)001:5591: / rdo rje bsdams pa'i mthe bong nang du bcug pa bcings la /
NK020(wa)001:5592: badz+ra a be sha ya a ah zhes bzlas pas
NK020(wa)001:5593: dang po'i rdo rje dmar po 'bar ba'i rnam pa
NK020(wa)001:5594: char babs pa bzhin snying gar phab nas /
NK020(wa)001:5596: tish+tha badz+ra dri d+ho me b+ha ba /
NK020(wa)001:5597: sha shwa b+ho me b+ha ba hri da ya me /
NK020(wa)001:5598: a d+hi tish+ta sarba sid+d+hi m+me pra yats+tsha h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5599: ha ha ha ha hoh zhes sngar gyi phyag rgya dgrol /
NK020(wa)001:5600: yang sngar gyi phyag rgya las mthe bo'i rgyab tu mdzub mo bkab pa nang du bcug ste /
NK020(wa)001:5602: de bkrol nas se gol gtog cing /
NK020(wa)001:5603: badz+ra mush+ti bam gis brtan par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:5604: de nas rdo rje khu tshur gnyis kyi nang du mdzub mo gnyis sbyar nas gyen du 'phangs te /
NK020(wa)001:5605: sarba a p+aa ya a kar+sha na bi sho d+ha na badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)001:5606: ces pas rang rdo rje khu tshur du gyur pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5607: thugs ka'i 'od kyis ngan song rnams bslang bar bsam
NK020(wa)001:5608: / de rnams kyis bdag cag skyob tu gsol zhes brjod cing /
NK020(wa)001:5609: rang gis rdor bsdams las gung mo gnyis dang mtha'
NK020(wa)001:5610: ma bzhi rnams rtse mo so sor sbyar te dral
NK020(wa)001:5611: zhing / badz+ra p+aa n+ai bi s+pho ta ya /
NK020(wa)001:5612: sarba a p+aa ya ban+d+ha ni pra mo k+sha ya /
NK020(wa)001:5613: sarba a pa ya ga te b+h+yahsarba sat+w+aam sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra sa ma ya trata /
NK020(wa)001:5615: de nas gtso bo'i dam rgya rdor bsdams las gung
NK020(wa)001:5616: mo myu gu ltar mnyam par sgreng ba bcings la
NK020(wa)001:5617: / sa ma ya s+t+wam sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK020(wa)001:5618: ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ri h+aum badz+ra muh zhes
NK020(wa)001:5619: lan gsum gyis sngar rang gis /
NK020(wa)001:5620: sprul pa'i tshogs zhing gi lha rnams rang gi snyig
NK020(wa)001:5621: gar bsdus pas lha thams cad kyi bdag nyid kyi
NK020(wa)001:5622: byang sems zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5624: rang nyid skad cig gis rdor sems su gsal ba'i
NK020(wa)001:5625: snying gar zla ba la gnas pa'i rdo rje'i dbus
NK020(wa)001:5626: su gnyug ma'i yi ge badz+ra sa t+wa bsam /
NK020(wa)001:5628: swa b+h+au wa shud+d+hahsarba d+har+m+aa swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK020(wa)001:5629: zhes pas chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis stong par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5630: stong pa'i ngang las nam mkha'i phyogs su rang gi gnyug sems badz+ra sa t+wa /
NK020(wa)001:5631: dkar cha gtso bor gyur pa'i +aa li bcu drug
NK020(wa)001:5632: zhu ba las zla ba dang po badz+ra sa t+was
NK020(wa)001:5633: mtshan pa / dmar cha gtso bor gyur pa'i k+aa
NK020(wa)001:5634: li so drug zhu ba las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:5635: mtshan pa / gnyis pa / zla ba gnyis po
NK020(wa)001:5636: de badz+ra sa t+wa dang bcas pa las dang po'i
NK020(wa)001:5637: rdo rje 'od zer gyi phreng ba dang bcas pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5638: lte bar badz+ra sa t+was mtshan par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5641: badz+ra sa t+wa zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK020(wa)001:5642: rdo rje de las rdor sems kyis gtso byas pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5643: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi lha dpag med spros
NK020(wa)001:5644: / des sems can gyi khams thams cad rang rigs kyi lhar sad par byas /
NK020(wa)001:5645: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK020(wa)001:5646: rdo rje'i dbyings thams cad bsdus te thim pas rdo
NK020(wa)001:5647: rje de rang rigs kyi lha thams cad kyi rdul
NK020(wa)001:5648: phra rab 'dus pa'i bdag nyid du gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5649: bdag ni sems dpa' kun bdag grags /
NK020(wa)001:5650: bdag nyid kyang ni bdag la gnas /
NK020(wa)001:5651: badz+ra sa t+wa zla ba'i bdag nyid 'od kyi phreng
NK020(wa)001:5652: ba dang bcas pa'i rdo rje de nyid yongs su
NK020(wa)001:5653: gyur pa las / bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:5655: zhi zhing 'dzum la mtshan dpe'i lang tsho rab tu rgyas pa /
NK020(wa)001:5656: phyag g.yas pas rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar
NK020(wa)001:5657: gtod de 'dzin pa g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa
NK020(wa)001:5658: / ral pa'i thor cog can dar gyi na bza' dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:5659: pad zla'i gdan la sems dpa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5662: ma h+aa sa ma ya sat+wo&a ham /
NK020(wa)001:5664: mkha' ltar kun tu khyab pa'i bdag nyid du gyur pa'i nga rgyal bzung ngo //
NK020(wa)001:5665: rdo rje bsdams pa las mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba sems ma rdo rje ma'i dam rgya bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:5666: sa ma ya hoh zhes pas thams cad mnyam pa'i nga rgyal byas la /
NK020(wa)001:5667: sa ma ya sa t+wa a d+hi tish+tha swa mam /
NK020(wa)001:5668: zhes pa lan bzhis snying ga dang /
NK020(wa)001:5671: spyi bo rnams su dam rgya des gtugs pas /
NK020(wa)001:5672: mi shigs pa'i bdag nyid sems ma bzhi'i ngo bo rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:5675: sna tshogs rdo rje rnams kyis rgyas btab pas byin gyis brlabs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5676: de nas snying gar zla ba la h+aum yig bkod par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:5677: rdor sems kyi phyag chen bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:5679: de'i mthar sngags kyi phreng bas bskor bar bsam zhing klong pa'i tshul du /
NK020(wa)001:5682: de nas bzlas pa bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:5683: bdag de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i bdag
NK020(wa)001:5684: nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpar gsal ba'i thugs kar
NK020(wa)001:5685: zla ba la gnas pa'i h+aum yig dkar po sngags
NK020(wa)001:5686: phreng gis bskor ba las 'od zer 'phros sems can
NK020(wa)001:5687: thams cad kyi sdig sgrib dang sdug bsngal thams cad
NK020(wa)001:5688: sbyangs nas / slar 'dus pa sngags phreng la zhugs par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:5689: lha thams cad kyi bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' sngags badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5691: spro na de'i steng du rigs lnga'i sngags /
NK020(wa)001:5695: pad+ma a mi t+aa b+ha h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha
NK020(wa)001:5696: sid+d+hi +aah zhes pa rnams kyang ci rigs bzlas mthar
NK020(wa)001:5697: / yig brgya lan gsum gyis brtan par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:5698: de nas don byas pa'i sems can de rnams kyis
NK020(wa)001:5699: bdag rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bor gnas pa la
NK020(wa)001:5701: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aah+aa /
NK020(wa)001:5710: mtshan bargya'am bsdus pa la dga' na /
NK020(wa)001:5711: rang bzhin chos sku dag pa'i klong //
NK020(wa)001:5712: sna tshogs thabs mkhas thugs rje yis //
NK020(wa)001:5713: rigs lnga ye shes lngar ston pa //
NK020(wa)001:5714: rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal //
NK020(wa)001:5718: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla'i steng du b+h+rum las
NK020(wa)001:5719: rin po che'i bum pa yangs shing rgya che ba
NK020(wa)001:5720: / lha'i gos kyis mgul dkris pa /
NK020(wa)001:5721: dpag bsam shing gi kha rgyan can /
NK020(wa)001:5722: mtshan nyid thams cad rdzogs pa /
NK020(wa)001:5723: nang chu dang bcud sna tshogs kyis yongs su gang
NK020(wa)001:5724: ba'i rnam rgyal bum pa'i nang du ling tshe dgu
NK020(wa)001:5725: pa sgo phyi nang dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas khang
NK020(wa)001:5726: du gyur pa'i ling tshe dbus mar las bcom ldan
NK020(wa)001:5727: 'das rnam par snang mdzad yum bzhi sbas pa'i mtshan
NK020(wa)001:5728: mas bskor ba / phyogs kyi ling tshe bzhi'i lte bar shar du h+aum las mi bskyod pa /
NK020(wa)001:5729: lhor t+r+aam las rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK020(wa)001:5730: nub tu h+r+aihls snang ba mtha' yas /
NK020(wa)001:5731: byang du +aahls don yod grub pa /
NK020(wa)001:5732: de bzhi'i mdun rgyab g.yas g.yon rnams su rang rigs kyi sems dpa' bzhi bzhis bskor ba /
NK020(wa)001:5735: sgo rnams su sgeg sogs bcu gnyis /
NK020(wa)001:5736: phyi'i snam bu la sems dpa' bcu drug rnams bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:5737: thams cad kyang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:5738: las bum gyi nang du pad zlar khro bo rdo
NK020(wa)001:5739: rje gnod sbyin nag po mche ba zhal gyi grwa
NK020(wa)001:5740: gnyis su 'dzin pa rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5741: ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:5743: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:5745: chos dbyings ye shes rnam par dag /
NK020(wa)001:5746: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)001:5747: sems ma bzhi dang bcas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:5748: mchog tu dad pas phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:5749: me long ye shes rnam par dag /
NK020(wa)001:5750: mi bskyod rdo rje bcom ldan 'das //
NK020(wa)001:5751: sems dpa' bzhi dang bcas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:5752: mchog tu dad pas phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:5753: mnyam nyid ye shes rnam par rin chen 'byung ldan
NK020(wa)001:5754: bcom ldan sems dpa' bzhi dang mchog tu dad pas
NK020(wa)001:5755: kun rtog ye shes rnam par snang ba mtha' yas
NK020(wa)001:5756: bcom sems dpa' bzhi dang mchog tu dad pas nan
NK020(wa)001:5757: tan ye shes rnam don yod grub pa bcom sems
NK020(wa)001:5758: dpa' bzhi dang mchog tu chos kyi dbyings las ma
NK020(wa)001:5759: g.yos kyang // bde gshegs chos kyi dbyings bskul ba //
NK020(wa)001:5760: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad rnams la //
NK020(wa)001:5761: mchog tu dad pas tshad med bzhi dang bsdu ba bzhis //
NK020(wa)001:5762: bde gshegs thams cad spyan 'dren pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:5763: ye shes sgo skyong bzhi rnams la //
NK020(wa)001:5764: mchog tu sgo yi khyams kyi nang gnas pa //
NK020(wa)001:5765: byams pa la sogs bcu drug ni //
NK020(wa)001:5766: dang po rab dga' la sogs gnas //
NK020(wa)001:5767: sa gnas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:5770: 'jigs pa'i h+aum sgra nges sgrog cing /
NK020(wa)001:5771: bgegs rnams ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:5772: dngos grub ma lus stsol ba'i lha //
NK020(wa)001:5773: bgegs kyi dgra la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:5775: de nas gzungs thag la 'jus te /
NK020(wa)001:5776: lha rnams kyi sku'i cha thams cad las ye shes
NK020(wa)001:5777: lnga'i rang bzhin gyi bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun babs pas
NK020(wa)001:5778: bum pa gang bar dmigs te /
NK020(wa)001:5779: rnam rgyal du dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi sngags sam /
NK020(wa)001:5781: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ra h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5787: a b+hi she ka yang cung zad bzlas la /
NK020(wa)001:5790: badz+ra muhs gshegs su gsol la /
NK020(wa)001:5792: dam tshig pa zhu ba bum chu dang ro gcig tu gyur par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:5793: yig brgya brjod pas brtan par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)001:5794: de nas mdun bskyed sgrub mchod ni /
NK020(wa)001:5797: shu nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&aham /
NK020(wa)001:5799: chos thams cad stong nyid ye shes rdo rje'i rang bzhin du gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5800: stong pa'i ngang las e yam ram wam lam sum
NK020(wa)001:5801: las 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab dang bcas pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5802: steng du pad+ma la gnas pa'i sna tshogs rdo rje'i
NK020(wa)001:5803: lte ba la rdzogs pa'i ga zhal yas khang gru
NK020(wa)001:5804: bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bzhi dang ldan pa'i nang
NK020(wa)001:5805: du / de'i phyed tshad kyi gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK020(wa)001:5806: gnyis ka'ang phyi nas rim par sngo ser dmar ljang
NK020(wa)001:5807: dkar ba'i rtsig pa rim pa lngas bskor ba'i steng
NK020(wa)001:5808: du pha gu dang d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed la sogs
NK020(wa)001:5813: gzhal yas khang nang mar rtsig pa la reg pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5814: rdor phreng zlum po la brten pa'i ka ba brgyad
NK020(wa)001:5815: dang ldan pa'i re'u mig dgu'i phyogs bzhi dbus dang
NK020(wa)001:5816: lngar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa re re'i lte bar
NK020(wa)001:5821: byang du mkha' lding rnams kyis btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri pad+ma dang zla ba /
NK020(wa)001:5822: lha gnas gzhan rnams su pad zla'i gdan re re gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:5823: ri'u mig dbus ma'i lte ba'i gdan la /
NK020(wa)001:5825: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad sku mdog ser po kun tu zhal /
NK020(wa)001:5826: phyag gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:5827: rtsibs bzhi'i mdun du sa t+wa badz+ri h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5828: sems ma rdo rje ma'i ngo bo rdorje rtse lnga pa dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:5829: g.yas su rat+na badz+r+ai t+r+aam rin chen rdo rje'i ma'i ngo bo nor bu rin po che /
NK020(wa)001:5830: rgyab tu d+harma badz+ri h+r+aihchosa rdo rje ma'i ngo bo
NK020(wa)001:5831: pad+ma dkar dmar 'dab ma bcu drug pa'i 'dab brgyad
NK020(wa)001:5832: mthur du gyes shing 'dab brgyad steng du 'dzum pa'i
NK020(wa)001:5833: nang na dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa chud
NK020(wa)001:5834: pa / g.yon du karma badz+ri +aahrdo rje las ma'i
NK020(wa)001:5835: ngo bo sna tshogs rdo rje rwa bcu gnyis pa
NK020(wa)001:5836: pa / rnams so // ri'u mig shar ma'i lte
NK020(wa)001:5837: ba'i gdan la badz+ra ak+sho b+h+yah h+aum mi bskyod pa
NK020(wa)001:5838: dkar po g.yas sa gnon dang g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:5839: rtsibs bzhi'i mdun mar badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:5840: sems dpa' dkar po g.yas sor mo dbus ma gsum
NK020(wa)001:5841: bsgreng ba'i gung mo'i rtser rdo rje rtse lnga pa
NK020(wa)001:5842: thugs kar gtod pa'i tshul dang g.yon dril bu dkur
NK020(wa)001:5843: brten pa / g.yas su badz+ra r+aa dza dza rdo rje rgyal po ser po phyag gnyis lcags kyu /
NK020(wa)001:5844: rgyab tu badz+ra r+aa ga hohrdo rje chags pa dmar
NK020(wa)001:5845: po ut+pa la dmar po kha ma bye ba'i made'u
NK020(wa)001:5847: g.yon du badz+ra s+aa d+hu d+hu rdo rje legs pa
NK020(wa)001:5848: ljang gu snying gar phyag gnyis rdo rje dang bcas
NK020(wa)001:5849: pa'i mtheb mdzub kyis se gol rdeb pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:5850: ri'u mig lho'i lte ba'i gdan la rat+na sam+b+ha ba t+r+aam /
NK020(wa)001:5851: rin chen 'byung ldan sngon po g.yas mchog sbyin dang g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:5852: rtsibs bzhi'i mdun mar badz+ra rat+na t+r+aam rdo rje rin
NK020(wa)001:5853: chen sngon po g.yas khu tshur gyis rin po che
NK020(wa)001:5854: dpral ba dang g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK020(wa)001:5855: g.yas su badz+ra te dzar+ya rdo rje gzi brjid dmar po g.yas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:5856: rgyab tu badz+ra ke tu b+h+ri rdo rje rgyal mtshan sngon po g.yas rgyal mtshan /
NK020(wa)001:5857: g.yon du badz+ra ha sa ha rdo rje bzhad pa dkar po g.yas so'i phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:5858: re'u mig nub ma'i lte ba'i gdan la pad+ma a
NK020(wa)001:5859: mi t+aa b+h+aa h+r+ai snang ba mtha' yas dmar po
NK020(wa)001:5861: rtsibs bzhi'i mdun mar badz+ra d+harma h+r+aihrdo rje chos dmar
NK020(wa)001:5862: po g.yon pad+ma dkur brten pa'i kha g.yas pa'i mtheb
NK020(wa)001:5864: g.yas su badz+ra tik+sh+na d+h+r+ai rdo rje rnon po sngon
NK020(wa)001:5865: po g.yas ral gri 'phyar zhing g.yon thugs kar pusti
NK020(wa)001:5866: / rgyab tu badz+ra he tu krum rdo rje rgyu
NK020(wa)001:5867: ser po g.yas pa'i gung mo la 'khor lo rtsibs
NK020(wa)001:5869: g.yon du badz+ra b+h+aa shab+h+aa rdo rje smra ba dmar po g.yas rdo rjes mtshan pa'i lce 'dzin pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:5870: ri'u mig byang ma'i lte ba'i gdan la karma a
NK020(wa)001:5871: mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aahdona yod grub pa ljang gu g.yas
NK020(wa)001:5872: skyabs sbyin dang g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:5873: rtsibs bzhi'i mdun mar badz+ra karma kam rdo rje las
NK020(wa)001:5874: ljang ku g.yas pa'i gung mos sna tshogs rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:5875: thugs kar gtod cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa
NK020(wa)001:5876: / g.yas su badz+ra rak+sha ham rdo rje srung ba chen po phyag gnyis kyis go cha /
NK020(wa)001:5877: rgyab tu badz+ra yak+sha h+aum rdo rje gnod skyin sngon
NK020(wa)001:5878: po phyag gnyis rdo rje'i mche ba kha 'gram so
NK020(wa)001:5879: sor 'dzin pa / g.yon du badz+ra san+d+hi bam rdo
NK020(wa)001:5880: rje khu tshur ser po phyag gnyis dam tshig gi
NK020(wa)001:5881: khu tshur gyis rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'tshir ba'o
NK020(wa)001:5882: sor 'dzin pa / // mtshams kyi ri'u mig bzhi'i
NK020(wa)001:5883: shar lhor badz+ra l+aa s+ya h+aum sgeg mo dkar mo
NK020(wa)001:5884: snyems pa'i tshul gyis phyag gnyis dkur brten pa'i g.yas
NK020(wa)001:5885: sor 'dzin pa / // pas me long / lho
NK020(wa)001:5886: nub tu badz+ra m+aa le t+r+aam phreng ba ma ser
NK020(wa)001:5887: mo phyag gnyis kyi rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK020(wa)001:5888: nub byang du badz+ra g+hi rti h+r+aihglu ma dmar mo phyag gnyis kyis pi wam brdung ba /
NK020(wa)001:5889: byang shar du badz+ra n+ri t+ya a gar ma ljang
NK020(wa)001:5890: gu phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams nas
NK020(wa)001:5891: gar bsgyur ba / shar lho nas brtsams te grwa bzhir g.yas bskor du badz+ra d+h+au pe h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5892: spos ma dkar mo phyag gnyis kyis spos phor /
NK020(wa)001:5893: badz+ra push+pe tram me tog ma ser po g.yon me
NK020(wa)001:5894: tog gi snod 'dzin pa las g.yas pas 'thor ba
NK020(wa)001:5895: / badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aihmara me ma dmar skya phyag gnyis mar me'i mchod sdong /
NK020(wa)001:5896: badz+ra gan+d+he a dri chab ma ljang khu g.yon dung phor las g.yas pas dri byug pa /
NK020(wa)001:5897: shar nas g.yas bskor gyi sgo bzhir badz+ra am ku
NK020(wa)001:5898: sha dzahrdo rje lcags kyu dkar po phyag gnyis kyis
NK020(wa)001:5899: lcags kyu / badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum rdo rje zhags pa ser po phyag gnyis kyis zhags pa /
NK020(wa)001:5900: badz+ra s+pho ta bam rdo rje lcags sgrog dmar po phyag gnyis kyi lcags sgrog /
NK020(wa)001:5901: badz+ra +aa be sha a rdo rje 'bebs pa ljang
NK020(wa)001:5902: gu g.yas dril bu dpung mgo'i thad du 'khrol ba
NK020(wa)001:5903: / de rnams kyi phyag g.yon ma smos pa thams cad gdan la brten pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:5904: dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i phyogs bzhi'i lha snam la /
NK020(wa)001:5905: sarba sam s+k+aa ra pa ri shud+d+ha d+harma te ga
NK020(wa)001:5906: ga na sa mud+ga te s+w+aa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+he
NK020(wa)001:5907: ma h+aa na ya pa ri wa re s+w+aa h+aa
NK020(wa)001:5908: / shar du byang chub sems dpa' byams pa /
NK020(wa)001:5911: mya ngan dang mun pa thams cad nges par 'joms pa'i blo gros bzhi dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:5915: ye shes tog bzhi ser po /
NK020(wa)001:5919: d+r+wa ba can gyi 'od bzhi dmar po /
NK020(wa)001:5920: byang du rdo rje snying po /
NK020(wa)001:5923: kun tu bzang po bzhi ljang gu /
NK020(wa)001:5924: skal bzang gi sems dpa' bcu drug po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:5925: gtso 'khor thams cad kyang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan cing /
NK020(wa)001:5926: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga po dbu skra ral pa'i thor cog can /
NK020(wa)001:5927: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung dang nyi ma'i rgyab yol mnga' ba /
NK020(wa)001:5928: 'khor rnams sems dpa'i skyil mo krung dang zla ba'i rgyab yol can /
NK020(wa)001:5929: rdo rje gnod sbyin khro bo dang gzhan thams cad
NK020(wa)001:5930: zhi zhing 'dzum la sgeg pa'i lang tsho rab tu
NK020(wa)001:5931: rgyas pa'o // de nas rang h+aum mdzad kyi rgyal du 'phos nas /
NK020(wa)001:5932: badz+rod+g+ha ta sa ma ya pra be sha ya h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5933: zhes pa'i sngags rgyas sgo phye la /
NK020(wa)001:5934: rang rdo rje sems dpar nga rgyal 'phos pas ye shes pa spyan drang ste /
NK020(wa)001:5935: spos dang rdor dril 'dzin zhing dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK020(wa)001:5937: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK020(wa)001:5938: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha //
NK020(wa)001:5939: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:5940: bcom ldan rnam snang 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:5941: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK020(wa)001:5942: ni ka badz+ra d+h+aa tu bee ro tsa na sa
NK020(wa)001:5943: pa ri w+aa ra dri sh+ya hoh badz+ra d+h+aa tu
NK020(wa)001:5944: sa m+aa dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu ba'i rgya dang
NK020(wa)001:5945: / dzahh+aum bam hoh'i sngags rgyas sgo khang so sor
NK020(wa)001:5946: dgug gzhug bcings mnyes byas te spyan drangs pa la
NK020(wa)001:5948: bcom ldan 'dir ni byon pa legs //
NK020(wa)001:5949: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK020(wa)001:5950: bdag gi mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:5951: thugs rjes thugs dpag mdzad du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:5953: ga ga na sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:5955: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK020(wa)001:5956: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar //
NK020(wa)001:5957: lha yi chu ni dag pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:5958: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol //
NK020(wa)001:5959: badz+ra sarba de ba ta ar tsi ta a mri te ha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:5961: bdag dang 'gro la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:5962: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni //
NK020(wa)001:5963: ji srid mchod pa bdag bgyid na //
NK020(wa)001:5964: de srid bcom ldan bzhugs su gsol //
NK020(wa)001:5968: sogs kyis rnam lnga phul la /
NK020(wa)001:5969: badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5971: badz+ra +aa be sha +aah zhes pa'i sngags dang phyag
NK020(wa)001:5972: rgya bzhis sgo khang na bzhugs pa'i ye shes pa
NK020(wa)001:5973: rnams dam tshig pa la dgug gzhug bcing mnyes byas
NK020(wa)001:5974: la / rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi las rgya dang /
NK020(wa)001:5976: lan gnyis kyis phyi 'brang gi bgegs bskrad cing bsrung /
NK020(wa)001:5977: rdo rje khu tshur gyi las rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:5978: badz+ra san+d+hi bam gyis sgo bcad /
NK020(wa)001:5979: de nas skabs 'dir phyag rgya bzhis rgyas gdab ste /
NK020(wa)001:5983: zhes zhabs brdabs pas dga' ba bskyed nas rnam snang gi dam rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:5985: mdun gyi ye shes pa la blta /
NK020(wa)001:5988: rgyab tu nyi ma'i 'od khyim grub /
NK020(wa)001:5989: sa ma ya s+t+wam a ham /
NK020(wa)001:5990: rnam snang gi nga rgyal bya /
NK020(wa)001:5992: lan gsum bzlas pas thugs kar nyi ma la snying po bsam /
NK020(wa)001:5993: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ra h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:5994: zhes lan gsum brjod cing snying po'i mthar bkod /
NK020(wa)001:5995: des mtshon te rigs gzhan bzhi la /
NK020(wa)001:5996: rang rang gi dam rgya 'cha' zhing sngags gzhan rnams 'dra ba las /
NK020(wa)001:5997: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ra'i tshab tu /
NK020(wa)001:6004: thal mo rtse sprad pa'i zhabs brdabs pas dga' ba bskyed /
NK020(wa)001:6005: rdor sems kyi dam rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:6006: badz+ra sa t+wa dri sh+ya yis blta /
NK020(wa)001:6010: sa ma ya s+t+wam a ham gis nga rgyal /
NK020(wa)001:6011: badz+ra sa t+wa gsum gyis thugs kar zla bar snying po /
NK020(wa)001:6015: des mtshon te rdo rje rgyal po sogs rang rang gi dam rgya 'cha' zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6017: badz+ra r+aa dza sogs rang sngags kyis barje ba ma gtogs 'dra'o //
NK020(wa)001:6018: de ltar rgyas btab pas lha thams cad kyi snying
NK020(wa)001:6019: gar dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pas mtshan par
NK020(wa)001:6020: gyur / de la so so'i dam rgya 'ching tshul ni /
NK020(wa)001:6021: rdo rje bsdams pa gzhir bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)001:6022: gung mo myu gu ltar mnyam par sgreng ba rnam snang /
NK020(wa)001:6023: gung mo nang du gshibs nas sbas pa mi bskyod pa /
NK020(wa)001:6024: gung mo rin chen 'dra ba rin 'byung /
NK020(wa)001:6025: gung mo pad+ma ltar dgug pa mtha' yas /
NK020(wa)001:6026: rdor bsdams zlum po las mdzub mo bkug pa don grub /
NK020(wa)001:6027: rdor bsdams las gung mo gshibs te sgreng zhing mthe
NK020(wa)001:6028: bong dang mthe chung bzhi phral nas sgreng ba ni
NK020(wa)001:6029: rdor sems // mdzub gnyis lcags kyu 'dra ba rdo rje rgyal po /
NK020(wa)001:6030: mdzum gnyis lto sbyar nas brkyang pa rdo rje chags pa /
NK020(wa)001:6031: mtheb mdzub kyi se gol snying gar rdeb pa rdo rje legs pa /
NK020(wa)001:6032: mthe bong gshibs shing mdzub rtse sprad pa las tshigs bcag pa rdo rje rin chen /
NK020(wa)001:6033: rdo rje thal mo las mtheb mdzub sngar ltar byas pa rdo rje gzi brjid /
NK020(wa)001:6034: rdor basngamasa las srin lags mthe chung gnyis mnyam par gshibs pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK020(wa)001:6035: de nyid bskor nas kha'i phyogs bzhag pa rdo rje bzhad pa /
NK020(wa)001:6036: mthe bong mnyam gshibs mdzub rtse gnyis bkug pa rdo rje chos /
NK020(wa)001:6037: gung mo gshibs te sgreng ba'i rtse bkug pa rdo rje rnon po /
NK020(wa)001:6038: de las srin lag dang mthe chung gshibs ba rdo rje rgyu /
NK020(wa)001:6039: rdor basngagasa las mthe bong gnyis phan tshun du phye
NK020(wa)001:6040: la thal mo bkan te kha'i phyogs bzhag pa rdo
NK020(wa)001:6041: rje smra ba / rdor bsdams las mthe bong mathe'u chung rtse sprad de bkyed pa rdo rje las /
NK020(wa)001:6042: de las mdzum mo gshibs te snying gar brkyang pa rdo rje bsrung ba /
NK020(wa)001:6043: mdzub gnyis bkug pa lcags kyu ltar byas shing mthe
NK020(wa)001:6044: chung gnyis gshibs pa mche ba ltar byas pa rdo
NK020(wa)001:6045: rje gnod sbyin / mthe chung gnyis kyi nang du
NK020(wa)001:6046: mthe bong bcug pa'i rtsa ba mdzub mo gnyis kyis
NK020(wa)001:6048: rdor bsdams kyi mthe bong mnyam pa snying gar bzhag pa sgeg mo /
NK020(wa)001:6049: rdo rje thal mo phreng ma /
NK020(wa)001:6050: rdo rje thal sbyar te kha nas dbyung ba glu ma /
NK020(wa)001:6051: rdor thal bskor ba spyi bor bzhag pa gar ma /
NK020(wa)001:6052: rdor bsdams bcing ba mthur du blug pa spos /
NK020(wa)001:6053: rdor thal phye nas gyen du 'thor ba me tog /
NK020(wa)001:6054: rdor bsdams las mthe bong mnyam pa mar me /
NK020(wa)001:6055: rdor thal phye nas brkyang ba byug pa /
NK020(wa)001:6056: rdor bsdams las mdzub mo g.yas pa bkug pa lcags kyu /
NK020(wa)001:6057: rdor bsdams las mthe bong g.yas pa nang du bcug la mdun pa zhags pa /
NK020(wa)001:6058: mthe bong mdzub mo so sor rtse sprad pa gdu bu lta bu lcags sgrog /
NK020(wa)001:6059: rdo rje bcing ba las mdzub mo nang du bcug la mthe bong gnyis kyis bsdams pa dril bu'o //
NK020(wa)001:6061: lha thams cad kyi lkog mar h+r+aihls pad+ma dmar po
NK020(wa)001:6062: 'dab brgyad kyi 'dab mar a las zla ba'i steng
NK020(wa)001:6063: du h+aum las rdo rje rtse lnga dkar po chur
NK020(wa)001:6065: rdo rje'i lte bar lha rang rang gi chos yig rigs lnga la badz+ra dz+ny+aa na re re dang /
NK020(wa)001:6066: sems dpa' dang sgeg sogs bcu gnyis la rim par /
NK020(wa)001:6091: +aa ya he dzah +aa ya he h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6093: g+han+de a +aahrnamasa kyis mtshan pas rang sgra grags par mos zhing ngag nas brjod do //
NK020(wa)001:6095: lha thams cad kyi thugs kar sna tshogs rdo rje re re gsal bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:6096: dku g.yon du khu tshur bcings pa kha sbyar ba
NK020(wa)001:6097: las 'og ma mdzub mo dang steng ma mathe'u chung
NK020(wa)001:6098: nas bkrol te ba dan bskyod pa sngon du 'gro
NK020(wa)001:6099: ba'am / bsdus pa la'ang pad bskor sngon du 'gro
NK020(wa)001:6100: bas rang rang gi las rgya bca' bzhin du rigs
NK020(wa)001:6101: ba'am / lnga la / badz+ra d+h+aa tu re re dang /
NK020(wa)001:6131: so so'i las rgya 'ching tshul ni /
NK020(wa)001:6132: rnam snang la byang chub mchog rgya /
NK020(wa)001:6133: mi bskyod rin 'byung don grub gsum lag g.yon nu
NK020(wa)001:6134: ma g.yon pa'i thad du chos gos kyi grwa 'dzin
NK020(wa)001:6135: pa'i tshul dang g.yas sa gnon sogs so so'i phyag
NK020(wa)001:6136: chen / snang mtha' phyag gnyis gnyam bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:6137: lag g.yas rdo rje gsor tshul dang g.yon bsgying ba dang bcas pa ni rdor sems /
NK020(wa)001:6138: lag gnyis lcags kyu 'dzin pa lta bu rdo rje rgyal po /
NK020(wa)001:6139: mda' 'phang tshul rdo rje chags pa /
NK020(wa)001:6140: mtheb mdzub kyi se gol snying gar gzhag pa rdo rje legs pa //
NK020(wa)001:6141: khu tshur gnyis gshibs dpral bar bzhag pa rdo rje rin chen /
NK020(wa)001:6142: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis steng 'og tu sbyar ba snying gar bzhag pa rdo rje gzi brjid /
NK020(wa)001:6143: khu tshur g.yon par g.yas pa'i gru mo btsugs pa rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK020(wa)001:6144: g.yas g.yon so phreng 'dzin tshul kha phyogs bskor ba rdo rje bzhad pa /
NK020(wa)001:6145: g.yas pa'i mtheb mdzub kyis g.yon pa'i pad+ma kha 'byed pa ltar byed pa rdo rje chos /
NK020(wa)001:6146: snying gar g.yon pa ral gri mdud pa ltar byed pa rdo rje rnon po /
NK020(wa)001:6147: rdo rje khu tshur kha sbyar la mgal me ltar bskor ba rdo rje rgyu /
NK020(wa)001:6148: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis kha nas dbyung ba ltar byed pa rdo rje smra ba /
NK020(wa)001:6149: rdo rje thal mo gar bskor bkrol nas 'gram g.yas g.yon dang spyi bor bzhag pa rdo rje las /
NK020(wa)001:6150: go cha bkon tshul rdo rje srung ba /
NK020(wa)001:6151: khu tshur las mthe chung gnyis mche ba lta bu kha 'gram du bzhag pa rdo rje gnod sbyin /
NK020(wa)001:6152: khu tshur gnyis dku g.yon du mnan pa rdo rje khu tshur /
NK020(wa)001:6153: rdo rje bsgyings tshul gyis 'dud pa sgeg mo /
NK020(wa)001:6154: phreng ba bcing pa phreng ma /
NK020(wa)001:6155: rdo rje tshul kha nas dbyung ba glu ma /
NK020(wa)001:6156: rdo rje gar bskor ba gar ma /
NK020(wa)001:6157: rdo rje khu tshur gyis bdug pa dang 'thor ba
NK020(wa)001:6158: dang bskor ba dang byug pa ltar bya ba mchod
NK020(wa)001:6160: khu tshur las g.yas pa'i mdzub mo dang g.yon pa'i mthe chung bcing ba lcags kyu dang /
NK020(wa)001:6161: mkhrig ma mdud pa zhags pa /
NK020(wa)001:6162: mdzub gnyis gdu bu ltar byas pa lcags sgrog /
NK020(wa)001:6163: rgyab gnyis mnyam ste mnan pa dril bu'o //
NK020(wa)001:6165: lha thams cad kyi thugs kar zla ba la dang
NK020(wa)001:6166: po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa re gsal gtab la
NK020(wa)001:6167: / sngags ni las rgya bzhin las thog ma'i yig bor ba yin la /
NK020(wa)001:6168: phyag rgya'i sgar mdun bskyed gsal 'debs kyi mngon rtogs ltar 'ching ngo //
NK020(wa)001:6169: 'dir ma zad sngar gyi dam rgya'i mjug tu so
NK020(wa)001:6170: so'i sngags snying po'i mthar bkod de lan gsum bzla
NK020(wa)001:6171: ba dang / chos rgya'i sngags rnams 'don pa'i tshe
NK020(wa)001:6172: yang lha so so'i phyag chen ston pa'i lugs 'byung
NK020(wa)001:6173: ba dang / ste / nges par dgos pa ma
NK020(wa)001:6174: yin kyang lha de dang de ni 'adi'o zhes shes
NK020(wa)001:6176: khyams phyi ma'i sems dpa' rnams la ni rim pa
NK020(wa)001:6177: bzhin 'khor lo bsgyur ba bzhi'i phyag rgyas btab par
NK020(wa)001:6178: bya'o // de nas rdo rje rin chen gyi dam rgya dang badz+ra rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)001:6180: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la rin po che'i cod pan gyis dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)001:6181: rdor thal las gung mo gshibs te sgreng ba'i tshigs
NK020(wa)001:6182: dbus mar mdzub rtse bkug pa sbyar ba spyi bor
NK020(wa)001:6183: bzhag nas / badz+ra d+h+aa t+w+ai shwa r+ai h+aum badz+r+ai ni a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)001:6184: rdor tha las gung mo gshibs sgreng mchog mar bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)001:6185: badz+ra badz+r+ai ni h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)001:6186: de'i gung mo bcag ste rin chen ltar byas pa rna ltag g.yas par bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)001:6187: rat+na badz+r+ai ni h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)001:6188: rdor thal gyi gung srin mathe'u chung gsum pad 'dab ltar byas pa ltag par bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)001:6189: d+harma badz+r+ai ni h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)001:6190: sor mo thams cad brkyang ba rna ltag g.yon par bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)001:6191: karma badz+r+ai ni h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)001:6192: zhes gzhan thams cad la rin po che rtse bran gyi cod pan gyis dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)001:6195: snying mgrin ltag snying nu bar dang /
NK020(wa)001:6196: snying mgrin rgyab dang dpral ba dgur /
NK020(wa)001:6197: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis mdud pa 'ching bzhin du go bgos la /
NK020(wa)001:6198: rna ba'i steg du lag phye ste /
NK020(wa)001:6199: badz+ra tush+ya hoh zhes thal mo rtse sprad de gsham brdabs nas brkyang bas /
NK020(wa)001:6200: dar dkar pos gnas dgur mdud de rna ba'i steng
NK020(wa)001:6201: nas yar lcugs la lhag ma lus mnyam du dpyangs
NK020(wa)001:6202: par bsam mo // de nas mchod pa yak+sha dang mes bsang /
NK020(wa)001:6204: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod du
