NK020(wa)001:6205: yig zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod rdzas rnams kun
NK020(wa)001:6206: tu bzang po'i mchod pa'i sprin phung ltar bzang zhing
NK020(wa)001:6207: rgya che ba nam mkha'i mtha' klas par bsam la
NK020(wa)001:6209: shap+da'i bar lan gsum gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)001:6211: lha sogs bdag gir ma byas pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:6212: me tog chu skyes thang skyes rnams //
NK020(wa)001:6213: thub pa'i skyes mchog rnams la 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:6214: sarba ta th+aa ga ta push+pe p+au dza me g+ha
NK020(wa)001:6215: sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum
NK020(wa)001:6216: / gnas 'di 'am ni gang dag spos kyi shing bzang po //
NK020(wa)001:6217: lha yi spos sogs rmad byung ba //
NK020(wa)001:6218: thub pa'i dbang phyug rnams la 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:6219: d+h+au pe gnas 'di 'am ni rin chen bzang po cher 'bar dang //
NK020(wa)001:6220: snang ba'i shing las byung ba dang //
NK020(wa)001:6221: nyi ma zla ba la sogs 'od //
NK020(wa)001:6222: phyogs rnams kun tu spros te 'bul //
NK020(wa)001:6223: +aa lo ke gnas 'di 'am dri yi shing rnams bzang po'i chab //
NK020(wa)001:6224: phyogs rnams kun tu spros pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:6225: thub pa'i dbang phyug gan+d+he gnas 'di 'am zhal zas ro mchog brgya ldan pa //
NK020(wa)001:6226: thams cad sbyar ba'i bshos 'di dag /
NK020(wa)001:6227: thub pa'i nee wid+ya gnas 'adi'am dri med yid du 'ong ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:6228: sil snyan dam pa 'di dag ni //
NK020(wa)001:6229: thub pa'i dbang shap+da de nas las rin po che sna bdun la sogs pa yid kyis sprul te /
NK020(wa)001:6230: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:6232: srid pa'i 'khor lo rgyun bcad de //
NK020(wa)001:6233: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK020(wa)001:6234: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsakra rat+na p+au dzi te h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6235: bde bar gshegs pa nor bu rin chen bkres shing 'phongs pa rgyun bcad de //
NK020(wa)001:6236: 'byor ba phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6237: ma ni bde bar btsun mo shes rab dbyings kyi don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)001:6238: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bar shog /
NK020(wa)001:6240: bde bar blon po bsam yas bstan pa rab 'dzin cing //
NK020(wa)001:6241: yon tan thams cad ldan par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6242: ma h+aa ta bde bar glang po bla med theg par rab zhon nas //
NK020(wa)001:6243: thams cad mkhyen grong bgrod par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6244: ha sti bde bar rta mchog srid pa'i gzeb las nges grol te //
NK020(wa)001:6246: tu rang+ga a shwa bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:6247: dmag dpon rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK020(wa)001:6248: phal gyi rgol ba tshar bcad nas //
NK020(wa)001:6249: bsnyengs bral mchog ni thob par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6250: sarba ta th+aa ga ta khang+ga rat+na p+au dzi te h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6251: kha dog dbyibs legs yid 'ong rgyan phreng ldan //
NK020(wa)001:6252: phyogs dus kun tu gzugs mchog ci mchis pa //
NK020(wa)001:6253: mos blos dkyil 'khor lha la bdag 'bul na //
NK020(wa)001:6254: bzhes shig bla med grub mchog stsal du gsol //
NK020(wa)001:6255: sarba ta th+aa ga ta r+au pa k+aa ma gu na badz+ra p+au dzi te +aahh+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6256: phyogs dus kun na zin dang ma zin pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:6257: yon tan tshig brjod sgra snyan yid 'ong ldan //
NK020(wa)001:6258: mos blos dkyil 'khor bzhes shig bla med shap+da k+aa ma phyogs dus kun na tsan+dana sbrul snying dang //
NK020(wa)001:6259: a kar la sogs dbang po tshim byed dri //
NK020(wa)001:6260: mos blos bzhes shig gan+d+he phyogs dus kun na ro dang bcud ldan pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:6261: lus sems brtas byed ro mchog ci mchis pa /
NK020(wa)001:6262: mos blos bzhes shig ra sa phyogs dus kun na 'jam mnyen 'khril chags pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:6263: reg bya'i khyad par dbang po tshim byed rnams //
NK020(wa)001:6264: mos blos bzhes shig s+pha r+she zhes pa rnams kyang so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas dbul lo //
NK020(wa)001:6265: de nas lus kyi gang sngon du 'gro bas gsang ba'i lha mo brgyad kyi las rgya bcas te /
NK020(wa)001:6266: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pa na /
NK020(wa)001:6267: rdo rje rin chen bla na med //
NK020(wa)001:6268: rdo rje chos ni glu blangs pas //
NK020(wa)001:6269: rdo rje las kun byed par 'gyur //
NK020(wa)001:6272: badz+ra rat+na ma nu t+ta ram /
NK020(wa)001:6274: badz+ra kar+m+aa ka ro d+b+ha be /
NK020(wa)001:6277: badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aih badz+ra n+ri t+ye +aah badz+ra d+h+au pe h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6279: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih badz+ra gan+d+he +aah spro na
NK020(wa)001:6280: rig ma bcu drug dang rdor dril byin gyis brlabs
NK020(wa)001:6281: nas dam tshig gsum gyi mchod pa'ang bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:6282: de nas rdor dril 'dzin cing dbyangs dang bcas pas bstod pa bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:6284: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK020(wa)001:6285: chos dbyings ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:6286: rdo rje mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK020(wa)001:6287: phyag 'tshal rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK020(wa)001:6288: gzung 'dzin rdo rje brtan pa'i sa //
NK020(wa)001:6289: me long ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:6290: rdo rje sa gnon phyag rgya can //
NK020(wa)001:6291: phyag 'tshal rdo rje mi bskyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6292: rin chen rdo rje 'bar ba'i me //
NK020(wa)001:6293: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:6294: rdo rje mchog sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK020(wa)001:6296: mtha' yas rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK020(wa)001:6297: kun rtog ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:6298: rdo rje ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK020(wa)001:6299: phyag 'tshal snang ba mtha' yas la //
NK020(wa)001:6300: don yod rdo rje bskyod pa'i rlung //
NK020(wa)001:6301: nan tan ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:6302: rdo rje skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK020(wa)001:6303: phyag 'tshal rdo rje don grub la //
NK020(wa)001:6304: me long ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK020(wa)001:6305: sems ma rdo rje'i phya rgya ste //
NK020(wa)001:6306: rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga la //
NK020(wa)001:6307: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:6308: mnyam nyid ye shes byin rlabs rin chen sems ma'i phyag rgya rin chen ser po zur brgyad la //
NK020(wa)001:6309: bstod cing gus pas kun rtog ye shes byin chos
NK020(wa)001:6310: kyi sems ma'i phyag pad dkar 'dab ma bcu drug
NK020(wa)001:6311: la // bstod cing bya grub ye shes byin las
NK020(wa)001:6312: kyi sems ma'i phyag rdo rje rgya gram ljang gu
NK020(wa)001:6313: la // la // bstod cing gus pas rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK020(wa)001:6314: rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa kun //
NK020(wa)001:6315: rdo rje dang po kun tu bzang //
NK020(wa)001:6316: phyag 'tshal phyag na rdo rje la //
NK020(wa)001:6317: rdo rje rgyal po sangs rgyas mchog rdo rje lcags kyu de bzhin gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:6318: nges pa'i rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK020(wa)001:6320: rdo rje chags pa bde chen po //
NK020(wa)001:6321: rdo rje mda' ni dbang byed pa //
NK020(wa)001:6322: bdud kyi 'dod pa rdo rje che //
NK020(wa)001:6323: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gzhu khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6324: rdo rje legs pa sems dpa' mchog /
NK020(wa)001:6325: rdo rje mgu ba dga' ba che //
NK020(wa)001:6326: rab dgyes rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK020(wa)001:6327: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dgyes khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6328: rdo rje rin chen rdo rje don //
NK020(wa)001:6329: rdo rje nam mkha' nor bu che //
NK020(wa)001:6330: nam mkha' snying po rdo rje phyug /
NK020(wa)001:6331: phyag 'tshal rdo rje snying khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6332: rdo rje gzi brjid 'bar ba che //
NK020(wa)001:6333: rdo rje chen po rin chen dpal //
NK020(wa)001:6334: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dpa' khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6335: rdo rje bzhad mo bzhad pa chen //
NK020(wa)001:6336: rdo rje 'dzum pa ngo mtshar che //
NK020(wa)001:6337: dga' zhing rab dga' rdo rje ston //
NK020(wa)001:6338: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dga' khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6339: rdo rje chos rab de nyid ston //
NK020(wa)001:6340: rdo rje pad ma rab dga' byed //
NK020(wa)001:6341: 'jig rten dbang phyug rab mdzes spyan //
NK020(wa)001:6342: phyag 'tshal rdo rje spyan khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6343: rdo rje rnon po theg pa che //
NK020(wa)001:6344: rdo rje ral gri mtshon chen po //
NK020(wa)001:6345: 'jam dpal rdo rje rab tu zab //
NK020(wa)001:6346: phyag 'tshal rdo rje blo khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6347: rdo rje rgyu dang snying po che //
NK020(wa)001:6348: rdo rje 'khor lo tshul chen po //
NK020(wa)001:6349: rab bskor rdo rje las byung ba //
NK020(wa)001:6350: phyag 'tshal rdo rje snying po la //
NK020(wa)001:6351: rdo rje gsung ba rang rig mchog /
NK020(wa)001:6352: rdo rje zlos pa rab sgrub sbyin //
NK020(wa)001:6353: mi gsung rdo rje mchog grub pa //
NK020(wa)001:6354: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gsung khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6355: rdo rje las rab rdo rje dka' //
NK020(wa)001:6356: las kyi rdo rje kun rab sgrol //
NK020(wa)001:6357: rdo rje nges par rgya che ba //
NK020(wa)001:6358: phyag 'tshal rdo rje las khyod la //
NK020(wa)001:6359: rdo rje bsrung ba brtan pa che //
NK020(wa)001:6360: rdo rje go cha sra ba che //
NK020(wa)001:6361: rdo rje brtson 'grub thub dka' ba //
NK020(wa)001:6363: rdo rje gnod sbyin thabs chen po //
NK020(wa)001:6364: rdo rje mche ba 'jigs pa che //
NK020(wa)001:6365: bdud 'joms rdo rje mi zad pa //
NK020(wa)001:6366: phyag 'tshal rdo rje drag po la //
NK020(wa)001:6367: rdo rje mtshams sbyor rab tu sdud //
NK020(wa)001:6368: rdo rje 'ching ba rnam grol byed //
NK020(wa)001:6369: rdo rje khur tshur dam tshig mchog /
NK020(wa)001:6370: phyag 'tshal rdo rje khu tshur la //
NK020(wa)001:6371: rnam dag rdo rje thugs kyi yum /
NK020(wa)001:6372: mi dmigs rdo rje mtshan ma 'joms //
NK020(wa)001:6374: phyag 'tshal rdo rje sgeg mo la //
NK020(wa)001:6375: rnam dag rdo rje yon tan yum //
NK020(wa)001:6376: yid bzhin re ba skong bar mdzad //
NK020(wa)001:6377: rdo rje phreng ba'i phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:6378: phyag 'tshal rdo rje phreng ba la //
NK020(wa)001:6379: rnam dag rdo rje gsung gi yum //
NK020(wa)001:6380: gsung rab rgya mtsho sgrog pa'i don //
NK020(wa)001:6381: rdo rje pi wam phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:6382: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dbyangs mkhan la //
NK020(wa)001:6383: rnam dag rdo rje las kyi yum //
NK020(wa)001:6384: las kyi rdo rje 'gro don mdzad //
NK020(wa)001:6385: bdud 'dul rdo rje phyag rgya gar //
NK020(wa)001:6386: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gar mkhan la //
NK020(wa)001:6387: sprin lding rdo rje bdug pa mo //
NK020(wa)001:6388: rdo rje tshim byed kun tu tshim //
NK020(wa)001:6389: rdo rje spos khang phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:6390: phyag 'tshal rdo rje bdug pa la //
NK020(wa)001:6391: lta mdzes rdo rje thams cad mdzes //
NK020(wa)001:6392: rdo rje me tog kun tu mdzes //
NK020(wa)001:6393: rdo rje me tog phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:6394: phyag 'tshal rdo rje me tog la //
NK020(wa)001:6395: 'od gsal rdo rje mda' yi me //
NK020(wa)001:6396: rdo rje spyan gyis ma rig sel //
NK020(wa)001:6397: rdo rje gsal byed phyag rgya 'dzin /
NK020(wa)001:6398: phyag 'tshal rdo rje mar me la //
NK020(wa)001:6399: rdo rje tsan+dana bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK020(wa)001:6400: rdo rje bdud rtsis rnam rtog 'khru //
NK020(wa)001:6401: rdo rje dag byed phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:6402: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dri chab la //
NK020(wa)001:6403: rnam dag bskul byed thugs rje'i don //
NK020(wa)001:6406: phyag 'tshal rdo rje lcags kyu la //
NK020(wa)001:6407: mi gtong rdo rje chos kyi don //
NK020(wa)001:6410: phyag 'tshal rdo rje zhags pa la //
NK020(wa)001:6411: rdo rje chos nyid mi 'gyur don //
NK020(wa)001:6412: rdo rje mgyogs byed glog ltar myur //
NK020(wa)001:6413: rdo rje lcags sgrog phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:6414: phyag 'tshal rdo rje lcags sgrogs la //
NK020(wa)001:6415: rdo rje 'bebs pa brtan pa'i mchog /
NK020(wa)001:6416: rdo rje bskyod mdzad kun gyi las //
NK020(wa)001:6418: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dril bu la //
NK020(wa)001:6419: sgo yi khyams kyi nang gnas pa //
NK020(wa)001:6420: byams pa la sogs bcu drug ni //
NK020(wa)001:6421: dang po rab dga' la sogs gnas //
NK020(wa)001:6422: sa gnas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:6424: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs rnams
NK020(wa)001:6425: kyis bdag cag sems can thams cad kyi don mdzad
NK020(wa)001:6427: de nas dkyil 'khor brtan pa'i ched du bzlas pa bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:6428: rdo rje 'dzin ma'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK020(wa)001:6431: rang nyid mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs la /
NK020(wa)001:6432: rigs so so dang rang tha mi dad par bsam ste /
NK020(wa)001:6434: badz+ra d+ha ras mi bskyod pa /
NK020(wa)001:6437: bi shwa d+ha ras don grub /
NK020(wa)001:6438: ta th+aa ga t+aa sa ma ya ma ti kra
NK020(wa)001:6439: ma ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ya d+ha ra
NK020(wa)001:6440: +aa t+ma ko &aham gis gtso bo rnam snang dang
NK020(wa)001:6441: tha mi dad par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:6442: sngags de rnams sprel nas lan gsum bzlas pas nga rgyal bzung /
NK020(wa)001:6444: rang nyid rigs 'dus rdo rje sems dpa'i rnams pas
NK020(wa)001:6445: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas 'thon te rang gnas su
NK020(wa)001:6447: lha rnams kyi zhal nas sngags kyi sgra dang thugs
NK020(wa)001:6448: rje'i 'od zer 'phros pas sems can thams cad kyi
NK020(wa)001:6449: sdig sgrib sbyangs par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:6453: pad+ma a mi t+aa b+ha h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha
NK020(wa)001:6454: sid+d+hi +aah zhes pa rnams brgya rtsa tsam re dang
NK020(wa)001:6457: pad+ma badz+ri h+r+aih karma badz+ri +aah badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6458: badz+ra r+aa dza dzah badz+ra r+aa ga hoh badz+ra s+aa d+hu d+hu /
NK020(wa)001:6463: badz+ra d+harma h+r+aih badz+ra tik+sh+na d+hi /
NK020(wa)001:6472: badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aih badz+ra n+ri t+ye +aah badz+ra d+h+au pe h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6474: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+ai badz+ra gan+d+he +aah badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6476: badz+ra +aa be sha ya +aah sarba sam s+k+aa ra
NK020(wa)001:6477: pa ri shud+d+ha d+harma te ga ga na sa mud+ga
NK020(wa)001:6478: te swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+he ma h+aa na ya
NK020(wa)001:6479: pa ri w+aa re s+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:6480: zhes pa rnams nyer gcig gam bdun bdun tsam re dang /
NK020(wa)001:6482: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa yo g+ai shwa ri h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6483: zhes pa'ang ci nus bzla zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6485: de nas 'das gtor dang cha gsum gtor ma sngar ltar gtor zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6486: sbyin sreg kyang ci 'grub bya ste log na yod do //
NK020(wa)001:6487: de nas dbang chog ltar slob dpon rang nyid dkyil
NK020(wa)001:6488: 'khor du 'jug cing slob ma la dbang bskur bar
NK020(wa)001:6489: bya'o // de nas rjes chog ni /
NK020(wa)001:6490: mchod pa kha gsol te byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)001:6491: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pu sh+pe p+au dza sogs nas /
NK020(wa)001:6494: sogs lha mo brgyad kyis kyang mchod /
NK020(wa)001:6495: bstod par 'os pa sogs kyis bstod nas /
NK020(wa)001:6496: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:6497: khyed rnams la mkhyen pa'i ye shes /
NK020(wa)001:6499: mdzad pa'i phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba lags pas /
NK020(wa)001:6500: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:6501: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu thams cad sku tshe brtan
NK020(wa)001:6502: zhing thugs kyi bzhed pa'i don lhun gyis 'grub pa
NK020(wa)001:6503: dang / bdag dang sems can thams cad bde zhing skyid par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK020(wa)001:6504: khyad par du'ang bdag nyid chen po khyed rnams la
NK020(wa)001:6505: ci 'byor pa'i mchod pa ji snyed kyis mchod pa'i
NK020(wa)001:6506: mthus / bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK020(wa)001:6507: cad kyi sgrib gnyis byang zhing tshogs gnyis rdzogs te
NK020(wa)001:6508: myur du bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sa
NK020(wa)001:6509: la 'god pa'i bka' drin stsal du gsol /
NK020(wa)001:6511: lho so so'i dam rgya bcas te snying po lan gsum gyi mthar /
NK020(wa)001:6512: badz+ra muhzhesa phyag rgya bkrol bas /
NK020(wa)001:6513: lha ye shes pa rnams dam tshig pa las phye nas bzhugs par mos la /
NK020(wa)001:6514: rdo rje rin chen gyi dam rgya snying ga gnas btegs te mdzod spur bzhag la /
NK020(wa)001:6515: badz+ra rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK020(wa)001:6516: zhes rang dang phyag rgya'i lha thams cad la dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)001:6517: sarba mu t+r+aam mee tri ku ru wa ra ka ba tse nam ma /
NK020(wa)001:6518: zhes lag gnyis khu tshur bsdams te /
NK020(wa)001:6520: zhes gnas dgur mdud pa bcings la /
NK020(wa)001:6521: badz+ra tush+ya hoh zhes thal mo'i gsham brdab te brkyang bas go bgo /
NK020(wa)001:6522: re zhig dkyil 'khor mi gshegs na /
NK020(wa)001:6523: mdun bskyed kyi ye shes pa /
NK020(wa)001:6524: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyis brtan bzhugs byas nas
NK020(wa)001:6525: bdag bskyed kyi phyag rgya dgrol zhing go ba khyad
NK020(wa)001:6526: par ro // gang ltar yang yig brgya mang du bzla zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6527: ma rnyed yongs su sogs kyis bzod gsol byas te /
NK020(wa)001:6528: badz+ra sa t+wa sa mchod yon phul nas /
NK020(wa)001:6529: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad /
NK020(wa)001:6530: ces sogs kyis sngar phye ba'i ye shes pa rnams gshegs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:6532: de'i tshe rdor sems kyi phyag rgya bcings te /
NK020(wa)001:6533: dkyil 'khor la lan gsum bskor nas /
NK020(wa)001:6535: zhes phyag rgya de nyid spyi bor bkrol bas /
NK020(wa)001:6536: bdag mdun gyi ye shes pa thams cad dag pa'i zhing du gshegs /
NK020(wa)001:6537: lag gnyis kyi srin lag mathe'u chung mthe bong rnams
NK020(wa)001:6538: lug rgyud du sbrel zhing gung mdzub brkyang ba chan
NK020(wa)001:6539: pa'i rgyas srung 'khor gyi mtshams bkrol te gshegs /
NK020(wa)001:6541: dzahh+aum bam hohs rang la bsdus te /
NK020(wa)001:6543: da nas bar chad bsrung ba'i phyir rdo rje las /
NK020(wa)001:6546: rdo rje khu tshur bzhi'i dam rgya 'ching zhing sngags lan gsum re brjod pas bsrung /
NK020(wa)001:6547: rang rdor sems su gsal ba'i snying gar brtan g.yo thams cad 'od gsal du bcug par mos la /
NK020(wa)001:6548: a k+aa ro bzla bas rdul tshon bsdus zhing phyags te dman pa rnams chu bor dor /
NK020(wa)001:6550: dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad gsang sngags dang /
NK020(wa)001:6551: rig sngags dang gzungs sngags dang snying po dang phyag
NK020(wa)001:6552: rgya'i sgo nas tshogs gnyis rlabs po che myur du
NK020(wa)001:6553: rdzogs te bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi go
NK020(wa)001:6554: 'phang myur du thob par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:6555: tshe 'di la'ang bdag gzhan thams cad kyi nad dang gdon gyi rigs su gyur pa thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:6556: rmi ltas mtshan ma ngan pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:6557: gzhan gyi bsam sbyor ngan pa sogs gnod pa dang
NK020(wa)001:6558: bar chad kyi rigs su gyur pa mi mthun pa'i
NK020(wa)001:6559: phyogs thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:6560: bkra shis pa dang yid la bsam pa thams cad chos dang mthun par 'grub par gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:6561: ji ltar dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK020(wa)001:6562: sems dpa' rnams kyis bsngosa pa dang smon lam btab
NK020(wa)001:6563: pa de bzhin du bdag gis kyang bsngo zhing smon
NK020(wa)001:6567: rnam par snang mdzad ye shes dam pa mtsho chen ldan //
NK020(wa)001:6568: zla ba nya 'dra'i sku mnga' srid pa mthar phyin pa /
NK020(wa)001:6569: dgongs pa mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa /
NK020(wa)001:6570: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:6571: mi 'khrug rgyal po srid dang gti mug rnam sbyong ba /
NK020(wa)001:6572: dge ba mnyam med sems can don rdzogs rab ldan pa //
NK020(wa)001:6573: mgon po yon tan rdzogs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK020(wa)001:6574: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan rnams kyis brgyan byas shing //
NK020(wa)001:6575: yang dag 'byor pa'i sbyin pa sbyin mdzad mi bslu ba //
NK020(wa)001:6576: rin chen 'byung ldan zhes bya'i bkra shis bkra shis
NK020(wa)001:6577: dam bsam gtan dang ni ting 'dzin pha rol phyin
NK020(wa)001:6578: gnas shing // ye shes pad+ma'i steng bzhugs dpag med tshe ldan pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:6579: 'od dpag med pa'i byin rlabs bkra shis bkra shis
NK020(wa)001:6580: dam pa des kyang sems can don phyir las la
NK020(wa)001:6582: 'gro ba thams cad 'ching bas bcings las sgrol mdzad pa //
NK020(wa)001:6583: thugs mchog don yod grub pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK020(wa)001:6584: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK020(wa)001:6585: ces brjod cing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas me tog 'thor ro //
NK020(wa)001:6586: 'dir yo ga'i chog gzung phal che bar /
NK020(wa)001:6587: yo ga rang lugs kyi sgrub tshul la sngags rgya sogs mang bas sgrub dka' bar bzung nas /
NK020(wa)001:6588: zor yang ba'i dbang du mdzad de /
NK020(wa)001:6589: bla med kyi cho ga'i rigs 'gre sbyar ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:6590: lag len zhib pa'i phyos rnams su'ang kun rig gi rgyas 'gebs dang /
NK020(wa)001:6591: der zhal 'phang ba tsam mdzad mod /
NK020(wa)001:6592: de lta na'ang lugs 'di la tshad mar gyur pa
NK020(wa)001:6593: glan gyi rig 'dzin rnams kyi dgongs pa ltar 'dir
NK020(wa)001:6594: ni yo ga rang lugs kyi sgrub tshul bkod pa
NK020(wa)001:6595: ste / de la yang glan bsod nams mgon po'i yo ga'i las sdebs che bar /
NK020(wa)001:6596: phyag rgya ma bkrol na gsal bar bya /
NK020(wa)001:6597: bkrol na rnal 'byor chen po bskyed pa rdzogs par bya /
NK020(wa)001:6598: de mi nus na rnal 'byor gcig dang ldan par byar rung /
NK020(wa)001:6599: zhes lhag chad sogs kyi nyes pa sbyang phyir rdo
NK020(wa)001:6600: rje shugs 'jug gis mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK020(wa)001:6601: zhugs nas me tog 'bul ba'i tshe gsungs pa ltar
NK020(wa)001:6602: / rgyas par rnal 'byor chen po sgom dgos par bzhed na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:6603: ha cang spros pas 'dir btang snyoms su byas te /
NK020(wa)001:6604: rnal 'byor gcig pa'i lugs su bkod pa yin no //
NK020(wa)001:6605: de la'ang 'dzam gling pan+di ta'i mdo'i yo ga'i sgrub thabs su /
NK020(wa)001:6606: rang nyid rdor sems su sems dpa' lus sgrub dang
NK020(wa)001:6607: shas cher 'dra ba'i cho ga dam tshig gi phyag
NK020(wa)001:6608: rgyas sgrub par mdzad pa snang na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:6609: 'dir rnal 'byor chen po'i nang tshan bdag byin rlabs
NK020(wa)001:6610: kyi cho gas sgrub pa nyid 'brel bar mthong nas
NK020(wa)001:6613: glan ston chen po rdo rje'i 'od kyis mdzad pa'i
NK020(wa)001:6614: las sdebs 'gos gtsang pa las brgyud de 'ongs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:6615: yi ger / de nas rdo rje sgrub pa lha thams cad cho ga gsum gyis bskyed do //
NK020(wa)001:6616: de mi nus na lha'i ming brjod cing nga rgyal bya'o /
NK020(wa)001:6617: zhes gsungs pa'i rgyas pa rdo rje sgrub pa'i las
NK020(wa)001:6618: ha cang mang bas 'dir so so'i ming sngags brjod
NK020(wa)001:6619: pa tsam gyis bskyed pa yin no //
NK020(wa)001:6620: 'o na bdag bskyed la rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK020(wa)001:6621: mdun bskyed la rdo rje sgrub byed tshul ji ltar zhe na /
NK020(wa)001:6623: 'dir bdag bskyed du bris pa'i bdag byin rlabs rdor
NK020(wa)001:6624: sems su bskyed pa'i thugs ka'i snying po'i mthar sngags
NK020(wa)001:6625: phreng bkod pa yan chad song rjes /
NK020(wa)001:6626: rang gzhi lus rdor sems kyi snying gar zla dkyil gyi steng du dkyil 'khor sprul /
NK020(wa)001:6627: rang gzhi lus las phye nas snying gar zhugs te
NK020(wa)001:6628: bdag 'jug len pa ni bsnyen pa dang nye bsnyen
NK020(wa)001:6630: snying ga'i dkyil 'khor rang dang bcas pa gzhi lus kyi lha'i thugs kar bstim nas /
NK020(wa)001:6631: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas sems dpa' lus sgrub bya /
NK020(wa)001:6633: rten gzhi lus dang brten pa nyer brgyad po la ye shes pa spyan drangs te bstim /
NK020(wa)001:6635: de nas sngar bzhin bdag 'jug blangs rjes /
NK020(wa)001:6637: rdor dril byin gyis brlabs nas dam tshig gsum bzung ste mchod pa rnams so //
NK020(wa)001:6638: yang rdo rje sgrub pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:6639: rang rdor sems su bskyed pa nas bdag 'jug snga
NK020(wa)001:6640: ma'i ming dbang gi bar bshad ma thag pa ltar
NK020(wa)001:6641: byas rjes / lha rang rang gi phyag chen 'cha' bzhin du rdo rje bsgrub pa bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:6642: de'ang mdun bskyed kyi lha re re bzhin la /
NK020(wa)001:6644: dang pos rang dam tshig pa re bsreg pa'i rkyen gyis so so'i phyag mtshan du bsgyur /
NK020(wa)001:6645: sngags gnyis pas de'i nga rgyal bya /
NK020(wa)001:6646: sngags gsum pas lha so so'i zhal phyag gi rnam
NK020(wa)001:6647: par bsgyur te sgom pa ni rdo rje sgrub pa'o
NK020(wa)001:6648: // de nas ye shes pa bcug la phyag rgya bzhis rgyas 'debs pa sogs bya ba yin no /
NK020(wa)001:6649: der ma zad bdag bskyed rnal 'byor chen po'i lugs
NK020(wa)001:6650: su mdzad pa'ang bsnyen pa bsdus pa'i lugs yin pas
NK020(wa)001:6651: / rgyu mtshan de dag gi phyir na /
NK020(wa)001:6652: yi ge 'di la rgyas pa'i yan lag du ma bsnan du yod mod /
NK020(wa)001:6653: dor bya ni med par rlom mo //
NK020(wa)001:6654: dpang gyur glan ston man ngag bzhin //
NK020(wa)001:6656: bzhad byed chos kyi nyi ma'i dpal //
NK020(wa)001:6657: legs bshad 'od stong spro bzhin shar //
NK020(wa)001:6658: yo ga'i theg pa'i sgrub thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:6659: 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo las /
NK020(wa)001:6660: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'i dkyil 'khor drug bshad pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:6663: gang thugs mi 'gyur bde ba che'i //
NK020(wa)001:6664: snang brnyan 'gag med zhi khro'i lhar //
NK020(wa)001:6665: ston mdzad dpal ldan rdo rje sems //
NK020(wa)001:6666: drin can bla ma'i zhabs la 'dud //
NK020(wa)001:6667: bla med bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor khyad //
NK020(wa)001:6668: bshad nas rgyud lugs gtsor byas chu bo bzhi //
NK020(wa)001:6669: gang du bskur ba thun mong rtsa dkyil gyi //
NK020(wa)001:6670: cho ga rje yi gsung la kha 'phangs ston //
NK020(wa)001:6671: de ltar yo ga man chad yan lag gi dkyil 'khor drug song nas /
NK020(wa)001:6672: 'dir bla med kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa la don gsum ste /
NK020(wa)001:6673: nang dbang dang sgrub dbang gang du bskur bya'i dkyil 'khor bdun pa dang brgyad pa'i khyad par bshad /
NK020(wa)001:6674: des de dang de la dkyil 'khor so so ba med dam snyam pa'i log rtog bsal /
NK020(wa)001:6675: da lta'i phyag bzhes ltar gyi sgrub dkyil rje bla mas mdzad pa la kha 'phang ba'o //
NK020(wa)001:6677: nang dbang gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK020(wa)001:6678: sgrub dbang gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK020(wa)001:6680: bskyed bya rten dang brten par bcas pa'i dkyiil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:6681: gyi ngo bo rje bla mas mdzad pa'i sgrub thabs
NK020(wa)001:6683: nang dbang 'byung chu'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor zur du 'byed pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK020(wa)001:6684: ji ltar bskyed pa'i cho ga ma h+aa yo ga
NK020(wa)001:6685: dang sgo bstun nas cho ga gsum bskyed la sogs
NK020(wa)001:6686: pas rim gyis bskyed pa'i tshul ston te /
NK020(wa)001:6687: 'dren pa'i las byang che le las /
NK020(wa)001:6688: de nas ting 'dzin gsum bsgoms te /
NK020(wa)001:6689: gzhal yas khang du gsung yig 'bru so so las thugs phyag mtshan /
NK020(wa)001:6690: de las sku phyag rgya rdzogs par bskyed nas /
NK020(wa)001:6691: ye shes kyi lha spyan drangs la /
NK020(wa)001:6694: slob ma dkyil 'khor du drangs te /
NK020(wa)001:6696: de bas na 'dir yan lag gi dkyil 'khor bdun
NK020(wa)001:6697: pa nang dbang gi dkyil 'khor ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK020(wa)001:6698: sgrub thabs la / spyir sngon 'gro dang /
NK020(wa)001:6699: rjes kyi rim pa rnams dang /
NK020(wa)001:6700: dngos gzhi'i dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa man
NK020(wa)001:6701: chad sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs sor bzhag las
NK020(wa)001:6703: ting 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:6704: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa gnyis la
NK020(wa)001:6705: khyad par gyi sgos chos cung zad yod pa bsgyur
NK020(wa)001:6706: tshul ni / ting 'dzin gsum gyi skabs su /
NK020(wa)001:6707: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad skye ba med
NK020(wa)001:6708: pa'i dbyings zhes sogs lhug pa rnams don la mi
NK020(wa)001:6709: 'gal yang / rnam pa rgyud lung gnyis kyi rang
NK020(wa)001:6710: skad ma 'dres par phyed pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:6711: gsum gyi bshad pa bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)001:6713: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad mi dmigs shing spros pa dang bral ba stong pa nyid gyur /
NK020(wa)001:6715: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK020(wa)001:6716: sems can rnams la 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK020(wa)001:6717: snying rje chen po mkha' khyab tu snang bar gyur
NK020(wa)001:6719: rang rig snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin a dkar po'i rnam par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:6720: gzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i skabs su /
NK020(wa)001:6721: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin a yig dkar po dri ma med par gsal ba las /
NK020(wa)001:6722: e am ra sum kem ram rnams chad /
NK020(wa)001:6723: 'od zer 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)001:6724: yum lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa 'byung ba lnga'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:6727: de nas rten gzhal yas khang dngos sgom pa'i tshe /
NK020(wa)001:6728: de'i dbus su rgyu'i a las b+h+r+aum chad /
NK020(wa)001:6729: b+ha ga gsang ba'i 'od zer las /
NK020(wa)001:6731: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+he ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6732: zhes pas sgra gdangs kyi rkyen gyi b+h+r+aum yig 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)001:6733: nam mkha' thams cad pho brang gi gzhal yas khang 'byams klas par grub pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:6735: gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6738: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la /
NK020(wa)001:6739: ji ltar bsgom pa'i tshul dang /
NK020(wa)001:6740: bsgom bya lha so so'i mngon rtogs so //
NK020(wa)001:6742: cho ga gsum gyis rim par bskyed par bya ba ste /
NK020(wa)001:6743: rgyu'i a las zhi khro'i yi ge 'khor lo'i sprin phung rim pa bzhin spro ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:6744: steng khang zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang bya byed gnyis kyi gnas su /
NK020(wa)001:6752: sems dpa' brgyad kyi gnas su /
NK020(wa)001:6759: m+aum hoh thub pa drug gi gnas su /
NK020(wa)001:6760: k+r+aim trum srum pram k+sham ye /
NK020(wa)001:6764: h+aum hoh 'og khang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su /
NK020(wa)001:6766: dbang mchog dang khrag 'thung dgu'i gnas su h+aum yig zung dgu /
NK020(wa)001:6767: glo 'bur dang gru chad la ha brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:6768: khyams dang po'i phyogs mtshams su he brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)001:6770: khyams gnyis pa'i phyogs mtshams su a brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)001:6771: sgor dzahh+aum bam hoh khyams gsum par b+h+yo nyi shu rtsa brgyad phyogs rer drug drug dang /
NK020(wa)001:6773: khyams bzhi par e sum cu rtsa gnyis phyogs rer bdun bdun dang sgo bzhir re re /
NK020(wa)001:6774: khyams lnga par h+aum bdun dang sgor ting bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:6775: khyams drug par h+aum bco brgyad phyogs rer gsum gsum
NK020(wa)001:6776: dang shar nub kyi nang dang sgo bzhir re re
NK020(wa)001:6777: / khyams bdun par h+aum yig zung sum cu phyogs
NK020(wa)001:6778: mtshams brgyad du gsum gsum dang shar nub kyi nang
NK020(wa)001:6780: khyams brgyad pa'i shar phyogs su dzah lhor h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:6782: byang du hohrnamasa drug cu drug cu /
NK020(wa)001:6783: khyams dgu par ma drug cu phyogs rer bco lnga bco lnga ste /
NK020(wa)001:6784: thams cad kyang lha rang rang gi kha dog tu gsal bar gyur pa la /
NK020(wa)001:6785: a zhes brjod pas gzhi'i a de 'od du zhu
NK020(wa)001:6786: nas yig 'bru rnams la khyab par thim pas shin
NK020(wa)001:6789: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK020(wa)001:6790: slar 'dus nas yig 'bru rnams la thim pa 'od
NK020(wa)001:6791: du zhu ba las lha so so'i phyag mtshan du
NK020(wa)001:6793: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK020(wa)001:6794: slar 'dus nas phyag mtshan rnams la thim pa 'od
NK020(wa)001:6795: du zhu ba nyid lha rnams kyi gsang sngags brjod
NK020(wa)001:6796: pa'i rkyen gyis zhi khro lnga brgya zhe bdun gyi
NK020(wa)001:6797: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lha de dang de'i skur bkra
NK020(wa)001:6798: lam gyis gsal bar gyur pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:6802: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah dbus
NK020(wa)001:6803: kyi gdan la bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang
NK020(wa)001:6805: rgyud lung man ngag lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6807: zhes pa'i bar dkyus ltar dang /
NK020(wa)001:6808: zhar byung mgron thabs kyi lha bsgom pa'i skabs su /
NK020(wa)001:6809: dkyil 'khor chen po'i steng 'og phyogs mtshams kyi srung
NK020(wa)001:6810: ba'i 'khor lo la khro bcu yab yum rang rang
NK020(wa)001:6811: gi phyag brnyan phra men nyi shu dang bcas pas
NK020(wa)001:6812: bskor ba'i dbus gzhal yas khang chen po'i 'og gzhi
NK020(wa)001:6813: pad+ma'i chu ba'i mdun du rdo rje gzhon nu yab
NK020(wa)001:6814: yum dang / gzhan yang sprul pa dang yang sprul /
NK020(wa)001:6815: nag mo mche gshog can dang /
NK020(wa)001:6817: go bgo lus bsrung gi bar dkyus ltar ro //
NK020(wa)001:6818: de bzhin du dkyil chog la'ang mtshan bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis sa sbyang ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:6819: lha sta gon gyi rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa'i tshe /
NK020(wa)001:6820: rang gi thugs ka'i h+aum las sa bon spros te bsgom zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6822: yan lag rab gnas kyi las bum /
NK020(wa)001:6823: yan lag can gyi lha bum sta gon gyi lha
NK020(wa)001:6824: rnams cho ga gsum bskyed byed ba'i khyad par tsam
NK020(wa)001:6825: las / gzhan thams cad rje bla mas mdzad pa'i
NK020(wa)001:6826: dkyil chog dri med 'od phreng bzhin shes par bya'o
NK020(wa)001:6827: las / // de dag kyang khro lung che ba'i sgom khog las /
NK020(wa)001:6828: rgyud kyis lha bskyed lung gis gsal btab la /
NK020(wa)001:6829: zhes pa ltar lha rnams rgyud ltar cho ga gsum
NK020(wa)001:6830: gyis bskyed nas lung gi zhi khros gsal 'debs pa
NK020(wa)001:6831: yin no // yang 'dir bsgom bya'i lha grangs la cung zad dpyad par bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:6832: de yang dbang chog ni che mchog tu rigs 'du zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6833: zhi khro'i gtso bo kun bzang dang che mchog gnyis ni /
NK020(wa)001:6834: a nu rang gzhung gi sgom tshul ltar lha rnams lus la 'god pa'i tshe /
NK020(wa)001:6835: de gnyis gzhi lus kyi lha yin pas sam /
NK020(wa)001:6836: yang na dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi khyab byed rigs drug pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK020(wa)001:6837: der ma zad gtso bo gnyis dbang mchog dang gsum
NK020(wa)001:6838: yab yum phye ba'i lha drug po lung gi zhi
NK020(wa)001:6839: khro'i tshig zin las kyang mi 'byung ba ltar logs
NK020(wa)001:6841: re zhig lha lnga brgya zhe gcig byung la /
NK020(wa)001:6842: de'i steng du rdo rje gzhon nu dang khro bcu yab yum /
NK020(wa)001:6843: khra thabs nyi shu ste zhe gnyis bsnan nas lha
NK020(wa)001:6844: grangs lnga brgya dang brgyad cu gya gsum du nges
NK020(wa)001:6845: pa yin te / 'dren pa'i las byang che ler /
NK020(wa)001:6846: de nas bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang pos
NK020(wa)001:6847: skad cig yud la nam mkha' gang nas gang du
NK020(wa)001:6848: khyab pa thams cad du dbang gi dkyil 'khor zhi
NK020(wa)001:6849: khro'i lha lnga brgya dang brgyad cu rtsa gsum gyis
NK020(wa)001:6852: bang rim dang po'i steng du zhi ba'i lha zhe gnyis bkod /
NK020(wa)001:6854: phyogs mtshams steng 'og dang man+dala gyi rtsar phur pa'i lha zhe gnyis dgod /
NK020(wa)001:6856: nang dbang gi dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa las /
NK020(wa)001:6857: dkyil 'khor dgu yi rim par slob dpon gdan /
NK020(wa)001:6858: ma gtogs brgyad la lnga brgya brgyad cu gsum /
NK020(wa)001:6860: mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas pa'i yan lag
NK020(wa)001:6861: gi dkyil 'khor bdun pa ma h+aa'i sgrub thabs le
NK020(wa)001:6862: tshan no // gnyis pa sgrub dbang gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:6863: rtsa rgyud las gsungs pa dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor te /
NK020(wa)001:6864: de yang ji ltar bskyed pa'i cho ga a nu'i theg pa rang lugs bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:6865: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad rang gi phung khams skye mched du 'du zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6866: de nyid gdod nas lha'i rang bzhin du shes pas /
NK020(wa)001:6867: lha rnams kyi gsang sngags brjod pa tsam gyis dwangs
NK020(wa)001:6868: pa'i mtsho la gza' skar shar ba ltar gcig car
NK020(wa)001:6869: du gsal 'debs pa yin pas na /
NK020(wa)001:6870: bskyed tshul dang cho ga ma gzhi rje'i sgrub thabs
NK020(wa)001:6871: dngos grub char 'bebs ltar las mi 'dra ba'i khyad
NK020(wa)001:6872: par las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK020(wa)001:6873: rjes chog gi skabs su phra mo re gnyis tsam dang /
NK020(wa)001:6874: bye brag bskyed bya khro bo'i rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo chas mi mthun pas /
NK020(wa)001:6875: de dag gi kha bsgyur tshul ni /
NK020(wa)001:6877: dngos gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gsum nas /
NK020(wa)001:6878: rdo rje'i kun tu spras pa /
NK020(wa)001:6880: phyi nang rim pa dgu pa zhes pa /
NK020(wa)001:6881: rim pa lnga pa zhes bsgyur zhing gzhan dkyus ltar las /
NK020(wa)001:6883: khyams gru bzhi pa lnga rim phyogs mdog can gyi
NK020(wa)001:6884: bar khyams bzhi la sgo sgo khyud can rgyan med
NK020(wa)001:6885: pa gnyis gnyis te brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)001:6886: phyi khyams lnga pa la sgo rta babs la sogs
NK020(wa)001:6887: pa sgo rgyan dang ldan pa'i sgo dgus kun tu
NK020(wa)001:6888: gsal bar gyur pa'i nang ma gru chad dang bcas
NK020(wa)001:6889: pa'i lte ba ri'u mig dgu pa /
NK020(wa)001:6890: de'i phyir 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa drug rim gyis bskor ba'i lte ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:6891: 'khor lo rim pa gnyis pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:6892: drug pa gsum gyi mthar rdo rje dang /
NK020(wa)001:6894: 'bar ba'i phreng ba ste mu khyud sum rim dang /
NK020(wa)001:6895: 'khor lo rim pa gzhan bzhi la mu khyud rkyang pa re res bskor ba /
NK020(wa)001:6896: phyi nas rim pa bzhin khyad par du gyur pas spags pa /
NK020(wa)001:6898: byol song gtso bo brgyad re res dregs pa pho mo mnan pa /
NK020(wa)001:6901: 'khor lo rnams kyi phyogs kyi rtsibs la pad+ma nyi zla dregs pa'i gdan dang /
NK020(wa)001:6902: lha gnas gzhan rnams su nyi ma dang zhing gi
NK020(wa)001:6903: gdan la sogs pa rigs dang mthun pa'i gdan re
NK020(wa)001:6904: re / pho brang steng gi 'khor lo'i lte bar seng ge'i khri cha gnyis /
NK020(wa)001:6906: steng khang zhi ba rdzogs pa'i /
NK020(wa)001:6907: 'phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6910: 'og khang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i skabs su /
NK020(wa)001:6911: dang po gtso bo bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:6912: sa nga sh+r+ai he ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga
NK020(wa)001:6913: ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra tsan+da sarba
NK020(wa)001:6914: dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum
NK020(wa)001:6915: s+w+aa h+aa / sa nga shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:6916: zhes brjod pas rgyu byang chub kyi sems nyid sngags kyi sgra gdangs kyi sad pa las /
NK020(wa)001:6917: dbus kyi gdan la bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po
NK020(wa)001:6918: rdo rje sa nga sh+r+ai he ru ka sku mdog
NK020(wa)001:6919: mthing nag nyi ma bye ba'i 'od ltar 'bar ba'i
NK020(wa)001:6920: gzi byin can / zhes pa nas /
NK020(wa)001:6921: rdzogs par snang ba'i bdag nyid chen por gyur pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:6923: gnyis pa khrag 'thung drug cu rtsa bzhi bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:6924: phyogs kyi ri'u mig bzhi la rigs bzhi'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:6925: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aah+aa /
NK020(wa)001:6926: badz+ra shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:6927: shar du rdo rje rgyal tshab zhes bya ba'i zhe sdang rdo rje dkar po g.yas rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:6930: rat+na sogs kyis barje ba 'gre shes par byas la /
NK020(wa)001:6932: lhor rdo rje gung phur zhes bya ba'i nga rgyal rin chen sngon po g.yas rin po che /
NK020(wa)001:6934: nub tu rdo rje king zhes bya ba'i 'dod chags pad+ma dmar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK020(wa)001:6936: byang du rdo rje las zhes bya ba'i phrag dog sna tshogs pa ljang gu g.yas rgya gram /
NK020(wa)001:6937: thams cad kyi g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin cing /
NK020(wa)001:6938: zhe sdang rdo rje ma sogs rang mdog gi yum dril bu bsnams pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK020(wa)001:6939: mtshams kyi ri'u mig bzhi la cho 'phrul chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:6940: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa nu ma h+aa sh+r+ai sogs /
NK020(wa)001:6941: shar lhor nam mkha'i dbang phyug sngo skya /
NK020(wa)001:6943: lho nub tu rnam grol sbyin pa dmar ser /
NK020(wa)001:6945: nub byang du rnam grol sgrog pa dmar ljang /
NK020(wa)001:6947: byang shar du thams cad grub pa ser skya /
NK020(wa)001:6948: bzhi ka phyag g.yas gar bsgyur zhing /
NK020(wa)001:6949: g.yon gyis yum nam mkha'i dbang mo sogs rang mdog can dril bu bsnams pa la 'khyud pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:6951: ru dra rnam gsum sogs sh+lo ka gnyis /
NK020(wa)001:6952: 'khor lo dang po rtsibs brgyad kyi phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir dam tshig chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:6953: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai sogs /
NK020(wa)001:6954: shar du rdo rje snying po dkar po g.yas rdo rje'i myu gu /
NK020(wa)001:6956: lhor nor bu'i snying po ser po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu /
NK020(wa)001:6958: nub tu pad+ma'i snying po dmar po g.yas pad+ma'i myu gu /
NK020(wa)001:6960: byang du bkod pa'i snying po ljang gu g.yas ral gri'i myu gu /
NK020(wa)001:6961: de thams cad g.yon 'khyud stabs kyi yum rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:6962: dbang phyug ma sogs rang mdog can dril bu bsnams
NK020(wa)001:6965: rnam shes bzhi dang yul bzhi cing snang yang /
NK020(wa)001:6966: dam tshig chen po bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)001:6967: lha rtog gnyis med rtogs las mi 'da' ba'i /
NK020(wa)001:6968: dam tshig chen po lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)001:6970: 'khor lo rim pa gnyis pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir tshan med pa'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:6971: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mee tri gar+b+ha /
NK020(wa)001:6972: shar du byams pa'i snying po dkar po g.yas rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:6974: lhor snying rje'i snying po ser po g.yas rin chen /
NK020(wa)001:6976: nub tu dga' ba'i snying po dmar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK020(wa)001:6978: byang du btang snyoms kyi snying po ljang gu ga yas ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:6979: de thams cad g.yon skyabs sbyin gyis yum bde ba'i
NK020(wa)001:6980: dbang phyug ma sogs skyabs sbyin gyi dril bu bsnam
NK020(wa)001:6983: dbang po bzhi dang dus bzhi cing snang tshad med
NK020(wa)001:6984: yab yum tshad med rnam bzhi'i yon tan ma lus
NK020(wa)001:6985: pa / ye shes chen por ma 'dres yongs rdzogs shog /
NK020(wa)001:6987: 'bar ba'i phreng bas bcad pa'i phyir rol /
NK020(wa)001:6988: 'khor lo rim pa gsum pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir rol pa chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:6989: sarba ta th+aa ga ta yak+sha /
NK020(wa)001:6990: shar du yak+sha he ru ka smug nag rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:6992: lhor rak+sha he ru ka sngo nag be con /
NK020(wa)001:6994: nub tu bi sha he ru ka dmar nag pad+ma /
NK020(wa)001:6996: byang du bi shwa he ru ka ljang nag phag gi mche bas mtshan pa'i ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:6997: de thams cad g.yon b+hany+dza dmar gyis gang ba 'dzin pas /
NK020(wa)001:6998: yum yak+sha shwa r+ai ka la sogs pa g.yas mche
NK020(wa)001:6999: bas mtshan pa'i dril bu dang g.yon b+han dmar bsnams
NK020(wa)001:7002: phrag dog sdang snyems gti mug cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)001:7003: khrag 'thung yab yum brgyad du bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)001:7004: rnam bzhi dregs pa'i rgyu 'bras kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)001:7005: dbyings dang ye shes rol pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK020(wa)001:7007: 'khor lo rim pa bzhi pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir 'jigs byed chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:7008: sarba ta th+aa ga ta te shwa /
NK020(wa)001:7009: shar du te shwa he ru ka smug nag rdo
NK020(wa)001:7010: rjes mtshan pa'i seng ge'i rgyal mtshan kha gdengs pa
NK020(wa)001:7012: lhor ke shwa he ru ka ser nag rin po
NK020(wa)001:7013: ches mtshan pa'i stag gi rgyal mtshan kha gdengs pa
NK020(wa)001:7015: nub tu pe shwa he ru ka dmar nag pad+mas mtshan pa'i spyan ki'i rgyal mtshan kha gdengs pa /
NK020(wa)001:7017: byang du bi shwa he ru ka ljang nag ral
NK020(wa)001:7018: gris mtshan pa'i dom gyi rgyal mtshan kha gdengs pa
NK020(wa)001:7019: / de thams cad g.yon dung dmar 'dzin pas ke
NK020(wa)001:7020: sha shwa r+ai ka la sogs pa la 'khyud cing
NK020(wa)001:7021: / / yum rnams kyang phyag mtshan yab ltar las rgyal mtshan la dril bus mtshan pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:7023: gnyis 'dzin rtog pa'i sdug bsngal cir 'jig byed yab
NK020(wa)001:7024: yum brgyad du gdug can ma lus dngangs shing 'jigs
NK020(wa)001:7025: byas nas // sgrol sbyor zad myos las bzhi mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)001:7027: 'khor lo rim pa lnga pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir 'joms byed chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:7028: sarba ta th+aa ga ta trag shwa /
NK020(wa)001:7029: shar du trag shwa he ru ka smug nag rdo rjes mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)001:7031: lhor hri shwa he ru ka ser nag rin po ches mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)001:7033: nub tu ka shwa he ru ka dmar nag pad+mas mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)001:7035: byang du pa sha he ru ka ljang nag rgya gram gyis mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)001:7036: de thams cad g.yon dung mar 'dzin pas trag sha
NK020(wa)001:7037: shwa ra'i ka sogs yum rnams yab ltar las zhing
NK020(wa)001:7038: dbyug la dril bu sgra sgrog pas mtshan pa bsnams
NK020(wa)001:7041: ma rungs gdug pa'i dngos po 'joms byed yab yum
NK020(wa)001:7042: brgyad du gdug pa can rnams 'joms par byed pa
NK020(wa)001:7043: yi // sgrol zhing stob pa'i phrin las mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)001:7045: 'khor lo rim pa tha ma'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir za byed chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:7046: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ru ti /
NK020(wa)001:7047: shar du ru ti he ru ka smug nag g.yas pas snying za ba /
NK020(wa)001:7049: lhor rag ti he ru ka ser nag g.yas nang khrol za ba /
NK020(wa)001:7051: nub tu kh+aa hi he ru ka dmar nag g.yas ske khrag 'jib pa /
NK020(wa)001:7053: byang du sa ha he ru ka ljang nag g.yas yan lag za ba /
NK020(wa)001:7054: de thams cad g.yon dung dmar 'dzin pas /
NK020(wa)001:7055: yum ru ti shwa r+ai ka sogs g.yas dril bu 'khrol zhing g.yon b+hany+dza bsnams pa la 'khyud pa /
NK020(wa)001:7056: lha tshogs de thams cad kyang 'bar ba'i gar dgu dang ldan zhing /
NK020(wa)001:7057: dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK020(wa)001:7058: so so'i gdan la rol pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:7060: chags sdang rmongs pa'i rtog pa za byed yab yum
NK020(wa)001:7061: brgyad du bsgral ba'i zhing rnams ma lus gnas ston
NK020(wa)001:7062: nas // spong len med par spyod pa'i mthu thob shog /
NK020(wa)001:7065: phyogs kyi ri'u mig brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)001:7066: 'khor lo dang po dang gnyis pa'i lha rnams zhi bar mdzad pa ltar na /
NK020(wa)001:7067: rigs lnga dang sems dpa' yab yum tshang bas /
NK020(wa)001:7068: steng khang zhi dkyil logs su ma bsgoms kyang chad par mi 'gyur ram snyam mod /
NK020(wa)001:7069: 'dir ni rgya bdun 'grel sogs su zhi ba yin
NK020(wa)001:7070: pa'i gsal byed med cing bskyed sngags dang mtshan gyi
NK020(wa)001:7071: kyang khro bo ston par ma zad /
NK020(wa)001:7072: rtsa rgyud kyi rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi le'u las /
NK020(wa)001:7073: spyan 'bar ba drug cu rtsa bzhi ni he ru ka yab yum drug cu rtsa bzhir gsal lo //
NK020(wa)001:7074: zhes dbu nyer gcig la spyan gsum gsum ste re gsum /
NK020(wa)001:7075: sbas spyan gcig bcas re bzhin sbyar ba'i lha thams cad he ru kar gsungs ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:7077: mdo chen kun 'dus rgyud ltar tshogs chen 'dus /
NK020(wa)001:7078: a nu gtso ltar zhi 'od khro he ru /
NK020(wa)001:7079: che mchog rgyal po badz+ra rgyal tshab ni /
NK020(wa)001:7080: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar byas pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:7081: yang 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad kyi lha rnams phyogs rtsibs la bkod nas /
NK020(wa)001:7082: mtshams rtsibs rnams stong par 'jog pa ni rnal 'byor sa'i sgrol ma las /
NK020(wa)001:7083: 'di dag ni 'khor lo'i rtsibs re re la go rim bzhin du dgod ces zer na /
NK020(wa)001:7084: yod mtshams kyi 'khor lo ye shes kyi yul bas stong par bzhag ste /
NK020(wa)001:7085: phyogs kyi 'khor lo rnams la thabs dang shes rab sbyor ba'i stangs stabs su bzhugs /
NK020(wa)001:7086: zhes gsungs pa ltar bkod pa ste /
NK020(wa)001:7087: thabs shes so sor dgod par 'dod na /
NK020(wa)001:7088: phyogs rnams su yab dang mtshams la yum rnams spel te dgod do //
NK020(wa)001:7089: gsum pa bka' nyan gyi 'khor rnams bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7090: gru chad kyi lha snam nang ma la gsang ba'i bu mo'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:7092: shar lho'i shar du mdzod ldan ma sogs gzhan 'dra ba las /
NK020(wa)001:7093: bzhugs gnas kyi khyad par ni /
NK020(wa)001:7094: lho nub kyi lhor chom rkun ma /
NK020(wa)001:7095: nub byang gi nub tu rab rmongs ma /
NK020(wa)001:7096: byang shar gyi byang du ro lang ma /
NK020(wa)001:7098: lho nub kyi nub tu drod mo /
NK020(wa)001:7099: nub byang gi byang du dur khrod ma /
NK020(wa)001:7100: byang shar gyi shar du gtum mo /
NK020(wa)001:7102: gru chad kyi lha snam phyi ma la dga' ba'i bu mo'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:7104: shar lho'i shar du seng gdong ser mo sogs sngar ltar 'agre'o //
NK020(wa)001:7108: shin tu gsod pa chen po'i 'khor khro bo bcu
NK020(wa)001:7109: rang rang gi za byed mche ba can gyi gdong
NK020(wa)001:7111: sprul pa khra thabs nyi shu dang bcas pa'i steng 'og gi khro bo shar nub dang /
NK020(wa)001:7112: mtshams kyi khro bo rnams rang gnas /
NK020(wa)001:7113: phyogs kyi khro bo bzhi po shar stod la sogs
NK020(wa)001:7114: pa'i phyogs kyi sgo dang po rnams su bzhugs pa'o
NK020(wa)001:7116: rus mgo tshigs mgo'i khro bcu yab yum za gsod bsgoms pa'i mthus /
NK020(wa)001:7117: kha mas gsum gdug pa ma lus sogs so //
NK020(wa)001:7118: khyams de nyid la ma mo brgyad dang ging bco brgyad kyang bzhugs te /
NK020(wa)001:7119: ma ma dun b+h+yo brgyad kyis /
NK020(wa)001:7123: rdo rje kun bzang ma dang /
NK020(wa)001:7124: rdo rje ye shes mchog dang /
NK020(wa)001:7125: rdo rje dpung sgrol ma dang /
NK020(wa)001:7127: rdo rje srog gcod ma dang brgyad phyogs rer gnyis gnyis so //
NK020(wa)001:7129: sha khrag rtsa yi dngos po ma mo brgyad du bsgoms pa'i tshe srog sogs so //
NK020(wa)001:7130: kim ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7141: de dag gi sbyor ba'i yum khams gsum dbugs 'gengs chen mo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7146: rna nyan phra ma mkhan dang /
NK020(wa)001:7147: rbod gtong len par byed ma dang /
NK020(wa)001:7148: snying rjes sgrol ba chen mo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7149: phyag tshang mnyes byed chen po dang bco brgyad po
NK020(wa)001:7150: shar nub tu lnga lnga dang lho byang du bzhi
NK020(wa)001:7152: gur rtsibs bco brgyad sogs so //
NK020(wa)001:7153: shar smad la sogs pa'i phyogs bzhi'i sgo gnyis pa rnams su shin tu gus pa'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:7154: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah shar sgor rta gdong ma dkar mo sogs so /
NK020(wa)001:7158: shar du mkha' 'gro dga' byed ma /
NK020(wa)001:7165: bong bu'i gdong ma dang bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:7174: shar lhor bya rgod gdong ma /
NK020(wa)001:7177: sna tshogs mchog gi gzugs can ma dang bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:7178: lho nub tu bong bu'i gdong ma /
NK020(wa)001:7185: lce sbyang 'khor can ma dang bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:7186: byang shar du bum sna ma /
NK020(wa)001:7189: d+ha shwa g+r+ai ba dang bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)001:7190: phyogs mtshams kyi bzhi bzhi rigs bsdus pas mkha' gro brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)001:7191: de dag rdzu 'phrul gyis 'gro ba'i sprul pa mdzes
NK020(wa)001:7192: sdug 'od 'bar sogs shugs 'gro brgyad dang bcas pa'o
NK020(wa)001:7194: so dang rus pa'i mkha' 'gro shugs 'gro bsgoms pa'i sogs so //
NK020(wa)001:7195: phyogs kyi sgo dang po bzhir /
NK020(wa)001:7196: sh+r+ai badz+ra mud+ga ra mu kha shwa ra y+aa ya
NK020(wa)001:7197: na mah shar sgor dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs
NK020(wa)001:7198: ma sogs so // sgo gnyis pa bzhir /
NK020(wa)001:7201: shar sgor gling bzhi mgyogs ma sogs dang /
NK020(wa)001:7203: sha khrag rtsa yi dngos po sring mo bzhi ru sogs so //
NK020(wa)001:7207: khyab byed chen mo khyung gi mgo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7208: gsod byed chen mo sre mong mgo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7209: mgyogs ma snyegs byed khra'i mgo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7211: myos byed smig bu'i mgo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7212: rkun mo byi la'i mgo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7213: gdug byed sbrul gyi mgo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7214: sgrin byed pha wang gi mgo can brgyad po phyogs dang mtshams la bzhugs shing /
NK020(wa)001:7215: phyogs kyi sgo gnyis gnyis te brgyad la /
NK020(wa)001:7219: seng ge dang pha wang gi gdong can brgyad do //
NK020(wa)001:7221: sna tshogs rtog pa'i snang ba cir rdo rje phra
NK020(wa)001:7222: men bsgoms srid gsum gdug pa'i tshogs rnams kun bsgral
NK020(wa)001:7223: nas // mngon spyod drag po'i 'phrin las lhun grub shog /
NK020(wa)001:7225: khyams de nyid kyi phra men brgyad po re re'i g.yon phyogs su /
NK020(wa)001:7226: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu rta ra phata rak+mo h+aum brgyad kyis /
NK020(wa)001:7227: shar du 'bar ma nyi zer can sogs so //
NK020(wa)001:7231: rdo rje gnod sbyin ma dza gad kyis bkang ba'i
NK020(wa)001:7232: byi ru la sogs pa'i phor pa thogs pa brgyad
NK020(wa)001:7233: phyogs mtshams dang / sgor srin mo rak+tasa bkang pa'i gzhong pa thogs pa brgyad do //
NK020(wa)001:7235: 'jig rte bskyed sdud dngos po gnod sbyin srin mo
NK020(wa)001:7236: bsgoms pa'i sman gyis gso zhing chags pas bsdus byas
NK020(wa)001:7237: nas // thabs shes bde bas kun tu khyab par shog /
NK020(wa)001:7240: ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo nas /
NK020(wa)001:7242: shar stod nas rim bzhin sogs dang /
NK020(wa)001:7243: phyogs kyi ma drug gi phyi rol tu /
NK020(wa)001:7244: b+ha na b+ha na am ku sha dzah ha la ha la pa sha h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7246: pa tsa pa tsa gan+de hoh kro d+ha kro d+h+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7249: shar smad du mi mo gser gyi mdun zhu can dang /
NK020(wa)001:7250: shar lhor dung gi spyang mo mgo dgu ma /
NK020(wa)001:7251: lhor mi mo stag gi tshul can /
NK020(wa)001:7252: lho nub na lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma /
NK020(wa)001:7253: nub stod du mi mo dung gi tshul mchu can /
NK020(wa)001:7254: nub byang na zangs kyi spyang mo mgo dgu pa /
NK020(wa)001:7255: byang na mi mo lcags kyi mchu can ma /
NK020(wa)001:7256: byang shar na g.yu spyang mgo dgu ma /
NK020(wa)001:7257: shar stod na steng gi pho nya lcags kyi bya khra chen mo /
NK020(wa)001:7258: nub smad du 'og gi pho nya lcags kyi byi ba chen mo ste /
NK020(wa)001:7259: pho nya'i gtso mo bcu 'khor dang bcas pas sum brgya drug cu rnams bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:7261: lus bcud rtsa mdud dngos po pho nya sum brgya
NK020(wa)001:7262: drug cu dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral
NK020(wa)001:7263: nas / gnod pa'i bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK020(wa)001:7265: bzhi pa rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7266: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7267: rgyu'i rta babs kyi phyi rol khor yug zlum po la sogs so //
NK020(wa)001:7268: lnga pa zhar byung mgron thabs kyi lha bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7269: rta babs kyi sgor rdo rje kham rgya ma drug dang /
NK020(wa)001:7272: las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin las phyag rgya'i
NK020(wa)001:7273: mchod pa'i 'go'i lag pa byin rlabs kyi l+aam m+aum
NK020(wa)001:7274: m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par gyur zhes pa'i
NK020(wa)001:7276: rnal 'byor mchog gi lag gnyis la //
NK020(wa)001:7278: a dang ma gnyis gsal bzhag ste //
NK020(wa)001:7279: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med sbyar //
NK020(wa)001:7282: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sprad la //
NK020(wa)001:7283: zhes sogs zhi ba yab yum gyi spyi rgya yan dang /
NK020(wa)001:7285: mnyam pa'i tshul du gnas pa la /
NK020(wa)001:7286: ma yi steng du a nyid bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:7287: bya ba thams cad bral ba'i rgya //
NK020(wa)001:7289: a dang ma yi 'bru bcu rnams //
NK020(wa)001:7293: a dang ma yi 'bru bcu rnams /
NK020(wa)001:7294: so sor bcangs te myu gur bya //
NK020(wa)001:7295: shin tu gtod de kun tu bsgyur //
NK020(wa)001:7297: ma yi sbyin pa gtong tshul la //
NK020(wa)001:7298: a yis thams cad skyob byed pa //
NK020(wa)001:7299: 'di ni tshad med chen po yi //
NK020(wa)001:7300: kun la snyoms pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)001:7301: ma nyid khrag rnams 'phrog pa'i snod //
NK020(wa)001:7302: a nyid so 'phreng mche bar sbyar //
NK020(wa)001:7303: 'di ni thams cad rol pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:7304: 'jigs tshul ston pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)001:7305: a dang ma gnyis rting sbyar te //
NK020(wa)001:7306: so 'phreng mche ba'i tshul gyis ni //
NK020(wa)001:7307: shin tu kha glal pa yi tshul //
NK020(wa)001:7309: ma yis bzung ste 'then nas ni //
NK020(wa)001:7310: a yis gdengs shing 'joms byed pa //
NK020(wa)001:7311: 'joms byed chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)001:7312: ma dang a yis mgo mjug nas //
NK020(wa)001:7313: bzung ba'i tshul du byas nas ni //
NK020(wa)001:7315: za byed chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)001:7316: a dang ma yi shes rab las //
NK020(wa)001:7317: g.yas g.yon tshul gyis bsgyur byas te //
NK020(wa)001:7318: so so ji ltar yin thabs sbyar //
NK020(wa)001:7319: khrag 'thung rnams kyi yum gyi rgya //
NK020(wa)001:7321: 'khor gzhan rnams kyi rgya byed par spro na /
NK020(wa)001:7322: koo sing zhal 'phangs pa ltar blangs rjes /
NK020(wa)001:7324: dpa' bo gdan las bzhengs nas ni //
NK020(wa)001:7325: phyogs mtshams kun tu bltas byas nas //
NK020(wa)001:7326: shin tu 'gying shing brjid par bya //
NK020(wa)001:7327: a dang ma yi 'bru rnams ni //
NK020(wa)001:7328: so sor bsdams nas dkur brten bya //
NK020(wa)001:7329: 'di ni khro bo spyi yi rgya //
NK020(wa)001:7330: de nas rta gdong sogs sgo ma dang /
NK020(wa)001:7331: dbang mo'i rgya zhal 'phangs ltar blang zhing /
NK020(wa)001:7332: 'bar ma rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)001:7334: sde tshan so so'i mthar yang /
NK020(wa)001:7335: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:7337: bzlas pa'i dus so so'i sngags bsgyur ba tsam las
NK020(wa)001:7338: gzhan go bgo lus bsrung gi bar sgrub thabs kyi
NK020(wa)001:7339: dkyus ltar bya ba yin no //
NK020(wa)001:7340: de bzhin du dkyil chog kyang /
NK020(wa)001:7341: sgrub dbang kho na'i tshe sa chog mi dgos na'ang
NK020(wa)001:7342: rtsa dkyil logs sgrub lta bu'i tshe spyir dri med
NK020(wa)001:7344: khyad par sa sbyang bzung dang /
NK020(wa)001:7345: lha bum sta gon gyi bskyed bya rten dang brten
NK020(wa)001:7346: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi khyad par bsgyur ba tsam las
NK020(wa)001:7347: gzhan med do // mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du
NK020(wa)001:7348: byas pa'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor brgyad pa a
NK020(wa)001:7349: nu'i sgru thabs kyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:7350: gnyis pa des de dang de la dkyil 'khor so
NK020(wa)001:7351: so ba med dam snyam pa'i log rtog bsal ba
NK020(wa)001:7352: ni / nang dbang dang sgrub dbang gi dkyil 'khor 'di gnyis ni /
NK020(wa)001:7353: don la yan lag can rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor yin te /
NK020(wa)001:7354: dang po ma h+aa dang thun mong pa'i rtsa dkyil lam /
NK020(wa)001:7356: gnyis pa thun min gyi mdo rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK020(wa)001:7357: tshogs chen 'dus pa'ang dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya ste /
NK020(wa)001:7359: des na de gnyis ka rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor yin pas /
NK020(wa)001:7360: rgyud lugs kyi chu bo bzhi de dang de gang rung du bskur rung ste /
NK020(wa)001:7362: 'dir yan lag gi dkyil 'khor so sor phye ba
NK020(wa)001:7363: man ngag gi lugs sam mdo yongs rdzogs kyi chu
NK020(wa)001:7364: bo bzhi dang / rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du bskur bya rgyud lugs kyi chu bo bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)001:7365: lugs gnyis gcig tu dril nas bskur ba'i phyag bzhes
NK020(wa)001:7366: 'di la sgrub dbang la dkyil 'khor zur du ma
NK020(wa)001:7367: mdzad pas / de dang de la dkyil 'khor so
NK020(wa)001:7368: sor med dam snyam pa'i log rtog skye srid pas
NK020(wa)001:7370: deng sang phyag bzhes su mi mdzad kyang /
NK020(wa)001:7371: dkyil 'khor gnyis po'i kha bsgyur lugs go bde bar sbyar ba yin la /
NK020(wa)001:7372: de yang dkyil 'khor de dang der 'byed pa'i khungs ni /
NK020(wa)001:7373: slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyis mdzad pa'i las tho'i nang dbang gi skabs su /
NK020(wa)001:7377: dur khrod gsang ba'i lugs su bzhengs /
NK020(wa)001:7378: zhes so sor gsungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK020(wa)001:7379: dur khrod gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:7380: 'dir bkod phyi ma nyid yin pas /
NK020(wa)001:7381: rtsa rgyud kyi dkyil 'khor 'di nyid ston pa tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub lugs kyi le'ura /
NK020(wa)001:7382: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba 'di rgya cher bshad do //
NK020(wa)001:7384: sgrub pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK020(wa)001:7385: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi mdo //
NK020(wa)001:7388: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs kyi dbang gnyis gcig
NK020(wa)001:7389: tu dril nas bskur ba'i lugs 'dir sgrub dbang gi
NK020(wa)001:7391: rgyud lugs kyi phyi dbang rtsa dkyil du slar yang zlos te bskur bas /
NK020(wa)001:7392: chad pa dang lhag pa'i skyon gnyis ka gnas so zhe na /
NK020(wa)001:7394: de ltar mdzad pa'i dgos pa ni gzhan du rgyas par bshad cing /
NK020(wa)001:7397: gsum pa da lta'i phyag bzhes ltar gang du bskur
NK020(wa)001:7398: ba'i sgrub dkyil rje bla mas mdzad pa la kha
NK020(wa)001:7399: 'phang ba ni / mdo dbang la yan lag gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK020(wa)001:7400: yan lag can rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gnyis su phye nas /
NK020(wa)001:7401: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi skabs su tshogs chen 'dus pa thun mong gi dkyil 'khor bzhengs te /
NK020(wa)001:7402: der rgyud lugs kyi phyi dbang dang /
NK020(wa)001:7403: rgyud dang man ngag thun mong gi nang dbang /
NK020(wa)001:7404: rgyud lugs gtso bor byas pa'i sgrub dbang gi mjug
NK020(wa)001:7405: tu gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo gnyis mdor bsdus
NK020(wa)001:7407: chu bo bzhi rdzogs mdzad pa'i sgrub mchod cho ga gzhung ni /
NK020(wa)001:7408: rje bla ma dam pa'i gsung rab legs bshad rmad
NK020(wa)001:7409: du byung ba'i sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs dang
NK020(wa)001:7410: / dkyil chog dri med 'od 'phreng ltar shes par bya zhing /
NK020(wa)001:7411: de ltar na'ang sgrub thabs kyi rgyas 'bring bsdus pa'i 'dor len dang /
NK020(wa)001:7412: dkyil chog tu zhal 'phangs gnang ba'i slob ma sta gon la sogs pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:7413: der ma zad sgrub chen dang sbrel ba'i bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i chings kyi sgrub khog /
NK020(wa)001:7414: phyi nang gi rab gnas sbyin sreg la sogs pa
NK020(wa)001:7415: rnams rigs mthun gyi sde tshan sdebs pa'i zur 'debs
NK020(wa)001:7417: de dang der shes par bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:7418: rgyud lung dkyil 'khor gyi khyad par phye bas log
NK020(wa)001:7419: rtog bsal nas phyag bzhes kyi gnad ngo sprad pa'i
NK020(wa)001:7420: le tshan no // yongs grags ngag bgros kho na'i rjes //
NK020(wa)001:7421: ma bzlas shes brtson dbang po yis //
NK020(wa)001:7423: zhib dpyad legs bshad dpal du bskrun //
NK020(wa)001:7424: 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo las /
NK020(wa)001:7425: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7426: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa'i skabs te gsum pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:7429: 'gyur bde'i bag chags ches phra ba'ang //
NK020(wa)001:7430: mchog bde'i gnyis med ye shes kyi //
NK020(wa)001:7431: rdo rjes gtan bcom sku bzhi'i bdag /
NK020(wa)001:7432: dpal ldan bla ma la btud nas //
NK020(wa)001:7433: bde chen ye shes chu bo'i rgyun //
NK020(wa)001:7434: dngos grub rba rlabs g.yo ba can //
NK020(wa)001:7435: legs bshad chog gzhung 'bab stegs las //
NK020(wa)001:7436: skal ldan zhing sar lhung lhung 'bebs //
NK020(wa)001:7437: 'dir mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas pa'i gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK020(wa)001:7439: don dam byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis las /
NK020(wa)001:7440: dang po kun rdzob byang sems kyi dbang lus la bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:7441: bla ma'i lus dkyil du bskur ba yin pas /
NK020(wa)001:7442: phyi mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor bsham pa la ltos mi dgos shing /
NK020(wa)001:7443: slob dpon dngos dbang bskur ba'i nus pa med pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:7444: slob ma bla ma yab yum gyi gsang rdzas mkha'
NK020(wa)001:7445: gsang las dngos su len mi nus par ma zad
NK020(wa)001:7446: / bdud rtsi'i 'phrad dang sbyar nas kyang 'thung mi nus pa'i rtog pa can yin na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:7447: gsang rdzas bdud rtsi ril bu tsam la brte nas /
NK020(wa)001:7448: dngos su sgrub tu mi rung ba'am mi nus pa
NK020(wa)001:7449: thams cad ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgrub par bya ba
NK020(wa)001:7450: yin mod / de lta na'ang gang zag de lta bu'i ngor bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor bsham pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:7451: sngon du sgrub pa'i cho ga mdzad pa phyag bzhes su snang zhing /
NK020(wa)001:7452: de la'ang rin chen 'phreng ba sogs su sman sgrub
NK020(wa)001:7453: kyi rigs 'gre sbyar te khro mkhar gyi dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:7455: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du zhal byang la brten nas
NK020(wa)001:7456: khro mkhar gyi dkyil 'khor gyi bdud rtsi bsgrubs zin
NK020(wa)001:7457: pas 'dir logs sgrub mi dgos par ma zad /
NK020(wa)001:7458: skabs 'dir bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor de ltar sgrub dgos pa'i shes byed kyang med pas na /
NK020(wa)001:7459: 'dir glan gyi zab dbang gi las med dang /
NK020(wa)001:7460: glan rdor 'od kyi phyag bzhes ltar 'gos kyi las tho dang /
NK020(wa)001:7461: bkol byang sogs yig rnying gi dgongs pa ltar sgrub par byed pa la /
NK020(wa)001:7463: bdud rtsi byang sems kyi lde gu sogs rdzas sum
NK020(wa)001:7464: cus chag chag btab pa'i gzhir 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK020(wa)001:7466: mtha' rdo ra 'od 'phreng gis bskor ba bri /
NK020(wa)001:7467: 'dir sgo rdzogs 'dri ba'i phyag len kyang byung mod /
NK020(wa)001:7468: bdud rtsi'i stan tsam yin pas 'dis chog go /
NK020(wa)001:7469: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi'i khar b+hany+dza dum bu
NK020(wa)001:7470: gcig pa'i nang du dza gad la bla ma yab
NK020(wa)001:7471: yum gyi gsang rdzas byang sems kyi phabs sbyar ba'i
NK020(wa)001:7472: bdud rtsi ril bu btab pa bur sbrang sogs kyi
NK020(wa)001:7474: kha dar dmar gyis bcad pa'i steng du mkhar ba'i
NK020(wa)001:7475: me long la sngar gyi rdzas sum cus byug pa'i
NK020(wa)001:7476: khar sin+d+hura snyoms par bkram pa la /
NK020(wa)001:7477: yum gyi mkha' mtshon pa'i chos 'byung gi dbus su
NK020(wa)001:7478: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad lte ba dang bcas par zla
NK020(wa)001:7479: gam dgu bris pa la skyes pa'i sa bon nam
NK020(wa)001:7480: ma 'byor na cu gang gis lha dgu'i mtshan ma
NK020(wa)001:7481: dgod / mtha' bskor du ci 'byor pa'i mchod gtor dang /
NK020(wa)001:7482: tshogs kyi yo byad rnams bsham mo //
NK020(wa)001:7485: 'di ltar chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa
NK020(wa)001:7486: kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnams par dag pa
NK020(wa)001:7487: las / badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK020(wa)001:7488: zhes brjod pas bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje yab
NK020(wa)001:7489: yum rjes chags kyis snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub
NK020(wa)001:7490: kyi sems sprin khro bo dang mtshon cha'i tshogs mkha'
NK020(wa)001:7491: khyab tu spros pas bgegs thams cad chos nyid bde
NK020(wa)001:7492: ba chen pa'i dbyings su sbyangs /
NK020(wa)001:7493: tshur 'dus pa las 'od gsal bde ba chen po'i
NK020(wa)001:7494: rang mdangs rdo rje srung ba'i 'khor los mi phyed
NK020(wa)001:7497: zhi khro'i lha tshogs mkha' khyab tu sad par dmigs nas //
NK020(wa)001:7498: lus 'di rtsa yi gtso bo phal pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:7499: ye nas sprul skur gnas pa ma shes te //
NK020(wa)001:7500: dbyibs kyi lha sku rtsa la bsgom ma shes /
NK020(wa)001:7501: sprul skur rang bzhin lhun grub 'bras bur bshags //
NK020(wa)001:7502: lus gnas yi ge longs skur gnas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7503: lam du ma shes bde ba ma bsgoms pas //
NK020(wa)001:7504: gtum mo drod kyi 'bras bu ma thob ste //
NK020(wa)001:7505: 'bras bu longs spyod rdzogs pa'i ngang du bshags //
NK020(wa)001:7506: ye nas bdud rtsi thig le chen po ni //
NK020(wa)001:7507: chos sku dri ma med par gnas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7508: ma shes ma rtogs bdud rtsir ma sbyangs pa //
NK020(wa)001:7509: 'bras bu chos kyi sku yi ngang du bshags //
NK020(wa)001:7510: ye nas thams cad ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK020(wa)001:7511: ma sbyangs gnas lugs don du ma rtogs pas //
NK020(wa)001:7512: lam bstan rdo rje rba rlabs lam ma bsgoms //
NK020(wa)001:7513: 'bras bu ngo bo nyid kyi sku ru bshags //
NK020(wa)001:7514: zhes thabs lam dbang gi 'bras bu'i bshags pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:7515: de nas dam bca' ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:7516: bde ba chen po'i gseng lam gyis sems can gyi don sgrub pa'i lhag bsam brtan pos //
NK020(wa)001:7518: ma rtogs log par 'khyams pa rnams //
NK020(wa)001:7519: rgyal ba'i sras su bskyed nas ni //
NK020(wa)001:7520: 'khor ba'i rgyun rnams bcad par bya //
NK020(wa)001:7521: de nas byin dbab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7522: bdag nyid rdo rje he ru ka yab yum snyoms
NK020(wa)001:7523: par zhugs pa'i dga' ba'i sgras ye shes kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:7524: lo thabs cad mkha' khyab tu sad nas bdag gnas
NK020(wa)001:7525: yo byad rnams la thim pas bde ba chen pa'i
NK020(wa)001:7528: a la la ho b+ha ga w+aan sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:7530: zhes bdud rtsi lngas spags pa'i 'doms dkris kyi ras
NK020(wa)001:7531: dang gu gul sogs kyi spos sreg cing rol mo'i
NK020(wa)001:7532: sgra bya'o // de nas mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7533: ram yam kham gis mchod rdzas kyi dngos 'dzin thams cad bsregs gtor sbyangs /
NK020(wa)001:7534: stong pa'i ngang las mchod snod kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i dbyings su /
NK020(wa)001:7535: mchod rdzas rnams ye shes kun tu bzang po'i rol
NK020(wa)001:7536: par mnyam par sbyor ba'i bde ba chen po byang
NK020(wa)001:7537: chub kyi sems kyi rang rtsal 'dod yon gyi rnam
NK020(wa)001:7538: pa thams cad par 'char ba'i sprin chen por gyur
NK020(wa)001:7539: / +aahh+aum ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7541: ma h+aa rak+ta b+h+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:7542: na mas+sa man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:7543: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK020(wa)001:7548: chos thams cad skye ba med pa'i dbyings ye ji
NK020(wa)001:7549: bzhin pa kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par
NK020(wa)001:7550: dag pa'i ngang la dar cig mnyam par bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:7551: de'i ngang las 'gag med snying rje rig pa'i rtsal
NK020(wa)001:7552: snang ye shes kun tu bzang po'i rol pa rang
NK020(wa)001:7553: bzhin lhun grub tu snang ba las /
NK020(wa)001:7554: dbyings dang ye she gnyis su med pa'i sras bde
NK020(wa)001:7555: ba chen po rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems a
NK020(wa)001:7556: yig dkar po dri ma med pa /
NK020(wa)001:7559: a yig yongs su gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)001:7560: bdag nyid skad cig gi bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo
NK020(wa)001:7561: rje sems dpa' sngon po zhi zhing 'dzum la mtshan
NK020(wa)001:7562: dpe'i lang tsho rab tu rgyas pa /
NK020(wa)001:7563: g.yas rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing /
NK020(wa)001:7564: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK020(wa)001:7565: rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:7566: rang snang gi yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug
NK020(wa)001:7567: ma sngon mo g.yas dril bu dang g.yon rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:7568: 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK020(wa)001:7569: dar gyi chas gos lnga dang rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)001:7570: yab kyi gnas lnga'i rtsa 'khor gyi dbus su +aam
NK020(wa)001:7571: h+aum s+w+aa h+aam rnams 'phros 'dus yongs su gyur pa
NK020(wa)001:7572: las spyi bor rnam par snang mdzad dkar po /
NK020(wa)001:7573: mgrin par 'ed dpag med dmar po /
NK020(wa)001:7574: snying gar mi bskyod pa sngon po /
NK020(wa)001:7575: lte bar rin chen 'byung ldan ser po /
NK020(wa)001:7576: gsang bar don yod grub pa ljang khu /
NK020(wa)001:7577: de rnams g.yas rang rtags thugs ka dang /
NK020(wa)001:7578: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK020(wa)001:7579: yan lag bzhi la h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes pas sgo ba bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:7580: yum gyi gnas lnga'i rtsa 'khor gyi dbus su l+aam
NK020(wa)001:7581: p+aam m+aum m+aam t+aam rnams 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur
NK020(wa)001:7582: pa las / spyi bor spyan ma dkar mo /
NK020(wa)001:7583: mgrin par gos dkar mo dmar mo /
NK020(wa)001:7584: snying gar dbyings phyug ma sngon mo /
NK020(wa)001:7585: lte bar m+aa ma k+ai ser mo /
NK020(wa)001:7586: gsang bar sgrol ma ljang khu /
NK020(wa)001:7587: de rnams g.yas dril bu dkur brten cing g.yon rang rtags thugs ka /
NK020(wa)001:7588: dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa pas lag g.yas la mi pham ma /
NK020(wa)001:7591: b+ha ga'i sgor ral gcig ma rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)001:7592: de nas yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum las rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga pa lte bar h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7594: bu gar a yig ye shes kyi me 'bar ba dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:7595: yum gyi mkha' +aahls pad+ma ze'u 'brur h+r+aihdamara po 'bar bas mtshan pa'i nang dang /
NK020(wa)001:7596: phyi rol sin+d+hu ra'i dkyil 'khor dbyer med lhun gyis
NK020(wa)001:7597: grub pa'i gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i dbus su
NK020(wa)001:7598: rtsa dgu'i ngo bo 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad lte ba
NK020(wa)001:7599: dang bcas pa'i steng du zla gam re res mtshan
NK020(wa)001:7600: pa la / byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ye
NK020(wa)001:7601: shes kyi ngo bo he ru ka yab yum goo
NK020(wa)001:7602: r+ai brgyad kyis bskor bar bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:7603: yum gyi mkha' dbyings zla gam la //
NK020(wa)001:7604: grub pa'i gzhal yas khang du bskyed //
NK020(wa)001:7605: rtsibs brgyad zla gam dgur gsal la //
NK020(wa)001:7606: byang chub sems las phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:7607: lha dgu gsal ba'i ye shes bskyed //
NK020(wa)001:7608: des ni thams cad rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK020(wa)001:7611: h+aum big+h+n+aan+ta krita phata kyis bsang /
NK020(wa)001:7613: stong pa'i ngang las badz+ra tsakra zhes brjod pas bdud
NK020(wa)001:7614: rtsi'i snod b+hany+dza dum bu gcig pa dpral ba rang
NK020(wa)001:7615: la bstan pa yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du
NK020(wa)001:7616: bcud ye shes lnga'i ngo bor zhu bas yongs su
NK020(wa)001:7617: gtams pa'i spris ma 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i rnam
NK020(wa)001:7623: zhes brjod pas 'khor lo' lte bar mi bskyod pa yab yum /
NK020(wa)001:7624: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du rnam snang /
NK020(wa)001:7627: byang du don grub rnams yab yum kha sbyor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:7628: de nas rang dang mdun gyi bdud rtsi me long dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad la /
NK020(wa)001:7629: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK020(wa)001:7630: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya sogs kyi rdo rje gsum du brlab /
NK020(wa)001:7631: rang 'dra'i ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK020(wa)001:7632: e h+ye hi sa spyan drangs //
NK020(wa)001:7634: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra gyis brtan par byas /
NK020(wa)001:7639: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK020(wa)001:7640: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK020(wa)001:7641: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK020(wa)001:7642: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che //
NK020(wa)001:7644: de nas rjes chags kyis bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:7645: rang gzhi lus rdor sems yab yum dang /
NK020(wa)001:7646: bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor yab yum du gsal bas /
NK020(wa)001:7647: phan tshun lta bas chog mi shes pa la mig zhu zhing blta bas gzugs kyi dga' ba bskyed /
NK020(wa)001:7648: de nas sgra thos pas mi ngoms pa'i ngag snyan pos yab yum bsnol mar /
NK020(wa)001:7649: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:7653: steng 'og gi dri zhim rgyas pa snom zhing ti ba su khe /
NK020(wa)001:7654: lce mchu 'jib pa'i ro myang bas gan+d+he tsit+ta /
NK020(wa)001:7659: dgyes pa rdo rje'i cho 'phrul las //
NK020(wa)001:7660: byang chub char sprin dbab tu gsol //
NK020(wa)001:7661: zhes bskul ba'i lan du yab kyis //
NK020(wa)001:7662: e ma yid kyi dga' bde mo //
NK020(wa)001:7663: gdung ba'i snying 'phreng shes rab gzungs //
NK020(wa)001:7665: bde ba'i rdo rje byang chub 'bar //
NK020(wa)001:7667: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes phan tshun bzung 'khyud bsdams pas mnyes te /
NK020(wa)001:7669: 'dod pa'i dbang mo thams cad ni //
NK020(wa)001:7670: chags pas 'gying ba'i gtso mo yin //
NK020(wa)001:7671: chags pa rnam par sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK020(wa)001:7672: 'dod pa gnas su drang bar bya //
NK020(wa)001:7673: zhes yab yum dgyes par rol pa'i bde ba'i sgras
NK020(wa)001:7674: de bzhin gshegs pa ma lus shing lus pa med
NK020(wa)001:7675: pa thams cad zhi ba rigs lnga dang he ru
NK020(wa)001:7676: ka rigs lnga yab yum gyi rnam par nam mkha'
NK020(wa)001:7678: de thams cad stong gsum 'gengs pa tsam gyi 'dod
NK020(wa)001:7679: chags chen po'i rol pas byang chub sems kyi ngo
NK020(wa)001:7680: bor zhu / rang dang bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor la thim /
NK020(wa)001:7681: rang gi lus dkyil gyi rigs lnga yang rjes chags
NK020(wa)001:7682: kyi mes zhu ba dang lhan cig tu sku'i dbyibs
NK020(wa)001:7683: brgyud / yum gyi mkha' la byang sems kyi char
NK020(wa)001:7684: chen po phab pas mkha' gsang gi dkyil 'khor rnams
NK020(wa)001:7685: bde ba chen pos mnyes par byas /
NK020(wa)001:7686: de las kyang byang chub kyi sems sprin mkha' khyab tu spros //
NK020(wa)001:7688: nyan rang rnams 'gog pa las bslang ste bde ba'i ye shes kyi myu gu bskyed /
NK020(wa)001:7689: byang sems rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyi shes sgrib
NK020(wa)001:7690: phra mo rnams sbyangs te chos sku'i ngang du brlan
NK020(wa)001:7691: par byas / sems can thams cad kyi sgrib pa bsal nas 'od gsal du sbyangs /
NK020(wa)001:7692: tshur 'dus pa dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams rol pa'i
NK020(wa)001:7693: byang sems dang lhan cig thod pa'i bdud rtsi la
NK020(wa)001:7694: 'dren pas byin gyis brlabs par bsam ste /
NK020(wa)001:7695: h+aum badz+ra ng+h+rika m+aum d+h+aa t+we shwa r+ai /
NK020(wa)001:7696: sogs rigs lnga yab yum sbrel ba'i sngags sham du /
NK020(wa)001:7697: sh+r+ai ma h+aa su kha bo d+hi badz+ra h+aum hoham /
NK020(wa)001:7698: zhes snyan pa'i dbyangs la bcug ste ci nus bzla /
NK020(wa)001:7699: mthar bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor gyi rigs lnga'ang bde ba'i ngo bor zhu ste /
NK020(wa)001:7702: cha gsum gtor ma las gzhung bsrang ba'i sngon du gtong ba'i phyag len ltar yang rung la /
NK020(wa)001:7704: de nas dbang chog ltar slob dpon 'jug cing slob
NK020(wa)001:7705: ma la kun rdzob byang sems kyi zab mo'i dbang
NK020(wa)001:7707: yab yum sbyor ba'i sems sprin gyis /
NK020(wa)001:7708: mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor gyis mtshon pa'i snod bcud thams cad sbyangs nas rang la thim /
NK020(wa)001:7709: bdag nyid kyang bde ba chen pos snang gsum 'gags
NK020(wa)001:7710: pa'i 'od gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i dbyings su
NK020(wa)001:7712: de'i ngang las zung 'jug rdo rje sems dpa'i skur langs te /
NK020(wa)001:7713: smon lam dang bkra shis ni //
NK020(wa)001:7714: 'pho chen bcu gnyis dbu ma'i lam du bzhugs //
NK020(wa)001:7715: gtum mo 'bar bas zla ba bdud rtsir zhu //
NK020(wa)001:7716: 'byung ldog dga' bzhi'i 'gros rdzogs mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:7717: bde chen ye shes tshe 'dir mngon gyur shog /
NK020(wa)001:7718: chos nyid gsang ba yum gyi b+ha ga'i klong //
NK020(wa)001:7719: ye shes rdo rje rjes chags mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:7720: bde chen byang chub sems kyi bden pa des //
NK020(wa)001:7721: srid zhi'i dge legs yongs rdzogs bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:7722: ces me tog 'thor zhing rol mo'i sgra sbyar ro //
NK020(wa)001:7724: yum gyi mkha'i dkyil 'khor la zhi ba zhe gnyis
NK020(wa)001:7725: bskyed par mdzad pa ni rigs pa ma yin te
NK020(wa)001:7726: / rtsa rgyud kyi gsang sbyor sgrub pa'i le'ura lha
NK020(wa)001:7727: dgu bskyed par sngar gsal 'debs kyi tshe brjod pa
NK020(wa)001:7728: / bzhin dang / des me long gi dkyil 'khor yang de ltar bri dgos par grub ste /
NK020(wa)001:7729: phyi gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bzhin du nang yum
NK020(wa)001:7730: gyi mkha' la'ang bsgom dgos par bshad pa'i phyir de
NK020(wa)001:7731: skad du'ang le'u de las yab yum gyi gnas lngar
NK020(wa)001:7732: rigs lnga yab yum bskyed pa dang rjes 'brel du
NK020(wa)001:7734: gzungs su byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7735: de yi gzugs kyi phung po la /
NK020(wa)001:7736: bde bar gshegs pa'i sa bon lnga //
NK020(wa)001:7738: rgyas btab byin rlabs dbang bskur nas //
NK020(wa)001:7739: bde gshegs yum lnga'i sku mchog gsal //
NK020(wa)001:7740: rdo rje thabs la'ang de bzhin te //
NK020(wa)001:7741: de ltar gsal bar gyur pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:7742: yum gyi mkha' la me ri bsgom //
NK020(wa)001:7743: gsang ba dbugs kyi zla gam la /
NK020(wa)001:7744: byang chub sems kyi spro bsdu bya //
NK020(wa)001:7745: gzugs brnyan ji ltar gsal ba bzhin //
NK020(wa)001:7746: chags pa'i mkha' la de bzhin no //
NK020(wa)001:7748: 'di nyid gsang dbang gi cho gzhung la sbyor rigs pa'ang 'grel chung las /
NK020(wa)001:7749: rnal 'byor bde ba chen po'i dngos grub sgrub pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:7750: gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:7752: 'gro ba rgyal ba'i sras su bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK020(wa)001:7753: gsang sbyor sgrub pa'i le'u gsungs so //
NK020(wa)001:7755: gsung ngag zab mo bdud rtsi'i rgyun //
NK020(wa)001:7756: rna ba'i dbang po'i 'jug ngogs las //
NK020(wa)001:7759: kun rdzob byang sems kyi gsang dbang lus la bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:7762: rnam 'gyur du mar snang yang dbyings ye shes //
NK020(wa)001:7763: dbyer med don dam byang sems dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK020(wa)001:7764: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rang rig rdo rje sems //
NK020(wa)001:7765: ji bzhin mngon gyur drin can bla mar 'dud //
NK020(wa)001:7766: rang gnas ye shes don dam byang sems dbang //
