NK020(wa)001:7767: ngo sprod gnad kyis rang ngo sprod pa'i thabs //
NK020(wa)001:7768: lta ba ye 'byams gsang dbang rdzogs chu yis //
NK020(wa)001:7769: chog gzhung kun bzang don gyi 'phrin las brtsam //
NK020(wa)001:7770: gnyis pa don dam byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:7771: dri dang ba byung gis chag chag btab pa'i gzhi
NK020(wa)001:7772: la pad 'dab bcu drug mu khyud phyi nang dang
NK020(wa)001:7773: bcas pa'i mthar snying gi rtsa ba mdun dang rtse
NK020(wa)001:7774: mo rgyab phyogs su bstan pa bri /
NK020(wa)001:7775: tshon ni pad 'dab lte ba dang bcas pa dmar po /
NK020(wa)001:7776: mu khyud nang ma 'od zer dang /
NK020(wa)001:7777: phyi ma dkar po la rdo rje sngon po'i 'phreng ba /
NK020(wa)001:7778: dbus kyi lte ba la a dkar po mgo rgyab mdun du bstan pa'i zhal sprod /
NK020(wa)001:7779: 'dab ma rnams la'ang a dkar po zhal nang du blta ba bri /
NK020(wa)001:7780: bum pa a dkar gyi mtshan ma can gyi nang
NK020(wa)001:7781: du bcud bum rdzas spyi dang mthun pa'i steng du
NK020(wa)001:7782: skye bdun pa'i sha dang ring bsrel sogs dam rdzas
NK020(wa)001:7783: byin can gyi phab kyang blug cing /
NK020(wa)001:7784: 'bras bu can gyi shing dang rma bya'i mdongs kyis kha brgyan la /
NK020(wa)001:7785: bum chu a las chos nyid rgyu rkyen med pa'i
NK020(wa)001:7786: bdud rtsir bsam nas dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi
NK020(wa)001:7787: la 'god / bum pa'i khar dgongs nyams kyi glu
NK020(wa)001:7788: gsung ba po'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi tsakli yang bzhag
NK020(wa)001:7789: la 'god / / dkyil 'khor gyi mthar ci 'byor pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:7791: tshogs kyi yo byad la sogs pas bskor /
NK020(wa)001:7793: thog mar zhi ba'i 'phrin las gzhung bsrang bar gsungs kyang /
NK020(wa)001:7794: dbang 'di dus tshigs bcad nas phyis bskur ba la dgongs kyi /
NK020(wa)001:7795: ding sang rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ma bsdus par sbrel nas mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK020(wa)001:7796: zhi ba'i chog 'phrin zur du bya mi dgos pas /
NK020(wa)001:7797: khyad par gyi las gzhung kun bzang don gyi 'phrin las la 'jug ste /
NK020(wa)001:7799: bar du bcad bya gcod byed thams cad rgyu rkyen med par rang byung /
NK020(wa)001:7800: byed pa po med par lhun gyis grub pas rnam
NK020(wa)001:7801: par mi rtog pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag nas
NK020(wa)001:7803: mi rtog ye shes bgegs bsal nas /
NK020(wa)001:7808: zhes rnam par mi rtog mi phyed pa'i rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:7809: ye shes kyi rang rtsal me 'bar ba dang bcas
NK020(wa)001:7812: sdig sgrib thams cad dmigs med bya rtsol med pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag nas /
NK020(wa)001:7814: gzhi nyid ma bcom lhun gyis grub pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7815: dgag sgrub gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK020(wa)001:7816: bzang ngan gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK020(wa)001:7817: ma bcos byang chub ngang du bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:7818: lta ba'i rang bzhin bza' gtad med pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7819: bza' gtad gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK020(wa)001:7820: yul sems gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK020(wa)001:7821: rang sa byang sems klong du bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:7822: sgom pa cog bzhag dmigs gtad med pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7823: dmigs gtad gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK020(wa)001:7824: bzhag 'jog gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK020(wa)001:7825: cog bzhag byang sems klong du bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:7826: spyod pa 'dzin med blang dor med pa la /
NK020(wa)001:7827: blang dor gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK020(wa)001:7828: gtsang rme gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK020(wa)001:7829: lhug pa byang sems klong du bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:7830: dam tshig bsrung med 'da' nyams med pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7831: 'da' nyams gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK020(wa)001:7832: bshags gso gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK020(wa)001:7833: bsrung med byang sems klong du bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:7834: sa lam bgrod med rtsol sgrub 'das pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7835: rtsol sgrub gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK020(wa)001:7836: bgrod thob gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK020(wa)001:7837: bgrod med byang chub klong du bshags par bgyi //
NK020(wa)001:7838: 'bras bu ji bzhin ye sangs rgyas pa la //
NK020(wa)001:7839: spang thob gnyis su lta ba thang re chad //
NK020(wa)001:7840: rgyu 'bras gnyis su 'dzin pa nyon re mongs //
NK020(wa)001:7841: lhun gnas byang sems klong du bshags par bgyis //
NK020(wa)001:7842: de nas mchod gtor brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7843: dngos 'dzin rnams lhag mthong gi me //
NK020(wa)001:7845: zhi gnas kyi chus bsregs gtor bkrus par mos pas /
NK020(wa)001:7847: zhes snang med kyi ngang la dar gcig bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:7848: de'i ngang las ye ji bzhin pa kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong du /
NK020(wa)001:7849: ye shes kun tu bzang po'i rtsal snang ma 'gags pa /
NK020(wa)001:7850: rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa'i 'dod yon gyi rol mor shar bar mos nas /
NK020(wa)001:7851: +aahh+aum ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7852: ma h+aa ba lim ta h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7853: ma h+aa rak+ta b+h+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:7857: yum kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong skye med spros
NK020(wa)001:7858: pa dang bral ba ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK020(wa)001:7859: nyid rnam pa gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas par
NK020(wa)001:7860: mos nas / gsal gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7861: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na rat+na man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK020(wa)001:7866: sim ha r+aa dza ni ti ra bam /
NK020(wa)001:7868: rmad byung byang chub sems kyi gnas //
NK020(wa)001:7869: gzhal med khang mdzes de dag ni //
NK020(wa)001:7871: rin chen las byas shin tu snang //
NK020(wa)001:7872: nyi ma zla ba'i gdan dang 'od //
NK020(wa)001:7873: zhing rnams gdan chen gsal bar gyur //
NK020(wa)001:7875: de nas brten pa bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7876: yul dbyings de nyid yul can ye shes dang gnyis
NK020(wa)001:7877: su med pa rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK020(wa)001:7878: 'khor bde ba chen po nyid rnam pa bcom ldan
NK020(wa)001:7879: 'das kun tu bzang po mthing ga phyag mnyam bzhag
NK020(wa)001:7880: dang / zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung can /
NK020(wa)001:7881: kun tu bzang mo dang 'du 'bral med par bzhugs
NK020(wa)001:7882: pa'i rtsal snang zhi khro rig 'dzin bka' sdod dang
NK020(wa)001:7883: bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams su ma 'gags par
NK020(wa)001:7884: shar ba thams cad kyang rang byung gi ye shes
NK020(wa)001:7885: gcig gi rol par sad par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:7886: thugs tsit+ta rin po che'i pho drang mtshon byed brda'i dkyil 'khor yang /
NK020(wa)001:7887: dbyings rgyu rkyen med par rang byung ba kun tu bzang mo dang /
NK020(wa)001:7888: ye shes byed pa po med par lhun grub tu
NK020(wa)001:7889: shar ba kun tu bzang po gnyis gdod nas ma
NK020(wa)001:7890: skyes pa'i chos nyid yi ge a'i rnam pa dang
NK020(wa)001:7891: / ye shes kyi rtsal snang tshogs brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)001:7892: dbyings kyi rtsa snang yul brgyad kyang gdod nas dag
NK020(wa)001:7893: pa'i kun bzang a yig bcu drug gi rnam par
NK020(wa)001:7894: bzhugs par mos nas 'di skad ces /
NK020(wa)001:7895: rang gi snying por rang byas la //
NK020(wa)001:7896: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:7897: sangs rgyas mi sgom bdag nyid sgom //
NK020(wa)001:7898: rang gi lha ni kun bzang sgom //
NK020(wa)001:7899: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK020(wa)001:7901: dpal chen khrag 'thung ma mo'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:7902: gzhan yang rnam pa mang po'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:7903: lha dang lha min rlung lha dang //
NK020(wa)001:7904: gshin rje klu dang me lha dang //
NK020(wa)001:7905: gnod sbyin srin po 'byung po'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:7906: dbang med dad pas 'dus pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:7907: lha yi tshogs kyis gang ba rnams //
NK020(wa)001:7908: rnal 'byor rang rig chen po yis //
NK020(wa)001:7909: gsang ba'i gnas rnams gcig tu sgom //
NK020(wa)001:7910: ye shes rang byung byang chub sems //
NK020(wa)001:7911: sangs rgyas thams cad bdag gis byas //
NK020(wa)001:7912: ye shes lha rnams rang las byung //
NK020(wa)001:7913: 'di ni rmad du byung ba'i sku //
NK020(wa)001:7914: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dam pa yin //
NK020(wa)001:7915: mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgya //
NK020(wa)001:7916: mi bskyod pa ni ye shes che //
NK020(wa)001:7917: mi len pa ni bdag med cing //
NK020(wa)001:7918: ming 'dir tshig bral mnyam nyid do //
NK020(wa)001:7920: de nas ye shes pa drang zhing bstim pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:7921: ye nas 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa la mnyam par bzhag nas 'di skad ces /
NK020(wa)001:7922: sangs rgyas mi gshegs bdag nyid gshegs //
NK020(wa)001:7923: lha yang gzhan nas 'bod mi dgos //
NK020(wa)001:7924: bya ba med pas las rnams zin //
NK020(wa)001:7925: e h+ye hi k+aa ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:7926: dzahdzah bud+d+ha sa t+wa a ti yo ga sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:7928: de nas bdag nyid kyis rang gi ye shes yul
NK020(wa)001:7929: med rang gsal du mjal ba la ngo mtshar ba'i
NK020(wa)001:7930: tshul gyis / gang la sangs rgyas gus mdzad pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:7931: don de la yang phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:7932: sangs rgyas kun la brtser dgongs nas //
NK020(wa)001:7933: gang gi don du mdzad pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:7934: don mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:7936: chos kun mnyam nyid du rtogs pa las mi 'da'
NK020(wa)001:7937: na sgul bskyod thams cad phyag rgya las mi 'da'
NK020(wa)001:7938: ste / phyag rgya mi bskyod yan lag bskyod /
NK020(wa)001:7939: rang byung mchog gi phyag rgya'o //
NK020(wa)001:7940: de nas phyi mdo sde dang mthun pa rnam par grol ba'i phung po lnga dang /
NK020(wa)001:7941: nang rgyud sde dang mthun par sman gtor rak+ta'i mchod
NK020(wa)001:7942: pa rnams 'khor gsum mi rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK020(wa)001:7943: bya rtsol med pa'i ngang du dbul te /
NK020(wa)001:7945: phung po tshogs kyi yan lag 'di //
NK020(wa)001:7946: rnam grol phung po lnga ru thim //
NK020(wa)001:7947: bdag las byung ba'i khu ba yis //
NK020(wa)001:7948: bdag gi lus la rab brgyan te //
NK020(wa)001:7949: dngos grub mchog rnams bdag las byung //
NK020(wa)001:7950: sman mchog nad sel bder 'tsho ba //
NK020(wa)001:7951: dug gsum sman mchog byang chub sems //
NK020(wa)001:7953: lhun gyis grub pas mi bsngo zhing //
NK020(wa)001:7954: gdod nas dag pa'i bdud rtsi yin //
NK020(wa)001:7955: bud+d+ha ba da pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)001:7956: mchod pa gzhan la mi mchod do //
NK020(wa)001:7957: bdag nyid kun gyi lha yin pas //
NK020(wa)001:7958: kun gyi mchod pas bdag la mchod //
NK020(wa)001:7959: kun mchod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK020(wa)001:7960: chos nyid dag pa'i rgyan du gsungs //
NK020(wa)001:7961: mi bzungs gtor bas gtor ma yin //
NK020(wa)001:7962: bud+d+ha sa t+wa ma h+aa ba lim ta rak+ta kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)001:7963: de nas gdod nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK020(wa)001:7964: pas 'bras bu gzhan nas btsal du med pa'i phyir
NK020(wa)001:7965: smon pa med pa'i ngang las sgyu ma'i tshul gyis
NK020(wa)001:7967: gang gi don du byas pa'i don //
NK020(wa)001:7968: de dag bdag la grub gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:7970: don de bdag gis rig gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:7971: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:7972: sangs rgyas kun sangs rgyas gyur cig /
NK020(wa)001:7976: +aahh+aum la bya zhes gsungs pa'i don /
NK020(wa)001:7977: phyi ltar na lung bum pa can nam dbugs rang
NK020(wa)001:7978: babs gang rung gi steng nas 'byung 'jug gnas gsum
NK020(wa)001:7979: yi ge gsum gyi gdangs su mos pas rdo rje'i
NK020(wa)001:7980: bzlas pa bya / nang ltar sgo lnga gsal la rtog med kyi ngang nas rlung so mang bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:7981: gsang ba ltar brjod bya rjod byed thams cad dang
NK020(wa)001:7982: bral ba'i chos nyid kyi ngang bsal bzhag med par
NK020(wa)001:7983: klod de / snying po mi brjod bdag nyid brjod //
NK020(wa)001:7984: rang gi snying po rang sngags kyis //
NK020(wa)001:7985: grub pa'i snying po chud mi za //
NK020(wa)001:7987: dngos grub gzhan nas mi slong ste //
NK020(wa)001:7988: mi gsung mnyam bzhag sngags tshig go //
NK020(wa)001:7989: bud+d+ha ba da ma h+aa a ti yo ga sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)001:7990: sha pa ru pa a hoh su kha de ba shi shi /
NK020(wa)001:7991: zhes pa'i dgongs pa bskyang ngo //
NK020(wa)001:7992: de nas grags stong chos nyid kyi rang sgras bstod pa ni //
NK020(wa)001:7993: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i yon tan ma btsal lhun grub la //
NK020(wa)001:7994: blang dor gnyis med kyi ngang nas nges shes bskyed pa ste /
NK020(wa)001:7995: sangs rgyas kun bas sngar sangs rgyas //
NK020(wa)001:7996: mi shes dri ma ye nas med //
NK020(wa)001:7997: dpal gyi rnam rgyal de bzhin du //
NK020(wa)001:7998: longs spyod dbang phyug dpal dang mnyam //
NK020(wa)001:7999: rdo rje nyi ma gzi brjid dang //
NK020(wa)001:8001: bzhed cing dam du mdzad pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:8002: dga' mgu rangs pa rnams su gyur //
NK020(wa)001:8003: pad+ma bzhad pas chos kun gyi //
NK020(wa)001:8004: rtogs mdzad sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK020(wa)001:8005: byang chub sems 'di brnyes gyur nas //
NK020(wa)001:8006: skad cig gcig la rtogs gyur te //
NK020(wa)001:8007: snying po byang chub nyid du 'gyur //
NK020(wa)001:8008: rdo rje gdan la yang sangs rgyas //
NK020(wa)001:8009: sku med chos kyi sku yis stong gsum zil gyis gnon //
NK020(wa)001:8010: gsung med rig pa'i gsung gis bstan pa rgyas par sgrog /
NK020(wa)001:8011: rtog med ye shes thugs kyis cir yang sa le mkhyen //
NK020(wa)001:8012: ston pa kun tu bzang la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK020(wa)001:8013: de nas dam can la bcol bskul gtor ma bsngo ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8014: 'khor gsum mi dmigs pas bya rtsol dang bral ba'i ngang nas /
NK020(wa)001:8015: chos kyi dbyings ni nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK020(wa)001:8016: byang chub rnyed dka' rang la yod bzhin du //
NK020(wa)001:8017: gsang ba'i snying po gang la gnas pa na //
NK020(wa)001:8018: dam can rgya mtsho rnams kyang de na gnas //
NK020(wa)001:8019: thugs rje rgya mtsho yon tan kun la khyab //
NK020(wa)001:8020: lha dang klu yang bden pa'i bka' nyan te //
NK020(wa)001:8021: tshogs kyi rgyan rnams bkram pa yang //
NK020(wa)001:8022: mnyam pas rim pa'i bkod pa med //
NK020(wa)001:8023: gcig pas phyogs su bsngo dang bral //
NK020(wa)001:8024: de nas tshogs rdzas bkram zhing brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:8025: chos thams cad gtsang dme gnyis med blang dor dang
NK020(wa)001:8026: bral ba ye nas dag pa'i bdud rtsi yin pas
NK020(wa)001:8027: rdzas bsag cing bskyar brlab mi dgos pa'i don la
NK020(wa)001:8029: tshogs kyi rgyan rnams bkram pa yang //
NK020(wa)001:8030: rang bzhin gnas pas dbri ba med //
NK020(wa)001:8031: yid kyis bshams pa'i yon bdag ste //
NK020(wa)001:8032: bltas pas stobs ni bkram pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:8033: de nas mchod bshags stob pa bya ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8034: mchod bya mchod byed mchod rdzas kun gnyis med kyi ngang du ro gcig par bltas la /
NK020(wa)001:8036: rnam par rtog med dus gsum rgyal ba'i thugs //
NK020(wa)001:8037: nyon mongs zhen pa'i dbang gis rang 'thas kyang /
NK020(wa)001:8038: don rtogs gsal ba'i skyes bu gnyis su med //
NK020(wa)001:8039: chos nyid lham me lhang nges gsal ba'o //
NK020(wa)001:8040: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du thams cad gcig /
NK020(wa)001:8041: bde chen rgyal po lhun grub la /
NK020(wa)001:8042: lhun grub mthar phyin mchod pa bzhes /
NK020(wa)001:8044: de nas bar 'dir dbang chog bzhin don dam byang sems kyi dbang sems la bskur bar bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:8045: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyang rang
NK020(wa)001:8046: gi sems nyid las gzhan du ma gyur par thag
NK020(wa)001:8047: bcad nas ye shes la ye shes rol pa'i tshul
NK020(wa)001:8048: gyis tshogs rdzas rnams la longs spyod la /
NK020(wa)001:8049: lhag ma btang zhing bka' bsgyur bya ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8050: zag med kyi bdud rtsir ye nas dag pa 'khor
NK020(wa)001:8051: gsum mi dmigs pa'i ngang nas bsngo bsgyur bya ba
NK020(wa)001:8052: ste / lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK020(wa)001:8053: 'gyur ba ma yin drang por gnas //
NK020(wa)001:8054: de nas rjes chog dkyil 'khor bsdu pa ni //
NK020(wa)001:8055: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo yang rang byung ye shes
NK020(wa)001:8056: kyi rtsal snang tsam las bskyed pa'i bya byed la
NK020(wa)001:8057: ltos pa med pa'i phyir bsdu ba'ang ma grub pas
NK020(wa)001:8058: / skye 'gag med pa'i chos nyid dbyings ye gnyis
NK020(wa)001:8059: med byang chub sems kyi ngang la bsal bzhag med
NK020(wa)001:8060: / par bzhag nas / nam mkha' bzhin du mtha' mnyam zhing //
NK020(wa)001:8061: gzhan la ltos 'gyur chos ma yin //
NK020(wa)001:8062: de las langs te rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni //
NK020(wa)001:8063: spyod lam thams cad du zhen 'dzin dang bral ba
NK020(wa)001:8064: sgyu ma lta bu'i ngang nas dge ba'i las rnams
NK020(wa)001:8065: la brtson pas chad mthar bsal te /
NK020(wa)001:8066: bla ma mchod dang bstod pa dang //
NK020(wa)001:8067: de bzhin bsod nams thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:8068: ma chags mi g.yo'i stobs med par //
NK020(wa)001:8071: de nas smon lam shis brjod ni /
NK020(wa)001:8072: thig le chen por sku dang zhing khams rdzogs //
NK020(wa)001:8073: dam tshig chen por spang blang mtshan ma dag /
NK020(wa)001:8074: khyab brdal chen por re dogs mdud pa grol //
NK020(wa)001:8075: rdzogs pa chen por chos sku mngon gyur shog /
NK020(wa)001:8076: rtsa brgyud bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:8077: rang rig byang chub sems kyi rang rtsal nyid //
NK020(wa)001:8078: chos dbyings kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong du //
NK020(wa)001:8079: ye shes rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8080: ces brjod cing me tog 'thor ba dang rol mo'i sgra bya'o //
NK020(wa)001:8081: man ngag gnad kyis ye shes zhal //
NK020(wa)001:8082: rang ngo sprod thabs rtsal dbang gi /
NK020(wa)001:8083: chos gzhung chos nyid rjes 'gro'i dpal /
NK020(wa)001:8084: bya rtsol med pa'i 'phrin las so //
NK020(wa)001:8085: don dam byang sems kyi dbang sems la bskur pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi le tshan no //
NK020(wa)001:8086: 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo las /
NK020(wa)001:8087: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo'i dkyil 'khor gnyis bshad pa'i skabs te bzhi pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:8091: 'gag med sprul pa'i zlos gar gyis //
NK020(wa)001:8092: don mdzad rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK020(wa)001:8093: btud nas 'chi med sgrub thabs bri //
NK020(wa)001:8094: 'dir mtha' brten tshe dbang gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)001:8095: dri dang ba byung dang bdud rtsis chag chag btab pa'i gzhi la /
NK020(wa)001:8096: byin gyis brlabs pa'i thig tshon gyis dkyil 'khor khyams
NK020(wa)001:8097: spangs pa'i gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs brgyad ma'i
NK020(wa)001:8098: nang du / rtsa thig la thug pa'i rdo rje
NK020(wa)001:8099: ra ba zlum bskor gyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab ma
NK020(wa)001:8100: brgyad pa'i lte bar zla gam dmar po la logs
NK020(wa)001:8101: nang du / mdun bstan / tshon shar dkar /
NK020(wa)001:8105: rtsig pa 'ang nang nas dmar dkar ser sngo ljang ba /
NK020(wa)001:8106: phyi'i khor yug pad rdor 'od phreng rnams spyi dang 'dra bar bri zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8107: lha gnas rnams su so so'i mtshan ma ji ltar rigs pa 'god /
NK020(wa)001:8108: dbus su many+dzi'i khar rin po che'i bum chas ldan /
NK020(wa)001:8113: bdud rtsi ste lnga tshan lnga dang /
NK020(wa)001:8114: tshe rten du 'os pa'i rdzas sa'i snying po gser /
NK020(wa)001:8118: rtsi'i mar te snying po lnga'i bcud kyi gang bar bya te /
NK020(wa)001:8119: b+hany+dza mtshan ldan lcang lo can gyis kha bcad la rdo rje'i gzungs thag gis btags pa bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:8120: rgyas par na de'i phyi rol du gsang yum bzhi'i rin po che'i bum pa dang /
NK020(wa)001:8121: grwa bzhir lha spyi la ya mtshan 'byung ba'i bum
NK020(wa)001:8122: pa zhes pa thod pa mtshan ldan nam kham sa'i
NK020(wa)001:8123: bum pa bzhi 'jog par gsung na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:8124: ma 'byor na dbus kyi bum pa gcig pu la bsdus kyang mi 'gal /
NK020(wa)001:8125: tshe 'brang ni gsang yum gyi bum pa bkod yod
NK020(wa)001:8126: na bzhi byas la so so'i khar 'jog par bshad
NK020(wa)001:8127: kyang 'dir bum pa gcig du bsdus pa'i tshe dkyil
NK020(wa)001:8129: tshe ril dang tshe chang gnyis tshe 'brang dang bum
NK020(wa)001:8130: bcud la tshang na'ang phyag len ltar logs su bkod
NK020(wa)001:8131: pa rnams pa gsal bas g.yas su tshe ril /
NK020(wa)001:8134: mtha' bskor du zhabs bsil dang bzhi bsnol /
NK020(wa)001:8136: rang gi mdun du rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi las bum dang /
NK020(wa)001:8139: mda' rgod sgro mar dar le brgan dang gser g.yu
NK020(wa)001:8140: me long rnams btags pa sogs yo byad thams cad
NK020(wa)001:8142: khrus dang tsan+dana gyi dril bgos nas stan la 'dug ste /
NK020(wa)001:8144: tshogs zhing rnams mkha' khyab tu gsal btab la /
NK020(wa)001:8145: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal /
NK020(wa)001:8146: zhes sogs rgyun bshags kyis rgyud sbyangs nas /
NK020(wa)001:8147: rang nyid pad+ma he ru ka yab yum du gsal
NK020(wa)001:8148: ba'i shangs kyi h+aum ring dang sems sprin khro mtshon
NK020(wa)001:8149: 'bar ba'i rnam par spros pas bgegs thams cad tshar
NK020(wa)001:8150: bcad / tshur 'dus pa bsrung ba 'i gur du 'khrigs par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:8151: phata phata badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la /
NK020(wa)001:8156: stong pa'i ngang las mchod snod dbyings kyi zhing khams
NK020(wa)001:8157: bsam gyis mi khyab par mchod rdzas ye shes lnga'i
NK020(wa)001:8158: rnam rol nam mkha' gang bar bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:8159: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:8160: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK020(wa)001:8164: stong pa'i ngang las snod b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i dbyings su
NK020(wa)001:8165: bcud sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo
NK020(wa)001:8166: bor gnas pa la 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams
NK020(wa)001:8167: cad bsdus nas zhu zhing 'dres pas ye shes kyi
NK020(wa)001:8168: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'gyur par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8171: de nas dngos gzhi la gsum las /
NK020(wa)001:8172: dang po ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed cing bskur brlab bya ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8173: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad skye ba med pa'i dbyings ye ji bzhin pa'i ngang las /
NK020(wa)001:8174: de ltar ma rtogs pa la 'gag med snying rje
NK020(wa)001:8175: rig pa'i rtsal snang ye shes kyi rol par shar
NK020(wa)001:8176: ba las / dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med
NK020(wa)001:8177: pa bde ba chen po byang chub kyi sems a
NK020(wa)001:8179: de las e yam wam lam sum ram /
NK020(wa)001:8181: zhes cho 'phrul gyi rang sgrar grags pa las yum
NK020(wa)001:8182: lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa 'byung bzhi ri
NK020(wa)001:8183: rab me'i 'khor yug dang bcas pa'i dbus su ye
NK020(wa)001:8184: shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK020(wa)001:8185: gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa rta babs brgyad dang ldan
NK020(wa)001:8186: pa'i dbus su rdo rje ra bas zlum por bskor
NK020(wa)001:8187: ba'i nang pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa /
NK020(wa)001:8188: lte bar zla gam dmar pos mtshan pa /
NK020(wa)001:8189: tshad dang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa
NK020(wa)001:8190: bde ba can gyi zhing khams lta bur gyur pa'i
NK020(wa)001:8191: lte ba dang / phyogs kyi 'dab ma bzhir /
NK020(wa)001:8196: shang shang rnams kyis btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri pad nyid zla ba ste lnga brtsegs /
NK020(wa)001:8197: mtshams kyi pad 'dab bzhi dang grwa bzhir pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK020(wa)001:8198: gtso bo'i mdun rgyab g.yas g.yon dang sgo bzhir pad nyi'i gdan re re /
NK020(wa)001:8199: sems nyid a yig dkar po dbus kyi gdan steng babs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:8202: zhes brjod pas bcom ldan 'das snang mtha' tshe dang
NK020(wa)001:8203: ye shes dpag tu med pa dang yum gos dkar
NK020(wa)001:8204: mo gnyis ka phyag g.yas pas pad+ma dmar po 'dzin
NK020(wa)001:8205: pa / phyogs kyi 'dab ma bzhis l+aam zhes pas rnam snang dang spyan ma 'khor lo /
NK020(wa)001:8207: rin 'byung dang m+aa ma k+ai rin po che /
NK020(wa)001:8209: mi bskyod pa dang dbyings phyug ma rdo rje /
NK020(wa)001:8211: don grub dang sgrol ma ral gri /
NK020(wa)001:8212: yab yum thams cad phyag g.yon 'chi med bdud rtsis gang ba'i bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)001:8213: yab rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil krung la yum rnams pad+ma'i skyil krung gis 'khril ba /
NK020(wa)001:8214: gtso bo'i phyogs bzhi'i gdan la mdun nas g.yas bskor du /
NK020(wa)001:8216: rgyal mtshan mchog ldan ma rin po che'i rgyal mtshan dang lcags kyu /
NK020(wa)001:8218: rin chen gter 'dzin ma gter gyi bum pa dang zhags pa /
NK020(wa)001:8220: dbang bskur ldan ma dbang bskur ba'i bum pa dang lcags sgrog /
NK020(wa)001:8222: dpal ldan mdzod ldan ma rin po che'i za ma tog dang dril bu /
NK020(wa)001:8226: dz+r+aim am zhes pas mtshams kyi 'dab ma bzhir sa snying sogs thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:8227: yul gyi sems ma bzhi dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:8230: m+aum hoh zhes pas grwa bzhir byams pa sogs dbang po'i sems dpa' bzhi /
NK020(wa)001:8231: dus bzhi'i sems ma dang bcas pa /
NK020(wa)001:8232: sems dpa' yab yum thams cad kyang g.yas rang rang
NK020(wa)001:8233: gi phyag mtshan dang g.yon tshe'i bum pa 'dzin pa
NK020(wa)001:8234: / yab rnams g.yas brkyang ba'i phyed skyil la g.yon nas so so'i yum gyis 'khyud pa /
NK020(wa)001:8235: dzahhum bam hoh zhes pas sgo bzhir lcags kyu ma sogs g.yas rang rtags dang g.yon tshe bum /
NK020(wa)001:8236: lha mo brgyad po g.yon brkyang ba'i phyed skyil gyis bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:8237: gtso 'khor thams cad kyang sku mdog dkar po gsal 'tsher 'bar ba /
NK020(wa)001:8238: zhi ba'i nyams dgus rgyas shing /
NK020(wa)001:8239: dar gyi chas gos lnga dang rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis mdzes par spras pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:8240: mgo bo'i gnas lngar rigs lnga'i dbang rgya 'ching bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:8241: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha n+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko & ham /
NK020(wa)001:8247: zhes spyi bo'i gnas lngar de bzhin gshegs pa lnga
NK020(wa)001:8248: rjes chags kyis zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun
NK020(wa)001:8251: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas bsgyur /
NK020(wa)001:8252: chu lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa yongs su gyur
NK020(wa)001:8253: pa las de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngas dbu brgyan
NK020(wa)001:8254: par gyur / spyi mgrin snying gar zla ba pad+ma nyi ma la gnas pa'i +aahh+aum /
NK020(wa)001:8255: 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang /
NK020(wa)001:8257: mi bskyod pa rnams kyis rgyas btab par bsam la /
NK020(wa)001:8258: rdo rje'i phyag rgya gnas gsum du gtug cing /
NK020(wa)001:8259: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma kho & ham /
NK020(wa)001:8262: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gnyis su
NK020(wa)001:8263: med par byas pa la mchod cing bstod pa ni
NK020(wa)001:8264: / ga go na'i phyag rgya bcings la /
NK020(wa)001:8265: rang gi snying ga'i 'od zer gyis bskul bas de
NK020(wa)001:8266: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bde ba chen po'i ngang
NK020(wa)001:8267: las chos 'phrul gyi rol pa ye shes kyi 'khor
NK020(wa)001:8268: lo'i rnam par badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK020(wa)001:8269: dzahh+aum bam hohs dgug gzhug bcings mnyes kyis dbyer med gyur pa la /
NK020(wa)001:8270: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas rang nyid gtso bo gnyis
NK020(wa)001:8271: pas rnam pas thon nas dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgo'i
NK020(wa)001:8272: thad du gnas pas mchod cing bstod par bsam zhing
NK020(wa)001:8273: / na ma sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi
NK020(wa)001:8274: shwa mu she b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na
NK020(wa)001:8275: hi mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:8276: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra
NK020(wa)001:8277: p+au dzi te na mah sa man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga
NK020(wa)001:8278: ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)001:8279: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ng+h+au pe ng+h+au /
NK020(wa)001:8281: +aa lo ke h+r+aih gan+d+he ga na /
NK020(wa)001:8282: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)001:8283: i dam push+pe d+h+au pe ba lim pra t+ai ts+tsha hohkha ram kh+aa hi /
NK020(wa)001:8284: zhes kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol sman gtor rnams kyis mchod nas /
NK020(wa)001:8286: h+r+aih bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med /
NK020(wa)001:8287: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel //
NK020(wa)001:8288: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK020(wa)001:8289: rdo rje'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:8290: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i gsung //
NK020(wa)001:8291: gsung rab dam pa yi ge med //
NK020(wa)001:8292: brjod du med cing spros bral ba //
NK020(wa)001:8293: rdo rje'i gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:8294: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i thugs //
NK020(wa)001:8295: chags med ye shes gnyis mkhyen pa //
NK020(wa)001:8296: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi //
NK020(wa)001:8297: rdo rje'i thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)001:8300: hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK020(wa)001:8301: cad kyi bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal snang ba
NK020(wa)001:8302: mtha' yas la sogs pa rigs lnga'i tshe dang ye
NK020(wa)001:8303: shes dpag tu med pa 'khor dang bcas pa thams
NK020(wa)001:8304: cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK020(wa)001:8305: khyed rnams la phrin las su gsol ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8306: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK020(wa)001:8307: kyi yon tan dang dngos grub kyi skal ba gang
NK020(wa)001:8309: khyad par du'ang 'gyur ba med pa'i tshe /
NK020(wa)001:8311: rgud pa med pa'i lang tsho sogs skye shi med
NK020(wa)001:8312: pa rdo rje'i tshe dang ye shes kyi dngos grub
NK020(wa)001:8313: gang lags pa thams cad sngon gyi thugs dam las
NK020(wa)001:8314: ma 'da' bar dus da lta nyid du stsal du
NK020(wa)001:8315: gsol / gsum pa tshe sgrub pa'i cho ga la bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)001:8319: ma grub na spogs pa'i cho ga'o //
NK020(wa)001:8321: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang gnyis su med par gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)001:8323: bum pa'i dkyil 'khor logs su phye nas mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)001:8324: bdag nyid pad+ma tshe dpag med du gsal ba'i thugs
NK020(wa)001:8325: kar nyi zla'i ga'u kha sbyor gyi gzhal yas khang
NK020(wa)001:8326: gi dbus su +aa yuh byang chub sems kyi rang
NK020(wa)001:8327: bzhin thig le dmar po'i rnam par 'khyil ba gsal
NK020(wa)001:8329: gnyis pa la gnyis kyi dang po tshe dgug pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:8330: rang gi thugs ka'i tshe rten las 'od zer gsang yum tshe 'dzin ma bzhi dang /
NK020(wa)001:8331: de las kyang dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad la
NK020(wa)001:8332: 'phros pas rim par bskul ba'i 'od zer phyir song
NK020(wa)001:8333: sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams cad la khyab pas phyogs
NK020(wa)001:8334: bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rje'i
NK020(wa)001:8335: nus mthu dang / khyad par nub phyogs pad+ma dbang
NK020(wa)001:8336: gi zhing khams na bcom ldan 'das tshe dang ye
NK020(wa)001:8337: shes dpag tu med pa 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs
NK020(wa)001:8338: kar phogs pas thugs dam bskul te /
NK020(wa)001:8339: dpal be'u nyi zla'i ga'u nas byang chub sems kyi
NK020(wa)001:8340: +aa yuhdakara dmar 'od kyi rnam par gsal zhing 'bar
NK020(wa)001:8341: ba'i rang bzhin can bsdus te bdag dang bum nang
NK020(wa)001:8343: yang 'od zer 'phros 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK020(wa)001:8344: la phog pas rdo khab len gyis lcags bsdu ba
NK020(wa)001:8345: ltar / phyi 'byung ba bzhi'i mdangs dang bcud /
NK020(wa)001:8346: nang 'gro drug sems can ma lus pa'i tshe dang
NK020(wa)001:8347: bsod nams gzi byin thams cad 'chi med kyi bdud
NK020(wa)001:8348: rtsi 'od zer dkar dmar gsal 'bar gyi rnam par
NK020(wa)001:8349: bsdus te / bum nang gi lha'i thugs ka dang /
NK020(wa)001:8350: bdag gi snying ga'i tshe rten la thim par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8353: b+h+r+aum badz+ra +aa yu she h+aum a /
NK020(wa)001:8355: skabs skabs su tshe'i pho nya bskul zhing btang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8356: bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od kyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK020(wa)001:8357: tshogs rnams bskul bas so so las rang 'dra ba'i
NK020(wa)001:8358: sprul pa grangs med pa spros te /
NK020(wa)001:8359: 'khor 'das sno bcud kyis mdangs dang tshe bcud bkrag
NK020(wa)001:8360: dang gzi byin bsod nams dang ye shes thams cad
NK020(wa)001:8361: bsdus nas bdag dang sgrub rdzas rnams la thim par
NK020(wa)001:8362: bsam nas / mda' dar g.yab cing spos rol dang bcas pas /
NK020(wa)001:8363: h+r+aih nub phyogs pad+ma dbang gi zhing khams nas //
NK020(wa)001:8364: bcom ldan rigs lnga yab yum tshe dpag med //
NK020(wa)001:8365: sems dpa' sems ma sgo mar bcas rnams kyis //
NK020(wa)001:8366: tshe dang ye shes dgug pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK020(wa)001:8367: n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aa yu she dzahdzahh+aum +aah 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK020(wa)001:8368: dkar mo mgyogs ma zhi byed 'od 'phro'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)001:8369: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK020(wa)001:8370: rdo rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK020(wa)001:8371: n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aa yu she 'gro ba yongs kyi
NK020(wa)001:8372: tshe sngon mo mgyogs ma rgyas mdzad 'od tshe dang
NK020(wa)001:8373: gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i rdo rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i
NK020(wa)001:8374: n+ri b+h+rum h+aum +aa yu she 'gro ba yongs kyi
NK020(wa)001:8375: tshe la dmar mo mgyogs ma dbang byed //
NK020(wa)001:8376: tshe dang gzi brjid rdo rje tshe mchog n+ri b+h+r+aum
NK020(wa)001:8377: h+aum +aa 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la ljang mdog
NK020(wa)001:8378: mgyogs ma drag byed tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs rdo
NK020(wa)001:8379: rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK020(wa)001:8380: n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aa yu she dzahdzahh+aum +aah gnyis pa tshe bstim pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:8381: tshe dpag med kyi thugs dpal gyi be'u nyi zla'i
NK020(wa)001:8382: ga'u nas 'chi ba med pa'i bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma
NK020(wa)001:8383: dmar gsal 'bar ba'i rnam par byung ba bdag gi
NK020(wa)001:8384: snying ga'i tshe rten la sib kyis thim pas bkrag
NK020(wa)001:8385: mdangs gzi byin 'bar ba'i 'od kyis lus nang thams
NK020(wa)001:8386: cad mer khrig gis gang bas tshe'i 'gal rkyen thams
NK020(wa)001:8387: cad bsal nas 'chi ba med pa rdo rje tshe'i
NK020(wa)001:8388: dngos grub thob par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8389: h+r+aih nub phyogs tshe yi dbyings mchog gi /
NK020(wa)001:8390: pad+ma dbang gi zhing khams su //
NK020(wa)001:8391: byams ldan ye shes tshe dpag med //
NK020(wa)001:8392: thugs kyi dpal be'u rin po che //
NK020(wa)001:8395: dmar gsal 'bar ba'i tshe mchog de /
NK020(wa)001:8397: spros pas dgu lung dam pa yis //
NK020(wa)001:8398: tsit+ta'i sbubs la bkrag tu bslan //
NK020(wa)001:8400: spyi bo'i gnas lngar bum chu gtig cing /
NK020(wa)001:8401: rigs lnga so so'i dbang rgya 'ching bzhin du /
NK020(wa)001:8402: +aam a ro lika p+aam r+aa ga ra ti badz+ra +aa yu she a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:8403: dzi na dzika l+aam dwe sha ra ti badz+ra +aa
NK020(wa)001:8404: yu s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika m+aam mo ha ra ti badz+ra
NK020(wa)001:8405: +aa yu h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika m+aum d+h+aa t+we shwa r+ai
NK020(wa)001:8406: badz+ra +aa yu h+aam pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika t+aam badz+ra ra
NK020(wa)001:8407: ti badz+ra +aa yu she a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:8408: gsum pa la gnyis kyi dang po tshe sba ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8409: de ltar byang chub sems kyi tshe bstim pas /
NK020(wa)001:8411: bstim bya tshe dang bsod nams ye shes kyi rgyud gsum ste /
NK020(wa)001:8412: de thams cad byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin gdod nas ma skyes pa'i chos nyid yin pas /
NK020(wa)001:8413: de nyid la sangs rgyas kyis kyang rku zhing 'phrog pa'i gnas med de /
NK020(wa)001:8414: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i byang chub
NK020(wa)001:8415: kyi sems spros bral 'chi med gnyug ma'i rang bzhin
NK020(wa)001:8417: h+r+aih tshe yi ngo bo rgyud gsum po //
NK020(wa)001:8418: srog gi ngo bor gzhal yas khang //
NK020(wa)001:8421: 'chi ba med pa'i srog btsugs te //
NK020(wa)001:8422: 'gyur ba med pa'i g.yung drung yin //
NK020(wa)001:8423: chos nyid dbyings su tshe sbas pas //
NK020(wa)001:8424: dus gsum rgyal ba dgrar langs kyang //
NK020(wa)001:8425: de la bzung zhing brtag tu med //
NK020(wa)001:8426: gnyis pa rgyas gdab pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:8427: 'chi med gnyug ma'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag pa'i ngang las /
NK020(wa)001:8428: de'i phyag rgyar gsal ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8429: rang gi snying gar zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor /
NK020(wa)001:8430: de'i sgor rta mgrin yab yum rgya gram dang bum pa 'dzin pas bsrung ba'i las mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)001:8431: zla gam gyi nang na rin po che dpal be'u zur brgyad pa 'bar ba /
NK020(wa)001:8432: de'i steng du nyi zla'i ga'u kha sbyor /
NK020(wa)001:8433: yas mas nas rdo rje rgya gram gnyis kyis gtams
NK020(wa)001:8434: pa'i steng 'og gi rwa rtse 'od zer gyi thag
NK020(wa)001:8435: pas bcings pa / nyi zla'i nang du gu h+ya gser gyi rdo rje mtshon gang ba /
NK020(wa)001:8436: de'i lte bar +aahh+aum dmar po 'od 'bar ba rnams kyis rgyas btab par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8438: skye med dbyings su sbas nas kyang /
NK020(wa)001:8439: tha mar phyag rgya bdun gyis gdab /
NK020(wa)001:8440: dang po sku gsung thugs kyi rgya //
NK020(wa)001:8441: gnyis pa gnon pa'i rgya gram rgya //
NK020(wa)001:8442: gsum pa rta mchog dpal gyi rgya //
NK020(wa)001:8443: bzhi pa rin chen dpal be'u ste //
NK020(wa)001:8444: lnga pa gser gyi gu h+ya'o //
NK020(wa)001:8445: drug pa zla gam dmar po la //
NK020(wa)001:8447: rgya bdun rim pas btab pa las //
NK020(wa)001:8448: sus kyang 'da' bar mi nus so //
NK020(wa)001:8450: bzhi pa ma grub na spogs pa'i cho ga ni /
NK020(wa)001:8451: yun ring bsgrubs nas ma 'grub na slar khro dkyil du bri sgom zhal bsgyur ba yin pas /
NK020(wa)001:8452: shar chog tsam la ma sgoms kyang chog mod /
NK020(wa)001:8453: de ltar na'ang lag len gyi rnam bzhag mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK020(wa)001:8454: bri ba ma grub kyang ting nge 'dzin gyis zhal bsgyur tsam byed par spro na /
NK020(wa)001:8456: zhes pas zhi ba'i lha tshogs rnams skad cig gis khro bo'i skur gyur pa ni /
NK020(wa)001:8461: byang du karma he ru ka yab yum thams cad g.yas rigs lnga'i rang rtags dang g.yon tshe bum /
NK020(wa)001:8462: sems dpa' brgyad gnas mar gyur nas pad 'dab dang grwa'i g.yas phyogs dang /
NK020(wa)001:8463: sems ma rnams yul ma brgyad du gyur nas gnas ma re re'i g.yon du bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)001:8464: sgo bzhir rta gdong ma sogs dang /
NK020(wa)001:8465: gtso bo'i phyogs bzhir gsang yum khro mo bzhi rnams g.yas so so'i phyag mtshan dang /
NK020(wa)001:8467: gtso 'khor thams cad kyang sku mdog dmar po me'i
NK020(wa)001:8468: phung po lta bu khro gtum bzod par dka' ba'i
NK020(wa)001:8469: gzi byin 'bar bar gyur pa las /
NK020(wa)001:8470: phata dzahs bum pa'i dkyil 'khor kyang mdun du phye nas /
NK020(wa)001:8471: bdag nyid pad+ma he ru ka'i thugs kar tshe rten gsal ba las /
NK020(wa)001:8472: 'od zer nyi ma'i gdung byed lta bu tsha zhing
NK020(wa)001:8473: rtsub pa'i rtse las dbang gi lha mo tsan+da l+ai
NK020(wa)001:8474: dmar mo g.yas lcags kyu dmar po 'bar ba dang
NK020(wa)001:8475: / g.yon tshe'i snod rin po che'i za ma tog dkar po thogs pa dpag tu med pa spros /
NK020(wa)001:8476: nam mkha'i khams thams cad khengs pas /
NK020(wa)001:8480: snod bcud kyi tshe dang gzi byin thams cad dang /
NK020(wa)001:8481: khyad par 'chi bdag gshin rje la sogs pa'i gdon
NK020(wa)001:8482: bgegs thams cad kyi lag nas tshe bcud dang gzi
NK020(wa)001:8483: byin 'od dmar gsal gyi rnam par 'phrogs pa g.yon
NK020(wa)001:8484: pa'i za ma tog tu bsdus te /
NK020(wa)001:8485: rang dang bum pa tshe'i gzhal yas khang la thim par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8489: tshe'i pho nya btang ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8490: h+r+aih 'jigs byed 'das pa'i dus na mngon byung ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:8491: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba //
NK020(wa)001:8492: dpal chen khrag 'thung rigs lnga 'khor bcas kyis //
NK020(wa)001:8493: tshe dang ye shes 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK020(wa)001:8494: n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aa yu she dzahdzahh+aum a /
NK020(wa)001:8495: ye shes khro bo 'bar ba yi //
NK020(wa)001:8496: thugs kyi dpal be'u'i 'od zer las /
NK020(wa)001:8497: dbang gi lha mo mang po spros //
NK020(wa)001:8498: za ma tog dang bcas pa yi //
NK020(wa)001:8499: lcags kyu dkar dmar lag na thogs //
NK020(wa)001:8500: khyod kyis 'gro drug thams cad kyi //
NK020(wa)001:8501: tshe dang gzi byin thams cad 'phrogs //
NK020(wa)001:8502: za ma tog tu bsdus nas kyang //
NK020(wa)001:8503: sgrub mchog bdag la bstim par mdzod //
NK020(wa)001:8504: mi 'gyur tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)001:8505: badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha mo n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aa yu she dzahdzahh+aum a /
NK020(wa)001:8506: zhes bkug nas tshe bstim pa man chad sngar bzhin bya ba yin no //
NK020(wa)001:8507: de ltar khro bor bsgyur mi bsgyur gang ltar yang sba zhing rgyas btab pa yan song ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:8508: bar 'dir 'das ma 'das kyi gtor ma btang zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8509: de nas dbang chog ltar tshe'i dbang bskur ro //
NK020(wa)001:8511: mchod pa kha gsos te byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK020(wa)001:8515: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK020(wa)001:8518: ma rnyed yongs su sogs kyis bzod par gsol /
NK020(wa)001:8520: 'dir ni gzugs dang sogs kyis brtan bzhugs bya /
NK020(wa)001:8522: khyed kyis sems can sogs kyis ye shes pa gshegs /
NK020(wa)001:8523: dam tshig pa rang gi thugs ka'i 'od kyis snod
NK020(wa)001:8524: bcud thams cad sbyangs nas gzhal yas khang la thim
NK020(wa)001:8526: 'khor rnams gtso bo yab yum la /
NK020(wa)001:8528: de thugs ka'i thig le la /
NK020(wa)001:8529: de yang mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su thim par bsam nas /
NK020(wa)001:8530: sngar khro bor ma bsgyur nam /
NK020(wa)001:8534: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK020(wa)001:8535: zhes pas thun mtshams kyi lhar langs te /
NK020(wa)001:8539: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha ham /
NK020(wa)001:8541: lus rdo rje'i go chas bzhu lugs su g.yogs pas
NK020(wa)001:8542: sgo gsum rdo rje gsum dang dbyer med du bcings
NK020(wa)001:8543: par bsam mo // de nas bsngo ba ni /
NK020(wa)001:8544: 'dis mtshon dus gsum dge ba'i mthus //
NK020(wa)001:8546: bcom ldan tshe dpag med mgon gyi //
NK020(wa)001:8547: go 'phang myur du thob par shog /
NK020(wa)001:8549: byin rlabs bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:8550: rtsa brgyud bla ma'i bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8551: tshe dang ye shes dpag med gter //
NK020(wa)001:8552: snang ba mtha' yas bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8553: ye shes bzhi yi rang bzhin can //
NK020(wa)001:8554: rigs bzhi yab yum bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8555: skye mched rnam dag rgyal ba'i sras //
NK020(wa)001:8556: sems dpa' sems ma'i bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8557: gsang ba'i bu mo tshe gter 'dzin //
NK020(wa)001:8558: mgyogs ma bzhi yi bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8559: tshad med bzhi ldan phyag rgya bzhis //
NK020(wa)001:8560: sgo skyong srung ma'i bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8561: gang la bsam pa'i don 'grub pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:8562: don grub mchog gi bkra shis shog /
NK020(wa)001:8563: ces rol mo'i sgra 'khrol zhing me tog gi sil
NK020(wa)001:8564: ma phyogs thams cad du 'thor bas dge legs su
NK020(wa)001:8565: bya'o // 'dir mdo dbang gi tshe chog snga ma
NK020(wa)001:8566: rnams su dkyil 'khor lte ba 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK020(wa)001:8567: pa sogs sgyu 'phrul gyis khog phub nas mdzad pa
NK020(wa)001:8568: bya'o // shas che na'ang / 'dir ni mdo rang rkang tshugs pa'i dbang du byas nas /
NK020(wa)001:8569: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu gsum pa rdo rje tshe sgrub pa las gsungs pa ltar bris pa ste /
NK020(wa)001:8570: de'ang rgya mdud 'grel du lte ba ling tshe dgu'i dbus su pad 'dab brgyad /
NK020(wa)001:8571: ling tshe rnams dang sgo khyud bzhir zla gam /
NK020(wa)001:8574: phyogs phyogs gnas su tshom bur bri //
NK020(wa)001:8575: zhes pa'i tshom bu zhes pa la snyegs pa yin nam snyam ste /
NK020(wa)001:8576: rigs bzhi'i 'khor du rang rigs kyi sems dpa' yab
NK020(wa)001:8577: yum bzhi bzhis bskor bas spyir lha nga brgyad tsam
NK020(wa)001:8578: gsungs pa dang / tshe rten bskyed pa'ang rgya bdun
NK020(wa)001:8579: gyis rgyas 'debs pa'i skabs su 'grel pa 'dir lugs
NK020(wa)001:8580: gnyis gsungs pa'i snga mar yum gyi mkha' dang yab
NK020(wa)001:8581: kyi thugs kar bskyed pa gnyis 'dam ka dang /
NK020(wa)001:8582: rgya bdun gyi 'dren tshul kyang snga ma 'dir bkod pa dang phal che ba 'dra zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8583: phyi ma tshigs bcad du mdzad pa 'grel chung rnal
NK020(wa)001:8584: 'byor sa'i sgron ma dang dgongs pa mthun pa sogs
NK020(wa)001:8585: rgya 'grel dang rgyud kyi mchan rnying rnams su 'grel
NK020(wa)001:8586: tshul tha dad pa mang na'ang /
NK020(wa)001:8587: 'dir rtsa rgyud kyi rgyud tshig dngos bstan ltar bkral
NK020(wa)001:8588: ba 'di nyid rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK020(wa)001:8589: ka bya sla bar ma zad /
NK020(wa)001:8590: rang blo'i go phyogs la gnad kyang 'dus par go nas /
NK020(wa)001:8591: rong zom chos kyi bzang pos mdzad pa'i mdo'i tshe sgrub kyi man ngag ltar bris pa yin no //
NK020(wa)001:8592: ci'i phyir 'di nyid gnad 'dus shing kun gyi dngos bstan du 'gyur zhe na /
NK020(wa)001:8596: dbus su zla gam dmar po dang phyi rol gru bzhi par sgo bzhir ldan //
NK020(wa)001:8597: tha ma 'dab brgyad kyi rdo rje ra bas bskor //
NK020(wa)001:8600: rigs bzhi sangs rgyas yab yum dang /
NK020(wa)001:8601: so so'i 'khor gyi sems dpa' rnams //
NK020(wa)001:8603: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi rnams bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:8605: gsang ba'i bu mo bzhi bkod bzhag /
NK020(wa)001:8607: 'dir tshom bur zhes pas kyang rigs chung bsta par ma nges te /
NK020(wa)001:8610: de bzhin tshom bu rim par brgyud //
NK020(wa)001:8611: ces sgo ma'i bar 'od zer rim par spro ba la tshom bu zhes gsungs pa ltar dang /
NK020(wa)001:8612: tshe rten yang rngam glog las /
NK020(wa)001:8613: tshe dpag med pa'i thugs ka nas /
NK020(wa)001:8615: nyi zla'i ga'ura gnas pa de /
NK020(wa)001:8617: zhes snying gar bskyed la gsal ba dang /
NK020(wa)001:8618: phyag rgya bdun yang lus kyi gnas gzhan la 'debs pa las /
NK020(wa)001:8619: snying ga'i tshe rten la 'debs pa 'di nyid 'brel chags par mngon pa'i phyir ro //
NK020(wa)001:8620: rgyud don man ngag ma nges pas /
NK020(wa)001:8621: mdo dbang tshe chog phal che bar /
NK020(wa)001:8622: rang gzhung sgos chos rgyang bsrings mod //
NK020(wa)001:8623: phyin chad legs bshad dpal 'di longs /
NK020(wa)001:8624: 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo las /
NK020(wa)001:8625: mtha' rten tshe'i sgrub thabs bshad pa'i skabs te lnga pa'o //
NK020(wa)001:8627: mi phyed rdo rje'i tshig gis dam bcings pa'i //
NK020(wa)001:8628: gzhung zab dgongs don 'byed nus blo dman yang //
NK020(wa)001:8629: bla ma'i drin gyis cha tsam rtogs pa gang //
NK020(wa)001:8630: rang blo goms dang gzhan la'ang phan phyir spel //
NK020(wa)001:8631: dag gsal ngag gi sbyor ba'i rta bdun gyis //
NK020(wa)001:8632: skal bzang dbang phyogs ri bo'i rtser drangs nas //
NK020(wa)001:8633: legs bshad chos kyi nyi ma 'od po ches //
NK020(wa)001:8634: dpal ldan bla ma'i bzhed dgongs gsal bar byas //
NK020(wa)001:8635: de phyir tshul 'dir nyes pa yod mi snyam //
NK020(wa)001:8636: rgya la rmongs dang rnam g.yeng le lo yis //
NK020(wa)001:8637: nongs par gyur rnams thog med gzigs mnga' ba'i //
NK020(wa)001:8638: spyan sngar 'gro kun sdig dang lhan cig bshags //
NK020(wa)001:8639: 'dir 'bad rnam dkar dge ba nyi zla'i 'gros //
NK020(wa)001:8640: mtha' dag 'gro sems mkha' la rtag 'char bas //
NK020(wa)001:8641: mchog bde'i dngos grub snang ba mi zad pa //
NK020(wa)001:8642: 'dod dgur 'jo bas phan bde'i dpal 'bar shog /
NK020(wa)001:8643: mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas pa'i yan lag
NK020(wa)001:8644: gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod
NK020(wa)001:8646: rje bla ma dam pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi sras
NK020(wa)001:8647: mchog dam pa sku na gzhon nur gyur kyang rig
NK020(wa)001:8648: pa'i gnas phal mo che thugs su chud pa'i pan+di
NK020(wa)001:8649: ta yang dag pa'i lam gyi sa mkhan chen po
NK020(wa)001:8650: rdo rje'i mtshan can gyi bkas bskul ba ltar rtsom
NK020(wa)001:8652: nye bar bstan 'gro'i dpal mgon pad gling lnga pa
NK020(wa)001:8653: gsung sprul ngag dbang kun bzang rdo rje'i zhal snga
NK020(wa)001:8654: nas bka' stsal nan can dang /
NK020(wa)001:8655: gzhan yang zangs la mkhar sprul sku rin po che dang /
NK020(wa)001:8656: thang 'brog sprul pa'i sku sogs sngon goms kyi yon
NK020(wa)001:8657: tan mnga' ba'i skyes chen dam pa 'gro don nus
NK020(wa)001:8658: pa du ma'i gsung gis bskul zhing /
NK020(wa)001:8659: khyad par dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi
NK020(wa)001:8660: gzugs rigs dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi khyab bdag mtshan
NK020(wa)001:8661: brjod par dka' ba rje btsun bla ma dam pa
NK020(wa)001:8662: gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i bka' lung gis dbugs
NK020(wa)001:8663: 'byin pa'i gnang ba legs par thob pa la brten
NK020(wa)001:8664: nas / gang gi zla med pa'i bka' drin kho
NK020(wa)001:8665: nas 'tsho ba'i skal ba can gnyos kyi dge slong
NK020(wa)001:8666: rmongs pa d+harma sh+r+ais rang lo lnga bcu pa'i steng
NK020(wa)001:8667: du son pa nyi ma zhes pa chu mo lug
NK020(wa)001:8668: gi lo nag pa zla ba'i yar ngo'i tshes bcu
NK020(wa)001:8669: bzhi'i nyin gangs ri'i khrod kyi pad+ma 'od o rgyan
NK020(wa)001:8670: smin grol gling gi chos grwar sug bris su sbyar
NK020(wa)001:8671: nas / ba'o // 'dis kyang bstan pa dang sems
NK020(wa)001:8672: can la phan pa rgya chen po 'byung ba'i rgyur
